NK075(bu)002:1: // u pa de sha tsi t+ta ti ka t+ai kakh+y+aa&a&a&at+aa
NK075(bu)002:2: r+k+k+aam ra smi n+aa ma bi ha ra ti sma
NK075(bu)002:5: / // man ngag thugs kyi thigs pa'i 'grel bshad nyi ma'i 'od zer zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK075(bu)002:8: kun khyab chos dbyings mtha' bral kun rig cing //
NK075(bu)002:9: kun lam theg mchog don ston kun bzang dang //
NK075(bu)002:10: rgyal tshab rgyal ba rig lnga gsang bdag sogs //
NK075(bu)002:11: dgongs pa dbyer med dgongs brgyud rnams la 'dud //
NK075(bu)002:12: theg mchog bla med theg don khong chud nas //
NK075(bu)002:13: rig pa rang grol rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i sras //
NK075(bu)002:14: mi la brgyud dang mi min gnyis la sogs //
NK075(bu)002:15: rig 'dzin rig par brgyud pa rnams la 'dud //
NK075(bu)002:16: gsang sngags bla med dgongs don ma lus kun //
NK075(bu)002:17: snyan nas rim par snyan du rab brgyud nas //
NK075(bu)002:18: don dam bcud kyi don rnams rtogs gyur pa'i //
NK075(bu)002:19: snyan brgyud gang zag rgyun mi chad la 'dud //
NK075(bu)002:20: sangs rgyas bstan pa gangs ri bsgribs pa'i rtser //
NK075(bu)002:21: gsang ba'i theg mchog nga ros theg dman gnon //
NK075(bu)002:22: dad ldan 'khor tshogs snying rjes rab bskyangs nas //
NK075(bu)002:23: smin grol lam la bkod mdzad de la 'dud //
NK075(bu)002:24: ye nas gnas lugs phyogs bral dkyil 'khor rgyas //
NK075(bu)002:25: shes bya kun gsal 'od dkar d+r+wa bas mdzes //
NK075(bu)002:26: rgyal ba'i dgongs don dbyer med bsil zer 'phro //
NK075(bu)002:27: mtshan can ri bong 'dzin la mi phyed 'dud //
NK075(bu)002:28: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho cher //
NK075(bu)002:29: don bcud yid bzhin rin chen 'di don rnams //
NK075(bu)002:30: ded dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas len //
NK075(bu)002:31: dad ldan rnams kyis rim par rgyal mtshan rtser //
NK075(bu)002:32: btags nas shes rab gsum gyis gsol btab nas //
NK075(bu)002:33: don bcud dgos 'dod rgyun mi chad pa 'di //
NK075(bu)002:34: bshes gnyen don la skam pa 'ga' zhig la //
NK075(bu)002:35: don bcud 'dod rgu 'byung snyam 'di bri bya //
NK075(bu)002:36: 'dir theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK075(bu)002:37: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK075(bu)002:38: lung thams cad kyi spyi rje /
NK075(bu)002:39: man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK075(bu)002:40: bka' gsang ba bas kyang ches gsang ba /
NK075(bu)002:41: yang gsang bla na med pa /
NK075(bu)002:42: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa /
NK075(bu)002:43: sems dang ye shes rang snang du ston pa'i rgyud /
NK075(bu)002:44: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i don gyi bcud phyung ba /
NK075(bu)002:45: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i sgyu 'phrul
NK075(bu)002:46: spyi gcod thugs kyi thigs pa 'di la spyi don
NK075(bu)002:47: gsum ste / 'chad nyan ci ltar bya ba'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:48: gang 'chad par byed pa dam chos kyi rnam bzhag /
NK075(bu)002:49: 'chad nyan mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum mo //
NK075(bu)002:51: 'chad pa po slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid /
NK075(bu)002:52: nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid /
NK075(bu)002:53: dang po slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK075(bu)002:54: mtshon bya don gyi rgyud rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)002:55: po sems kyi de kho na nyid ston pa'i mtshon
NK075(bu)002:56: byed tshig gi rgyud rtsa bshad man ngag dang bcas
NK075(bu)002:57: pa'i tshig don ston nus pa /
NK075(bu)002:58: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi don la mkhas pas gsang ba'i mdzod gsum dang ldan pa /
NK075(bu)002:59: phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang rdzogs par thob pa /
NK075(bu)002:60: gsang sngags bab chol du mi spyod pa'i gsang gnyer thub pa /
NK075(bu)002:61: rgyud don yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po bcu la ma rmongs pa /
NK075(bu)002:62: dkyil 'khor dang dbang gi las kyi rim pa /
NK075(bu)002:63: 'phrin las zhi drag la sogs pa las kyi tshogs bsgrub pa'i thabs la ma rmongs pa /
NK075(bu)002:64: nyams myong gi drod 'chang ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:66: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK075(bu)002:67: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK075(bu)002:69: rnal 'byor mtha' ldan shin tu bsten //
NK075(bu)002:71: de las bzlog pa ni ngan pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas spang bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:72: gzhan yang chos bshad tshul phan yon rnams ni logs su shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:73: gnyis pa nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK075(bu)002:74: snod kyi skyon bzhi dang bral dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:76: gzhi dad pa med pa kha sbub /
NK075(bu)002:77: dran 'dzin lan med pa zhabs rdol /
NK075(bu)002:78: grogs brtson 'grus med pa gzhog ral /
NK075(bu)002:79: brtse gdung dam tshig med pa dug can gyi skyon bzhi dang bral zhing /
NK075(bu)002:86: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK075(bu)002:87: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:89: gnyis pa gang 'chad nyan byed pa dam chos kyi rnam bzhag la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)002:90: gdams ngag 'jug ngor shes par bya ba'i phyir dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:91: don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:92: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs dang gsum du gnas pa las /
NK075(bu)002:93: dang po spyir chos ngos bzung ba la mang du bshad kyang /
NK075(bu)002:94: 'di rtogs chos dang lung chos gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:95: lung chos la sde snod dang rgyud sde gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:96: rgyud sde la phyi nang gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:97: nang pa la gsum yod pa las 'di ma h+aa yo ga /
NK075(bu)002:98: de la bde bar gshegs pa'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK075(bu)002:99: de la brten pa'i man ngag gnyis las 'di man ngag /
NK075(bu)002:100: de la rgyud kyi don ma nor bar rtogs pa'i man ngag dang /
NK075(bu)002:101: bslab cing nyams su blang ba'i man ngag gnyis las /
NK075(bu)002:102: 'di ni rgyud kyi don ma nor rtogs pa'i man ngag /
NK075(bu)002:107: sgyu 'phrul spyi'i khog dbub kyi man ngag yin no //
NK075(bu)002:108: gnyis pa don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa la /
NK075(bu)002:109: bka' thams cad phun sum tshogs pa lngas 'chad /
NK075(bu)002:110: bstan chos sam man ngag thams cad rtsis 'go lngas 'chad pa las /
NK075(bu)002:111: 'di ni man ngag yin pas rtsis 'go lngas 'chad par bya ste /
NK075(bu)002:113: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:114: man ngag spyi don rtsis 'go klad nas gzhom //
NK075(bu)002:116: khungs btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:117: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par
NK075(bu)002:118: bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gar
NK075(bu)002:119: gtogs pa dang / bstan pa la mtshan nges shing
NK075(bu)002:120: don gyi mdo tsam zhig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:121: mtshan ci la btags pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:122: brtsom pa la don yod par bya ba'i phyir dgos ched gang gi don mdzad pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:123: shes shing khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir dbu zhabs su don dus bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK075(bu)002:125: spyir bstan bcos brtsams pa'i tshad la /
NK075(bu)002:126: rab chos nyid bden pa'i don mthong ba /
NK075(bu)002:127: 'bring yi dam lha'i zhal mthong zhing lung bstan thob pa /
NK075(bu)002:128: tha ma bka'i dgongs don khrol zhing theg pa'i shan
NK075(bu)002:129: 'gyed cing la zlos pa tshig don la mkhas shing
NK075(bu)002:130: bye brag phyed pa zhig gis brtsams dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:132: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab //
NK075(bu)002:133: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yi //
NK075(bu)002:134: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK075(bu)002:135: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK075(bu)002:136: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK075(bu)002:138: gzhung 'di nyid kyi rtsom pa po slob dpon chen
NK075(bu)002:139: po sangs rgyas gsang ba ni brtsams tshad gsum dang
NK075(bu)002:141: sngon sbyangs pa yun ring la dar drags pa'i stobs kyis /
NK075(bu)002:142: chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs rtogs shing khong du chud pa /
NK075(bu)002:143: yi dam gyi lha rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK075(bu)002:144: gyi zhal mthong zhing snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i
NK075(bu)002:146: tshig dbang lha mo dbyangs can ma ljags la zhugs /
NK075(bu)002:148: spyan ras gzigs snying rje la zhugs /
NK075(bu)002:149: phyag na rdo rje mthu stobs la zhugs /
NK075(bu)002:150: khyad par du gzhung 'di'i rgyud kyi ston pa rdo
NK075(bu)002:151: rje sems pa'i zhal 'du 'bral med par gzigs pa
NK075(bu)002:152: / rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i brjod bya shan 'byed cing la zlos pa /
NK075(bu)002:153: tshig don la nor 'khrul dang lhag chad mi mnga'
NK075(bu)002:154: zhing bye brag phyed pa'i brtsams tshad rab 'bring gsum
NK075(bu)002:155: dang ldan pa'i slob dpon des mdzad /
NK075(bu)002:156: yang na tha ma rigs pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas pa zhig dgos zhes bya ba yang snang bas /
NK075(bu)002:157: slob dpon 'di nyid rgya gar chu bzhi'i pan+di ta
NK075(bu)002:158: rnams kyi bla phud du gyur cing 'khor lnga brgya
NK075(bu)002:159: dang bcas pa lus lhag med du gshegs shing /
NK075(bu)002:160: ri bo rtse lngar 'phags pa 'jam dbyangs dang lhan cig tu bzhugs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:161: gnyis pa bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung
NK075(bu)002:162: tshugs par bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus shing
NK075(bu)002:165: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems //
NK075(bu)002:166: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud dag las //
NK075(bu)002:168: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya ba'i nang nas btus shing /
NK075(bu)002:169: phyogs ma h+aa yo gar gtogs /
NK075(bu)002:170: gsum pa mtshan ci la btags pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:176: don la btags pa dang lnga las /
NK075(bu)002:178: don rang gi ngo bo la btags pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:179: mtshan don rgyas bshad ni 'og gzhung 'grel du shes so //
NK075(bu)002:180: bzhi pa dgos ched gang zag gang gi don du mdzad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:184: ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag chos kyi mig can /
NK075(bu)002:185: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i sgor 'jug nus pa'i
NK075(bu)002:186: las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams kyi don du
NK075(bu)002:187: mdzad pa'o // lnga pa dbu zhabs su don dus bstan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:188: klad don du gzhung don zhabs don gsum du shes par bya zhing /
NK075(bu)002:190: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba /
NK075(bu)002:193: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba dang le'u bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:195: spyir theg pa rnams gdul bya'i snang bas phye lugs /
NK075(bu)002:196: bye brag tu mchog ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa ngos bzung lugs /
NK075(bu)002:197: de la rab la mtshan bstan /
NK075(bu)002:201: dang po shes par bya ba'i yul la lnga /
NK075(bu)002:202: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi don nyams su blangs pa /
NK075(bu)002:203: tha ma drod tshad rtags dang ldan pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam la sbyor tshul lo //
NK075(bu)002:204: mchog gsang sngags kyi lam la'ang /
NK075(bu)002:208: lam gyi gtso bo dang cha rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:209: cha rkyen la lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang ngam /
NK075(bu)002:211: sngags dang phyag rgya mchod pa dang bcu'o //
NK075(bu)002:212: 'bras bu la gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:213: mthar thugs sangs rgyas thob lugs rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:214: des ni spyi don gyis khog dbub pa bsdus pa mdo tsam bkod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:215: rgyas pa ni logs su shes so //
NK075(bu)002:216: gzhung don gyi sa bcad pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:217: tshig don gyi 'bru gnyer ba gnyis ni 'og bshad
NK075(bu)002:218: bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs dang 'brel pa yin
NK075(bu)002:220: dngos kyi skabs la spyi don rnam pa gsum du bstan te /
NK075(bu)002:228: de la rgya gar la bshad pa mang du snang na yang /
NK075(bu)002:229: don du mi 'gro bar 'dug pas 'dir ma smos so //
NK075(bu)002:230: kho bo'i bla mas 'di ltar du 'dod de /
NK075(bu)002:231: rgya gar la 'bru gnyer med de 'dod rgyal gyi sgra'o //
NK075(bu)002:232: rdza ma dang pho ru la 'bru gnyer med pa dang 'dra gsung /
NK075(bu)002:233: 'o na thog mar smos pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)002:234: 'phags pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams
NK075(bu)002:235: kyang der byon nas bstan pa sde snod rgyud sde
NK075(bu)002:237: khungs btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK075(bu)002:238: lo pan rnams kyis phyi rab pa rnams la drin gzhag par bya ba'i phyir thog mar smos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:239: de la lo ts+aa pa la /
NK075(bu)002:241: mkhas pa ni zhu chen gyis lo ts+aa /
NK075(bu)002:242: sgra rkyang pa mkhas na sgra sgyur lo ts+aa /
NK075(bu)002:243: sgra kun bsgyur mi nus shing mchan tsam btab nas mchan bu lo ts+aa /
NK075(bu)002:244: rgya gar ma phyin nas bod du pan+di ta gdan
NK075(bu)002:245: drangs nas bsgyur ba ni go lo ts+aa dang bzhi
NK075(bu)002:246: yod pa la / gzhung 'di nyid kyi lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog ni /
NK075(bu)002:247: tshig don gnyis ka la mkhas pa zhus chen gyi lo ts+aa ba des bsgyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:248: rgya gar gyi bshad pa mkhas pa rnams kyis sgra la 'dod rgyal gyi sgra dang /
NK075(bu)002:249: sgra don gyi sgra gnyis las /
NK075(bu)002:250: rgya gara ni 'phags pa'i yul yin te 'dod rgyal gyi sgra'o //
NK075(bu)002:251: yul de pa rnams kyi skada du'am /
NK075(bu)002:252: yang na du la srog gcig pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:254: du la sogs pa la dang mthun /
NK075(bu)002:255: ces gsungs pas bstan bcos 'di la tsit+ta bin+d+hu u pa de sha na ma /
NK075(bu)002:257: bod la bod dang bod chen gnyis kyi bshad pa
NK075(bu)002:258: mang du snang yang don chung bas ma bris so
NK075(bu)002:263: thad logs su bsgyur ba gsum yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:265: gcus pa dang bsnor ba mi mnga' ba'i phyir thad logs su bsgyur ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:266: tsit+ta thugsa kyi thugs kyi bin+d+hu thigas pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:267: u pa de sha man ngag n+aa ma zhes bya ba zhes bsgyur la /
NK075(bu)002:268: de yang mtshan don de nyid la yang /
NK075(bu)002:270: brjod bya'i tshig gnyis dang sbyar nas bshad de /
NK075(bu)002:271: dang po ltar na thugs spros pa thams cad dang
NK075(bu)002:272: bral zhing sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de
NK075(bu)002:273: nyid 'khor 'das kun gyi dngos gzhir shar kyang zab
NK075(bu)002:275: de nyid sems nyid gcig pu las min pas nyung /
NK075(bu)002:276: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad de nyid las 'byung zhing ma g.yos pas 'dus /
NK075(bu)002:277: mtha' tha snyad ci ltar byung yang bsam brjod kyis
NK075(bu)002:278: yul dang bral bas ma 'phros pa dang gsum gyi
NK075(bu)002:279: nang nas thagas pa'i don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:280: de lta bu'i sems nyid gcig pu rtogs pas mchog pas ni dka' blas med pas tshegs chung la /
NK075(bu)002:281: de rtogs na gnas lugs rig pa'i phyir don che bas na man ngag ces bya ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:283: brjod bya'i don de nyid ston par byed pa'i rgyud thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i nang nas /
NK075(bu)002:284: thugs kyi thigs pa 'di nyid bsdus pa las /
NK075(bu)002:285: thigs pa'i mtshan la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)002:286: le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i nang nas /
NK075(bu)002:287: 'dir le'u bzhir byas pas nyung la /
NK075(bu)002:288: stong phrag brgya pa'i don yang snang ba bzhir bshad la /
NK075(bu)002:289: 'dir yang snang ba bzhir bshad pa'i don 'dir 'dus la /
NK075(bu)002:290: ldem dgongs la sogs pa yan lag rgyas par ma bshad pas na ma 'phros pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:291: de la rgyud sde le'u stong phrag brgya yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:292: 'dir snang ba bzhi'i le'u bzhi nyams su len pas chog pas ni tshegs chung ba yin la /
NK075(bu)002:293: snang ba bzhi'i don de rtogs na /
NK075(bu)002:294: stong phrag brgya pa'i don rnams khong du chud pas don che bas na man ngag ces bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:296: bcoma ldana dpal rdor sems dapa'a gtso //
NK075(bu)002:297: kun mkhyen rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK075(bu)002:298: 'khor lo snying po ston mdzad pa //
NK075(bu)002:299: gnyis med yid kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK075(bu)002:300: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa bshad pa'i gzhir drang /
NK075(bu)002:301: de'i khyad par gyi chos la lnga /
NK075(bu)002:302: gang gis na sdon byung dus su sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK075(bu)002:303: rjes 'jug tu 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis gang la na /
NK075(bu)002:306: chos 'chad pa'i gtso bo kun tu bzang po dang gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:307: de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:308: theg pa dgu la bcom lugs dgu bshad kyang /
NK075(bu)002:310: bcom zhes pa 'phrin las kyi mtshan to //
NK075(bu)002:311: nyon mongs pa lnga ma spangs ye shes su shar ba'i nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK075(bu)002:312: phung po lnga ma spangs rigs lngar shar ba ni phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK075(bu)002:313: rnam rtog gi dri ma ma spangs gnas su dag
NK075(bu)002:314: nas skye 'chi med pa'i don mngon du gyur pa
NK075(bu)002:316: 'bras bu sangs rgyas gzhan du mi tshol te phung
NK075(bu)002:317: khams skye mched thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK075(bu)002:318: shar / 'khor bar ltung mi dogs te nyon mongs
NK075(bu)002:319: pa sa bon dang bcas pa ma spangs gnas su
NK075(bu)002:320: dag pas re dogs gnyis dang bral ba lha'i bdud
NK075(bu)002:321: shar / bcom pa'o // ldana zhes pa yon tan gyi mtshan yin te /
NK075(bu)002:322: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i rgyan 'khor
NK075(bu)002:323: nyer lnga la sogs pa rnams thugs rang rig pa'i
NK075(bu)002:324: ye shes la rang bzhin gyis ldan no //
NK075(bu)002:325: lung gra chad la nyal ba zur la bslang ba 'chad pa po'i gnyer bya yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:326: 'adsa zhes pa mtshan nyid kyis mtshan te yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' las 'das pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:327: dapala zhes pa che ba'i mtshan te /
NK075(bu)002:329: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal ni gzhi
NK075(bu)002:330: mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi
NK075(bu)002:331: sku la bya'o // rig pa rang snang ba'i dpal ni /
NK075(bu)002:332: gzhi de nyid rtogs pa'i lam mthar phyin pa'i bdag don chos sku la bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:333: thugs rje chen po zhar las byung ba'i dpal ni /
NK075(bu)002:334: de nyid rtogs pa mthar phyin cing gdul bya'i don
NK075(bu)002:335: la gzugs sku rnam gnyis kyis don mdzad pa la
NK075(bu)002:336: bya'o // dpal gsum po de nyid ngo bo nyid kyis ldan zhing /
NK075(bu)002:337: rdo rje ni ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa /
NK075(bu)002:338: rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa mtshan nyid skye 'jigs dang bral ba /
NK075(bu)002:339: yon tan btsal ba med pa /
NK075(bu)002:341: de ltar chos lnga po lhun gyis grub cing skye 'jig dang bral ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:342: semas ni ma skyes mi 'gag spyod yul dang bral
NK075(bu)002:343: ba'i don la skad cig kyang ma g.yos par sems
NK075(bu)002:344: pa'o // dpal ni gong gi don la ma g.yos
NK075(bu)002:345: par stobs kyis snang stong gi mtha' gnyis sam dngos
NK075(bu)002:346: 'dzin gyi bag chags thams cad rang shugs kyis 'joms
NK075(bu)002:348: gtso ni ma rtogs sems can gyi dus su phung
NK075(bu)002:349: khams thams cad kyi gtso bo rnam shes yin la
NK075(bu)002:350: de nyid rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du shar ba'i dus
NK075(bu)002:351: su rnam shes gnas su gyur pa la rdo rje
NK075(bu)002:353: 'dir thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yin pas dkyil 'khor
NK075(bu)002:354: gyi gtso bor bzhugs pas rdo rje sems dpa' dang
NK075(bu)002:356: ji lta ji snyed dbyer med pa'i ye shes kyis
NK075(bu)002:357: shes bya'i chos kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su mkhyen
NK075(bu)002:358: cing / yod med dam rtag chad kyi mtha' gnyis
NK075(bu)002:359: dang bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i rgyal ba de bzhin
NK075(bu)002:360: gshegs pa kun gyi thugsa kyi dgongs pa chos kyi
NK075(bu)002:361: 'khor lo brgyad khri bzhi stong bskor ba'i nang nas
NK075(bu)002:362: 'bras bu'i mchog gsang sngags bla med kyi rgyud gsang
NK075(bu)002:363: ba'i snying po don gab sbas rnams mngon du ston
NK075(bu)002:364: par mdzad pa'i kun tu bzang po dang gnyis las
NK075(bu)002:365: cing / / 'o na 'khor lo dang chos ci tsug ltar sgra mthun na /
NK075(bu)002:366: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i 'khor lo de dang po 'gro ba'i sngon du 'khor lo de bskor /
NK075(bu)002:367: de nas 'khor lo des thams cad gcod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:369: kun mkhyen yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs nas chos 'khor bskor /
NK075(bu)002:371: de'i nyon mongs pa gcod pa dang gsum gyis chos mthun pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:372: gong gi kun mkhyen rgyal ba kun gyi thugs zhes pa 'di ni /
NK075(bu)002:373: sgyu 'phrul rang gzhung la brtags na sangs rgyas thams cad rigs lnga la bsdu /
NK075(bu)002:374: rigs lnga la thugs kyis rigs rdo rje sems dpa' la bsdu /
NK075(bu)002:375: bcom ldan dpal rdor sems sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs ye shes lnga yin la /
NK075(bu)002:376: ye shes lnga yang thugs kyi gtso bo chos dbyings ye shes la 'dus pa'i don la /
NK075(bu)002:377: kun mkhyen rgyal ba kun gyi thugs gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:378: sangs rgyas gsang bas nang na /
NK075(bu)002:379: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs rnams kun gyi bdag /
NK075(bu)002:380: rigs dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag por shog /
NK075(bu)002:383: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK075(bu)002:384: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK075(bu)002:386: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs rnams kun gyi gtso bo yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:387: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs kyi bdag nyid yin par rbad bcad pas //
NK075(bu)002:389: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' yin par mngon no //
NK075(bu)002:390: spyir ston pa la 'dren pa rang byung gi ston pa spyi'i gzugs can yin /
NK075(bu)002:391: bye brag gi ston pa ni rgyal tshab rgyud kyi ston pa ni rgyal ba rigs lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:392: gsang bdag dang gnyis yin par shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:394: sngon byung du slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK075(bu)002:395: bas bstan bcos brtsams pa'i thog mar rjes 'jug tu
NK075(bu)002:396: 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis 'chad nyan byed pa'i thog
NK075(bu)002:397: mar 'tshal / tshul ji ltar du 'tshal na gsum ste /
NK075(bu)002:400: mi phyed 'dres pa'i phyag yin te /
NK075(bu)002:401: ston pa rnam pa gnyis kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:402: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa gnyis shar
NK075(bu)002:403: nub kyi nam mkha' ltar dbyer med pa'i ngang du
NK075(bu)002:404: rtogs pa ni mi phyed 'dres zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:406: sgom pa goms pa'i phyag gam /
NK075(bu)002:407: sgrub pa po thabs kyi phyag ni gzhung 'di nyid
NK075(bu)002:408: kyi don rnams bde blag tu rtogs shing nyams su
NK075(bu)002:409: len nas bsgrubs pa mthar phyin pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:410: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa spyod pa rab kyi phyag
NK075(bu)002:411: ni lus gus pa dang bcas pa smad lnga sa
NK075(bu)002:412: la gtugs / ngag dwangs ba dang dad pas bstod pa dbyangs su bcas /
NK075(bu)002:413: yid ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:414: dgos ched ci'i phyir phyag 'tshal ba la /
NK075(bu)002:415: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas bstan bcos
NK075(bu)002:416: brtsams pa'i thog mar ston pa khyad par can gnyis
NK075(bu)002:417: la mchod par brjod pas sgrib pa byang tshogs rdzogs
NK075(bu)002:418: / bar chad rgyud nas dag ste /
NK075(bu)002:419: brtsams pa mthar phyin pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:420: gzhung mdzes pa'i dgos pa rnams yod do //
NK075(bu)002:421: rgyas bshad ni logs su shes so //
NK075(bu)002:422: gsum pa bshad par dam bca' ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:423: bgrang bshad par dam bca' ba dngos dang /
NK075(bu)002:431: gang gi don du bstan na skal ldan phyir /
NK075(bu)002:432: 'o na rang bzo ma yin nam zhe na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems /
NK075(bu)002:433: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud dag lasa /
NK075(bu)002:434: bldab par mi 'gyur ram zhe na //
NK075(bu)002:435: rgyud nas 'thor ba rnams bsdus te //
NK075(bu)002:436: 'o na lhag chad can du ma song ngam zhe
NK075(bu)002:437: na legas par zhes pa ni khog bsdebs bsdus don
NK075(bu)002:441: don gyi go rims bsdeb na /
NK075(bu)002:442: snang stong dbyer med kyi don khong du chud cing skye 'jig dang bral ba'i phyir rdo rje /
NK075(bu)002:443: don de nyid la 'da' nyams med pa'i phyir semsa zhes bya ste /
NK075(bu)002:444: de gdul bya'i ngo la kha sbyor gyi longs sku chen por shar nas /
NK075(bu)002:445: chos ston pa des sgyu snang bzhin ngo bo ma grub pas stong pa'i shes rab ste /
NK075(bu)002:447: 'phrul med las cir yang shar ba snang ba thabs te /
NK075(bu)002:449: d+r+wa ba dbyer med pa 'brel pa thabs shes dbyer
NK075(bu)002:450: med de rtags lha yab yum kha sbyor dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:451: / de ltar bshad pa'i bden gsum dbyer med de
NK075(bu)002:452: nyid sems can kun la stor bral med par gnas
NK075(bu)002:453: kyang gasnga ba bzhi'i dbang gis chod cing zab cing
NK075(bu)002:454: rtogs dka' bas de nyid la chos thams cad kyi
NK075(bu)002:455: bcud 'dus pas snying po gdul bya'i ngo la gzhi
NK075(bu)002:456: lam 'bras gsum byung yang gzhi bden gsum dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:457: de nyid gcig pu las min pas gzhi lam 'bras
NK075(bu)002:458: gsum rgyun mi chad cing rgyud gcig pa'i mtshon bya
NK075(bu)002:459: / don de nyid / mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud
NK075(bu)002:460: le'u stong phrag brgya par gsungs pa de dag gi
NK075(bu)002:462: dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung ba'i nor bu rin po
NK075(bu)002:463: che dang 'dra ba'i don gyi bcud thugs kyi thigs
NK075(bu)002:464: pa 'di nyid / dngos 'khor dang ma 'ongs pa'i
NK075(bu)002:465: gang zag shes rab kyi mig dang ldan pa ma
NK075(bu)002:466: h+aa'i sgor 'jug pa'i las 'phro skala ba dang ldan
NK075(bu)002:467: pa rnams kyi don bya ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:468: don lhag chad med par legas para rgyal ba'i bka' dang /
NK075(bu)002:469: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag dang /
NK075(bu)002:470: rang gi nyams myong gis rtogs pa'i rig pa tshad ma gsum dang mi 'gal bar byas nas /
NK075(bu)002:471: gang zag gzu lums can dang rwa chod can dgag pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:477: man ngag gab pa mngon du ngo sprad nas /
NK075(bu)002:478: tshig rgyas par bshad pa rnams don phyin ci ma
NK075(bu)002:479: log par mdor bsdus te bde blag tu rtogs par
NK075(bu)002:480: bya ba'i phyir / dper na skyes bu ya rabs
NK075(bu)002:481: pa rnams kyis bya ba ci byed kyang dam bca'
NK075(bu)002:483: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas kyang /
NK075(bu)002:484: thugs kyi dgongs pa zhal du tshig don ma 'dres
NK075(bu)002:485: par sings kyi phyung ste bstan bcos 'di nyid gzhan
NK075(bu)002:487: zhes brtsams par dam bca' ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:488: de la dam bca' khengs skyung dang 'brel pa /
NK075(bu)002:489: dam bca' dgos ched dang 'grel pa /
NK075(bu)002:490: dam bca' mdor bstan dang 'brel pa /
NK075(bu)002:491: dam bca' brtsams tshul dang 'brel pa rnams su yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:492: 'dir mdor bstan brtsam tshul dgos ched gsum dang 'brel par shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:494: dper na phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po las ni chu
NK075(bu)002:495: thigs pa gcig blangs pa la chu'i mtshan nyid tshang
NK075(bu)002:496: ba bzhin du / sems dang ye shes rang snang
NK075(bu)002:497: du ston pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba
NK075(bu)002:498: thugs kyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)002:499: po'i nang nas slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas nyer
NK075(bu)002:500: len gyi shes rab kyis rgyud don de nyid kyi
NK075(bu)002:501: don rnams legs par bsdus nas bstan bcos thugsa thigs
NK075(bu)002:502: 'di brtsams pa la rgyud kyi don 'dus shing ma
NK075(bu)002:504: dper na mi 'jigs seng ge'i phung po la /
NK075(bu)002:505: gcan gzan gzhan gyis mi tshugs shing phar la zil
NK075(bu)002:506: gyis gnon zhing gnod pa dang bral ba ji bzhin
NK075(bu)002:507: du / tshig don la sgro bskur lung ma bstan
NK075(bu)002:508: gsum dang tshad ma gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon dang
NK075(bu)002:509: du / bral cing / gzhan gyis dogs pa gzugs
NK075(bu)002:510: pa'i 'jigs pa dang bral cing phar la zil gyi
NK075(bu)002:511: du / bral cing / gnon pa'o // de lta
NK075(bu)002:512: bu'i sems dang ye shes rang snang du ston pa'i
NK075(bu)002:513: thugsa kyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)002:514: po'i don bcud thugs thigs 'di la dbye na 'og
NK075(bu)002:515: nas bshad pa'i gsum po yin te /
NK075(bu)002:517: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba /
NK075(bu)002:518: 'bras bu bde bar gshegsa pa'i snang ba /
NK075(bu)002:519: gdul bya'i lam gyi snang ba dang gsum gyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:520: bo la brten nas mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud gzhi
NK075(bu)002:521: lam 'bras gsum gyi dbye ba rgyas par lus rnam
NK075(bu)002:523: gzhi dang lam gnyis shes bya shes byed du 'brel /
NK075(bu)002:524: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis thob bya 'thob byed du 'brel /
NK075(bu)002:525: gzhi 'bras gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:526: don la gzhi lam 'bras gsum ngo bo gcig pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:527: 'o na gcig na gsum byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ci
NK075(bu)002:528: yin zhe na gzhi bden gsum dbyer med kyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:529: bor gcig pa yin pa la snang ba gsum gyi
NK075(bu)002:530: ngo bo tha dad du byung ba de la rkyen
NK075(bu)002:531: gang gis byas na rang ngo ma shes shing blo
NK075(bu)002:532: 'khrul pa'i yul snang bas so sor 'dzin pas bag
NK075(bu)002:533: chags de nyid las grol bar byed pa la gnas
NK075(bu)002:535: rtogs pa'i cha nas lam mthar phyin pa'i cha nas 'bras bu dang gsuma du snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:536: gong du bshad pa'i snang ba gsum po de dag
NK075(bu)002:537: 'khrul ba snang ba'i rkyen gyis phye ba yin pas
NK075(bu)002:540: ngo ma shes pa'i cha nas 'khrul pa /
NK075(bu)002:541: de la grol bar byed pa'i cha nas lam mthar
NK075(bu)002:542: phyin pa'i cha nas 'bras bu'i snang ba dang bzhi
NK075(bu)002:543: daga tu dbye nas bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:544: rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs pa'i rgyud lung rnams dang /
NK075(bu)002:545: mkhas grub gong ma rnams kyis rigas pa'i man ngag gi bstan bcos kun la gsal bar bashada do //
NK075(bu)002:546: gzhung rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:548: dang po snang ba bzhir mdor bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:550: de ltar rgyud dang man ngag la snang ba bzhi'i yan lag tu phye nas bshad na'ang /
NK075(bu)002:551: don la dbyer med pas na rdo rje theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:552: de gdul bya'i ngo la byed las sam dgos ched
NK075(bu)002:553: ma 'dres pa'i sgo nas snang ba rnam pa bzhi
NK075(bu)002:554: po'i don rgyas par dbye nas bshad na 'di lta
NK075(bu)002:555: ste / de la snang ba bzhi /
NK075(bu)002:556: rgyud gsum spyi'i go don brgal lan dang bcas pa bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:558: brgal lan gyi sgo nas mtha' yongs su chod par bya ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:559: go don ni gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i rgyud ces bya ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:561: chos thams cad kyi ye nas 'byung gzhi /
NK075(bu)002:562: rang bzhin bcos slad dang bral ba /
NK075(bu)002:563: snang ba ni rang rig pa'i rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:564: de ka la skabs kyis rgyud ces bya ste /
NK075(bu)002:565: gang zhig dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel pa dang ldan pas na rgyud do //
NK075(bu)002:567: gzhi la shes bya ye ldan gyi dgos pa tshang zhing /
NK075(bu)002:568: gzhi dang lam gnyis shes bya dang shes byed du 'brel /
NK075(bu)002:569: gzhi dang 'bras bu gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel lo //
NK075(bu)002:570: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba'i rgyud ni /
NK075(bu)002:571: thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga rgyud la skyes pa'am skye ru rung ba zhig la gdul bya /
NK075(bu)002:572: 'jug cing bgrod par byed pa zhig la lam /
NK075(bu)002:573: bstan pa blo dang 'tsham par snang ba zhig la snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:574: de ka la skabs kyis rgyud ces kyang 'dogs /
NK075(bu)002:575: lam la bgrod pa yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang zhing /
NK075(bu)002:576: lam dang gzhi gnyis shes bya dang shes byed du 'brel /
NK075(bu)002:577: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis thob bya dang thob byed du 'brel /
NK075(bu)002:578: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la /
NK075(bu)002:579: gang zhig smin pa zhig 'bras bu /
NK075(bu)002:580: nar son pas na bde bar gshegs pa /
NK075(bu)002:581: rtogs pa'i rig pa sku dang ye shes su rang snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:582: de ka la skabs kyis rgyud ces kyang 'dogs te /
NK075(bu)002:583: 'bras bu la thob bya ye ldan gyis dgos pa
NK075(bu)002:584: tshang zhing 'bras bu dang gzhi gnyis bdag nyid gcig
NK075(bu)002:585: pur 'brel / 'bras bu dang lam gnyis 'thob bya dang thob byed du 'brel pas na rgyud do //
NK075(bu)002:586: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:587: yul yul can gnyis med las log cing gnyis su zhen pas na log rtog /
NK075(bu)002:588: de ma yin la der bzung bas na 'khrul pa /
NK075(bu)002:589: las dang log rtog gis blo ngor snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:590: de la 'brel pa dang dgos pa med pas 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:591: pa'i snang ba ni snang ba yin kyang rgyud ma
NK075(bu)002:592: yin no // gnyis pa brgal lan ni /
NK075(bu)002:593: rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par
NK075(bu)002:594: snang ba zhig gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba yin
NK075(bu)002:597: dang po ltar na gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba ma yin par thal /
NK075(bu)002:598: rtogs nas snang dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:600: sems can thams cad rang grol du thal /
NK075(bu)002:601: ma rtogs pa'i dus na rig rtsal 'gag med du
NK075(bu)002:602: shar ba'i phyir ro zhe na rig rtsal 'gag med
NK075(bu)002:603: du shar ba gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba yin
NK075(bu)002:604: kyang ma rtogs sems can gyi dus su 'khrul snang
NK075(bu)002:605: sna tshogs su shar la rtogs pa'i dus su ye
NK075(bu)002:607: bstan pa blo dang 'tsham par snang ba zhig gdul bya lam snang yin na /
NK075(bu)002:608: de nyams su blangs pas gsang sngags kyi 'bras bu thob bam mi thob /
NK075(bu)002:609: mi thob na lam nyams su blangs pa don med du thal /
NK075(bu)002:610: 'dod na le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK075(bu)002:611: thos bsam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK075(bu)002:612: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK075(bu)002:614: thob na mu stegs rtag chad kyis kyang thob par thal /
NK075(bu)002:616: rtag chad gnyis su gang gi blo zhen pa //
NK075(bu)002:617: don gyi snying po nyid la gol bar gsungs //
NK075(bu)002:618: zhes pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:619: bstan pa blo dang 'tsham par snang ba zhig lam snang yin la /
NK075(bu)002:620: de nyams su blangs pas gsang sngags kyi 'bras bu dngos su thob /
NK075(bu)002:621: la las brgyud nas 'thob par byed pas skyon las grol lo /
NK075(bu)002:622: rtogs pa'i rig pa sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK075(bu)002:623: 'khor du rang snang ba zhig 'bras bu bde bar
NK075(bu)002:624: gshegs pa'i snang ba yin na /
NK075(bu)002:625: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin chos can mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin par thal /
NK075(bu)002:627: yi ge 'khor lo mngon gzigs nas //
NK075(bu)002:629: 'dod na lam pa yin pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:630: lhun grub rig 'dzin bag la nyal gyi dri ma
NK075(bu)002:631: yod cing rtogs pa'i rig pa mthar thug pa gcig
NK075(bu)002:632: sku dang ye shes su snang ba de 'bras bu'i
NK075(bu)002:634: byas pas skyon las grol lo //
NK075(bu)002:635: gnyis med las bzlog cing gnyis su snang ba 'khrul pa'i snang ba yin na /
NK075(bu)002:636: 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du thal 'dod na 'phrul gyi me long las /
NK075(bu)002:638: zhes gsungs pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:639: las dang log rtog gis glo bur du snang ba zhig 'khrul snang yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:640: 'khrul par snang dus gzhi las ma g.yos kyang //
NK075(bu)002:641: 'khrul par snang ba'i snang ba de nyid shes bya'i
NK075(bu)002:642: gshis la ma grub pa'i phyir 'gro la shes rgyud
NK075(bu)002:644: byas pas skyon las grol lo //
NK075(bu)002:645: yang snang ba bzhi gcig gam tha dad ce na /
NK075(bu)002:646: snang ba bzhi po bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po las ma g.yos pas gcig la rang ldog ni /
NK075(bu)002:647: gzhi ni ma rtogs la ma 'khrul pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:648: 'khrul pa ni ma rtogs la 'khrul pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:649: lam pa ni rtogs bzhin 'khrul pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:650: 'bras bu ni rtogs la ma 'khrul pa yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:651: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du snang ba bzhir grangs nges te /
NK075(bu)002:654: go rim yang gong du bshad pa bzhin nges pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:655: gnyis pa snang ba bzhi bye brag tu phye ste rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:656: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:657: log rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:658: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:659: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:664: gzhi'i ngo bo ngos bzung de nyid 'khor 'das lhun grub tu bstan pa'i dpe don dang /
NK075(bu)002:665: gzhi de la 'khor 'das snang tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:666: gzhi de'i don rtogs par bya ba'i phyir 'khrul pa dang ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK075(bu)002:667: snang ba dang rgyud kyi nges tshig go //
NK075(bu)002:668: dang po gzhi'i ngo bo la 'khor 'das lhun grub tu bstan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:669: de las nang tshigs su bcad na bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:671: gang du dgos pa gang nges dang /
NK075(bu)002:672: ngo bo dmigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:677: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:679: gzhi chos nyid ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas su
NK075(bu)002:680: yod pas lhan cig pa dang go phye ba'i 'khor
NK075(bu)002:681: gyis chos nyid shes su btub /
NK075(bu)002:682: rtogs su btub pa'i dgos ched yod de /
NK075(bu)002:683: yungs kar la mar nag lhun grub tu yod pas brdeg brtsog byas na mar 'byung ba lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:685: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung khungs sam gzhi yin pa'i phyir na gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:687: chos thams cad rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK075(bu)002:688: bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar ye
NK075(bu)002:689: nas gnas pa'o // de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i don lnga pa las /
NK075(bu)002:690: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK075(bu)002:691: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ste //
NK075(bu)002:694: rnam rtog kun gzhi ma yin la //
NK075(bu)002:695: rang bzhin med pa don gyi gzhi //
NK075(bu)002:697: snang dang mi snang gnyis ka min //
NK075(bu)002:698: yod med gnyis ka dbyer med do //
NK075(bu)002:701: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK075(bu)002:704: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)002:705: de ni lung gi tshad mar bzhag /
NK075(bu)002:706: ces pa ni lung du ma nas gsal lo //
NK075(bu)002:707: bzhi pa don gyi dmigs bzung ba la don dam dbyer med gsum rang la gnas tshul ni /
NK075(bu)002:709: snang ba bzhi'i thog mar gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba bstana pa'i don bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:710: byang ba stong pa'i rang bzhin skye med don dam dang /
NK075(bu)002:711: chub ba snang ba'i rang bzhin sgyu ma kun rdzob /
NK075(bu)002:712: semas gnyis su med pa'i rig pa ste bden gsum
NK075(bu)002:713: dbyer kyi don de nyid kyis rgyud drag las kyis
NK075(bu)002:714: 'gro ba mang po'i ste kun gyi sems rgyud la
NK075(bu)002:715: ngo bo nyid dam rang chas kyi ldan nas yod
NK075(bu)002:716: kyang rang ngo ma shes pas yul yul can phyin
NK075(bu)002:717: ci log tu rtogsa shing 'khrul pa'i ngo bor shar
NK075(bu)002:718: la der shar ba' rgyu ni brgyud rgyu bde gshegs
NK075(bu)002:719: snying po bden gsum gyi don de nyid kun gyi
NK075(bu)002:720: gzhir gnas kyang mtshungs rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma
NK075(bu)002:721: rig pas ngo ma shes lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu
NK075(bu)002:722: kun tu brtags pas ma rig pas 'gro ba rigs
NK075(bu)002:723: drug dang lhan cig tu byed pa'i rgyu byasa /
NK075(bu)002:724: nyer len nam 'phen pa'i rgyu bag chags mthu can des 'phen pa'i rgyu byas /
NK075(bu)002:725: spyi'i rgyu ni bdag tu rtogs pa yin te de las thams cad byung ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:729: dge ba'i las dge bcus mtho ris gnas bcu /
NK075(bu)002:730: sdig pa mi dge ba bcu'i las kyis ngan song gnas bcu /
NK075(bu)002:731: mi g.yo ba'i las kyis khams gong ma gnyis su skye ba'i rkyen byed cing /
NK075(bu)002:733: zhe sdang gi rkyen gyis dmyal bar skye /
NK075(bu)002:737: phrag dog gis lha ma yin /
NK075(bu)002:738: nga rgyal gyis lhar skye ba'i rkyen byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:739: 'dod chags nga rgyal phrag dog rang khams mtho ris gnas gsum du skye ba ma yin /
NK075(bu)002:740: dge bcu bsags kyang gong gi dug gsum gyis 'phags pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:741: de ltar 'khrul pa'i rgyu rkyen gnyis kyi sgo nas
NK075(bu)002:742: gong du bshad pa bzhin du 'khor 'das tha dad
NK075(bu)002:743: du shar te shar ba'i dus de nyid na'ang dper
NK075(bu)002:744: na gsera las byas pa'i gzugs 'gros kyi rnam pa
NK075(bu)002:745: ji ltar snang yang ngo bo gser la gcig pa
NK075(bu)002:746: bzhina du / gzhi'i gnas lugs de las ma bcos
NK075(bu)002:747: pas na rang byung sgrib g.yog dang bral ba'i ye
NK075(bu)002:748: shes de'i ngo bo la 'khor 'das kyi snang tshul
NK075(bu)002:749: ci ltar byung yang tha dad med de gcig pa'o
NK075(bu)002:750: bzhina du / // 'o na ci'i phyir gcig na
NK075(bu)002:751: rang byung ye shes de yang 'ching ba 'khor ba
NK075(bu)002:752: dang grola ba mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis ka'i
NK075(bu)002:755: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de nyid kyi
NK075(bu)002:756: rtsal 'gag med du shar ba la de ngo ma
NK075(bu)002:758: ngo shes pa la 'das pa 'byung ngo //
NK075(bu)002:759: de ltar 'khor 'das gnyis kyi gzhi gcig pas /
NK075(bu)002:760: lam rnal 'byor pas gzhi don de nyid lta bas gtan la pheb pa'i tshe na /
NK075(bu)002:761: dper na me long grub pa dang ni g.ya' 'grub
NK075(bu)002:762: pa dus gcig pas me long dang g.ya' la spang
NK075(bu)002:764: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:765: lhan skyes ye shes gnyis gzhi gcig cing rig ma
NK075(bu)002:766: rig tsam las min pa phan tshun mi mthun pa
NK075(bu)002:767: ltar byas nas ma rig pa spangsa pa la rig
NK075(bu)002:768: pa ye shes skyes pa med de ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:769: de nyid rig pa ye shes su shar ba yin
NK075(bu)002:770: pa la / gsang sngags 'bras bu'i theg pa'i don
NK075(bu)002:771: la blo shed ma bye ba'i byis pa rgyu mtshan
NK075(bu)002:772: nyid theg pa bas ma rig pa 'di nyid 'khor
NK075(bu)002:773: ba'i gzhi yin pa dang rnam byang mya ngan las
NK075(bu)002:774: 'das pa'i las dkar po'i bag chags sogs gzhi byed
NK075(bu)002:775: cing sad pa'i rten tsam byas la /
NK075(bu)002:776: ma rig pa spangs nas dag pa'i ngo bo la rig pa'i ye shes rtogs pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:777: spang gnyen gnyis mi gcig ste dper na me chu gnyis mi gcig pa bzhin no //
NK075(bu)002:778: zhes smra na'ang de ltar ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:779: gnas lugs kyi don la mkhas pas 'bras bu'i theg
NK075(bu)002:780: pa bas gzhi rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:781: bo la 'khor 'das lhun grub tu gnas te /
NK075(bu)002:782: gnas pa'i rgyu mtshan ni sems nyid 'di nyid sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:783: de ltar smra dus smra ba las 'das pa bsam
NK075(bu)002:784: pa'i blo de nyid chos nyid bsam blo las 'das
NK075(bu)002:785: pa'i yin no // 'o na sems can 'di nyid
NK075(bu)002:786: sangs rgyas min na sems can las sangs rgyas logs
NK075(bu)002:787: su tshol dgos na sol ba la dung mi 'byung
NK075(bu)002:788: pa'i yin no // ba bzhin du / sems can
NK075(bu)002:789: la sangs rgyas mi srid de gzhi tha dad pa'i
NK075(bu)002:790: pa'i yin no // ba bzhin du / phyir ro
NK075(bu)002:791: // 'o na sems can sangs rgyas yin na dung
NK075(bu)002:792: las sol ba mi 'byung ba bzhin du sems can
NK075(bu)002:793: mi srid de sangs rgyas pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:794: de bas na kho bo'i bla mas ni /
NK075(bu)002:795: sems can sangs rgyas yin par yang go dgos /
NK075(bu)002:796: min par yang go dgos gsungs pas /
NK075(bu)002:797: de'i don rig ma rig gong du bshad pa bzhin khong du chud pa gal che'o //
NK075(bu)002:798: de la 'khor 'das snang tshul la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:800: sems rigs rgyud med pa las 'khor 'das su snang zhing ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:802: 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa'i dus su yang da lta'i lus 'di sku /
NK075(bu)002:805: de yin pa'i don ni 'di skad du gsang ba'i
NK075(bu)002:806: snying po sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa'i rgyud nyid las
NK075(bu)002:807: gsungs te / bde bar gshegsa pa'i sku snang bzhin
NK075(bu)002:808: ngo bo ma grub pas ye shes sgyu mar gzugs
NK075(bu)002:809: sku rnam gnyis su shar nas gdul bya'i ngo la
NK075(bu)002:810: gsungs te / snang ba dang / ma rig 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:811: snang gi ngo bor 'gro drug gi lus snang bzhin
NK075(bu)002:812: ngo bo ma grub pas log rtog sgyu mar sna
NK075(bu)002:813: tshogs su shar nas snang ba gnyis ngo bo gcig
NK075(bu)002:814: gsungs te / snang ba dang / pas so // 'o na ci'i phyir gcig na /
NK075(bu)002:815: rig pa 'di nyid kyi rtsal 'gag med du shar
NK075(bu)002:816: ba la rig ma rig gi dbang gis sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)002:817: kyi sku dang sems can gyi lus su snang ba
NK075(bu)002:818: ma gtogs pa / ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)002:819: dang sems can gyi rigsa tha dad dang dag ma
NK075(bu)002:820: dag gi rgyud tha dad du so sor brtag tu
NK075(bu)002:821: ma gtogs pa / med de / ci'i phyir na
NK075(bu)002:822: 'khrul pa'i gzhi rtsa ma rig pa yin la de
NK075(bu)002:823: la brtags na dang po bskyed pa'i gzhi med bar
NK075(bu)002:824: du brtan pa'i rtsa ba med de ngos bzung dang
NK075(bu)002:825: bral zhing rang bzhin gyis stong pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:827: sems nyid la pho mo ma ning gi rigsa dang
NK075(bu)002:828: kha doga dkar ser dmar ljang dbyibs zlum po gru
NK075(bu)002:829: bzhi zla gam gru gsum la sogs pa gang yang
NK075(bu)002:830: med pas stong pa de nyid las ma g.yos bzhin
NK075(bu)002:831: du phyi snod kyi 'jig rten nanga bcud kyi sems
NK075(bu)002:832: can la sogs pa'i shes bya 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK075(bu)002:833: thams cad la ma 'gags par rang shar nas snang
NK075(bu)002:834: bas na thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:835: yang zhes pa snyeg pa'i tshig yin te /
NK075(bu)002:836: gong du brgyad cu pa'i lung thal nas /
NK075(bu)002:837: 'dir gsang snying gi lung drangs pa na yang ni sgyu 'phrul dra ba gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK075(bu)002:838: 'khor ba'i dus su bdag 'dzin sems can gyi sdug
NK075(bu)002:839: bsngal thams cad gshis la ma grub pas bacangas pa
NK075(bu)002:840: med pa'i phyir / 'das pa'i dus su rnam par
NK075(bu)002:841: grol ba po yang med pa ye gdod ma nas
NK075(bu)002:842: rang gi rig pa 'di nyid la sku dang ye
NK075(bu)002:843: shes su lhun gyis rdzogsa shing gsal ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:844: sangsa rgyas kyis thugs su chud pa'i chos kyang de
NK075(bu)002:845: nyid yin ces rgyud las gsungsa pas gzhi rang bzhina
NK075(bu)002:846: rgyud shes bya gshis kyi gnas lugs de nyid kyi
NK075(bu)002:847: ngo bo la ni ma riga pa dang rig pa
NK075(bu)002:848: ye shesa la tha dad du 'dzin du med de
NK075(bu)002:849: // dper na nam mkha' dwangsa ba de nyid la
NK075(bu)002:850: sprin gyi gnas bcas kyang byung yang nam mkha' rang
NK075(bu)002:851: // las byung / zhi yang nam mkha' rang la zhi ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:852: sems rang bzhin med pa de nyid la ma rig
NK075(bu)002:853: 'khrul snang sna tshogs 'byung zhing dag kyang rang dag
NK075(bu)002:854: tu 'gyur zhing logs su song ba med do //
NK075(bu)002:855: tha dad lhun grub tu gcig pa'i sems nyid de
NK075(bu)002:856: nyid mtha' thug med du dpe don gyis cir yang
NK075(bu)002:859: dang rig can gyi 'gro zhes pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:860: 'gro zhes pa'i 'bru gnur la ras la sogs pa'i dpe bzhag 'ga' zhig snang yang 'dir /
NK075(bu)002:861: dper na shel dwangs ba'i rigas can de la kha
NK075(bu)002:862: dog dkar ser dmar ljang kun gyi rkyen gang dang
NK075(bu)002:863: 'phrad pa'i kha dog bzhin du 'gyur nas 'gro yang
NK075(bu)002:864: ngo bo shes las 'gyur ba med pa ltar /
NK075(bu)002:865: rnam rtog gzung 'dzin gyi semas bde sdug bar pa la sogs mi mthun pa du ma shar kyang /
NK075(bu)002:866: semas nyid du ngo bo gciga yin pa la rkyen
NK075(bu)002:867: gyis bskyur bas rang gi sems nyid gcig pu de
NK075(bu)002:868: mtha' thugsa med par kun las shar te /
NK075(bu)002:869: cir yang 'char du rung ba'i dpe don dngos dang /
NK075(bu)002:871: dper na ar+ya ste 'phags pa rdo rje sems dpa'
NK075(bu)002:872: de nyid nor lha dzam b+ha la' skur snang nas
NK075(bu)002:873: / phyag g.yon pas ne'u le'i rgyal pa rin po
NK075(bu)002:874: ches gang ba las rin chen gyi char phyogs kun
NK075(bu)002:875: tu phab pa 'dra ba la rgyal po'i chos lugs
NK075(bu)002:876: yang dag dang ldan zhing dge bcu'i don gyis thams
NK075(bu)002:877: cad la khrims bca' bar byed pa'i 'khor lo sgyur
NK075(bu)002:879: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun du babs bram ze
NK075(bu)002:880: gtsang sbra dang ldan pa'i ya rabs dam pa rnams
NK075(bu)002:881: kyi gnas su sna tshogas pa'i rina chen gser dngul
NK075(bu)002:882: la sogs pa phal pa lnga bab tsi bi ra
NK075(bu)002:883: yi dwags kyi gnas su bye ma'i tshub ma dang
NK075(bu)002:884: grama pa la sogs pa rnams bab /
NK075(bu)002:885: dbul ba tan tra ste dbul po'i rigs rgyud kyi grong khyer du zas kyi lhad /
NK075(bu)002:886: gos kyi ras hrul la sogs pa longs spyod du mi 'dod pa rnams bab pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:887: rigs ngan shana ta ste shan pa dang rak+sha srin
NK075(bu)002:888: po'i gnas su sha khrag rus pa rnams bab gdola
NK075(bu)002:889: pa ste zhing las pa mi phal pa'i grong du
NK075(bu)002:890: mu tig la sogs pa rina po che sil ma'o
NK075(bu)002:891: // yang na 'bru rin po che nas la sogs pa'i 'bru sna tshogs sil ma bab na yang /
NK075(bu)002:892: rin po che'i char gacaga bab pa la bsod nams
NK075(bu)002:893: bsags che chung gi dbang gis gong du bshad pa
NK075(bu)002:894: ltar so sor snang ba bzhina du 'gro drug gi
NK075(bu)002:895: 'khrul snang gi spyod yul bzang ngan la sogs mtho
NK075(bu)002:896: dman tha dad du snang ba yang /
NK075(bu)002:897: rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de
NK075(bu)002:898: rang ngo rang gis ma shes pas tshogs brgyad yul
NK075(bu)002:899: du 'phro ba'i rkyen gang 'phrad kyis bsgyur nas der
NK075(bu)002:901: ci'i phyir rkyen gyis bsgyur btub ce na /
NK075(bu)002:902: sems nyid kyi ngo bo la rigsa rgyud dang phyogsa
NK075(bu)002:903: cha 'di 'dra zhig dngos por ngos bzung du med
NK075(bu)002:904: cing stong ste rgya gcig tu ma chad cing phyogs
NK075(bu)002:905: med du kun las shar ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:906: gtan tshigs de bas na sems nyid de la rkyen
NK075(bu)002:907: gang shar des bsgyur cing cir yang snang du btub
NK075(bu)002:908: bo // log rtog gi snang ba don la rang rgyud du med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:910: spyir ni sems can gyi shes rgyud kyis log rtog
NK075(bu)002:911: gi rnam grangs bsam yas pa zhig yod kyang ye
NK075(bu)002:912: gdod ma nas rang rgyud du grub nas yoda pa
NK075(bu)002:913: ma yin te / de la te na kyang gsum
NK075(bu)002:914: las skyon can dang bstan bya lhag ma can gnyis
NK075(bu)002:915: ma yin te / las / 'di skyon can gyis tshig yin te /
NK075(bu)002:916: rang rgyud du grub pa med kyang /
NK075(bu)002:917: 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i dbang gis yul yul can so
NK075(bu)002:918: sor 'dzin pa'i rtog pa bzang ngan phra rags rnams
NK075(bu)002:919: kun gzhi la baga chagas bsog sad kyi dbang gis
NK075(bu)002:920: / dper na chu rnyog ma la gzugs brnyan mi
NK075(bu)002:921: gsal bzhin du sems rang gis 'gyu 'thas rang 'gribsa
NK075(bu)002:922: shing dus rtag tu khams gsum du 'khor kyang /
NK075(bu)002:923: sems las logs su byung ba ma yin te de'i
NK075(bu)002:924: don ni 'di skad sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las gsungsa
NK075(bu)002:925: pa'ang dus thog ma med pa nas 'khrul nas log
NK075(bu)002:926: rtog sna tshogs su byung yang sems nyid rang byung
NK075(bu)002:927: ye shes las logs su skad cig kyang ma gyur
NK075(bu)002:929: ci'i phyir logs su ma gyur cing dbyer med na /
NK075(bu)002:930: rgyu ma rig pa rkyen las nyon gyis 'khrul pa
NK075(bu)002:931: sna tshogs byung yang dwangs rgyu sang rgyu yod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:932: phyir glo bur ba'i ming 'dogs so //
NK075(bu)002:933: ye nas glo bur ba med de /
NK075(bu)002:934: 'khor ba'i spyod yul sna tshogs tha dad du snang dus 'khrul pa thog ma 'di nas byung /
NK075(bu)002:935: dag pa'i dus su mtha' ma 'dir song med de /
NK075(bu)002:936: sems de nyid 'khrul snang sna tshogs su shar bas dbyer med ces bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:937: gong gi 'khrul pa bshad pa rnams kyang 'khrul pa
NK075(bu)002:938: kho nar ma yin ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi dgongs
NK075(bu)002:940: theg 'og gi gdams ngag gi don 'khrul pa dang ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid la bdun te /
NK075(bu)002:942: bden pa gnyis su 'dod pa 'khor 'das lhun grub la skyon brjod pa nyid 'khrul pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:944: semas nyid kyi rgyud la 'khor 'das gnyis po kun
NK075(bu)002:945: gyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams lhun grub tu gnas shing
NK075(bu)002:946: ngo bo dbyer pa ste dper na nor bu rin
NK075(bu)002:947: chen la dgos 'dod tha dad rnams ngo bo lhun
NK075(bu)002:948: grub tu gnas pa lta bu yin pa la /
NK075(bu)002:949: de ltar lhun grub yin par ma shes pa kha
NK075(bu)002:950: cig gis ma rig ye shes sam 'khor 'das kyi
NK075(bu)002:951: don mi mthun 'gal ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:952: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi ngo bo dbyer med lhun grub
NK075(bu)002:953: gcig tu 'dus pa mi 'thad zhesa theg dman mtshan
NK075(bu)002:954: nyid kyi gang zag tshig phyir blo 'brang ba dag
NK075(bu)002:955: gis brjod na'ang / de ltar ma rig ye shes
NK075(bu)002:956: sam 'khor 'das gnyis gzhi tha dad du 'dod nas
NK075(bu)002:957: phan tshun mi mthun par byas nas ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:958: spangsa rig pa ye shes rtogs par gang zag gang
NK075(bu)002:960: dper na dred mos rtsi tog gi lo 'bram la sogs ci zos kyang /
NK075(bu)002:961: khog par mi sdod byabs shin song bas 'grangs pa'i bya ba mi byed pa ltar /
NK075(bu)002:962: gsang ba bla na med pa'i theg pa 'di nyid
NK075(bu)002:963: kyi don 'og ma las lhag pa'i mchog dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:964: lhun grub dag ga la yoda de med do //
NK075(bu)002:965: 'khor 'das kyi ngo bo dang rang bzhin dang shes
NK075(bu)002:966: blo tha dad du 'dod pa la skyon brjod de
NK075(bu)002:967: don la tha mi dad du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:969: 'khrul pa'i dngos po kun nas bslang bas nyon mongas
NK075(bu)002:970: pa 'khor ba'i chos dang rnam par byang ba mya
NK075(bu)002:971: ngan las 'das pa'i chos gnyis kyi dngos po mi
NK075(bu)002:972: 'dra ste / 'khor ba'i ngo bo dngos po yin la /
NK075(bu)002:973: myang 'das kyi ngo bo dngos med yin zhes smra
NK075(bu)002:974: na ye gdod ma nas 'khor 'das gnyis kyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:975: bo tha dad yoda pa yina na /
NK075(bu)002:976: mtshan nyid rang gzhung gi nyon mongs pa spang zhing
NK075(bu)002:977: rtogs bya'i 'bras bu byang chub bsgrub tu med de
NK075(bu)002:978: / da lta'i sems ni nyon mongs pa kho na
NK075(bu)002:979: yin pas dper na sol ba las dung du mi
NK075(bu)002:981: 'o na ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:982: sems nyid ngo bo gcig la rig ma rig gis 'khor 'das gnyis byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:983: nyon mongs pa dngos bcas kyi ngo bo ngos bzung can de nyid /
NK075(bu)002:984: dngos med blo 'das byang chub snying po'i don ngo bo ngos bzung dang bral ba de ka yin /
NK075(bu)002:985: dper na chu la rnyog dwangs kyi rkyen gyis gzugs
NK075(bu)002:986: brnyan gsal mi gsal byung yang ngo bo chu la
NK075(bu)002:988: 'khor 'das so so'i rang bzhin nges te /
NK075(bu)002:990: 'das pa'i rang bzhin bde ba yin zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:991: yanga dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'i thabs
NK075(bu)002:992: kyi lam thos bsam sgom gsum gyi blos bcos su
NK075(bu)002:993: med de ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:994: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i lung des 'khor 'das tha dad
NK075(bu)002:995: du 'dod pa la skyon yod par gsungs pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:996: na gzhi chos nyid dri bral de nyid 'khrul rtog
NK075(bu)002:997: rang gi rgyur gansa pa thams cad dbyer med kyang
NK075(bu)002:998: / sems 'khrul pa'i blo 'di nyid rang chos nyid
NK075(bu)002:999: gshis kyi gnas lugs yin par ma shes nas shes
NK075(bu)002:1000: byed kyi blo 'di dang shes bya gzhi gnyis mi
NK075(bu)002:1001: gcig go zhes gnyis su smra na'ang /
NK075(bu)002:1003: bsam pa'i blo shes byed de ka rang shes bya gshis chos nyid de bzhin nyid yin te /
NK075(bu)002:1004: 'o na blo de la 'khrul pa'i bag chags sna tshogs yada pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:1005: gzhi de nyid la 'khrul pa'i bag chags thams cad
NK075(bu)002:1006: dag nas mada ces gnyis med kyi don ma mthong
NK075(bu)002:1007: ba'i tshig phyir blo 'brang ba'i phyogs su gtogsa pa
NK075(bu)002:1009: de la skyon 'di ltar yod de /
NK075(bu)002:1010: blo de nyid dang gnas lugs gzhi de gnyis la
NK075(bu)002:1011: 'brel ba med pas nam yang sngon gong du bshad
NK075(bu)002:1012: pa'i ngo bo dang rang bzhin tha dad la skyon
NK075(bu)002:1013: brjod pa bzhin blo dang gzhi gnyis mi gcig na
NK075(bu)002:1014: nyon mongs spang zhing byang chub bsgrub tu med pa
NK075(bu)002:1015: dang / yang dag pa'i lam gyis bcos su med
NK075(bu)002:1016: pa'i phyir gzhi blo tha dad du 'dod pas 'bras
NK075(bu)002:1017: bu thob zer ba ni bden pa min no //
NK075(bu)002:1019: rnam par mi rtogs pa'i ye shes gzhi'i ngo bo
NK075(bu)002:1020: de nyid rnam par rtog pa yi blo'i sems rgyud
NK075(bu)002:1021: 'di nyid dang lhan cig tu ldan nas yod pa'o
NK075(bu)002:1022: // lung rigs kyi sgo nas log rtog spang du med pa'i dpe don dang /
NK075(bu)002:1024: shes bya'i chos thams cad phyi 'byung ba lnga yum lnga nang phung po lnga yab lnga /
NK075(bu)002:1025: bar rnam par shes pa ye shes lnga'i sems dpa'
NK075(bu)002:1026: dang sems mar dag ces bya ba'am yang na dbyings
NK075(bu)002:1027: ka dag ye shes ka dag /
NK075(bu)002:1028: dag pa chen por dag ces bya ba yang /
NK075(bu)002:1029: dngosa po zhig bsal nas daga pa ma yin te
NK075(bu)002:1030: 'khrul snang gi phung khams skye mched du snang bdo
NK075(bu)002:1031: ba dang spyod bdo ba'i dus de nyid na rnam
NK075(bu)002:1032: par dag ces sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i lung las gsungs
NK075(bu)002:1033: pas loga rtog gi shes pa 'di nyid spang du
NK075(bu)002:1034: med de yang dag pa'i gnas lugs la ma g.yos
NK075(bu)002:1035: pa ni dpe 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' la
NK075(bu)002:1036: sprin dang 'ja' mtshon sna tshogs su snang ba'i tshe
NK075(bu)002:1037: / byung yang nam mkha' rang zhi yang nam mkha'
NK075(bu)002:1038: rang la zhi bas rang bzhin nam mkha' stong par
NK075(bu)002:1039: ngang ngam shugs kyis gnas te tha dad med pa
NK075(bu)002:1040: / bzhin no // bden gnyis blo dngos su 'byed pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:1042: gsang sngags las dgar ba'i gdams ngag la la gang
NK075(bu)002:1043: dag rgyu'a thega pa basa yul yul can kun tu
NK075(bu)002:1044: rtogsa pa kun rdzob 'khrul snang 'di nyid don dam
NK075(bu)002:1045: la dbyer med yod na don dam gyi ngesa tshiga
NK075(bu)002:1046: meda dgosa pasa / bden gnyis su dbye nas don
NK075(bu)002:1047: dam gyi mtshan nyid ni ma rig pa 'khrul pa
NK075(bu)002:1048: dag nas dwangs shing sgrib g.yog spros pa dang bral
NK075(bu)002:1049: bas gsal kun rdzob kyi mtshan ma dag para gang
NK075(bu)002:1050: 'dod pa don dam yin la bsam pa'i blo dag
NK075(bu)002:1051: la kun rdzob 'khrul snang de dag yod ces smra
NK075(bu)002:1052: na bden gnyis so sor ston pa rnam par rtog
NK075(bu)002:1053: pa'i blos brtags dpyad byas pa yin la chos nyid
NK075(bu)002:1054: blo las 'das pa'i don rtogs pa ni ma yin
NK075(bu)002:1055: meda dgosa pasa / no // bden gnyis kyi don
NK075(bu)002:1056: sgra ci bzhin du 'dzin pa 'khrul zhing mi 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:1057: pa ma 'khrul pa'i dpe don dang /
NK075(bu)002:1059: gsang sngags bla med kyi don la blo shed ma
NK075(bu)002:1060: phye zhing tshig phyir 'brang ba dag gis gsang sngags
NK075(bu)002:1061: kyi rgyud gzhung du dag pa gsum dang mnyam gnyis
NK075(bu)002:1062: sam bzhi gnyis med dag bshad zer nas kun rdzob
NK075(bu)002:1063: 'khrul pa de nyid don dam la ldog dgos pas
NK075(bu)002:1064: dag ma dag gnyis su phye bas sgra ci bzhin
NK075(bu)002:1065: pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas snod bcud rgyud rnams ma
NK075(bu)002:1066: dag pa zhig dag nas dag pa gsum du 'dod
NK075(bu)002:1067: pa dang / 'khor 'das bzang ngan mi mnyam pa zhig dag pa mnyam gnyis su 'dod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1068: yul sems gnyis 'dzin dag nas gnyis med du 'dod
NK075(bu)002:1069: cing gzhung gi sgra don tsam la brten nas tshig
NK075(bu)002:1070: lta la gang gis zhen cing bsgrub pa'i phyogsa kyang
NK075(bu)002:1071: de dang mthun par skye bar 'dod na mi skye
NK075(bu)002:1072: pa ste / yul gang ga dar tsa'i mi yi dwags bzhin du bsod nams chung bas /
NK075(bu)002:1073: spos dri la mi gtsang ba /
NK075(bu)002:1074: dar zab la tsher mar mthong nas /
NK075(bu)002:1075: zas gos longs spyod rnams kyi spyod yul dang bral ba yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1076: zas nor longs spyod kyi 'dod pas ni gdung ba'i dpe de bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:1077: sems nyid rang byung ye shes kyi ngang la 'khor
NK075(bu)002:1078: 'das dbyer med kyang 'khrul pa'i blo 'di nyid las
NK075(bu)002:1079: 'das nas / ye shes logs nas skye bar 'dod
NK075(bu)002:1080: na gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pas bslus nas dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:1082: sems nyid 'khor 'das lhun grub kyi ngang la thob
NK075(bu)002:1083: bya'i 'bras bu logs na med de re dogs dang
NK075(bu)002:1084: bral kyang sangs rgyas zhes pa'i 'bras bu bzang po
NK075(bu)002:1085: zhig logs nas thob par 'dod nas ye rngama za
NK075(bu)002:1086: ba'i sgra ci bzhin pa 'dzin na 'khrul pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1087: mi 'dzin pa mi 'khrul pa ganga gis shes pa
NK075(bu)002:1088: ni gang ga dar tsa'i mi mi gtsang bar mthong
NK075(bu)002:1089: ba de mi bsod nams gyis spos drir mthong ba
NK075(bu)002:1090: dang / des mthong bas tsher ma'i nang na bzhag
NK075(bu)002:1091: kyang bsod nams can des na baza'a la mthong ba
NK075(bu)002:1092: dang / bzhin du / 'khor 'das kyi chos thamsa
NK075(bu)002:1093: cad rang rig pa byang chub semas kyi ngo bor
NK075(bu)002:1094: lhun grub tu rtogs na de ni lung ste sgro
NK075(bu)002:1095: skur lung ma bstan gyi skyon dang bral zhing sangs
NK075(bu)002:1096: rgyas kyi dgongs pa rtogs pa'i tshad mar bzhag pa
NK075(bu)002:1097: dang / bzhin du / yin no // btsal thabs yod med gnyis kar tshol ba 'khrul pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1099: gzhi gnas lugs kyi ngo bor phyogs gcig tu gang yang ma grub pas /
NK075(bu)002:1100: 'khor 'das kyi lta ba phyogs rer bzung nas gzhal
NK075(bu)002:1101: bya yoda pa las btsal na sgro btagsa pa ste
NK075(bu)002:1102: / gang la btags na gzhi chos dbyings ci'i ngo
NK075(bu)002:1103: bor ma grub pa la yod par sgro btags pa'o
NK075(bu)002:1104: / // phyogs med du chos thams cad lhun gyis grub kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1105: 'khor 'das gtan nas ma grub par 'dod nas gzhal
NK075(bu)002:1106: bya meda pa las btsal na skur pa btab par
NK075(bu)002:1108: chos thams cad lhun grub tu gnas pa la skur pa btab pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1109: gzhan yang sgro btags brgyad dang skur btab bcu'i rgyas bshad rnams ni lam rim ltar shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:1110: 'ga' zhig gis gzhi'i skabs 'dir yod pa las btsal na sgro btags /
NK075(bu)002:1111: med pa la btsal na skur pas btab pa gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)002:1112: 'og gi 'khrul gzhi yod med gnyis la 'khrul pa gnyis don gcig par bshad kyang mi 'thad de /
NK075(bu)002:1113: 'dir ni gzhi'i don de nyid lta bas phyogs rer bzung nas sgro btags /
NK075(bu)002:1114: phyogs med du shar ba dgag na skur pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:1115: 'og 'khrul gzhi yod med ni ma rig pa dngos
NK075(bu)002:1116: por bzung ba dang gzhi'i ngo bor ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:1117: gtan nas med par 'dod yin no //
NK075(bu)002:1118: yada med gnyis la btsal basa na nges shes ma skyes na /
NK075(bu)002:1119: de ni lung ma bstan du 'gyur ba yin ces
NK075(bu)002:1120: rgyas pa'i lung las de skad gsungs pa'i phyir na
NK075(bu)002:1121: rang raga pa byang chub sems kyi ngo bo la
NK075(bu)002:1122: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thams cad lhun grub tu
NK075(bu)002:1123: gnas pa'i yoda med phyogs gcig tu dgag sgrub byas
NK075(bu)002:1124: nas blun po'i blo yin no //
NK075(bu)002:1125: don dbyer med la lhun grub phyogs gcig par 'dzin 'khrul pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1127: yod med dgag sgrub blun pa'i blo yin pa de
NK075(bu)002:1128: bas na chos thams cad sems kyi de kho na
NK075(bu)002:1129: nyid lhun grub kho na yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1130: rgyu'i theg pa sems tsam pa'i 'khrul snang gi yul
NK075(bu)002:1131: thams cad la sems kyis kun tu brtags pa gsum
NK075(bu)002:1132: gyi sgo nas brtags pa'i snang ba sems yin cing
NK075(bu)002:1134: dag ma dag gi gzhan gyi dbang gis rig ma rig la 'khor 'das gnyis snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1135: 'gyur ba med pa'i yongas su grub pa ni chos kyi dbyings rang la gnas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1136: phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs grub ni de nyid mngon du gyur pa sa bon dang bcas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1137: de ltar kun brtags gzhan dbang yongs grub gsum bye
NK075(bu)002:1138: brag tu phye ba'i sgo nas snang ba sems yin
NK075(bu)002:1139: sems rang rig rang gsal du 'dod nas 'khrul pa
NK075(bu)002:1140: dag nas don dam stong nyid thog na lhun grub
NK075(bu)002:1141: tu 'dod pa dang gsang ba basngagasa kyi lhun grub
NK075(bu)002:1142: 'dra'am zhe na / mi 'dra ste thams cad lhun
NK075(bu)002:1143: grub kyi ngang la mtshan nyid gsum du dbye bar
NK075(bu)002:1144: bya ba de dag med pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1145: gsum du phye ba de med pa'i dbang gis des
NK075(bu)002:1146: na dbyer med kyang don la med de gnyis gcig
NK075(bu)002:1147: byed pa lta bu ma yin cing gdod ma nas
NK075(bu)002:1148: 'khor 'das lhun grub dbyer med du 'dod pa yin
NK075(bu)002:1149: no // 'o na mtshan nyid gsum du phyes na
NK075(bu)002:1150: rang rig rang gsal du 'dod na sems tsam rtogs
NK075(bu)002:1151: pa des ni dbu ma'i don dam smra bsam brjod
NK075(bu)002:1152: mada blo 'das tsam yang khyod sems tsam pa'i rgyud
NK075(bu)002:1153: thog na mi 'jog ste mi rtog pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1154: gsang ba sngags kyis ci ltar 'dod zer na /
NK075(bu)002:1155: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes des shes bya
NK075(bu)002:1156: 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos kun la rgyas btab
NK075(bu)002:1157: pas thams cad lhun grub tu gnas shing /
NK075(bu)002:1159: sems nyid kyi rang bzhin shes bya 'khor 'das kyi
NK075(bu)002:1160: chos kun dang dbyera med du gnas pa la 'o
NK075(bu)002:1161: na dbu mas kyang de ltar du 'dod pas 'dra'am
NK075(bu)002:1163: dper na meda pa bzhi ltar stong nyid spros bral
NK075(bu)002:1164: gyi ngang du gnas pa la'ang dbyer med mngon gyur
NK075(bu)002:1165: med pa ste / med pa gzhi gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:1166: mi srid pa'i chos bzhi ltar ye nas med de
NK075(bu)002:1167: dbu ma rab tu mi gnas pa ltar du kun
NK075(bu)002:1168: rdzob don dam la ye nas ma grub par 'dod
NK075(bu)002:1169: pa dang / 'dus byas bum pa ltar zhig nas
NK075(bu)002:1170: med de rnal 'byor spyod pa ltar rig ma rig
NK075(bu)002:1171: la 'khor 'das byung ste 'khrul pa zhig nas don
NK075(bu)002:1173: rdzas can gyi mtshan nyid tha dad pa ltar gcig la gcig med pa /
NK075(bu)002:1174: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma /
NK075(bu)002:1175: kun rdzob don dam gnyis tha dad stong pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1176: rgyu bkag nas 'bras bu med pa ltar bkag nas
NK075(bu)002:1177: med de nyan rang ltar rgyu rnam rtog bkag nas
NK075(bu)002:1178: mi rtog pa stong par bsgrub par 'dod pa de
NK075(bu)002:1179: rnams kyis stong pa phyogs gcig tu 'dod pas gsang
NK075(bu)002:1180: sngags dbyer med kyi don mi rtogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1181: 'khrul pa dang ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid kyi skabs
NK075(bu)002:1182: 'dir sa mig bdun yod pa'i dgos ched blang bar
NK075(bu)002:1183: bya'o // gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i rgyud kyi nges tshig la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1187: ye gdod ma nas bden pa rnam gnyis dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:1188: pa yin pa'i phyir kun rdzob dgag don dam bsgrub
NK075(bu)002:1189: tu meda pa'i ye nas smra bsam las grol te
NK075(bu)002:1190: / shes bya 'khor 'das thams cad ye shes rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:1191: ma rig ye shes sam don dam kun rdzob mi
NK075(bu)002:1192: mthun pa gnyis 'dus par lam pa'i blos so sor
NK075(bu)002:1194: 'khor ba'ang gzhi ye shes rang snang /
NK075(bu)002:1195: 'das pa'ang gzhi ye shes rang snang /
NK075(bu)002:1196: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu dang /
NK075(bu)002:1197: dpag bsam gyi shing la dgos 'dod sna tshogs 'byung
NK075(bu)002:1198: ba ltar gzhi sems nyid kyi ngo bo la 'khor
NK075(bu)002:1199: 'das dbyer med du gnas pa la /
NK075(bu)002:1200: bden pa gnyis sgra ji bzhin du so sor mi
NK075(bu)002:1201: 'dra bar rtog pa ni gsang sngags dbyer med kyi
NK075(bu)002:1202: don la 'khrul te ma rtogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1203: de bas bden pa gnyis su med pa yang ci ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:1204: nam mkha' dang 'aja'a sprin dbyer med du snang ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:1205: snang ba kun rdzob dang stong pa don dam kun
NK075(bu)002:1206: tu sems nyid rang gsal bas dbyer med du rang
NK075(bu)002:1207: bzhin ngang gis 'khor 'das gnyis su shar nas snang
NK075(bu)002:1208: ba'o // 'o na ngang snang ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:1209: shes mkhan gyi sems badga dang shes bya'i yul gzhan
NK075(bu)002:1210: du ma brtagsa pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang las
NK075(bu)002:1211: ma g.yos kyang / shes bya ma 'dres par so
NK075(bu)002:1212: sora snang zhing rang rang gi las mthun pa'i gzugas
NK075(bu)002:1213: su snang ba de lta bu yi don ni ngang
NK075(bu)002:1214: du snang ba zhes sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las de
NK075(bu)002:1216: don de nyid 'dir drang zhing bgrod pa dang go yang sla rtogs kyang sla'o //
NK075(bu)002:1217: 'o na 'khrul snang 'khor bar shar dus gzhi chos nyid las g.yos sam zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:1218: chos nyid rang las ma g.yos te gzung 'dzin phyin
NK075(bu)002:1219: ci loga la shar dus de nyid yang dag pa
NK075(bu)002:1222: ma rig pa de nyid ye shes su gsal ba
NK075(bu)002:1223: dang nyon mongas sdug bsngal de nyid byang chub mchoga
NK075(bu)002:1224: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin zhes rgyas pa'i lung
NK075(bu)002:1225: las de skad gsungsa pa'i don gyis na /
NK075(bu)002:1226: ma rig de las 'pho nas ye shes logs nas
NK075(bu)002:1227: skye ba med de dper na mar me gsal ba'i
NK075(bu)002:1228: dus na mun pa logs su ma spangs mun pa
NK075(bu)002:1229: ngo bo nyid dang mi ldan pas mun pa de
NK075(bu)002:1230: nyid snang bar gsal ba yin kyang blun pos rgyu
NK075(bu)002:1231: mtshan nyid sa mun pa nag pa dang snang ba
NK075(bu)002:1232: gsal ba gnyis res mos su mthong nas bzung ba
NK075(bu)002:1233: bzhin du ma rig ye shes gnyis tha dad dag
NK075(bu)002:1234: rtog tu 'dod pa'i gnyis med las 'khrul pa dang
NK075(bu)002:1235: / mkhas pa gsang sngags pas mun pa snang ba
NK075(bu)002:1236: gnyis ngo bo tha dad kyis ris mi 'dra ba
NK075(bu)002:1237: mi lta ba bzhin du 'khora ba dang chos nyid
NK075(bu)002:1238: kyang de bzhin du ngo bo tha dad ma yin
NK075(bu)002:1239: / no // 'o na 'khrul pa rang chos nyid
NK075(bu)002:1240: yin na sems can la sangs rgyas thob mi dgos
NK075(bu)002:1241: shing lam thos bsam sgom gsum don med du mi
NK075(bu)002:1243: ma yin te sems nyid 'khrul snang sna tshogs su spangsa pa med para shar kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1244: sems nyid rang gi ngo bo la 'khrul pa gtan
NK075(bu)002:1245: nas grub ma myong bar kun dang bral ba ste
NK075(bu)002:1246: / dper na man ngag pun+da r+ai ka la dkar
NK075(bu)002:1247: ba min pa nag pa'i skyon med pa lta bu'i
NK075(bu)002:1248: / don gyis / gzhi gnas lugs rang gi ngo
NK075(bu)002:1249: bo la 'khor 'das kyi tha snyad med kyang gnas
NK075(bu)002:1250: / don gyis / pa la gzhi / ma rtogs pa la 'khrul pa rtogs pa la lam /
NK075(bu)002:1251: mthar phyin pa la 'bras bu sangs rgyas zhes tha snyad bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:1254: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba de ka la skabs kyis rgyud ces bya ste /
NK075(bu)002:1255: gang zhig dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel ba dang ldan pas na rgyud do //
NK075(bu)002:1257: gzhi la shes bya ye ldan gyi dgos pa tshang
NK075(bu)002:1258: zhing gzhi dang lam gnyis shes bya shes byed du
NK075(bu)002:1259: 'brel la gzhi dang 'brasa bu gnyis ngo bo bdag
NK075(bu)002:1261: brjod byed tshig gi rgyud 'di nyid la gang zag
NK075(bu)002:1262: gzu lums can dang ras chod can dgag pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:1263: tshig 'achala zhing 'khrugs nas yod kyang don la dgos
NK075(bu)002:1265: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i 'brela pa gsum dang ldan pa'i don gyi tan+t+ra ste rgyud ces bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:1266: gong gi lam dang 'bras bu 'chol tshang zer ba yang /
NK075(bu)002:1268: don la brtags na chos tshang ba zer ba 'dra /
NK075(bu)002:1269: 'di bris pa'i dbang yin min ba rtag par bya /
NK075(bu)002:1270: don la lam dang 'bras chos rnams rang la yod pa la gzhi /
NK075(bu)002:1272: mngon du gyur pa la 'bras bu yin par gsung /
NK075(bu)002:1274: de las gzhan pa'i thob bya med //
NK075(bu)002:1275: kun kyang smin zin bgrod pa min //
NK075(bu)002:1276: de nyid lam gyi ngo bo yin //
NK075(bu)002:1280: rang bzhin bcos bslad dang bral ba /
NK075(bu)002:1281: snang ba ni rang rig pa'i rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba /
NK075(bu)002:1282: gang zhig dgos pa tshang 'brel pa dang ldan pas
NK075(bu)002:1283: rgyud kyi tshig don gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na
NK075(bu)002:1284: le'u ste yas bgrangs dang po'i don du gada'o //
NK075(bu)002:1285: 'khrul pa'i snang ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1292: 'khrul pa'i gzhi dang 'khrul tshul dang 'khrul pa'i rang
NK075(bu)002:1293: bzhin gsum gyi sdom tshig des 'khrul pa'i don 'og
NK075(bu)002:1294: rgyas bshad de nges par shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:1296: de la gsum ste 'khrul gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:1301: gzhi sgro bkur dang bral ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1303: rigs drug gi 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi
NK075(bu)002:1304: semas nyid ni dper na nor bu rin chen la
NK075(bu)002:1305: rta dang / glang po che la sogs pa rang
NK075(bu)002:1306: rgyud du grub pa med kyang dgos 'dod sna tshogs
NK075(bu)002:1307: 'byung ba bzhin du sems la dngos po dkar dmar
NK075(bu)002:1308: la sogs par 'khrul pa rang rgyud du ma grub
NK075(bu)002:1309: rta dang / kyang / 'gro drug gis sems can
NK075(bu)002:1310: gyis ci ltara rang rang gi bsam pa ltar du
NK075(bu)002:1311: rta dang / kyang / / shar nas snang ba la /
NK075(bu)002:1312: 'khrul gzhi yoda byas pas sems ngos bzung dang bral
NK075(bu)002:1313: med byas pas 'khrul snang sna tshogs su shar bas
NK075(bu)002:1314: yod ces sgro btags pa dang med ces skur btab
NK075(bu)002:1315: dang bral zhing sems nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK075(bu)002:1316: gnas pa la // 'khrul gzhi yod pa las 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:1318: 'khrul gzhi rang rgyud du med pa la yod par
NK075(bu)002:1319: sgro 'dogas des dbang bsgyur nas 'khrul pa rang rgyud
NK075(bu)002:1320: du 'byung bar 'dod pa'i gang zag phyogs re ba
NK075(bu)002:1321: rnamas kyis gang la sgro 'dogs na semsa nyid dmigsa
NK075(bu)002:1322: su med pa ngos bzung dang bral ba la tshul
NK075(bu)002:1323: ci ltar du 'dod na 'khrul gzhi ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:1324: zhes bya ba dngos po can cig rang rgyud du
NK075(bu)002:1325: yod nas 'khrul pa'i gzhir gnas zhes smra ba la
NK075(bu)002:1326: / skyon ci yod na bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:1327: 'khrul pa rang rgyud du smra ba'i de yi rigs
NK075(bu)002:1328: rgyud mu stegs rtag par lta bar ltung ba dang
NK075(bu)002:1329: / sol ba la dung mi 'ong ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:1330: gzhi 'khor ba'i mthar ltung ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1331: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis 'khrul pa mi sel ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1332: gzhi gzung 'dzin can du thal ba'i skyon dang bzhi 'ong ngo //
NK075(bu)002:1333: 'khrul gzhi med pa la 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:1335: gzhi'i ngo bor 'khor 'das lhun grub tu gnas kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1336: 'khrul pa dang gzhi gnyis mi gcig ces skur pa
NK075(bu)002:1337: btab pa'i gang zag phyogs re ba 'ga' zhig gis
NK075(bu)002:1338: ni 'di ltar du bskur pa btab ste /
NK075(bu)002:1339: gang la skur pa btab na /
NK075(bu)002:1340: gzhi 'khor 'das lhun grub yin pa la tshul ci
NK075(bu)002:1341: ltar du btab na gzhi de dang bsam pa'i blo
NK075(bu)002:1342: gnyis mi 'dra bar so sor rtog ste /
NK075(bu)002:1343: dper na ri bong de la ra de ni mi
NK075(bu)002:1344: srid pa bzhin du gzhi ka dag gi ngo bo
NK075(bu)002:1345: la 'khrul pa ye nas med ces smra /
NK075(bu)002:1346: zhen pa blo'i ngo bo la gzhi ka dag med
NK075(bu)002:1347: do zhes smra na'ang skyon bzhii yod de skur pa
NK075(bu)002:1348: btab pa'i gang zag gang yin pa de mu stegs
NK075(bu)002:1349: chad lta bar ltung ba dang gzhi de dang blo
NK075(bu)002:1350: de gnyis tha dad cing mi 'dra na ri bong
NK075(bu)002:1351: gi rwa la sogs pa mi srid pa'i dpe kun
NK075(bu)002:1352: gzhi blo tha dad du smra mi de la 'byung
NK075(bu)002:1353: ste gzhi la ltos na myang 'das kyi mthar lhung
NK075(bu)002:1355: blo la ltos na 'khrul pa kun 'byung bas sangs
NK075(bu)002:1356: rgyas mi srid pa dang 'khrul pa glo bur du
NK075(bu)002:1357: 'byung bas 'khor ba la thog ma 'byung ba dang
NK075(bu)002:1358: 'ang gi sgras mthar sangs rgyas na'ang 'khrul pa glo
NK075(bu)002:1359: bur du 'ong nas sems can du 'byung srid do
NK075(bu)002:1360: // gnyis med phyogs gcig pa las 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:1362: gang zag la la 'ga' zhig gis ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:1363: gnyis 'dzin las ni ldog cing dag pa'i 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)002:1365: de ngo ma shes pa la 'khor bar snang zhes
NK075(bu)002:1366: smra na'ang lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa med
NK075(bu)002:1367: pa'i chos nyid kho na'i ngang yin na skyon yod
NK075(bu)002:1368: de / rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa bas ma rig
NK075(bu)002:1369: pa de nyid rnam byang gi rten tsam byed de
NK075(bu)002:1370: de / / bag chags bzang po'i sogs gzhi byed
NK075(bu)002:1371: pa dang 'khrul pa'i gzhi ma kho na yin par
NK075(bu)002:1372: 'dod kyang rnam byang gyi rten pa mi dgos 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:1373: ba'i gzhir ma rig pa med na 'khor ba 'byung
NK075(bu)002:1374: bar mi btub ste ci'i phyir mi btub na /
NK075(bu)002:1375: 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa dang rkyen las nyon
NK075(bu)002:1376: spang bas khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can 'byung bar
NK075(bu)002:1377: rigsa pa min te mi 'byung ngo //
NK075(bu)002:1378: phyogs re ba dang thun mong ma yin pa'i gnyis med las 'khrul pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1380: kun gzhi don dam chos nyid kyi ngo bo la
NK075(bu)002:1381: 'khrul gzhi yod byas pas ngos bzung dang bral med
NK075(bu)002:1382: byas pas 'khrul snang sna tshogs su shar bas 'khor
NK075(bu)002:1383: 'das kyi rigsa tha dad du med cing dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:1384: du gnas pa la rig ma rig las 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)002:1385: byung yang 'khor ba de yi rgyu ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:1386: dang rkyen las nyon de nyid kyi rang bzhin mi
NK075(bu)002:1387: dmigs pa de myang 'das kyi rang bzhin yin pas
NK075(bu)002:1388: dper na sman ga pur gyis tsha nad can la
NK075(bu)002:1389: phan grang nad can la gnod kyang ga pur la
NK075(bu)002:1390: ngo bo gcig pa ji lta ba bzhin du shes
NK075(bu)002:1391: bya 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cada ma
NK075(bu)002:1392: lus pa kun gyi rgyu dbyer med gcig tu gnas
NK075(bu)002:1393: pa las rig ma rig gi rkyen gyis 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)002:1394: mi mthun pa khyad par so sor shar nas snang
NK075(bu)002:1395: zhes rgyud la de skad gsungsa pa'i phyir na rig
NK075(bu)002:1396: ma rig gis rkyen gyis phye bas 'khor 'das so
NK075(bu)002:1397: sor snang ba'o // 'o na ci ltar du snang
NK075(bu)002:1398: na rgyas pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du
NK075(bu)002:1399: gsung ste lam rgyud lnga 'gro ba rigs drug 'khor
NK075(bu)002:1400: ba'i lus sna tshogs su snang ba ni sems 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:1401: pa'i rnam rtog gang shar dang mthun pa'i las gang
NK075(bu)002:1402: bsags kyi lus su snang ngo //
NK075(bu)002:1403: sku dang ye shes dbyer med pa sku'i mchog de
NK075(bu)002:1404: bzhin gshegs pa'i sku skye 'jig dang bral ba rdo
NK075(bu)002:1405: rje'i sku ye shes lnga'i rang 'od kyi gzugs su
NK075(bu)002:1406: snang ba ni rang sems rtogs pa'i ngo ka dang
NK075(bu)002:1407: mthun pa'i ye shes lnga'i rang 'od las rgyal ba
NK075(bu)002:1409: zhes lung las 'khor 'das tha dad du shar dus sems nyid du gcig par gsungs pas /
NK075(bu)002:1410: de bas na 'khor 'das kyi chos kun semas kyi
NK075(bu)002:1411: de bzhin nyid du gcig kyang mthong ba dag pa
NK075(bu)002:1412: dang ma dag pa gnyis ka'i rkyen gyis phye bas
NK075(bu)002:1413: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi spyod yul mi 'dra ba so
NK075(bu)002:1414: sor snang ngo // snang ba'i dus na gzhi chos
NK075(bu)002:1415: nyid kyi ngo bo de la 'khrul pa ma spangs
NK075(bu)002:1416: te 'khrul snang sna tshogs su shar shar dus 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:1417: pa'i ngo bo nyid du mi dmigs pa'i phyir 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:1418: gzhi'i mtshan ma yod ces sgro btags pa dang med
NK075(bu)002:1419: ces skur pas btab pa med de dbyer med du
NK075(bu)002:1420: sor snang ngo // gnas pa la / gang zag
NK075(bu)002:1421: phyogs 'dzin can gyis dbyer med la 'khrul pa mi
NK075(bu)002:1422: 'thad de gzhi rang bzhin ye nas rnam dag yin
NK075(bu)002:1423: la 'khrul pa ni glo bur gyis dri ma yin
NK075(bu)002:1424: sor snang ngo // gnas pa la / pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:1425: / zer nas dogas pa gzugs pa la'ang skyon med
NK075(bu)002:1426: de lta bas sems nyid gtan la pheb pa'i dus
NK075(bu)002:1427: su 'khrul snang gi sems 'di nyid ngos bzung dang
NK075(bu)002:1428: bral bas kun rdzob dagga pa med cing don dam
NK075(bu)002:1429: pas gnas lugs kyang logs nas blang du meda pa'i
NK075(bu)002:1430: sor snang ngo // gnas pa la / pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:1431: / phyir / phyogs re ba'i grub mtha'i gzhung ltar
NK075(bu)002:1432: du bden gnyis kyis dgag bsgrub ni gsang sngags kyi
NK075(bu)002:1433: gzhung 'di nyid mi dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:1435: skad yangs par byas la lan gdab pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1436: dog par byas la lan gdab pa gnyis las /
NK075(bu)002:1438: 'khrul gzhi yod med dbyer med gsum ka las kyang 'khrul te /
NK075(bu)002:1439: de gsum gang rung cig kho na las 'khrul pa ni ma yin no //
NK075(bu)002:1441: 'khrul gzhi yod pa las 'khrul te dpe thag khra
NK075(bu)002:1442: la sbrul 'dzin gyi shes pa zhugs pa lta bu'o
