NK075(bu)002:1443: // de yang a ro'i thig le'i skor las /
NK075(bu)002:1446: 'khrul gzhi med pa las kyang 'khrul pa 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:1447: dpe thang phrom zos pa'i rgan mo'i mig sngar nam mkha' la skra shad 'dzags pa lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:1449: nyi ma'i dkyil na mun med ltar //
NK075(bu)002:1450: ye shes rang snang ma gtogs pa //
NK075(bu)002:1451: nyon mongs 'khor ba ngang gis med //
NK075(bu)002:1454: dpe sman ga pur de tsha nad can la sman dang /
NK075(bu)002:1455: rlung nad can la dug tu 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK075(bu)002:1458: sman gyis phan gnod ci bzhin du //
NK075(bu)002:1459: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig pas //
NK075(bu)002:1461: mdor na rang bzhin rnam dag ye nas dri ma dang bral bar gnas kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1462: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa lhan cig skyes
NK075(bu)002:1463: pa'i ma rig pas rgyu byas rang snang la yul
NK075(bu)002:1464: du bzung bas gzung 'dzin gnyis snang kun brtags kyi
NK075(bu)002:1465: ma rig pas rkyen byas glo bur du 'khrul lo
NK075(bu)002:1466: // skad dog par byas nas lan gdab pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:1467: gzhi rang bzhin rnam dag yod med dbu ma'i mtha'
NK075(bu)002:1468: las grol ba de rang ngo rang gis ma shes
NK075(bu)002:1469: pas 'khrul lo // de yang 'di nyid kyi gzhi
NK075(bu)002:1470: sgro skur dang bral bar bshad pa'i skabs ltar du
NK075(bu)002:1471: pas 'khrul lo // / drug gi 'gro ba thams cad kyis //
NK075(bu)002:1472: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
NK075(bu)002:1473: ci ltar bsam pa snang ba la //
NK075(bu)002:1474: 'khrul gzhi yod med sgro skur bral //
NK075(bu)002:1476: 'o na de la 'khrul gzhi zhes bya ba de bde gshegs snying po la 'dod dam /
NK075(bu)002:1477: ma rig pa rgyu dang bcas pa la 'dod /
NK075(bu)002:1479: 'khrul pa'i ngo bo mi rnyed par 'gyur /
NK075(bu)002:1480: phyi ma ltar na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mi rnyed par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:1482: brgyud pa'am rgyu bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po /
NK075(bu)002:1485: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las //
NK075(bu)002:1486: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sbrul //
NK075(bu)002:1490: ma rig pas ngo ma shes te 'khrul pa spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1492: gong gi dbyer med las 'khrul pa ci ltar 'byung tshul ni /
NK075(bu)002:1493: ma rig pa dang rig pa ye shes dbyer med mtshungsa par ldan pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:1494: 'o na 'khrul pa ci ltar du 'byung na 'das
NK075(bu)002:1495: ma 'ongs da ltar dus gsum du chos nyid rang
NK075(bu)002:1496: byung gi ye shes dang rgyun du 'grogs kyang rang
NK075(bu)002:1497: ngo rang gis ma shes pas chos nyid kyis don
NK075(bu)002:1498: mngon sum du mthong ba med de dpe miga rang
NK075(bu)002:1499: gis mig rang tshur la mi mthong phar la yul
NK075(bu)002:1500: sna tshogs su mthong ba bzhin du sems kyis kyang
NK075(bu)002:1501: de lta bur tshur la rang mi rig /
NK075(bu)002:1502: phar la yul sna tshogs su shar ba'i stobs kyis
NK075(bu)002:1503: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i dus su snga phyi'i
NK075(bu)002:1504: chos thams cad lung btagsa pa ste ming dang dngos
NK075(bu)002:1505: po sna tshogs su btags pa nor sa'i spyod yul
NK075(bu)002:1506: sna tshogs su rgyun mi 'chad par shar ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:1507: bye brag tu phye ste bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1511: 'khrul tshul rgyas par bshad pa'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:1512: 'khrul pa'i dus dang 'khrul pa'i rgyu dang 'khrul pa'i rkyen dang /
NK075(bu)002:1513: 'khrul tshul dang 'khrul pa'i ngo bo dang 'khrul pa'i
NK075(bu)002:1514: rang bzhin dang 'khrul pa'i nyes dmigs dang bdun gyi
NK075(bu)002:1515: sgo nas 'og 'khrul pa'i don rgyas par bshad de
NK075(bu)002:1516: shes par bya'o // rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1521: tan+t+ra ste rgyud sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa de nyid las gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:1522: 'di lta ste thog ma med pa'i dus nas semsa
NK075(bu)002:1523: rang ngo ma shes te kha yan du btang zhing
NK075(bu)002:1524: gzung 'dzin phyin ci log la 'jola nyog tu spyod
NK075(bu)002:1525: cing 'khrul lo // gal te thog ma med pa
NK075(bu)002:1526: nas 'khrul pa ma byung zhing gzod glo bur du
NK075(bu)002:1527: 'khrul pa byung bar gyur na dus 'di tsam nas
NK075(bu)002:1528: byung zhes 'jig rten la thog ma'ang 'byung bar gyur
NK075(bu)002:1529: cing 'khrul lo // ba'i skyon yod / 'o na
NK075(bu)002:1530: 'jig rten la thog ma byung na skyon ci yod
NK075(bu)002:1531: na 'khrul pa'i glo bur du byung bas 'khrul pa
NK075(bu)002:1532: dang ye shes mi gcig pas lam thos bsam sgom
NK075(bu)002:1533: gsum don med du 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:1534: mthar sangs rgyas nas 'khrul pa glo bur du byung
NK075(bu)002:1535: nas sems can du 'gyur srid pa'i skyon yod pas
NK075(bu)002:1536: dus thog ma med pa nas 'khrul lo //
NK075(bu)002:1540: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu bde gshegs snying po dang /
NK075(bu)002:1541: mtshungsa par ldan pa'i rgyu ma rig pa dang 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:1542: pa dang lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK075(bu)002:1543: dang nyer len gyi rgyu dus gsum 'phen pa'i rgyu
NK075(bu)002:1544: las kyi bag chags smin nas skye ba la mi
NK075(bu)002:1545: 'da' ba dang lnga yis rgyas par bshad na 'di
NK075(bu)002:1549: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)002:1551: ma bcos pa rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:1552: bo la 'khor 'das kyi rigs tha dad dang rgyud
NK075(bu)002:1553: tha dad du med pa de nyid 'khrul pa de
NK075(bu)002:1554: nyid kyi rgyur gnas kyang snang ba'i phyir tan+t+ra ste
NK075(bu)002:1555: rgyud rgyas pa las kyang sngar dus thog ma med
NK075(bu)002:1556: pa nas dbyer med du 'khrul gsungsa pa'i don gyi
NK075(bu)002:1557: na / rgyu la lnga yod pa'i dang po'i ngo
NK075(bu)002:1558: bo nyid kyi rgyu rang byung ye shes kyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:1559: bo de nyid kyang 'khrul pa las gzhan du min
NK075(bu)002:1560: te gzhi chos nyid de ka 'khrul snang sna tshogs
NK075(bu)002:1561: su shar ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu bde bar
NK075(bu)002:1563: gong gi sngar gsungs zhes pa 'di la /
NK075(bu)002:1566: thog ma med nas sems yan btang //
NK075(bu)002:1567: phyin ci log la 'jol nyog spyad //
NK075(bu)002:1568: de la ngos bzung bzhed dang /
NK075(bu)002:1571: sman gyi phan gnod ci bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:1572: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig pas /
NK075(bu)002:1573: 'di yin pa 'dra bas brtag par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:1576: sngon gzhi'i skabs kyi dpe me long dang g.ya' nam
NK075(bu)002:1577: mkha' dang sprin gyi dpe rnam pa gnyis ltar du
NK075(bu)002:1578: gdoda ma nas gzhi chos nyid dang ma rig pa
NK075(bu)002:1579: mtshungs par ldan pas ma rig pa ye shes gnyis
NK075(bu)002:1580: su med pas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu lhan cig skyes
NK075(bu)002:1582: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)002:1584: yul yul can kun tu rtog pa gzung 'dzin rnam
NK075(bu)002:1585: pa gnyis po 'di theg pa spyi skad dang bstun
NK075(bu)002:1586: na lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu yin /
NK075(bu)002:1587: nyer len gyi rgyu dug gsum yin par bshad /
NK075(bu)002:1588: 'di de gnyis lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu la ngos bzung nas sa gzhung sprad pa nor ba 'dra /
NK075(bu)002:1589: de'i rkyen gyis brtas bslang pa /
NK075(bu)002:1590: 'dir nyer len la ngos bzung yang /
NK075(bu)002:1591: 'di las bsag tshul yin pas 'phen rgyu'i ngo bo yin /
NK075(bu)002:1592: 'od ma lta bur phyi mar snang ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:1593: 'phen pa'i ngo bo'i dpe kho na byung /
NK075(bu)002:1594: nye bar len pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)002:1596: gomas pa ni rgyun chags nas stobs zhugs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:1597: dang po ma rig pa kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK075(bu)002:1598: de'i thog nas skad gcig snga ma yul phyi ma
NK075(bu)002:1599: yul can du shar nas gzung 'dzin ngo bo gnyis
NK075(bu)002:1600: byung / gzung 'dzin de dang dus mnyam du bzang po la 'dod chags /
NK075(bu)002:1602: bar pa la gti mug 'byung ba dang dug gsum skyes pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:1603: 'khrul pa nye bar len pa'i rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)002:1606: nyon mongs de'i rkyen gyis las bsag tshul ni kun gzhi la bag chags kyi mthu brtasa pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1607: de'i bag chags sad cing bslangs pas 'bras bu nying mtshams sbyor ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:1608: dpe shing gzhu 'od ma la mda' gang rdzogs par
NK075(bu)002:1609: 'phen nas 'phen pa bar dor chud mi za nas
NK075(bu)002:1610: 'phen pas sa la phog pa lta bur las kyi
NK075(bu)002:1611: sa bon rtsub mo des 'phangs nas phyi mar lus
NK075(bu)002:1612: su snang zhing las 'bras chud mi za ba ni
NK075(bu)002:1613: 'phen pa'i rgyu'o // rkyen la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1617: gnas khams gsum 'di na gnas pa'i 'gro ba sems
NK075(bu)002:1618: can kun gyi skye shi 'khor ba'i kha brgyud nas
NK075(bu)002:1619: mtho ris dang ngan song 'khor ba'i rkyen ni las
NK075(bu)002:1620: nyon gyi stobs smin par byed /
NK075(bu)002:1621: las dkar po dge ba bcu dang las nag po
NK075(bu)002:1622: mi dge ba bcu smin pa yis khams gsum dang
NK075(bu)002:1624: dge bcu'i mtho ris gnas bcu /
NK075(bu)002:1625: mi dge ba bcus ngan song gnas bcu ste 'dod khams kyi gnas nyi shur skye bar byed do //
NK075(bu)002:1626: dge bcu'i steng du mi g.yo ba'i las te tshangs
NK075(bu)002:1627: pa'i gnas zhes tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan dang
NK075(bu)002:1628: po rtog dpyod / gnyis pa dga' bde /
NK075(bu)002:1630: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin dang bzhi la brtan pa
NK075(bu)002:1631: thob cing smin pa gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun
NK075(bu)002:1632: du skye zhing de'i spyod yul du snang ba dang
NK075(bu)002:1636: yod min med min gyi skye mched dang snyomsa par
NK075(bu)002:1637: 'jug pa bzhi'i mthu dang ldan zhing smin na khams
NK075(bu)002:1638: 'og ma la ltos na shes pa zab pa rtse
NK075(bu)002:1639: mo zhes gzugs med bzhi'i spyod yul du snang ste
NK075(bu)002:1642: rgyu spyi kar btang na mi /
NK075(bu)002:1643: 'bras bu spyi kar btang na lha ma yin stod
NK075(bu)002:1644: ris lhar brtsis pas rgyud lnga'i sems can kun gyi
NK075(bu)002:1645: lam du dug lnga nyams su len te /
NK075(bu)002:1646: smin nas rigs drug tu skye ba'i rkyen byed ces
NK075(bu)002:1647: tan+t+ra ste rgyud sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u don gsum
NK075(bu)002:1648: pa sa ma ya dam tshig rtsa ba bco lnga
NK075(bu)002:1649: ston pa'i le'u las 'byung bas der blta'o //
NK075(bu)002:1650: 'o na rgyu'i dus su las nyon gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:1651: rkyen gyi dus su las nyon gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:1653: spyir 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa /
NK075(bu)002:1655: de gnyis kyis bskyed pa'i 'bras bu khams gsum yin par bshad /
NK075(bu)002:1657: rgyu la btang ba'i rgyu mtshan ni 'khor ba la rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum byung yang /
NK075(bu)002:1659: rkyen las nyon yan chad rgyu la 'gro dgos /
NK075(bu)002:1660: rgyu ma rig pa shes sgrib yin pa la /
NK075(bu)002:1662: nyon mongs la las sgrib skye /
NK075(bu)002:1663: las sgrib kyi 'bras bu 'khor ba bskyed pa la dgongs nas /
NK075(bu)002:1664: mtshan nyid theg pa'i lugs la 'khor ba'i rgyu kun 'byung gi bden pa la /
NK075(bu)002:1666: las kyi kun 'byung gnyis rgyu la bzhag nas /
NK075(bu)002:1667: 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi bden pa bskyed par 'dod do //
NK075(bu)002:1668: de bzhin du sgyu 'phrul rtsa bshad gang nas kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1669: rkyen las nyon gnyis dang bcas pa 'khor ba bskyed pa'i rgyu yin gsungs /
NK075(bu)002:1670: rkyen gyi dus su las nyon gnyis bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)002:1671: gong gi rgyu lnga po'i nang nas spyir 'khor ba
NK075(bu)002:1672: tsam gyi rgyu ma gtogs pa khams gsum so sor
NK075(bu)002:1673: bskyed pa'i rgyu rkyen ma byung bas /
NK075(bu)002:1674: rkyen gyi dus su las dge mi dge g.yo ba gsum gyis khams gsum bskyed lugs dang /
NK075(bu)002:1675: dug lngas rgyud lnga'i sems can bskyed par shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:1678: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten phyi rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis nang bcud kyi sems can /
NK075(bu)002:1679: nang rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi 'khor lo'i tshul du
NK075(bu)002:1680: gnas khams gsum du bcud 'gro ba rigs drug las
NK075(bu)002:1681: kyi dbang gis yang nas yang du bskor ba'ang /
NK075(bu)002:1682: khams gsum gyi snang tshul gyi cha yi phye bas bcu gnyis 'dod khams la tshang ste /
NK075(bu)002:1683: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rgyu 'bras bcu gnyis las /
NK075(bu)002:1692: 'byung ba lnga dus kyi 'gyur ba dang drug go //
NK075(bu)002:1693: nang bcud kyi sems can rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi tshul du 'khor ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:1694: de yang ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed /
NK075(bu)002:1695: 'du byed rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa /
NK075(bu)002:1704: rga shi rnams lugs 'byung du zo chu'i khyud mo bzhin du 'khor ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:1705: gzugs khams dang gzugs med la rten 'brel bcu gnyis tshang ba'i nges pa med de /
NK075(bu)002:1706: gzugs khams la ma rig pa 'khor ba'i rgyu yin pas yod /
NK075(bu)002:1707: 'du byed la g.yo mi g.yo ba'i 'du byed gnyis las 'dir mi g.yo ba'i 'du byed yod /
NK075(bu)002:1708: rnam par shes pas las kyi skye gnas su 'khrid par byed /
NK075(bu)002:1709: ming dang gzugs kyis lus 'dzin par byed /
NK075(bu)002:1710: skye mched drug gis lus rdzogs par byed pas /
NK075(bu)002:1711: 'dir rdzus skyes yin pas de gsum med /
NK075(bu)002:1712: reg pa gsum 'dus nas yul yongs su gcod par byed /
NK075(bu)002:1713: tshor bas yul la nye bar longs spyod par byed /
NK075(bu)002:1714: sred pas yul bde ba la chags pa dang gsum
NK075(bu)002:1715: yod len pas rnam par shes pa skye ba dang
NK075(bu)002:1717: srid pas las nus pa thog med du gyur pas
NK075(bu)002:1718: 'dir las mngon gyur bsag tu med pas len srid
NK075(bu)002:1719: gnyis med / skye shi thog mtha' yin pas yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1720: rten 'brel bcu gnyis la bdun mngon gyur du yod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1721: gzugs med la skye shi 'khor ba'i thog mtha' yin pas yod /
NK075(bu)002:1722: ma rig pa'i thog na 'gog pas de gsum yod la gzhan mngon gyur med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1723: yang na khams gsum gyi lus yod med kyi chas
NK075(bu)002:1724: phye bas lus can rnams la mngon du 'khor la
NK075(bu)002:1725: / lus med rnams la bag chags kyi tshul du 'khor ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:1728: 'khrul pa'i rtog pa brtan pa'i 'khrul snang gi spyod
NK075(bu)002:1729: yul sna tshogs su shar ba ni 'khrul pa'i ngo
NK075(bu)002:1730: bo ste / spyir 'gro ba rigs drug so so'i
NK075(bu)002:1731: snang tshul mi 'dra ba phyi nang snod bcud sna
NK075(bu)002:1732: tshogs su snang ba dang bye brag tu rigs drug
NK075(bu)002:1733: re re la'ang lus la bzang ngan dang longs spyod
NK075(bu)002:1734: la che chung dang tshe la ring thung dang las
NK075(bu)002:1735: bo ste / dkar nag dang / mtho ris kyi
NK075(bu)002:1736: bde ba ngan song gi sdug bsngal dang bar ma
NK075(bu)002:1737: do btang snyoms tha dad sna tshogs su snang ba
NK075(bu)002:1738: bo ste / dkar nag dang / ni / 'khrul pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK075(bu)002:1739: 'o na 'khrul snang sna tshogs su shar ba 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:1740: snang sna tshogs su shar ba 'khrul pa'i ngo bo
NK075(bu)002:1741: yin na / gong gzhi'i skabs na /
NK075(bu)002:1742: 'khor 'das ngo bo tha dad na skyon yod /
NK075(bu)002:1743: ces pa dang 'gal lam zhe na mi 'gal te /
NK075(bu)002:1744: 'khrul pa sna tshogs su shar ba'i ngo bo de
NK075(bu)002:1745: nyid ngos bzung dang bral bas chos nyid rang byung
NK075(bu)002:1746: gi ye shes kyi ngo bo yin te /
NK075(bu)002:1748: 'khor ba spangs par gyur pa yi //
NK075(bu)002:1749: mya ngan 'das khyod mi bzhed kyis //
NK075(bu)002:1750: 'khor ba mi dmigs pa yis ni //
NK075(bu)002:1751: zhi nyid mgon po khyod kyis bstan //
NK075(bu)002:1752: ces pas 'khor 'das ngo bo gcig pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1755: dper na sgyu ma mkhan gyis rdzas sngags gang gi
NK075(bu)002:1756: sgo nas sgyu mas nor rdzas rta glang la sogs
NK075(bu)002:1757: gzhan bslus pa'i ched du sprul kyang mi rnams kyis
NK075(bu)002:1758: bden par bzung ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:1759: gzhi chos nyid la 'khrul pa med kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1760: rang ngo ma shes pas 'khrul snang nor ba'i spyod
NK075(bu)002:1761: yul sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin du shar nas snang
NK075(bu)002:1762: ba'o // 'o na 'khor 'das gnyis kyi rang bzhin mi gcig gam zhe na ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:1763: 'khrul snang gi rang bzhin de nyid myang 'das kyi
NK075(bu)002:1764: rang bzhin yin te dbu ma byang chub sems 'grel
NK075(bu)002:1765: las / me yi rang bzhin tsha ba dang //
NK075(bu)002:1766: bu ram rang bzhin mngar ba ltar //
NK075(bu)002:1767: de bzhin chos rnams thams cad kyi //
NK075(bu)002:1768: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du byos //
NK075(bu)002:1772: srid pa gsum gyi rtsa ba'i nyes dmigas kyi rgyu
NK075(bu)002:1773: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa las byung bas
NK075(bu)002:1774: sems nga zer / yul dang yul can bdag tu
NK075(bu)002:1775: rtog pa las rkyen kun brtags kyis 'khrul snang sna
NK075(bu)002:1776: tshogs su byung ba'i phyir der nyes pa sna tshogs
NK075(bu)002:1777: sems nga zer / bskyed de / 'gro drug gi
NK075(bu)002:1778: sdug bsngal sna tshogs myong zhing yang dag pa'i lam
NK075(bu)002:1782: de kho na nyid kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK075(bu)002:1784: sdug bsngal myong zhing yang dag pa'i lam dang bral
NK075(bu)002:1785: ba de yi dus na chos nyid rang byung ye
NK075(bu)002:1786: shes la nyams pa med de /
NK075(bu)002:1787: rgyud sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa de nyid las gsungs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:1788: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK075(bu)002:1789: nyi zla gza' skar mtshan mo'i ltas mi 'dra ba ste glog 'gyu ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1791: sprin mang sna tshogs su 'khrugsa nas 'byung bar 'gyur
NK075(bu)002:1792: yang nam mkha'i dbyingas rang las 'gyur zhing nyams pa
NK075(bu)002:1793: med bzhin du sems nyid mi dmigs pa chos kyi
NK075(bu)002:1794: dbyings de ni ma 'gags par shes bya 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)002:1795: bsam yas par shar ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:1796: rtogs pa'i ngo ka la ye shes kyi rang gzugs
NK075(bu)002:1797: sku gsung thugsa yon tan phrin las kyi gzugs sku
NK075(bu)002:1798: rmad byung sna tshogs su shar ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1799: ma rtogs pa'i snang ngo'i gzugs su 'jig rten gyi
NK075(bu)002:1800: gtso mchog ste tshangs pa brgya byin la sogs pa
NK075(bu)002:1801: gzhan yang rigs drug gi lus sna tshogs rnam pa
NK075(bu)002:1802: mang mor shar yang sems nyid chos kyi dbyings de
NK075(bu)002:1803: las gzhan du 'gyur zhing nyams pa med de /
NK075(bu)002:1804: de bas na gong gi 'khrul pa'i rgyu rkyen la sogs pa dus mas bshad kyang /
NK075(bu)002:1805: chos kyi dbyings sems kyi gnas lugs la 'gyur ba med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1806: rgyu'i theg pas ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1808: gong gis 'khor 'das dbyer med ma rig nas ma
NK075(bu)002:1809: 'dres yongs rdzogs dbyer med de dang bral ba'i spyan
NK075(bu)002:1810: bzang long ba dang 'dra ba'i rgyu mtshan nyid kyi
NK075(bu)002:1811: theg pa kha cig pa rnams kyis bden pa gnyis
NK075(bu)002:1813: kun rdzob de dang don dam de gnyis ni mi gcig ste /
NK075(bu)002:1814: kun rdzob dngos po yin la /
NK075(bu)002:1815: don dam stong ba dngos med yin par 'dod de /
NK075(bu)002:1816: bden gnyis tshul ji ltar du gnas na /
NK075(bu)002:1817: kun rdzob de nyid ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:1818: dag dgos pa'i phyir dang de bas gzhan du don
NK075(bu)002:1819: dam brjod du med de kun rdzob dag nas stong
NK075(bu)002:1820: pa don dam yin ces smras pa la /
NK075(bu)002:1821: dper na mar snum pa ma yin /
NK075(bu)002:1822: de bas logs na snum med zer ba dang 'dra bas /
NK075(bu)002:1823: 'khor 'das ra'i rwa ltar tha dad du 'dod pas sangs rgyas mi srid do //
NK075(bu)002:1824: 'o na ji ltar du 'dod na sems kyi ngo
NK075(bu)002:1825: bo la 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa la rig
NK075(bu)002:1826: ma rig gi dbang gis ma 'gags par 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)002:1827: tha dad du ma kun tu shar zhing 'brela pa'o
NK075(bu)002:1831: zhes pa 'bru mthun la yul yul can gnyis med
NK075(bu)002:1832: las log cing gnyis su zhen pas log rtog de
NK075(bu)002:1833: ma yin la der bzung bas na 'khrul pa las
NK075(bu)002:1834: dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'i gzhung gi mtshams
NK075(bu)002:1835: gcod cing 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrang gnyis
NK075(bu)002:1837: gdul bya'i snang ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1840: gdul bya'i snang ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1841: mchog gi theg pa bkar te bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1844: spyir gdul bya'i snang ba'i ngo bo'am nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)002:1846: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po dang /
NK075(bu)002:1847: theg pa 'og ma las rim gyis sbyangs pa'i dbang
NK075(bu)002:1848: rnon gyi blo'i snang ba'i rkyen gyis phye ba yi
NK075(bu)002:1850: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon gyis gdod ma nas chos
NK075(bu)002:1851: nyid ji lta ba bzhin mngon du byed la sbyangs
NK075(bu)002:1852: pa'i dbang rnon gyis theg pa sna tshogs kyi lam
NK075(bu)002:1854: mthar chos nyid ci lta ba bzhin rig dgos pa
NK075(bu)002:1855: yis de'i dbang gis kun mkhyen sangs rgyas kyis gdul
NK075(bu)002:1856: bya sems can gyi don du chos kyi 'khor lo
NK075(bu)002:1858: gdul bya gang mosa su snod blo dang bcud theg
NK075(bu)002:1859: pa de 'tsham por sbyar nas gsungs pa'i don gyis
NK075(bu)002:1860: na / gdul bya'i blo rigs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK075(bu)002:1861: pa las 'dul byed ston pas 'dul thabs kyi theg
NK075(bu)002:1862: pa bsam yasa pa zhig gsungs pa'ang gi sgras tshur
NK075(bu)002:1863: bsdus na theg pa rim pa dgur 'dus so //
NK075(bu)002:1864: des na bcud theg pa'i rnam grangs bsam yas pa zhig yod de /
NK075(bu)002:1865: snod gdul bya'i rkyen gyis phye bas na lam gdul bya'i snang ba zhes nges tshig su brjod do //
NK075(bu)002:1866: bye brag tu theg pa'i khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)002:1868: bcud theg pa de dang de'i rkyen snod gdul bya rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon de dang /
NK075(bu)002:1869: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon de dang /
NK075(bu)002:1870: gnyis po yis ci ltar du rtogs na rang bzhin
NK075(bu)002:1871: gyi dbang rnon gyis gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i don
NK075(bu)002:1872: gdod ma nas mngon du byed nus la /
NK075(bu)002:1873: sbyangs pa'i rnon pos theg 'og las rim gyis sbyangs
NK075(bu)002:1874: nas mthar gsang sngags de bzhin du mngon du byed
NK075(bu)002:1875: dgos pa rim pa ltar du lha mi'i theg pa
NK075(bu)002:1878: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang bzhi las bgrod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1879: mthar lnga pa 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa
NK075(bu)002:1880: yi don la sbyar ba'ang nges 'byung gi theg pa
NK075(bu)002:1881: dang bzhi la rim gyis brgyud de /
NK075(bu)002:1882: rang rang gi lta ba blo dngos ma 'phrod kyi
NK075(bu)002:1883: bar du sbyangs te de nas gong ma gong mar
NK075(bu)002:1885: mthar gsang sngags de nyid du sbyor ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:1887: 'di skad du rgyud gsangs ba'i snying po las gsungs pa 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:1891: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang bzhi yis nges par 'byung la /
NK075(bu)002:1892: de yang lha mis ngan song gsum las /
NK075(bu)002:1894: byang sems mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung la /
NK075(bu)002:1895: mthar gsang sngags kyi theg pa gcig gi don la
NK075(bu)002:1896: 'jug dgos pas theg pa kun gyi 'bras bur gnas
NK075(bu)002:1897: pa'o // theg pa thams cad kyi 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa gcig la'ang /
NK075(bu)002:1898: rkyen dbang po rno rtul gyi rkyen gyis phye ba'i
NK075(bu)002:1899: gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis su gyes pa dang phyi
NK075(bu)002:1900: nang gnyis la'ang blo rab 'bring tha ma gsum gyis
NK075(bu)002:1901: phye ba'i / sngags phyi pa la bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor gsum /
NK075(bu)002:1902: nang pa la ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum dang drug tu gyes pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1903: spyir gdul bya'i snang ba bsam yas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1905: chos nyid rang byung ye shes nyag gcig de nyid shes bya kun gyi 'byung gnas yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:1906: gdul bya rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams par snang
NK075(bu)002:1907: ste gzung 'dzin phyin ci log la mos pa'i gdul
NK075(bu)002:1908: bya dang sogsa kyi sgras rnal ma la mos pa'i
NK075(bu)002:1909: gdul bya gnyis / phyin ci log la mos pa la'ang rang bzhin gyis log pa phyal rgyang dang /
NK075(bu)002:1910: grub mthar 'jug nas log pa gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1911: tha ma grub mthar 'jug nas log pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1912: log pa mu stegs mur rtug dang /
NK075(bu)002:1913: theg chen la ltos na log pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:1914: mu stegs pa la ltos na ma log pa yi nyan rang ngo //
NK075(bu)002:1915: zhes chos rje rin po ches bzhed la /
NK075(bu)002:1917: tha ma log dang ma log pa /
NK075(bu)002:1919: tha ma grub mthar 'jug pa la mu stegs /
NK075(bu)002:1920: ma log pa nyan rang yan chad ngos bzung yin par gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:1921: rgyud kyi dgongs pa ltar bye brag tu dmigs ngos bzung na /
NK075(bu)002:1922: gzung 'dzin la zhen cing chos nyid ma rtogs pa phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen /
NK075(bu)002:1923: lta ba rtag chad kyi mthar zhen nas log par rtog pa mur rtug mu stegs /
NK075(bu)002:1924: phra ba chos kyi bdag ma rtogs /
NK075(bu)002:1925: rags pa gang zag gi bdag phyogs tsam rtogs pa nyan rang /
NK075(bu)002:1926: don dam bden pa'i gnas lugs rtogs kyang kun rdzob
NK075(bu)002:1927: bden pa'i gnas lugs ma rtogs pas bden gnyis dbyer
NK075(bu)002:1928: med yang dag pa nyid ma rtogsa pa dbu ma
NK075(bu)002:1929: sems tsam / lus ngag yid gsum spyod pas 'dul ba byed pa kri ya /
NK075(bu)002:1930: dgongas pa ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa gnyis ka gtso bor byed pa u pa ya /
NK075(bu)002:1931: ting nge 'dzin gtsor byed pa gzhan gyis rtogs dka' bas gsang ba ste yo ga dang /
NK075(bu)002:1932: bskyed rim gtsor byed pas sku yi rgyud ma h+aa dang /
NK075(bu)002:1933: rdzogs rim gtsor byed pa don gsal bas gsung gi
NK075(bu)002:1934: rgyud a nu dang zung 'jug gtsor byed pa don
NK075(bu)002:1935: zab pas na thugsa kyi rgyud a ti yo ga
NK075(bu)002:1936: rnams su snang / zhes rgyud gsang snying las gsungs pas /
NK075(bu)002:1937: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje skye ba'i yul dang sar
NK075(bu)002:1938: ma gyur pa yi gdul bya gcig kyang med pas
NK075(bu)002:1939: / de bas theg pa so sor gdul bya rang
NK075(bu)002:1940: rang gi blo dang 'tshams par snang ba'i rkyen gyis
NK075(bu)002:1942: don dam nges pa'i theg pa bsam yas na'ang /
NK075(bu)002:1943: 'dir da res ma h+aa'i theg pa bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:1944: theg pa mchog la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:1948: dbang po mchog gi blo dang 'tshams par snang ba'i
NK075(bu)002:1949: rkyen byas pa'i ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud sde ni
NK075(bu)002:1950: rnam pa gsum ste de'ang gzhi sems can dang sbyar
NK075(bu)002:1952: skyes pa rnams ni 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:1953: rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud ces bshad //
NK075(bu)002:1954: bud med rnams ni 'dul bya'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:1955: rnal 'byor ma yi rgyud bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:1957: lam rtsa rlung dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)002:1959: rtsa yi de nyid rtogs gyur pa //
NK075(bu)002:1960: de nyid ma yi rgyud ces bya //
NK075(bu)002:1961: rlung gi de nyid rtogs gyur pa //
NK075(bu)002:1962: de nyid rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud //
NK075(bu)002:1964: mthar thug 'bras bu dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)002:1965: ma rgyud ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NK075(bu)002:1966: pha rgyud ye shes chen po ste //
NK075(bu)002:1967: ma rgyud stong pa chen po yin //
NK075(bu)002:1969: yod pa rtsa rlung thig le sems dang bzhi ka
NK075(bu)002:1970: yod kyang rlung gtso bor byed pa pha rgyud rtsa
NK075(bu)002:1971: dang thig le gtso bor ston pa ma brgyud /
NK075(bu)002:1972: sems gtso bor ston pa gnyis med rgyud dang gsum las /
NK075(bu)002:1973: 'dir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba'i snying po ni
NK075(bu)002:1974: gnyis med ma ning lta bu zung 'jug gi rgyud
NK075(bu)002:1975: do // de lta bu gsang ba'i snying po'i don
NK075(bu)002:1976: tshul bzhin ci ltar du nyams su len na rdo
NK075(bu)002:1977: rje sems dpa' thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba'i
NK075(bu)002:1978: snying po'i rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad snang
NK075(bu)002:1979: ba bzhi por spyi gcod de /
NK075(bu)002:1980: khog dbub nas nyams su len dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:1981: de yang tshul ci ltar du khog dbub na /
NK075(bu)002:1982: man ngag gi de nyid kyis sngona mdor bstan gyi
NK075(bu)002:1983: skabs su bshad pa bzhin du snang bzhir bstana pa
NK075(bu)002:1984: la / gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:1985: ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba gnyis gong du song
NK075(bu)002:1986: nas gsum pa gdul bya lam gyi snang ba 'di
NK075(bu)002:1987: nyid nyams su len na lam gyi rkyen 'di yi
NK075(bu)002:1988: ge'i rgyud 'di nyid dang sbyar nas bshad dgos pa
NK075(bu)002:1989: la kha cig gis 'dir bshad pa'i rkyen thams cad
NK075(bu)002:1990: gdul bya la sbyar dgos zer ba ni mi rigs
NK075(bu)002:1991: te / ci'i phyir na sngon 'byung kun mkhyen sangs rgyas kyis chos gcig kho na gsungs pa la /
NK075(bu)002:1992: gdul bya rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams par go
NK075(bu)002:1993: bas theg pa sna tshogs 'byung ba'i rkyen gdul bya
NK075(bu)002:1994: yin la / rjes 'jug tu da lta rnal 'byor
NK075(bu)002:1995: pa rnams kyis lam nyams su len pa la chos
NK075(bu)002:1997: de shes par byed pa'i rkyen yi ges byed dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:1998: gong du theg pa sna tshogs 'byung ba'i rkyen gdul bya yin la /
NK075(bu)002:1999: 'dir nyams su len pa'i rkyen theg pa yin par gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:2000: theg pa der 'jug pa la gang rung gis 'jug nus pa ma yin /
NK075(bu)002:2001: las dag pa'i gang zag dbang po rnon po zhig dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:2002: blo mchog gi skal ba bcud theg pa mchog ma
NK075(bu)002:2003: h+aa dang snod gang zag dbang rnon gyi shes rab
NK075(bu)002:2004: gnyis la shes bya shes byed dam snod bcud dam
NK075(bu)002:2005: blo dang theg par 'brela pa'i gzhi ma yod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:2006: phyir / rtogs nus pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2007: dbang rnon de la dbang po rab 'bring tha ma gsum du byung ba'i blos phye ba'i /
NK075(bu)002:2008: gsang ba'i snying po'i don bshad lugs la thugs thigs
NK075(bu)002:2009: te brjod bya'i gtso bo gnas lugs gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)002:2012: tha ma 'bru gnyer dang gsum gyis sgo nas 'chad lugs 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:2014: de la gsum rab la mtshan bstan /
NK075(bu)002:2016: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2017: tha ma 'bras bu lam gyis thob par byed pas lam shes pa'i rgyu 'bru re nas bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2020: gdul bya thabs lam grol lam du bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2025: dang po dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa tsam
NK075(bu)002:2026: gyis don mtshon pa'i gsang ba'i snying po las ming
NK075(bu)002:2027: gi 'dogs lugs gsum dang ldan no //
NK075(bu)002:2030: rgyud dang ston pa'i mtshan thun mong pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2032: theg 'og gi lung ni drang lung yin la 'dir
NK075(bu)002:2033: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ci lta ba mtshon pas
NK075(bu)002:2035: gsang sngags yin te de yang dngos po'i chos thams
NK075(bu)002:2036: cad snang bzhin ngo bo ma grub pa sgyu ma
NK075(bu)002:2037: dang 'dra ba'i phyir skye ba med pa ste lha
NK075(bu)002:2038: ni yum / de nyid dangsa po kun rdzob 'khor ba dang dngos med 'das pa gnyis pa /
NK075(bu)002:2039: yul du snang ba ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2040: rig pa'i rtsal du legsa par snang ba ni 'phrul
NK075(bu)002:2041: med las cir yang 'char bas 'gag med de lha
NK075(bu)002:2042: ni yab bden pas gnyis pa'i don dra ba ltar
NK075(bu)002:2043: 'brel pas gnyis su med de lha ni yab yum
NK075(bu)002:2044: / dbyer med de nyid kyi ngo bo la gnyis
NK075(bu)002:2045: su med cing skye 'jig dang bral bas na rdo
NK075(bu)002:2046: / rje / dbyer med kyi don de rgyun chad med par gsal bas sems /
NK075(bu)002:2047: dgongs pa de brtan pas dngos po mtshan mas tshur
NK075(bu)002:2048: la mi tshugs shing phar la 'joms pas na dpa'
NK075(bu)002:2049: bo // ston pa des thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i
NK075(bu)002:2050: rgyud don gyi byed las kyi rim pa sna tshogs
NK075(bu)002:2051: su gsungs pas lha'i ming la rdo rje sems dpa'
NK075(bu)002:2052: bo // zhes btags pas / ston pa dang bstan
NK075(bu)002:2053: pa dbyer med du mtshan thun mong du bstan pa'o
NK075(bu)002:2054: bo // zhes btags pas / // che ba'i mtshan dang /
NK075(bu)002:2056: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa'i dgongs pa dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:2057: de ni brtan zhing 'gyur ba med pa'i theg pa
NK075(bu)002:2058: kun gyi 'byung khungs sam dngos gzhi yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2059: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por rtsal ma 'gags par
NK075(bu)002:2060: shar ba la phyogs 'dzin gyi rim pas theg pa
NK075(bu)002:2061: dgur shar ba'am / yang na theg pa 'og ma
NK075(bu)002:2062: thams cad lam stegs su bgrod nas mthar gsang ba'i
NK075(bu)002:2063: snying poo'i dan mngon du gyur dgos pas spyi lung
NK075(bu)002:2064: nges pa zhes pa mtshan du 'dogs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2065: mtshan gyi 'dogs lugs gsum las grangs kyi gnyis pa che ba'i mtshan no //
NK075(bu)002:2066: don rang gi ngo bo'i mtshan dang /
NK075(bu)002:2068: gzhan la bstan par dka' rang gis brtags par dka'
NK075(bu)002:2069: ba'i gsang ba la don gyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying
NK075(bu)002:2070: po de / tshul ci ltar du gsang na /
NK075(bu)002:2071: spyir rang bzhin gyi gsang ba /
NK075(bu)002:2074: mi bstan pa'i gsang ba dang bzhir bshad kyang 'dir
NK075(bu)002:2075: ni rang bzhin gsang ba bzhi yis chod nas so
NK075(bu)002:2076: skye nas lam pa yo ga man chad kun gyi
NK075(bu)002:2077: snang ngo la / rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don de mi snang ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2080: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK075(bu)002:2081: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK075(bu)002:2082: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK075(bu)002:2083: gzhan du min la shin tu gsang //
NK075(bu)002:2086: don dam bden pa'i dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du
NK075(bu)002:2087: lhun gyis grub pa rang chas su yod kyang rang
NK075(bu)002:2088: ngo rang gi ma shes te /
NK075(bu)002:2089: gang gis ma shes na lhan cig skyes pa'i ma
NK075(bu)002:2090: rig pas rang rig la nges pa'i shes pa ma
NK075(bu)002:2091: skyes pas skye med de gsang /
NK075(bu)002:2092: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba ni kun rdzob kyi bden
NK075(bu)002:2093: pa ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK075(bu)002:2094: du rang bzhin gyis gnas kyang rang ngo rang gis
NK075(bu)002:2095: ma shes te / gang gis ma shes na kun
NK075(bu)002:2096: tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas rang snang la mtshan
NK075(bu)002:2097: mar bzung bas 'gag med du shar ba de gsang
NK075(bu)002:2098: ma shes te / / ngo bo nyid kyi gsang ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:2099: dbyer med kyi bden pa ye nas rang chas su yod kyang ngo ma shes te /
NK075(bu)002:2100: gang gis ma shes na snang stong tha dad du bzung bas dbyer med de gsang /
NK075(bu)002:2101: shin tu gsang ba ni dbyer med spyod yul dang
NK075(bu)002:2102: bral ba'i don ye nas rang chas su yod kyang
NK075(bu)002:2104: gang gis ngo ma shes na yul yul can du
NK075(bu)002:2105: bzung bas spyod yul dang bral ba de gsang ngo
NK075(bu)002:2106: // snying po la don gyi bcud 'dus lugs la gsum /
NK075(bu)002:2108: 'bras bu'i bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po dang gsum mo //
NK075(bu)002:2110: rgyud 'di nyid bstan pa'i byin brlabs kyis go phye nas bstan pa thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)002:2111: 'bras bu'i snying po ni theg pa kun nas bsgrubs
NK075(bu)002:2112: pa'i mthar gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid mngon du
NK075(bu)002:2113: byed dgos pa'o // bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po ni /
NK075(bu)002:2114: gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas kyang smal gzhig brtags nas
NK075(bu)002:2115: gtan la phab kyang mthar thug de pa'i dgongs pa'i
NK075(bu)002:2116: spyod yul ni / snang spyod dang rtog tshogs thams
NK075(bu)002:2117: cad sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi
NK075(bu)002:2118: dkyil 'khor du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'o
NK075(bu)002:2119: spyod yul ni / // ma bcos pa'i de kho
NK075(bu)002:2120: na nyid dang ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid
NK075(bu)002:2121: spyod yul ni / // dang / gzhan ma yin pa de kho na nyid gsum du ldan te /
NK075(bu)002:2122: de yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK075(bu)002:2123: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa las //
NK075(bu)002:2124: de nyid ngo bo skabs kyis gsum //
NK075(bu)002:2125: zhes pas ma bcos pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2126: rtog tshogs thams cad rang rig las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2127: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes dkyil 'khor la /
NK075(bu)002:2128: blo ma bcos par bzhag pa ni ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK075(bu)002:2129: de la skabs kyis rgyu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du gdags so //
NK075(bu)002:2132: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor mang por snang ba mngon du byang chub pa ni ma nor ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:2133: de la skabs kyis 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid ces tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK075(bu)002:2135: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi ye shes las shes bya'am bsgrub bya gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2136: gzhan ma yin pa de kho na nyid do //
NK075(bu)002:2137: de la skabs kyis rgyu 'bras ro gcig pa'i de
NK075(bu)002:2138: kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so
NK075(bu)002:2139: // yang na ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid skye med kyi gshis /
NK075(bu)002:2140: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid 'gag med kyi gdangs /
NK075(bu)002:2141: gzhan ma yin pa de kho na nyid dbyer med kyi ngang /
NK075(bu)002:2143: bden pa dbyer med pa'i don ni nges pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2146: de yang 'grel pa spar khab las /
NK075(bu)002:2147: gzhi dang lam dang ngo bo yis //
NK075(bu)002:2148: nges pa rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NK075(bu)002:2151: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di /
NK075(bu)002:2152: thams cad kyi gshis la rang bzhin gyis gnas nges pas /
NK075(bu)002:2156: rgyud 'di nyid kyi lugs kyis 'bras bu lam du byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2157: 'bras bur nges pa ni rgyud 'di nyid kyis rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mngon du ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:2158: de lta bu'i ming gis don mtshon pa la /
NK075(bu)002:2159: bstan pa la mtshan thogs lugs lnga yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:2160: 'di ni 'dogs lugs gzhan las lhag pa'i don rang gi ngo bo la mtshan du 'dogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2161: yang na gong gi ston pa dang bstan pa'i mtshan thun mong dang /
NK075(bu)002:2163: phyogs re las mi mtshon la /
NK075(bu)002:2165: don rang gi ngo bo'i mtshan yin no //
NK075(bu)002:2166: zhes pa yang brtag par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:2169: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes nyag gcig kho
NK075(bu)002:2170: na las med pas de mtshon par byed pa'i tshig
NK075(bu)002:2171: gcig la brten nas blo rab kyis rtogs nus kyang
NK075(bu)002:2172: rim gyis pa ltar gzhung gi tshig rgyas pa'i 'bru
NK075(bu)002:2173: gnur gyis kyang blo rab la don cig char du
NK075(bu)002:2174: mtshon nas rtogs mi nus te /
NK075(bu)002:2175: tshig mtha'i sgrib pas de bas dpe sman pa 'tsho
NK075(bu)002:2176: byed gzhon nu'i shes rab kyis lus mgo 'jug gi
NK075(bu)002:2177: nad thams cad lag ngar gyi rtsa gcig pu'i nang
NK075(bu)002:2178: du rtog pa bzhin du blo rab la yi ge
NK075(bu)002:2179: bsdus pas te mtshan don tsam gyis rgyud dbu zhabs
NK075(bu)002:2180: kyi don rgyas par brda phrad tha snyad dang rgyud
NK075(bu)002:2181: dbu zhabs kyi tshig don rnams ni don du bsdus
NK075(bu)002:2182: pa yin no // 'o na mtshan don du rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don ma lus par 'du na /
NK075(bu)002:2183: rgyud don yongs su shes byed kyi dngos po bcu
NK075(bu)002:2184: bye brag tu phye la mtshan don dang dngos su
NK075(bu)002:2185: brang ci ltar sprad ce na /
NK075(bu)002:2186: dngos su brang sprad rgyu med kyang mtshan gyi don
NK075(bu)002:2187: gzhi lam 'bras gsum du gnas pas der cha rkyen
NK075(bu)002:2188: dang rgyud don shugs la 'dus so //
NK075(bu)002:2189: mtshan don gtan la phab pa'i dus su gdul bya thabs lam grol lam du bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2191: ming gsum pa ste tha ma don rang gi ngo
NK075(bu)002:2192: bo la ming du btags pa'i mtshan don gtan la
NK075(bu)002:2193: phab pa la gdul bya mos pa'i blos so sor
NK075(bu)002:2194: 'dod pa'i dbye bas shes rab can la grol lam
NK075(bu)002:2195: dang sbyar te phyi ltar bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2196: chags pa can la thabs lam de yang steng sgo
NK075(bu)002:2197: dang sbyar te nang ltar 'og sgo dang sbyar te
NK075(bu)002:2198: gsang ba dang nang ltar du bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2200: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba la gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:2204: rin po che la dang nas 'od yod kyang nyi
NK075(bu)002:2205: ma yi 'od phog pas sngar bas mdzes pa'i 'od
NK075(bu)002:2206: dang ldan zhing rin po chen cher gsal ba ltar
NK075(bu)002:2207: tshig gis rnam par dbye ba 'di sgron ma dang
NK075(bu)002:2208: 'dra ba'i blo shes rab phye bas dbang po 'bring
NK075(bu)002:2209: la shes bya gsang ba'i snying po la snang ba
NK075(bu)002:2210: mched de rtogs par bya ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2211: tshig gis rnam par dbye ba 'di rab la mtshan
NK075(bu)002:2212: bstan pa la ltos na rgyas pa'i tshig don bye
NK075(bu)002:2213: brag phye ba tshig don yin pa la tha ma
NK075(bu)002:2214: 'bru gnyer la ltos na nyung ste thigs par shar
NK075(bu)002:2216: de yang rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon gdod ma nas ma h+aa'i snod du gyur pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2217: theg 'og las rims kyis sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon mthar
NK075(bu)002:2218: ma h+aa'i snod du gyur pa rang bzhin dbang rnon
NK075(bu)002:2219: cig char du lam bgrod thabas dang /
NK075(bu)002:2220: sbyangs rnon rims kyis bgrod thabs gnyis su byung /
NK075(bu)002:2222: thabs shes gnyis su bzhed kyang /
NK075(bu)002:2223: gzhung rang la brtags na rims dang cig char gnyis yin par gsungs /
NK075(bu)002:2224: de gnyis la yang lam gyi yan lag dang cha rkyen du 'di rnams 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:2225: shes bya lam gyi yan lag dang /
NK075(bu)002:2226: bsgrub bya lam gyi yan lag gnyis so //
NK075(bu)002:2228: de rkyen yan lag rnam gnyis te //
NK075(bu)002:2229: sgrub byed rkyen dang shes byed rkyen //
NK075(bu)002:2231: don gyi go rim bsdeb na /
NK075(bu)002:2232: dang po thog ma la shes par bya ba'i yul lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:2233: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)002:2234: tha ma'i mchog gi lam thabs grol gnyis la brtan pa thob nas spros pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:2235: tshogs sgrub kyi sgo nas mthong lam la sbyor ba'i tshul dang gsum du bstan no //
NK075(bu)002:2238: shes par bya ba'i yul lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:2239: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam nyams su blangs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2240: tha ma drod tshad dang ldan nas 'bras bu mthong lam la sbyor ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:2245: dang po shes par bya ba'i yul la lnga ste rgyu gleng gzhi dang rkyen gleng bslangs dang /
NK075(bu)002:2246: dgos 'brel bzhi dang bshad thabs 'gren pa'i tshig bcu dang /
NK075(bu)002:2247: rgyud gdams shing gtad pa dang lngas rgyud gsang snying
NK075(bu)002:2248: gis bshad thabs rgyas bshad de rdzogs pa yin no
NK075(bu)002:2252: dgos 'brel bzhi dang 'dren pa'i tshig gi dpe dang /
NK075(bu)002:2258: thabs lam gyi rgyu gleng gzhi dang shes rab grol
NK075(bu)002:2259: lam gyi rgyu gleng gzhi don yang rgyas par bshad
NK075(bu)002:2260: cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:2264: thabs lam gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:2266: gleng gzhi mdor bstan la gnyis su byung ba'i snga ma thabs lam pa'i gleng gzhi 'tshogs lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:2267: ston pa dang gnas dang 'khor dang sdud pa po
NK075(bu)002:2268: dang dus dang bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa drug
NK075(bu)002:2269: 'tshogs dgos te / de la gnas ni thabs lam
NK075(bu)002:2270: steng sgo la snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo thams
NK075(bu)002:2271: cad kyi 'byung khungs yin pas rin po che dang
NK075(bu)002:2272: 'dra bas rtsa 'dab ma brgyad 'dus pa'i sgrom dkyil
NK075(bu)002:2273: 'tshogs dgos te / lo // 'og sgo'i gnas ni
NK075(bu)002:2274: bde ba'i ye shes su shar ba nyid yo ga
NK075(bu)002:2275: man chad kyis mi shes pa gsang ba'i bde stong
NK075(bu)002:2276: de nyid shes bya gang gi 'og tu song ba
NK075(bu)002:2277: 'tshogs dgos te / lo // min pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2278: yum gyi mkha' bskyed pas gnas yum gyi mkha' ste
NK075(bu)002:2279: 'tshogs dgos te / lo // min pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2280: / gnas de gnyis kyis phye bas ston 'khor phun
NK075(bu)002:2281: sum tshogs pa lnga'am drug po de yi ge e
NK075(bu)002:2282: wam ma ya bzhi yis gtan la phab nas shes
NK075(bu)002:2284: thabs lam steng sgo 'og sgo'i gleng gzhi bsdus pa dang sbyar te rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:2285: nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:2286: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2289: 'og gzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK075(bu)002:2290: zhes pas snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab ma brgyad de /
NK075(bu)002:2291: g.yas chos nyid kyi rtsa 'od dkar po zhi ba'i gnas /
NK075(bu)002:2292: rgyab ye shes kyi rtsa gru bzhi ser po rgyas pa'i gnas /
NK075(bu)002:2293: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa zla gam dmar po dbang gi gnas /
NK075(bu)002:2294: mdun las rang rgyud kyi rtsa dbyibs gru gsum dmar nag drag po'i gnas so //
NK075(bu)002:2295: 'di ni rgyal ba g.yung ston pa ltar du bkod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2297: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2299: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK075(bu)002:2300: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK075(bu)002:2302: srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dwangs ma lnga 'dus
NK075(bu)002:2303: kyi thig le ngo bo zlum po yi ge wam
NK075(bu)002:2304: gi dbyibs can de thabs lam steng sgo'i rtsa rlung
NK075(bu)002:2305: nyams blangs pa'i tshe thig le zhu bas /
NK075(bu)002:2306: rang la bde ba gsal bar ston pas na ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2307: bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2309: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK075(bu)002:2310: ye shes myong ba sdud par bshad //
NK075(bu)002:2312: yid la sogs pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes
NK075(bu)002:2313: lngar gsal ba nyams su blangs pas bshad pa dang
NK075(bu)002:2314: 'dra bas 'khor / sdud pa po yid kyi shes pa /
NK075(bu)002:2317: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2319: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK075(bu)002:2320: pa ra mar+tha don zab mo //
NK075(bu)002:2322: pa ra mar+tha'i sgra las drangs na /
NK075(bu)002:2323: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK075(bu)002:2324: y+aa na theg pa chen po ste /
NK075(bu)002:2325: de nyams su blangs pas ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs
NK075(bu)002:2326: can skyes pa ni bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'o
NK075(bu)002:2327: // dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2329: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK075(bu)002:2330: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK075(bu)002:2332: ye shes skyes pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:2333: dus gsum du 'dzin pa med pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus zhes bya ste dus so //
NK075(bu)002:2334: gsang ba ltar 'og sgo sbyar dang te bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:2335: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2337: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK075(bu)002:2338: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK075(bu)002:2340: yum gyi mkha' phyi khyams gru gsum drag po'i gnas /
NK075(bu)002:2341: bar khyams gru bzhi rgyas pa'i gnas /
NK075(bu)002:2342: skye gnas zla gam dbang gi gnas /
NK075(bu)002:2343: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum po zhi ba'i gnas so //
NK075(bu)002:2344: skad ces pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2346: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK075(bu)002:2347: wam dbyibs thig le bcas ston pa //
NK075(bu)002:2349: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje'i dbu la kun rdzob
NK075(bu)002:2350: ye shes kyi thig le wam yig gi dbyings su
NK075(bu)002:2351: rdzogs pas / rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i dbang
NK075(bu)002:2352: gis 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i byed pa po yin pa
NK075(bu)002:2353: rdzogs pas / dang / thig le de nyid kyis bde ba gsal bar byed pas na ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2354: bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2356: ma da ma nu sdom byed yin //
NK075(bu)002:2357: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK075(bu)002:2358: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK075(bu)002:2359: ces pas ma ta na sdom pa /
NK075(bu)002:2361: bde ba sdom par byed pas /
NK075(bu)002:2362: nyon mongs can gyi yid la sogs pa'i rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ni 'khor ro //
NK075(bu)002:2363: sdud pa po nyon mongs pa'i yid ces pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:2364: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2366: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK075(bu)002:2367: ya na theg chen 'di yin te //
NK075(bu)002:2369: pa ra ma r+tha na don pa /
NK075(bu)002:2370: ya na theg pa chen po dga' ba bcu drug
NK075(bu)002:2371: gi tha mar rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i bde
NK075(bu)002:2372: ba'i ye shes lhangs kyis nyams su myong ba ste
NK075(bu)002:2373: / rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2375: dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2377: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK075(bu)002:2378: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:2381: gtsug tor 'khor lo bsgyur ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:2382: mkha' gsang bde ba skyes pa'i tshe na /
NK075(bu)002:2383: dus ni phyogs gcig tu brjod du mi btub ste /
NK075(bu)002:2384: snga phyi'i 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral ba'i bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK075(bu)002:2385: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:2387: dus de la babs pa'i ming can nam /
NK075(bu)002:2388: yang na kun la 'jug pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2394: de ltar gsang ba 'og sgo'i gleng gzhi 'tshogs pa las thabs lam rang gi lung dang /
NK075(bu)002:2395: bla ma'i man ngag tshad ma gnyis dang sbrel nas nyan dgos /
NK075(bu)002:2396: rang gi rig pa tshad mas gtan la mi pheb ste /
NK075(bu)002:2397: 'khrul 'khor dang rlung bzung la pa'i thabs la rag las pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2398: shes rab grol lam gyi rgyu gleng gazhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:2403: blo gros te shes rab grol lam gyi rgyu gleng
NK075(bu)002:2404: bzhi la gnyis te theg 'og dang thun mong gzugs
NK075(bu)002:2405: sku rtags kyi gleng gzhi dang mchog ste khyad par
NK075(bu)002:2410: khyad par don gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:2412: chos sku'i gleng gzhi 'di ston pa kun bzang gi dgongs pa la mngon du tshogs kyang /
NK075(bu)002:2413: go phye ba'i 'khor la tshul ci ltar du gnas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2414: mthar mngon du gyur tshul ni /
NK075(bu)002:2415: shes bya gang gi 'og tu ma 'ongs pas bla
NK075(bu)002:2416: thams cad kyi bskyed pa'i gzhir gyur pas na ma
NK075(bu)002:2417: ste rang gi sems rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK075(bu)002:2418: po de nyid / kun gyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas gzhi'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2419: de nyid ma rtogs sems can gyi dus su rtog pa sna tshogs kyi byed las byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2420: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa na mkhyen brtse'i byed las sna tshogs byed pas ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2421: lam gyi byed las sna tshogs kyi sgo nas rtogs pas ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2422: de nyid ye shes kyi bye brag mang po ste
NK075(bu)002:2423: ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis ye shes lnga
NK075(bu)002:2424: la sogs par shar ba ni 'khor phun sum tshogs
NK075(bu)002:2425: pa dang / ye shes kyi bye brag ci ltar
NK075(bu)002:2426: shar yang ye shes thams cad dbyer med pa'i bdag
NK075(bu)002:2427: nyid rang byung gi ye shes ni sdud pa po
NK075(bu)002:2428: pa dang / dang / bstan pa'i ngo bo yang
NK075(bu)002:2429: logs na med de ye shes thams cad kyi bcud
NK075(bu)002:2430: thugs rang byung gi ye shes bsdus pa'i dngosa po
NK075(bu)002:2431: de bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2432: de'i ngang las chos nyid yongs rdzogs las ma g.yos
NK075(bu)002:2433: bzhin du shes bya ma 'dres par bkra zhing gsal
NK075(bu)002:2434: ba ni lung ste sgro bkur dang bral bas de'i
NK075(bu)002:2435: ngang la dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2436: de ni dus phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2437: go phye ba'i 'khor de la khyad par chos sku'i
NK075(bu)002:2438: gleng gzhi chos nyid de gnas nas yoda pas chos
NK075(bu)002:2439: sku'i gleng gzhi de mngon du rtogsa nas sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)002:2440: par 'gyur ro // thun mong rtags kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:2445: bdag don chos sku'i gleng gzhi mngon du gyur nas /
NK075(bu)002:2446: theg 'og gi gdul bya dang thun mong pa la gzugs sku rtags kyi gleng gzhi shar ba'ang /
NK075(bu)002:2447: gdul bya lugs 'byung zlog gis phye bas /
NK075(bu)002:2448: zhi ba dang khro bo'i mtshan ma mi 'dra ba gnyis kyi gzugs su shar nas snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:2452: zhi ba las khro bor snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:2455: gang gis gsungs pa'i ston pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2457: zhi ba'i ston pa ni gdul bya 'dren par mdzad
NK075(bu)002:2458: cing don chos nyid rang snang ma bcos pas na
NK075(bu)002:2459: rang byung de nyid skye 'jig dang bral zhing 'da'
NK075(bu)002:2460: nyams med pa'i rtagsa su phyag drug gi dang po'am
NK075(bu)002:2461: phyag gnyis ltar na mnyam gzhag gi steng na rdo
NK075(bu)002:2462: rje 'dzin pas drug pa rdo rje 'chang ngam lhan
NK075(bu)002:2463: cig pa'i 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho la /
NK075(bu)002:2464: bstan pa gsung lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyud kyi
NK075(bu)002:2465: ston pa rigs thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa
NK075(bu)002:2467: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las /
NK075(bu)002:2468: ye shes rgya mtsho 'og min gyi //
NK075(bu)002:2470: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK075(bu)002:2471: bka' sdod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK075(bu)002:2472: brjod pa med bzhin go bar mdzad //
NK075(bu)002:2473: dpag med ye shes yongs rdzogs pas //
NK075(bu)002:2474: zhing 'khor longs spyod phun tshogs ldan //
NK075(bu)002:2476: lam pa rnams kyi snang ngo la kun bzang de'i
NK075(bu)002:2477: rgyal tshab 'dzin cing sku gsung thugs sogs rgyud sna
NK075(bu)002:2478: tshogs ston pas ni 'chad pa'i skyes bus rigs lnga
NK075(bu)002:2479: dang khyad par du lha mi'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi
NK075(bu)002:2480: snang ngor byin rlabs kyi ston pa sdud pa por
NK075(bu)002:2481: snang nas sdud pa po dang gnyis yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:2482: thugs sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs 'dir 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' mdun na gnas shing /
NK075(bu)002:2483: sdud pa po yang phyag na rdo rjer 'dod de /
NK075(bu)002:2484: ston pa kun bzang gi mtshan nyid rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:2485: sa nang tshigs su bcad na gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:2486: dang po ston pa'i rang bzhin spyir bstan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2487: ston pa kun bzang gi dgongs pa'i rang bzhin chos
NK075(bu)002:2488: nyid de 'das ma 'ongs da lta dus gsuma gyi
NK075(bu)002:2489: chos las gud du mina te dbyer med du gnas
NK075(bu)002:2490: pas / ston pa'i rang bzhin 'khor 'das gnyis dang dbyer med ces bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:2494: rdo rje'i bdag nyid ces pa'i bar myang 'das dang dbyer med ston la /
NK075(bu)002:2495: ma lus pa zhes pa nas dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK075(bu)002:2496: zhes pa'i bar gyis 'khor ba dang dbyer med ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2497: gnyis pa bye brag tu longs sku 'chad pa'i skyes
NK075(bu)002:2498: bu dang mtshan nyid thun mong du bstan pa ni
NK075(bu)002:2500: 'dod yon lnga ma spangs longs spyod pa'i rtags su
NK075(bu)002:2501: rin po che'i dbu rgyan la sogs pa rgyan gyis
NK075(bu)002:2502: brgyan cing yab rkyang yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2503: 'dir nyon mongs pa chags rtog ma spangs bde stong
NK075(bu)002:2504: du longs spyod pa'i rtags su yab yum kha sbyor
NK075(bu)002:2505: gyi longs spyod rdzogs pa chen po'i skur bzhengs nas
NK075(bu)002:2506: / rang byung ye shes de kho na nyid yin
NK075(bu)002:2507: pa'i phyir rtags su sku mdun rgyab med par kun
NK075(bu)002:2508: tu zhal thal le bar gsal zhing gdul bya rang
NK075(bu)002:2509: rang gang la mos pa'i theg pa sna tshogs ston
NK075(bu)002:2510: pa'i longs sprul gyi sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa
NK075(bu)002:2511: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pas /
NK075(bu)002:2512: ston pa'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs rdul snyed du grags pa la /
NK075(bu)002:2513: 'dir sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsum mtshon pas dbu gsum /
NK075(bu)002:2514: ye shes drug mtshon pas phyag drug gam /
NK075(bu)002:2515: yang na bdag don du chos nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK075(bu)002:2516: las ma g.yos pa'i rtags su phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag
NK075(bu)002:2517: longs spyod pa'i rgyan thun mong gi mtshan dpe dang
NK075(bu)002:2518: / thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpe phyi nang
NK075(bu)002:2519: gsang gsum la sogs pa longs sku'i rgyan rnams kyis
NK075(bu)002:2520: / brgyan pa / gzhan don du brda'i sgo nas
NK075(bu)002:2521: chos ston par madzada pas mtshan dpe rgyas bshad ni
NK075(bu)002:2524: mnyam pa'i rdo rje'i rdzogs pa'i brtul zhugs kyi ste /
NK075(bu)002:2525: ming bzhi dang ldan pa'i skyil krung du bzhugas pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:2526: de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:2527: yab kyi bol gnyis barla g.yas g.yon gyi steng du bzhag pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2528: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid du rtogs nas mnyam pa'i skyil krung dang /
NK075(bu)002:2529: chos nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor rdzogs pas na rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung /
NK075(bu)002:2530: dgongs pa skye 'jig dang bral bas na rdo rje skyil krung /
NK075(bu)002:2532: yum gyi zhabs gnyis yab la 'khyud cing zhabs mthil gnyis sbyar nas rtse mo sprad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2533: nyon mongs brtul zhing bde ba chen po'i ngang la mi 'gyur bar bzhugs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2534: brtul zhugs kyi skyil krung zhes zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:2536: sku mdun dang rgyab med ces pa nas //
NK075(bu)002:2537: dbu gsum dang zhes pa'i bar gyis ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2538: gang du gsungs pa'i gnas dang /
NK075(bu)002:2540: ston pa de yi rten pa'i gnas la tshigs su bcad na gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:2541: dang po gnas kyi rang bzhin spyir bstan pa ni
NK075(bu)002:2542: gnas kyi rang bzhin ni gzhi yi 'og min la
NK075(bu)002:2543: nang tshan bdun yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:2544: 'dir ni don chos dbyings kyi gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2546: yang na longs spyod chen po ni 'og min te /
NK075(bu)002:2547: gnas 'di'i gzugs khams kyi rtse mo 'jig rten gnas
NK075(bu)002:2548: kyi 'og min las gnyis 'gyur gyis dpag pas na
NK075(bu)002:2549: / ma spangs rgyan tshogs kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK075(bu)002:2550: sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul te /
NK075(bu)002:2551: lam pa'i spyod yul min pas gsang ba'i gnas de na /
NK075(bu)002:2552: 'o na gnyis 'gyur gyis dpags te dngos su dpags sam don la dpags she na /
NK075(bu)002:2553: dngos su gzugs khams kyi 'og min las gnyis 'gyur gyis dpag pas na /
NK075(bu)002:2554: gang gis 'jig rten gyi mnar med la thug pas don las dpags par gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:2555: gnyis pa bye brag tu longs sku'i gnas ni /
NK075(bu)002:2556: spyir gzung yul gnas su dag pa la sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)002:2557: kyi zhing khams gnas su dag pa la gzhal yas
NK075(bu)002:2558: khang / rig pa gnas su dag pa la lha red pas /
NK075(bu)002:2559: des na lha'i sku dang lhan cig tu 'dus pa'i gzhal yas khang de'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)002:2560: ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2561: de yang gdul bya'i dgos 'dod skongs pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2562: rtags rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i gzhal yang khang
NK075(bu)002:2563: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ma spangsa 'bras bu lhun
NK075(bu)002:2564: grub kyis don rdzogs shing yon tan dpag tu med
NK075(bu)002:2565: pa rgyas pa don yin pa'i phyir rtags gzhal yas
NK075(bu)002:2566: khang gi dbyibs gru bzhi pa de yang chos kyi
NK075(bu)002:2567: dbyings la thug pa med pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2568: rtags bum pa'i mtho dman la tshad dpag tu med de de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:2569: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK075(bu)002:2570: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa thugs
NK075(bu)002:2571: rang rig pa'i ye shes la gcig pa don yin
NK075(bu)002:2572: la / rtags gzhal yas khang rtse mo sbra'am gur lta bur 'khyil ba de ting /
NK075(bu)002:2576: rnam par thar pa ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i sgo nas
NK075(bu)002:2577: ma h+aa'i rgan po a tir 'jug pa'i tshul ni
NK075(bu)002:2578: don yin la / rtags gzhal yas khang gi phyogs
NK075(bu)002:2579: bzhir sgo bzhi ni rgya sgo lta bu ma yin
NK075(bu)002:2580: don yin la / te / sgo glo 'bur du
NK075(bu)002:2581: yod pa la sgo rgyan dang ldan pa can no
NK075(bu)002:2582: don yin la / te / // theg pa gzhan
NK075(bu)002:2583: las 'dir bla na med pa'i theg pas dpags shing
NK075(bu)002:2584: der bgrod pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2585: rtags gzhal yas khang gi 'og gzhi 'bur 'phang du
NK075(bu)002:2586: rdo rje 'greng bu'am khru res lha snam gru chad
NK075(bu)002:2587: rtsibs mchan rtsibs lte ba rnams rim gyis dpags pa'o
NK075(bu)002:2588: // 'khor ba las rnam par thar pa'i theg pa brgyad bgrod pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2589: rtags sgo them zhabs su them skas rta baba phyi bzhi nang bzhi ste brgyad /
NK075(bu)002:2590: rang sa'i 'bras bu brgyad thob pa don yin la
NK075(bu)002:2591: rtags su rgyan rta bab brgyad dang ldan pa ni
NK075(bu)002:2592: / rta bab bzhi la bang rim re re la rgyan gnyis gnyis te brgyad ni /
NK075(bu)002:2593: rta rkang chu skyes rin chen sgrom //
NK075(bu)002:2594: ma skyes thabs kyi za rang tshags //
NK075(bu)002:2596: sna tshogs khyung mgo rim par dkrigs //
NK075(bu)002:2598: ye shes re rer yang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2599: rtags rigs thams cad kyi bdag nyid kun tu bzang
NK075(bu)002:2600: po dang ni bzang mo gnyis kyis badga po byed
NK075(bu)002:2601: pa'i gnas rigs bzhi'i kha dog can gyi rin po
NK075(bu)002:2602: che'i glo 'bur mkhar thabs bzhi yis mdzes par byed
NK075(bu)002:2603: pa dang / 'o na kun bzang yab yum dbus
NK075(bu)002:2604: su bzhugs pa bshad pa dang 'dir glo 'bur du
NK075(bu)002:2605: bskyed pa gnyis bldab ce na ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2606: chos 'chad pa'i dus su kun bzang yab yum dbus su bzhugs la /
NK075(bu)002:2607: sgom pa'i dus su kun bzang yab yum rigs thams
NK075(bu)002:2608: cad kyi byed pa po'am bskyed pa'i bdag nyid yin
NK075(bu)002:2609: pas / shar nub gnyis kyi glo 'bur gnyis kyi steng du bskyed de /
NK075(bu)002:2610: yang na kun bzang nyid kyis sprul pa thub pa drug byung ba yang der bskyed do //
NK075(bu)002:2613: mtha' yi 'dab mas kun g.yogs pa //
NK075(bu)002:2614: ye shes rtsig steng seng ge bltams //
NK075(bu)002:2615: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK075(bu)002:2616: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK075(bu)002:2617: dra ba dra phyed mgul 'khor ldan //
NK075(bu)002:2618: gzugs sogs lha mo 'khrigs pa ste //
NK075(bu)002:2619: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK075(bu)002:2620: bar snang khams kun sprin dpung bzhin //
NK075(bu)002:2622: thugs rje dang sprul pa'i 'phro 'du'i rgyun mi 'chad
NK075(bu)002:2623: pa dang ldan pa don yin la rtags su phreng
NK075(bu)002:2624: ba / bden pa gnyis su med pa don yin la rtags rin po che'i chun 'phyang ngo //
NK075(bu)002:2625: thabs ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa don yin la rtags mdzes gdung rin po che'i shar bu /
NK075(bu)002:2626: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag rgyan
NK075(bu)002:2627: du rdzogs pa don yin la rtags 'dod yon lnga'i
NK075(bu)002:2628: lha mo dpag tu med pa phyogs bcur 'khrigs shing
NK075(bu)002:2635: ka dung bcu drug gi phrag /
NK075(bu)002:2636: d+r+wa ba dra khugs kyi gseb nas mchod pa phul bar sgom /
NK075(bu)002:2637: sgo rgyan ni sgo khang nang gi rgyan dgu dang /
NK075(bu)002:2638: bcu gcig rdo rje'i 'greng bar la sogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2639: phyi yi rgyan ni ye nas mnyam pa nyid las
NK075(bu)002:2640: mi 'da' zhing nyon mongs pa gtan nas mi skye
NK075(bu)002:2642: rtags ta la'i ljon shing bcad zin brgyad dam bcu drug /
NK075(bu)002:2643: man ngag ltar na mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi gdan yin pas so /
NK075(bu)002:2645: gdul bya'i re ba yid la bsam pa bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:2646: skong ba don yin la rtags dpag bsam gyi shing
NK075(bu)002:2647: la rin po che'i tshong tshong gis spras pa la
NK075(bu)002:2648: / dril bu g.yer khas brgyan pa /
NK075(bu)002:2649: ta la'i grangs dang mthun pa /
NK075(bu)002:2650: de dag gi bar bar du rin po che'i phung po dang /
NK075(bu)002:2653: dpag bsam gyi grangs ltar yod do //
NK075(bu)002:2654: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2655: rtags 'jig rten gyi lha chen po rnams kyis bskor ba'i gdan la /
NK075(bu)002:2656: gser gyi sa gzhi'i steng ne'u seng sngon po'i thang /
NK075(bu)002:2657: de'i nang na me tog ldum zing dkar po'i tshal yod do //
NK075(bu)002:2658: de lta bu'i gzhal yas khang gi rgyan du mar
NK075(bu)002:2659: snang ba'ang des dri za kho rang gar bsdad pa'i
NK075(bu)002:2660: sar gansa khang yang rang shugs su grub pa bzhin
NK075(bu)002:2661: ston pa longs sku'i dgongs pa ye shes kyi rtsal
NK075(bu)002:2662: la gzhal yas khang rgyan dang bcas pa rang bzhin
NK075(bu)002:2663: gyis grub pas / ngo bo snang stong tha mi
NK075(bu)002:2664: dad pa phyogs bcu mu mtha' med par rang snang
NK075(bu)002:2666: rtags gzhal yas khang gi pany+tsa r+aa ga yongs su ma chad de sna rum pa ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2667: de nyid la rgya dang khyon dka' tshad gzung du
NK075(bu)002:2668: med cing spyod yul dang bral ba'i phyir gzhal yas
NK075(bu)002:2669: khang ngo // rang rig pa'i ye shes 'ba' zhig kun tu shar nas snang ba don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2670: rtags nang dang phyi rol lta bu gzhal yas khang
NK075(bu)002:2671: de la med de kun tu yang nang du gyur
NK075(bu)002:2672: pa'o // 'og gzhi gdan thabs ni ye shes lnga dang ldan pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2673: rtags 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lnga'am /
NK075(bu)002:2674: yang na 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan smon lam gus pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:2675: yon tan gyi che bas nas tshogs bcom pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:2677: thugs rig pa rang snang ba'i gdan dang lngar bshad
NK075(bu)002:2678: pa las dang po 'og gzhi ni chos kyi 'khor
NK075(bu)002:2679: lo rgyun chad med par bskor ba don yin la
NK075(bu)002:2680: / rtags 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa /
NK075(bu)002:2681: gnyis pa smon lam gus pa'i gdan ni /
NK075(bu)002:2682: sa mtha'i byang chub sems dpa' smon lam gyi dbang
NK075(bu)002:2683: gis seng ge la sogs par sprul pas lus gdan
NK075(bu)002:2684: du phul nas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK075(bu)002:2685: rna bas chos nyan cing shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs zhes rgya mtsho dang /
NK075(bu)002:2687: spar khab rnams las bshad kyang /
NK075(bu)002:2688: de dag ni rgyu'i theg pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:2689: rgyud mas sbyangs pa lam pa'i dbang yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2690: 'bras bu'i theg pa'am sgyu 'phrul gyi dbang du ston pa sku lnga lhun grub /
NK075(bu)002:2691: 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho yin pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2692: smon lam gus pa'i gdan 'dir bshad pa ma yin no //
NK075(bu)002:2693: gsum pa yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan ni /
NK075(bu)002:2694: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2695: de yang shes rab rang bzhin med pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2697: thabs 'gag pa med pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2699: thugs nyes pa'i skyon ma chagsa pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2701: bzhi pa sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan ni gdul
NK075(bu)002:2702: bya'i re ba skong bas dgos 'dod lhun gyi grub
NK075(bu)002:2704: rtags rin po che'i khri rkang /
NK075(bu)002:2705: de yang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid lhun gyi grub pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2706: rtags khri rkang re re la yang mdzod mig bdun bdun dang ldan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2707: lnga pa thugs rig pa rang snang gi gdan ni /
NK075(bu)002:2708: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs par 'bras bu'i chos rnams lhun gyis grub pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2709: rtags sems can lnga'i gdan du snang ba ste de yang dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)002:2710: thugs ni mi 'jigs rnam bzhis bdud bzhi 'joms /
NK075(bu)002:2711: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)002:2712: sku ni mi dge bcu rnams stobs bcus 'dul //
NK075(bu)002:2713: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)002:2714: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK075(bu)002:2715: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)002:2716: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal ba'i gsung //
NK075(bu)002:2717: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)002:2718: las ni 'phriin las bzhi yis thogs med sgrol //
NK075(bu)002:2719: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)002:2721: de la gdan gyi rim pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:2722: skyes bu lnga la lnga rtseg ste //
NK075(bu)002:2723: sems dpa' la ni sum rtseg go //
NK075(bu)002:2724: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK075(bu)002:2725: kun bzang yab yum bzhi rtseg go //
NK075(bu)002:2728: sgo ba yab yum la pad+ma dang nyi ma gnyis rtseg go //
NK075(bu)002:2730: dkyil 'khor la dgod pa'i tshe sum rtseg dang /
NK075(bu)002:2731: chos 'chad pa'i tshe lnga rtseg tu bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:2732: gdan gyi steng du zla ba 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)002:2733: gsang snying 'grel par mang du snang yang /
NK075(bu)002:2735: yang zhi ba la lha kun la zla ba steng du 'ong la /
NK075(bu)002:2736: khro lha kun la nyi ma steng du 'ong zhes bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:2737: de ltar ye shes kyi rtsal las gzhal yas khang
NK075(bu)002:2738: gi gdan dang rgyan du ma la shar nas snang
NK075(bu)002:2739: bas dbyings phyogs gcig tu bzung ba'i mtha' dang bral
NK075(bu)002:2740: bas gcig pa ma yin pas ye shes sna tshogs
NK075(bu)002:2741: su shar nas snang ba'i dus la rang bzhin med
NK075(bu)002:2742: de chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pas du ma'i
NK075(bu)002:2744: de yang gsang snying gi 'og min ces pa nas /
NK075(bu)002:2745: rin po che'i gdan la zhes pa'i bar gyis ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2751: gnas de na ston de la 'khor de gus pa'i
NK075(bu)002:2752: tshul du gtso 'khor gyi dgongs pa la dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:2753: kyang gdul bya'i snang ngo la gtso 'khor gyi tshul
NK075(bu)002:2754: du ston pa kun bzang gi rgyal tshab kyi tshul
NK075(bu)002:2755: 'dzin cing rgyud 'chang byed kyi skyes bu rgyal ba
NK075(bu)002:2756: rigs lnga yab yum bcu dang rgyal sras byang chub
NK075(bu)002:2757: sems dpa'i tshul 'dzin pa'i 'khor sems dpa' yab yum
NK075(bu)002:2758: bcu drug dang / 'jigsa byed khro tshul 'dzin pa'i 'khor khro bo yab yum brgyad /
NK075(bu)002:2759: thugsa rje sprul pa'i 'khor thub drug gi tshul 'dzin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2760: dad pa can gtam nyan pa'i 'khor sangs rgyas kyi
NK075(bu)002:2761: thugs rje dang gdul bya'i smon lam 'grel pa'i stobs
NK075(bu)002:2763: sogsa kyi sgras dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa lnga'i tshul 'dzin nas gzhal yas khang gi rgyab /
NK075(bu)002:2765: me tog ldum zing dkar po'i steng du bzhugs so //
NK075(bu)002:2768: 'khor de rnams kyi bzhugs tshul ni /
NK075(bu)002:2769: rigs lnga yab yum bcu ni /
NK075(bu)002:2770: ston pa kun bzang dang dgongs pa dbyer med pa'i bzhugs tshul gtso bo yab yum dang mthun no //
NK075(bu)002:2771: sems dpa' yab yum ni lam mthar ma phyin bar
NK075(bu)002:2772: du bdag gzhan gyi don bsgrub dgos pa'i tshul du
NK075(bu)002:2773: g.yon bskums / g.yas gdan la 'abba pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2774: khro bo yab yum ni sgo bsrung ba'i tshul du
NK075(bu)002:2775: zur gyis lta ba'am phyir lta ba'i zhabs gyad bkyag
NK075(bu)002:2776: thabs su dang / thub pa rnams ni 'gro ba'i
NK075(bu)002:2777: don rgyun chad med par mdzad pa'i phyir zhabs 'gro
NK075(bu)002:2778: thabs su dang / bar bzhugs pa'o // mang ba dang khyab pa'i tshad gnyis bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2780: de lta bu'i sprul pa dang rang rgyud pa'i tshogs /
NK075(bu)002:2782: tshad las 'das pa'i brjod kyis mi lang yang cha
NK075(bu)002:2783: lugs kyi rnam grangs ni gong gi bzhi bcu rtsa
NK075(bu)002:2785: yab yum gtso 'khor du bzhugs shing chos kyi dbyingsa
NK075(bu)002:2786: mu mtha' med par khyab pa'i rang bzhin mngon du
NK075(bu)002:2788: rtags gzhal yas khang lhas gang nas khyab par bzhugs so //
NK075(bu)002:2790: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pas //
NK075(bu)002:2792: gnyis su med par bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan no //
NK075(bu)002:2795: dpe nor bu rin po che la gdul bya rang
NK075(bu)002:2796: rang gi bsam pa bzhin du dgos 'dod 'byung ba
NK075(bu)002:2797: ltar du sdud pa po yang gdul bya rang gis
NK075(bu)002:2798: gang mos bzhin du sku mang'a ba'i gsang bdag nyid
NK075(bu)002:2799: ni snyan cha lnga ldan du yod pas rgyud de
NK075(bu)002:2800: yi bdag po yin pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2801: sdud pa po gsang bdag rang yin cing tan+t+ra ste
NK075(bu)002:2802: rgyud thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba de'i don sdud pa
NK075(bu)002:2803: po bsdus nas mi dang lha la sogs pa la
NK075(bu)002:2804: brgyud pa yang rang rang gi mos pa bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:2805: lha la ku ma ra ste 'jam dpal du snang
NK075(bu)002:2806: ba dang / klu la spyan tshor te spyan ras
NK075(bu)002:2807: gzigs su snang ba nas rgyud gsung par 'dod do
NK075(bu)002:2808: ba dang / // mi dang mi min te dam pa'i rigs can lnga ni /
NK075(bu)002:2809: gsang bdag tu snang ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:2810: de'i don ni gsang bdag da ni ston pa kun
NK075(bu)002:2811: tu bzang po de yi thugs las skyes pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:2812: / ston pas gsungs pa'i rgyud de yi don ni
NK075(bu)002:2813: gsang bdag des bsdus nas dam pa'i rigs can lnga
NK075(bu)002:2814: dang rgyal po dzahl sogs pa'i skal ldan rnams la
NK075(bu)002:2815: gsungs pa ni rigsa te 'thad do //
NK075(bu)002:2817: theg chen la mos pa 'jam dpal /
NK075(bu)002:2818: theg chung la spyan ras gzigs zer /
NK075(bu)002:2819: kha cig gi sku sgyu 'phrul la 'jam dpal /
NK075(bu)002:2821: thugs sgyu 'phrul la phyag rdor du 'dod pa snang yang dpyad par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:2824: chos sku longs sku sprul sku rdo rje'i sku mngon
NK075(bu)002:2825: par byang chub pa'i sku dang lnga ni lam pa'i
NK075(bu)002:2826: sa tshad mtho dman gyi blo yis phye ba'i 'khor
NK075(bu)002:2827: rnamas la so sor rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams
NK075(bu)002:2828: par chos bstan pa'i dus tha dad du snang yang
NK075(bu)002:2829: / 'dir ni ston pa sku lnga lhun gyis grub
NK075(bu)002:2830: pa kun tu bzang po des lhan cig pa yi
NK075(bu)002:2832: bstan pa gsung lnga dus gcig tu snang ba de
NK075(bu)002:2833: tshul ci ltar rtogs pa'i dus ni 'khor gang gis
NK075(bu)002:2834: ston pa kun bzang gi zhal mthong ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2835: bstan pa gsung lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i don de
NK075(bu)002:2836: rtogs nas sangs rgyas pa de'i tshe na yang dus
NK075(bu)002:2837: bzhi mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos pa yin te
NK075(bu)002:2839: ston pa kun bzang gi zhal mthong nas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2840: bstan pa gsung lnga lhun grub gsang ba'i snying po'i
NK075(bu)002:2841: don dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid mngon du gyur nas
NK075(bu)002:2842: / gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid gzhir nges /
NK075(bu)002:2846: de yang rang bzhina gsang ba'i snying po chos thams
NK075(bu)002:2847: cad mnyam pa'i ngang dus bzhi'i rtog pa dang bral
NK075(bu)002:2848: ba de go phye ba'i 'khor rnams la rtag pa
NK075(bu)002:2849: rgyun du ston 'khor bstan pa'i tshul du thugsa rje
NK075(bu)002:2850: 'dzom nas dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid las shugs ldan
NK075(bu)002:2852: nus ldan du lam mthar phyin nas shes bya bag
NK075(bu)002:2853: la nyal gyi dri ma dag pa'i dus la mngon
NK075(bu)002:2857: lam mthar phyin nas sangs rgyas pa de yi tshe
NK075(bu)002:2858: rang bzhin bcos bslad dang bral ba nges lung gsang
NK075(bu)002:2859: ba'i snying po de mngon du snang ste /
NK075(bu)002:2860: tshul ci ltar du snang na gsung lnga lhun grub
NK075(bu)002:2861: kyi tshul gyis snang mtshon bya 'khor gang la snang
NK075(bu)002:2862: na lhan cig pa'i 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho la
NK075(bu)002:2863: snang / snang ba'i ngo bo de gang yin na /
NK075(bu)002:2864: mtshon byed tshig gi bstan pa rang snang bas gsang ba'i snying po de nyid brjod do /
NK075(bu)002:2865: 'o na ston pa kun bzang gis lhan cig pa'i
NK075(bu)002:2866: 'khor la gsung ba'i tshe tshig tu brjod dam zhe
NK075(bu)002:2868: mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud de dag de'i dus su mtshon byed med par rang mtshan sgra ste /
NK075(bu)002:2869: dpe nyi zla shar ba dang chu ldeng mtha' dag
NK075(bu)002:2870: gi nang du gzugs thogs chags med par 'char bzhin
NK075(bu)002:2871: du / ston pa kun bzang gi zhal mthong nas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2872: 'khor gyi dri dag pa dang ston pa'i dgongs pa
NK075(bu)002:2873: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don 'khor la mngon
NK075(bu)002:2874: du gyur pa dus mnyam pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2875: zhi ba la khro bor snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2877: des 'gro ba mi la sogs pa gang dag gzugs
NK075(bu)002:2878: su snang ba'i yul la rang rang gi rigs mthun
NK075(bu)002:2879: snang na gcig la gcig dga' bar byed la rang
NK075(bu)002:2880: rang gi rig pa mi mthun pa'i dgra la ni
NK075(bu)002:2881: dga' ba de las sgyur bar byed pa'i 'jigsa gzugs
NK075(bu)002:2883: rgyal ba'i gleng gzhi de bzhin lugs 'byung rnams la zhi ba /
NK075(bu)002:2884: lug ldog rnams khro bo'i gleng gzhir bsgyur ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:2885: da ni gleng gzhi spyi'i go don ni /
NK075(bu)002:2886: rgyu gleng gzhi la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:2891: dgos ched ni gnyis te gleng gzhi tshogs pas bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2892: gleng gzhi tshogs lugs kyi lo rgyus la brten nas /
NK075(bu)002:2893: rjes 'jug gi lam pas yid ches shing 'jug pa'i dgos ched yod do //
NK075(bu)002:2895: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu'am gzhi yin pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2896: ngo bo ni phun sum tshogs pa drug ldan cig yin no //
NK075(bu)002:2897: rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:2898: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi /
NK075(bu)002:2899: rgyud khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi /
NK075(bu)002:2900: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi /
NK075(bu)002:2901: gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:2902: dang po sngags phyi rgyud yo ga man chad kyi spyod yul ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2906: nang ltar na gnas snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo //
NK075(bu)002:2907: ston pa srog mi shigs pa'i thig le wam gi dbyibs can /
NK075(bu)002:2908: 'khor rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rtog pa /
NK075(bu)002:2909: bstan pa don dam pa byang chub kyi sems ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can no //
NK075(bu)002:2910: dus snga phyi'i rtog pa dang bral te /
NK075(bu)002:2911: sdud pa po tshogs bdun kun gyi rjes su 'jug pa yid kyi rnam shes /
NK075(bu)002:2914: ston pa gsang ba'i rdo rje /
NK075(bu)002:2915: 'khor bde ba sdom par byed pa'i yid sogs rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rtog pa /
NK075(bu)002:2916: bstan pa dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha'i skad cig
NK075(bu)002:2917: ma rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes so
NK075(bu)002:2918: // dus sdon pa gsang ba'i sku gtsug tor 'khor lo sgyur ba'i dus so //
NK075(bu)002:2919: sdud pa po bde ba sdom par byed pa'i yid do //
NK075(bu)002:2920: 'di ni gleng gzhi bsdus pas ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2921: gnyis pa rgyud khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:2922: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2924: ston pa ni drug pa spyi'i gzugs can no //
NK075(bu)002:2925: 'khor ni dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor rigs lnga yab yum /
NK075(bu)002:2926: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ni sems dpa' dang sems ma /
NK075(bu)002:2927: 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor ni khro bo dang khro mo rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:2928: bstan pa ni rgyud gzhung 'di nyid do //
NK075(bu)002:2929: sdud pa po ni rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa'i
NK075(bu)002:2930: 'khor gyi nang nas phyag na rdo rjes bsdus so
NK075(bu)002:2932: 'di ni gsang snying gi le'u dang pos ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2933: gsum pa bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:2934: gnas phyogs bcu'i zhing khams mtha' yas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2935: ston pa thub pa drug go //
NK075(bu)002:2937: bstan pa 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun par chos ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2938: dus ni ston 'khor gnas gsum 'dzam pa'i dus so //
NK075(bu)002:2939: 'di ni gsang snying gi le'u gsum pa'i stod kyis ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2940: bzhi pa gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:2941: gnas bzod par dka' ba'i dur khrod chen po /
NK075(bu)002:2942: ston pa dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka /
NK075(bu)002:2945: dus gdul bya skabs la bab pa'i dus so //
NK075(bu)002:2946: 'di ni gsang snying gi le'u bco lnga pas ston no //
NK075(bu)002:2947: rkyen gleng bslang ba la gsum /
NK075(bu)002:2951: gong gi gleng gzhi de rnams kyi rjes su rkyen gyis gleng bslang ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:2952: de la sa nang tshigs su bcad na gsum ste /
NK075(bu)002:2953: ston pasa mdun bsu ste gnang bar zhal gyis bzhes nas gleng bslang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2954: 'khor gyis gus pas zhus nas gleng bslang ba dang skabs las gleng du langas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:2957: ston pas gnang ba dang 'khor gyis dri ba'i rkyen
NK075(bu)002:2958: du gang gyur pa ni phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams
NK075(bu)002:2959: ston pa kun bzang yab yum 'khril sbyor gyi skur
NK075(bu)002:2960: bzhengs nas mthar lam pa rnams la dbang bskur ba
NK075(bu)002:2961: 'di rkyen gyis gleng bslang ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2962: de la'ang yab kyis bslang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2963: yum gyis bslang ba'i rgyas bshad ni /
NK075(bu)002:2965: de nas bstan pa de ston pa des gsung la
NK075(bu)002:2966: ma rag pa ni rkyen gleng bslang zhes pa'i nges
NK075(bu)002:2967: pa'i tshig kyang de ltar du grub la rkyen gleng
NK075(bu)002:2968: bslang gi ngo bo'ang de yin no //
NK075(bu)002:2969: gnas skabsa kyi dris pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2970: lan 'debs pa ni gleng bslang ba smos ci dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:2972: dris pa dang len byed bdo bas na gleng langs
NK075(bu)002:2973: zhes pa'i nges tshig de nges par 'grub pa yin
NK075(bu)002:2976: thabs lam la spyod pa'i gleng gzhi 'tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2977: shes rab grol lam gyi gleng gzhi gang 'tshogs pa'i tshe na yang /
NK075(bu)002:2978: thabs grol gyi bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen byed cing
NK075(bu)002:2979: bstan pa 'byung la ma rag pa byed pa ste
NK075(bu)002:2980: / de yang lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi don bya ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:2981: dang po rgyu gleng gzhi tshogs pa nas ston pa'i thugs rjes rkyen gleng bslang bar 'gyur lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:2982: ston pas mdun bsu ba ste /
