NK075(bu)002:2984: gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2985: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang yin /
NK075(bu)002:2987: don dam nges pa'i tshig gis rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po don dngos su ston pa la /
NK075(bu)002:2988: de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:2989: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis mthar lam pa la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2991: gsang ba'i snying po'i don mngon du 'byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:2992: chos sku'i lhan cig pa'i 'khor du gyur pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2994: bag la nyal gyi dri ma dag pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:2995: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du gyur pa /
NK075(bu)002:2996: de rnams dus mnyam pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:2997: de yang yab kyis ye shes yum gyis dbyings /
NK075(bu)002:2998: zhal 'byor bas zung 'jug dang gsum gyis mtha' gru bcad pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)002:2999: rtags kun bzang yab yum gyi yab yum gyi thig le dbab bzlog byas nas /
NK075(bu)002:3000: byang sems nyi zla'i dbang byin pa la sogs pa dbang bzhi'i cho 'phrul bstan pa la /
NK075(bu)002:3002: 'khor la sems lnga cig char du dbyings ye shes zung 'jug gi mtha' gru rgyas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3003: thabs lam ltar na sems lnga /
NK075(bu)002:3004: thabs lam ltar bu cig char du bde stong gi
NK075(bu)002:3005: ye shes kyi mtha' gru ma lus par rgyas pa'o
NK075(bu)002:3006: // 'o na rgyud don dang gleng bslang dmigs 'dres zer na /
NK075(bu)002:3008: yab yum gyi skur bzhengs nas /
NK075(bu)002:3009: brda thabs kyis rgyud don 'byung ba'i rkyen byang sems kyis byas pas na /
NK075(bu)002:3010: rkyen gleng bslang ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3011: don de 'khor gyis rtogs pa la rgyud don du 'dod do //
NK075(bu)002:3012: de yang mthar lam pa des /
NK075(bu)002:3013: ston pa kun bzang gi zhal mthong nas /
NK075(bu)002:3015: rgyud don mngon du rgyur pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3016: bag nyal gyi dri ma chad pa la sogs pa dus skad cig gcig la rdzogs pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:3018: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas zhes pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3020: dus mtha'i skad cig nyid kyis gshegs //
NK075(bu)002:3022: go phye ba'i 'khor gyis gzhan gyi don bya ba'i
NK075(bu)002:3023: phyir du rgyu gleng gzhi 'tshogsa nas dbang thob nas
NK075(bu)002:3024: grol ba'i chos kyi sku'i 'khor de'i thugs rjes rkyen
NK075(bu)002:3025: gleng bslang bar 'gyur ba 'khor gyis gus pas zhu
NK075(bu)002:3026: ba ni thun mong gi gleng bslang ba yin te
NK075(bu)002:3027: / go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du /
NK075(bu)002:3028: 'di nyid rtogs pa la 'di nyid dang /
NK075(bu)002:3029: 'di nyid ma rtogs pa rnams la lam stegs gsungs
NK075(bu)002:3030: par zhu ba'i tshul byas pas zhal 'dzum pa dang
NK075(bu)002:3036: dgyes pa'i tshul drug gi sgo nas lhan cig pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3037: 'khor la mtshon byed gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud 'di
NK075(bu)002:3039: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3042: lam stegs kyi ston pa thub pa drug spro bar zhal gyis bzhes nas /
NK075(bu)002:3043: bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig gis rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK075(bu)002:3044: snying po'i don brgyud nas ston pa'i thabs chos kyi
NK075(bu)002:3045: sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:3046: 'di ni gsang ba'i snying po'i le'u gnyis pa ltar sprul pa mar 'gyed pa'i dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3047: dgongs 'dus ltar lam yar bgrod kyi dbang du /
NK075(bu)002:3048: mthar lam pa la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis dbang bskur bas rgyud don 'byung yang /
NK075(bu)002:3049: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du zhu ba byas pas /
NK075(bu)002:3050: ston pa kun bzang gi lam mthar phyin gyi sangs
NK075(bu)002:3051: rgyas de nyid la 'chad byed rig pa'i skyes bur
NK075(bu)002:3052: dbang bskur nas / ston pa'i mdun logs su seng
NK075(bu)002:3053: ge'i khri la bzhugs nas rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs sna
NK075(bu)002:3054: tshogs kyi sgo nas chos ston par bzhed do //
NK075(bu)002:3061: dang po brjod pa la yang brjod bya rjod byed gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:3062: brjod bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud yin
NK075(bu)002:3063: la de ci lta ba bzhin du rjod par byed
NK075(bu)002:3064: pa'i bdag po ston pa kun bzang gis rgyud kyis
NK075(bu)002:3065: don de nyid la rkyen yi ge'i rgyud dang tshig
NK075(bu)002:3066: tu snang ba rjod byed yin te /
NK075(bu)002:3067: de'i don ngang mo 'gros kyis 'brel pa'i rim pa dang ldan nas nyams su len dgos kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3068: gang zag gzu lums can dang ras chod can dgag pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:3069: rjod byed tshig rgyud 'di nyid la 'chola zhing 'khrugsa nas yod pa la /
NK075(bu)002:3070: de yang 'brel pa bzhi ldan gyi sgo nas nyams su len dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:3071: sngon byung du rgyu gleng gzhi tshogs nas rkyen gleng
NK075(bu)002:3072: bslangs nas rgyud don 'byung ba thabs yin pa dang
NK075(bu)002:3073: / de las rgyud 'di snang ba ni thabs de las byung ba yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3076: man ngag gab pa mngon du 'byin nas thabs grol
NK075(bu)002:3077: gyi lam gnyis mngon du rtogs nas nyams su len
NK075(bu)002:3078: pa'i rgyu / mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo thob pa ni 'bras bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:3079: rgyud don gyi dngos po ni dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3080: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo ni dgos pa'i yang dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3081: dgos sogs chos bzhi 'dir bkod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3082: dgongs 'dus dang spar khab ltar du 'brel pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3085: zur po che la sogs pa'i 'dod pa la /
NK075(bu)002:3087: bstan bcos la tshang lugs dang /
NK075(bu)002:3088: la las snod bcud la tshang lugs la sogs pa bshad srol mang du snang yang /
NK075(bu)002:3089: 'dir bshad pa ni ston pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3091: chos de dang rjes 'jug lam pa'i blo 'brel dgos lugs /
NK075(bu)002:3092: blos rtogs nas nyams su len pas mthar thug sangs
NK075(bu)002:3093: rgyas thob lugs su 'brel bar bshad pa yin no
NK075(bu)002:3094: // de yang gleng gzhi la thabs grol gnyis byung
NK075(bu)002:3095: bas de'i rjes su dgos 'brel bzhi yang thabs grol
NK075(bu)002:3096: ltar du nges par 'gro bas grol lam ltar du
NK075(bu)002:3097: thun mong du bshad pa ni gong du song bas
NK075(bu)002:3098: // / thabs lam ltar du thun mong ma yin par bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3099: rdo rje rtse mo'i byang sems kyi thig le chen
NK075(bu)002:3100: po dbab bzlog gi thabs dang bcas pa ni brjod
NK075(bu)002:3101: par bya ba'o // thig le dga' ba bcu drug gi bde ba ni rjod par byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3102: bde ba myong bar byed pa'i thig le bsdoms pa rlung dang bcas pa ni thabs so //
NK075(bu)002:3103: des rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i bde ba myong ba ni thabs las byung ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:3104: thig le bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni rgyu /
NK075(bu)002:3105: ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon du shar ba ni 'bras bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:3106: thabs lam gyi sems lnga rgyud du rim par skye ba ni dgos pa /
NK075(bu)002:3107: dga' ba bcu drug gi tha ma'i cha la sogs
NK075(bu)002:3108: pa'i dga' ba'i ye shes chen po ni dgos pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3109: yang dgos pa'o // 'dren pa'i tshig la gsum /
NK075(bu)002:3113: tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i dbu nas zhabs
NK075(bu)002:3114: kyi le'u'i grangs rnams kyi bshad thabs ni mdor bsdus
NK075(bu)002:3116: dpe me long la gzugs brnyan gsal ba ltar bshad
NK075(bu)002:3117: thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu yis rgyud kyis don mtshon
NK075(bu)002:3118: nus pas / de bas rgyud kyi le'u'i grangs rnams
NK075(bu)002:3119: bshad thabs su 'og nas bshad pa'i tshig bcu po
NK075(bu)002:3124: spyi don sdud pa'i tshig seng ge mchongs pa ltar bshad /
NK075(bu)002:3125: rnam par dbye ba'i tshig stag gi mchongs pa ltar /
NK075(bu)002:3126: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig khyung nam mkha' la lding ba ltar /
NK075(bu)002:3127: rang rkyen gnyer ba'i tshig gis rus sbal gnur 'gros lta bu /
NK075(bu)002:3128: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig dus kyi 'brug sgra /
NK075(bu)002:3129: gtar kha gegs sel gyi tshig glag mo gzan la 'jum pa /
NK075(bu)002:3130: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig rna phrug brag la 'dzeg pa /
NK075(bu)002:3131: 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros mtshon pa dpe yi tshig me long g.ya' dag pa /
NK075(bu)002:3132: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig seng ge'i phru gu'i
NK075(bu)002:3133: rtsal sbyong ba ltar bshad pa dang bcu yis tshig
NK075(bu)002:3134: thog tu don 'drena par shes par gyis la bshad
NK075(bu)002:3135: thabs bsdus pa bcu po de yang rgyud don gyi
NK075(bu)002:3136: bye brag mi 'dra ba'i dbye bas le'u'i rim pa
NK075(bu)002:3137: bzhin du bdag po gtso gang che ba ma gtogs
NK075(bu)002:3138: pa dang la bshad thabs kyi tshig bcu po bzhin
NK075(bu)002:3139: rnams tshang ba'i nges pa med /
NK075(bu)002:3141: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig mi dgos pa dang 'dra'o //
NK075(bu)002:3143: rnam par dbye ba 'brel mtshams sbyor ba /
NK075(bu)002:3144: rang rkyen gnyer ba ste spyi 'gro gsum ni le'u kun gyi shes par 'gyur ba'i thabs yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3145: yang na bdag slob dpon la bcu tshang mi dgos la /
NK075(bu)002:3146: gzhan slob ma la bshad na bcu ka tshang dgos /
NK075(bu)002:3148: slob dpon la dgos mi dgos dpyad par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:3150: seng ge mchongas pa'i dus na mchongs pa'i chos gcig
NK075(bu)002:3151: kha 'og tu sa tshigs du ma tshud pa ltar
NK075(bu)002:3152: du spyi don bsdus pa'i tshig gis rnam grangsa kyi
NK075(bu)002:3153: tshig lam mang po yang don gyi ngo bo gcig
NK075(bu)002:3154: tu khog dbub nas sdud par byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3156: b+y+aa g+h+ri ste stag mo mchongas pa'i tshe seng ge
NK075(bu)002:3157: mchongs pa la chos gcig yod pa de bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:3158: / bgrad par bya ba'i tshigs dum bur bcad nas
NK075(bu)002:3159: mchongs pa bzhin du rnam par dbye ba'i tshig gis
NK075(bu)002:3160: tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i tshig dang don
NK075(bu)002:3161: gyi dmigs pa so sor phye ba'i thabsa su bacada
NK075(bu)002:3162: nas ming 'dogs gsal bar ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3164: ka la sing+ka ste bya khyung lding ba'i dus su chosa bzhi po mtshon te /
NK075(bu)002:3167: gshog pa rlob pa'i rtsol ba med /
NK075(bu)002:3168: ngam 'brog dang g.yang sa la nyam mi nga /
NK075(bu)002:3169: bya lam la rjes med pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:3170: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig gis rnal 'byor pa'i lta ba spyan gyi 'phang bcad pa'i tshe /
NK075(bu)002:3171: theg pa thams cad khob 'og tu tshud /
NK075(bu)002:3172: lam bgrod pa'i rtsol ba med /
NK075(bu)002:3173: srid pa dang zhi ba la nyam mi nga /
NK075(bu)002:3174: blta bya lta byed blo yul du rtog pa med pas rtog pa'ang med do //
NK075(bu)002:3176: rus sbala 'grosa kyi chos gnyis yod de /
NK075(bu)002:3177: gnyis po'i don gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:3178: g.yo 'gul mi mngon par shugs kyis 'gro zhing /
NK075(bu)002:3179: sa stong mi lus par rjes kyis khyab pa dang mthar phyin pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:3180: rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig gis 'bru stong mi gzhag
NK075(bu)002:3181: tsheg gi gzer bus gdab cing don brda sprod par
NK075(bu)002:3182: byed pa dang / gzhung don mthar phyin dgos so //
NK075(bu)002:3184: dus min par mi 'byung dbyar gyi dus su 'brug sgra dang char pa 'byung /
NK075(bu)002:3185: de 'byung ba dang skye bo rnams kyis de ring
NK075(bu)002:3186: nas dbyar dgun dabye'o zhes dus tshod kyi spros pa
NK075(bu)002:3187: chod pa dang / chos gsum po desa yid ches pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:3188: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig gis theg pa 'og
NK075(bu)002:3189: ma'i chos skad kyis sel ma zhugs pa'i ma h+aa
NK075(bu)002:3190: rang gi bka' nas bshad pas gsang sngags kyi gtan
NK075(bu)002:3191: tshigs tshad ma la rtogs pa bzhi /
NK075(bu)002:3193: mnyam bzhi rnams theg 'og gi skabs su mi 'byung /
NK075(bu)002:3195: des the tshom chod cing dbyer med kyi lta ba
NK075(bu)002:3196: la yid ches pa dang gsuma gyis gzhung le'u'i skabs
NK075(bu)002:3197: dang sbyar nas bden gsum dbyer med kyi sgro 'dogs
NK075(bu)002:3198: chod nas don mngon sum du snang bar brda sprod
NK075(bu)002:3200: glag mo gzan la gzhug pa'i tshe mchu sder gyis phyi'i sha pags pa la mi lta nas bsal /
NK075(bu)002:3201: nang gi glo snying srog bcud 'byin par byed pa'i chos gnyis dang ldan pa ltar /
NK075(bu)002:3202: gtar kha gegs sel gyi tshig gis tshig la mi
NK075(bu)002:3203: ltos nas gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab nas grub
NK075(bu)002:3204: mtha'i don gyi dmigsa ngos bzung la /
NK075(bu)002:3205: slob ma la chos ston pa'i tshe gang mi gsal ba'i gegas rnams basla /
NK075(bu)002:3207: rna phrug brag la 'dzeg pa'i tshe skyes ma thag
NK075(bu)002:3208: tu brag me long gi ngos lta bu la rtse
NK075(bu)002:3210: ri dwags gzhan la mi 'tsham yang /
NK075(bu)002:3211: rna phrug rang la 'tsham pa'i chos gnyis dang ldan pa ltar /
NK075(bu)002:3212: ldem dgongas man ngag gi tshig gis gsang ba zab lam sbas tshul du bstan pa'i don rnams ni /
NK075(bu)002:3214: dgongs pa bzhi dang brgyad kyis khyad par thabs lam gyi don dang sbyar ba 'di /
NK075(bu)002:3215: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud man chad du mi 'tsham yang /
NK075(bu)002:3216: rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud nyams su len pa rnams la 'tshams pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3217: de la dgongs pa bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:3218: mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa /
NK075(bu)002:3221: gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs pa dang bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:3226: bsgyur ba la ldem pa dang brgyad do //
NK075(bu)002:3227: sangs rgyas la bzang ngan du 'dzin pa de las bzlog pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:3228: sangs rgyas rnam gzigs nga yin ces pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3229: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3230: dge ba la 'jug mi nus pa la dge ba phra mo byas pas sangs rgyas thob ces pas /
NK075(bu)002:3231: 'khor ba mtha' yod tsam gyis dus gzhan pa la dgongs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3232: yon tan chung ngu la barlomasa pa dag la mthong
NK075(bu)002:3233: lam ma mthong na don dam mi rtogs pa la
NK075(bu)002:3234: dgongs nas / sangs rgyas dpag med la ma bsten
NK075(bu)002:3235: na don dam mi rtogs zhes don gzhan la dgongs
NK075(bu)002:3236: dgongs nas / pa dang / dge ba byed pa la chog par 'dzin pa rnams la /
NK075(bu)002:3237: dge ba phyogs med du byed par basngagasa shing phyogs
NK075(bu)002:3238: gcig gi dge ba la smod pa ni gang zag
NK075(bu)002:3240: stong nyid la skrag pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3241: bya ba sna tshogs byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3242: stong nyid la zhen pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3243: lam la 'jug mi nus pa'i phyal ba dang bzhi las /
NK075(bu)002:3245: rang bzhin med pa la dgongs nas thams cad yod do //
NK075(bu)002:3247: zhes bshad pa ni gzhug pa la ldem pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3248: kun brtags la dngos po med par bshad /
NK075(bu)002:3249: gzhan dbang la rgyu rkyen rten 'brel yod par bshad /
NK075(bu)002:3250: yongs grub mi 'gyur bar bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3251: mtshan nyid la ldem pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3252: gdul bya rang rang gi bsod nams ngom pa la /
NK075(bu)002:3253: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rgyan cha lugs gzhal yas khang
NK075(bu)002:3254: zhing khams dag pa bstan nas gzhan zil gyis gnon
NK075(bu)002:3255: pa ni gnyen po la ldem pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3256: gdul bya phyin ci log drang ba'i don du don
NK075(bu)002:3257: du mi 'gyur ba la dgongs nas mtshams med pa
NK075(bu)002:3258: lnga byas na sangs rgyas thob /
NK075(bu)002:3261: de'i don rgyas bshad ni dgongs 'dus kyi le'u zhe lnga pa'i nang du gsal lo //
NK075(bu)002:3262: brgyad pa ni bya ngang mo 'gro ba'i tshe drang por 'gro zhing /
NK075(bu)002:3263: snga rjes phyi rjes kyis non nas rjes gnyis 'brel
NK075(bu)002:3264: pa'i chos rnam gnyis dang ldan pa ltar 'brel mtshams
NK075(bu)002:3265: sbyor ba'i tshig gis gzhan slob ma'i don byed nas
NK075(bu)002:3266: bshad pa'i tshe / ngang mo'i 'gros chos ltar le'u
NK075(bu)002:3267: gong 'og gi mtshams sbrel te de yang 'khrugs yod
NK075(bu)002:3268: bshad pa'i tshe / na / 'khrug ltar du sbrel nas drang por bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:3270: me longa gi nang du bzhin gyi skyon yon la
NK075(bu)002:3271: sogs ngos zin pa'i chos yod pa ltar mtshon pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3272: dpe tshig gis shin tu lkog gyur gyi don kun
NK075(bu)002:3278: don gyi phyogs gcig dper blangs pa'i de rnams kyis
NK075(bu)002:3279: mtshon nas thog tu don de dbab nas mi gsal
NK075(bu)002:3281: bcu pa ni mi 'jigas seng ge'i phru gu rtsal
NK075(bu)002:3282: sbyongs ba'i tshe ma'i yar mar phan tshun bsnol mar
NK075(bu)002:3283: mchongs nas ma'i sngon du drang por 'gro ba ltar
NK075(bu)002:3284: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyis tshig gi 'bru dang tshig
NK075(bu)002:3286: don gyi 'khrugs rnams go rim bsdeb /
NK075(bu)002:3287: dkyil gyi go rim barje la /
NK075(bu)002:3288: sgra ci bzhin pa ma yin /
NK075(bu)002:3289: don thun mong ba ma yin pa'i rgyud don phyin ci ma log par ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3290: dgos ched kyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:3292: rgyud kyi tshig gis don mtshon pa lam la mos
NK075(bu)002:3293: par bya ba'i gdul bya la bshad dgos pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:3294: / des bshad thabs bcu'i tshig rnam par phye bas
NK075(bu)002:3295: rgyud kyi don rnams ma 'dres par gsal bar byed
NK075(bu)002:3296: / de / de yang tshul ci ltar du gsal
NK075(bu)002:3297: na thabs lam dang grol lam kun gyi don la
NK075(bu)002:3298: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po gnas pa la bshad
NK075(bu)002:3299: thabs 'dren pa'i tshig gis mtshon par byas nas thabs
NK075(bu)002:3300: grol gyi don rang bzhin gsang snying de mngon du
NK075(bu)002:3305: 'khor gang zhig la gtad pa'i dngos po bstan pa gang de /
NK075(bu)002:3306: dgos ched ci yi phyir gtad ce na /
NK075(bu)002:3307: ston pa ni rgyal ba kun bzang rdo rje 'chang
NK075(bu)002:3308: des 'khor ni rgyal sras sdud pa mdzad pa'i phyag
NK075(bu)002:3309: na rdo rje lhan cig pa'i 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:3310: go phye ba'i 'khor ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag chos
NK075(bu)002:3311: kyi mig can dang sogas kyi sgras ma dang mkha'
NK075(bu)002:3312: 'gro ma rnams la gtad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3313: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud 'di nyid kyi don snang ba bzhi po de /
NK075(bu)002:3314: de yang rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams /
NK075(bu)002:3315: 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams /
NK075(bu)002:3316: lam gyi snang ba bgrod byar gdams /
NK075(bu)002:3317: 'bras bu'i snang ba thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3318: dgos ched ci'i phyir gtad pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3319: mi nub par bya ba'i phyir sdud pa po la gtad /
NK075(bu)002:3320: dar zhing rgyas par bya ba'i phyir gang zag chos kyi mig can la gtad /
NK075(bu)002:3321: bstana pa bsrung zhing thams cad du 'phel bar bya
NK075(bu)002:3322: ba'i phyir ma dang mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gtad
NK075(bu)002:3324: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u tha ma dang /
NK075(bu)002:3325: rgyas pa'i bud med btul ba'i le'u nang du gsal lo //
NK075(bu)002:3326: lam dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams rang gi skabs su 'byung bas 'dir ma bstan pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3328: gleng gzhi la sogs pa shes par bya ba'i yul
NK075(bu)002:3329: lnga po 'di nyid gsang snying gi shes bya yin
NK075(bu)002:3330: de bsgom par bya ba'i thabs min /
NK075(bu)002:3331: 'o na rgyud don nyams su len pa'i sgom thabs gar bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:3332: shes bya lnga po de yi phyi ma la thun
NK075(bu)002:3333: mong dang mchog gi lam gnyis bshad pa'i skabs la
NK075(bu)002:3334: shes dgos moda / de'i don ni bsgom bya rgyud
NK075(bu)002:3335: don gyi dngos po bcu ni 'og lam gyi skabsa
NK075(bu)002:3337: de bas 'dir shes bya lnga po'i skabs su bsgom bya bshad pa ma yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3338: bar du thun mong mchog gi lam bgrod tshul la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:3342: shes bya lnga gong du song nas bar du bsgom
NK075(bu)002:3343: bya la mos pas lam la gzhol nas bgrod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3345: lam stegs su thun mong spyi'i lam bgrod lugs la lha mi'i dge ba bcu /
NK075(bu)002:3347: byang sems kyi sems bskyed rnams /
NK075(bu)002:3348: rang rang gi gzhung bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:3349: khyad par theg mchog ma h+aa'i lam ste gnyis so //
NK075(bu)002:3350: mchog gi lam khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3354: tha ma theg mchog ma h+aa la yang gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:3355: so so skye bos 'dod yon lnga dngos su spyad
NK075(bu)002:3356: pas de dang rjes su mthun par thabs lam pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3357: lam la gzhol ba'i lugs dang /
NK075(bu)002:3358: mtshan nyid pas pha rol tu phyin pa'i lam la
NK075(bu)002:3359: spyod pa de dang rjes su mthun par shes rab
NK075(bu)002:3360: grol lam la gzhol ba'i lugs gnyis la'ang /
NK075(bu)002:3361: gdul bya'i dbang po rno rtul gyi phye bas thabs lam de dang /
NK075(bu)002:3362: shes rab grol lam de gnyis la'ang cig char dang rim gyis sbyor ba'i lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:3363: thabs grol rang rang gis rjes su mthun par lung
NK075(bu)002:3364: nang nas bshad pa bzhin du 'og rgyas bshad kyis
NK075(bu)002:3374: so so skye bos 'dod yon lnga yis bde ba
NK075(bu)002:3375: dngos por spyod pas de'i rjes su 'brang ba thabs
NK075(bu)002:3376: lam gyis bgrod pa la yang /
NK075(bu)002:3377: sbyangs pa'i las 'phro che chung ngam snod kyi blo
NK075(bu)002:3378: rno rtul dang bcud kyis skal ba yod med kyi
NK075(bu)002:3379: dbang gis phye ba la de yang rang rang gi
NK075(bu)002:3380: blo dang 'tshams par nyams su blang dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:3381: de yang blo che chung gi sgo nas rim cig char gnyis su dbye /
NK075(bu)002:3382: mtshan ma che chung gi sgo nas lha rtog gnyis su dbye /
NK075(bu)002:3383: gdul bya rags gzhan gyi sgo nas zhi khro gnyis su dbye /
NK075(bu)002:3384: rim pa 'dor mi 'dor gyi sgo nas thod rgal mthar gnyis su chags su dbye /
NK075(bu)002:3385: chags pa che chung gi sgo nas thabs grol gnyis su dbye ba la /
NK075(bu)002:3386: 'dir chags pa can rang rang gi blo dang 'atshamas
NK075(bu)002:3387: par thabs lam gyi gdams ngag gis grol bar byed
NK075(bu)002:3388: pa la bla ma nyams myong dang ldan pa /
NK075(bu)002:3390: las rgyas yon tan dang ldan pa /
NK075(bu)002:3391: rang gi las dag pa dang bzhi 'dzom pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:3392: yang na rtsa 'khor lo bzhi la thig le yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3393: rang gi thig le byed pa sdom pa'i thabs 'khrul
NK075(bu)002:3394: 'khor dang bcas pa'i stobs las bde stong gi ye
NK075(bu)002:3396: de la dbang po rno rtul gyi dbang gis dpe
NK075(bu)002:3397: khamas gsum gyi lus grub tshul gyis spyod pa mi
NK075(bu)002:3398: 'dra ba yis phye bas dang po 'dod khams pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3399: lus lhur len nas gnas pa la /
NK075(bu)002:3400: mngal nas rim par skyes la gzugs khams bardzusa skyes
NK075(bu)002:3401: su dwangs nas gzugs rdzogs par smin pa'i tshul de
NK075(bu)002:3402: bzhin du thabs lam steng sgo rims gyis pa dang
NK075(bu)002:3403: 'og sgo cig char du snang ba ni 'di ltar
NK075(bu)002:3409: shira ni rtsa tsakra ni 'khor lo ya mo cha drug ste /
NK075(bu)002:3412: dang po rgyu 'khor lo bzhi ni lte ba sprul
NK075(bu)002:3413: pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbus
NK075(bu)002:3414: na / thig le a thung gi dbyibs su gnas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3415: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad kyi dbus na /
NK075(bu)002:3416: thig le wam gi dbyibs su /
NK075(bu)002:3417: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na /
NK075(bu)002:3418: thig le a thung gi dbyibs su klad pa bde
NK075(bu)002:3419: chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum cu so gnyis
NK075(bu)002:3420: kyi dbus na / thig le ham gi dbyibs su gnas so //
NK075(bu)002:3422: sum mdo me'i 'khor lo na ra dang /
NK075(bu)002:3423: sgrom mado'am gshang kha rlung gi 'khor lo na ya dang bcas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3424: de la lam pas bsgom pa'i dus na /
NK075(bu)002:3425: 'og rlung bsdoms pa las rang gnas kyi yi ge
NK075(bu)002:3426: ya las sgrol ma ste rlung gyen du 'gro bas
NK075(bu)002:3428: des a thung gi me spar bas /
NK075(bu)002:3429: rtsa a wa d+hu ti'i nang du me sna zhugs /
NK075(bu)002:3430: de la brten pa'i lte ba'i thig le na rtogs pas 'khyags pa bzhus /
NK075(bu)002:3432: de nas rim pa snying kha'i thig le bzhus /
NK075(bu)002:3435: spyi bo'i 'khor lo rnams kyi thig le rtog pas 'khyags pa rnams bzhus nas /
NK075(bu)002:3436: lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba skyes pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3437: de nas thig le'i 'od zer spyi bo nas 'thon te /
NK075(bu)002:3438: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la bde stong gi mchod pa 'bul bas /
NK075(bu)002:3439: de pa rnams kyis ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba
NK075(bu)002:3440: mdzad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' de tshur 'dus spyi
NK075(bu)002:3442: 'od du zhu bas lus kun la khyab ste rkyal
NK075(bu)002:3443: pa zhos bkang ba bzhin du gyur par bsgoms pa
NK075(bu)002:3444: yis dga' ba bzhi bye brag tu bskyed pa'i cha
NK075(bu)002:3445: yin no // chos rje'i bzhed la /
NK075(bu)002:3446: bye brag bskyed pa'i cha 'di ltar du bshad de /
NK075(bu)002:3447: de nyams su blang ba'i rim pa'i bye brag ni /
NK075(bu)002:3448: dang po rtsa dang thig le la sogs pa gnas pa thabs /
NK075(bu)002:3449: de bsgoms nas goms pas gzung 'dzin phra rags rnams
NK075(bu)002:3450: dag nas don dam rtog med kyi ye shes bskyed
NK075(bu)002:3453: gzhung tshig mthun mi mthun dpyad do //
NK075(bu)002:3456: mkha' 'gro yod med mdor bskul bzhi /
NK075(bu)002:3458: mkha' 'gro yod par sgom thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:3460: mdor bsdus te sgom pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3461: 'khor lo bskul te sgom dang bzhi las dang po ni /
NK075(bu)002:3463: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo'i phyogs bzhi na /
NK075(bu)002:3464: rtsa ba zhi ye shes bzhi'i 'od dang bcas pa byung nas /
NK075(bu)002:3465: srog mi shig pa'i thig le bzhus pas /
NK075(bu)002:3466: bde ba'i ye shes rgyud la skyes pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3468: snying gi nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyi steng /
NK075(bu)002:3469: zla ba'i rnam bug nas mar shes pa gtad de bsgoms pas bde ba'i ye shes skyes pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3471: don dam par thig le la dbyibs dang kha dog tu grub pa med de /
NK075(bu)002:3472: de nyid la sems gtad de bsgoms pas bde ba'i ye shes skyes pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3474: 'og sgo bde ba'i lam nas ye shes kyi rlung byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:3475: gtum mo'i sa bon ra la phog pas me sbar /
NK075(bu)002:3476: de nas rtsa dbu ma nas yar zhugs te /
NK075(bu)002:3477: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo bzhu /
NK075(bu)002:3478: de nas rim par brgyud de /
NK075(bu)002:3479: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK075(bu)002:3480: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK075(bu)002:3481: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo rnams rim par bzhus nas /
NK075(bu)002:3483: bde ba'i rang bzhin du 'bar bar bsgom pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3484: 'khor lo sgom pa'i thabs yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3487: pho mo dang ma ning la sogs pa thams cad
NK075(bu)002:3488: de las sprul nas 'byung bas lte ba sprul pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3490: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo na yid kyi shes pa gnas shing /
NK075(bu)002:3491: yid kyis chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams
NK075(bu)002:3492: cad la dbang bsgyur bas snying kha chos kyi 'khor
NK075(bu)002:3493: lo zhes bya'o // mgrin pa zas thams cad la longs spyod cing /
NK075(bu)002:3494: de ltar spyod pa'i rtsa des ro kha ba mngar ba thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'am /
NK075(bu)002:3495: ro myong bar byed pas mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:3496: klad pa'i thig le chen po byang chub kyi sems yod pa 'di nyid /
NK075(bu)002:3497: bde ba thams cad 'byung ba'i gazhi'am ngo bo yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:3498: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:3499: yang lam rnam bkod las kyang 'di ltar du gsungs /
NK075(bu)002:3501: thig le rkyang pa dang rtsa dang thig le sbrag ma dang /
NK075(bu)002:3502: shin tu myur ba'i sgom thabs dang bzhis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK075(bu)002:3503: don dam par lte ba'i rtsa sor bzhi pa rgyus pa bldad pa'am bdag brkyangs pa lta bu /
NK075(bu)002:3504: dkar na re ba rang bzhin gyi yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:3505: de la shes pa gtad de bsgoms pas bde ba'i ye shes skyes pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:3508: rtsa de'i nang thig le yung kar 'bring po tsam
NK075(bu)002:3509: thig le kha dog dkar po zhig bsgom nas de
NK075(bu)002:3510: de la sems de gtad pas bde ba'i ye shes
NK075(bu)002:3511: skyes pa'o // rtsa dang thig le sbrag ma ni /
NK075(bu)002:3512: rtsa ri bong can zhes bya ba zla ba tshes pa 'dra ba /
NK075(bu)002:3513: skya khyug ge ba gnyis bsgoms pa'i bar du /
NK075(bu)002:3514: thig le dmar po sran ma tsam la shes pa
NK075(bu)002:3515: gtad de bsgoms pas bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'o
NK075(bu)002:3516: // shin tu myur ba'i sgom thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:3517: rtsa dang thig le dbyibs dang kha dog tu ma grub cing /
NK075(bu)002:3518: gang du yang mi gnas pas /
NK075(bu)002:3519: rkyal stong bus pa lta bu'i stong pa dang bcas
NK075(bu)002:3520: te bsgoms pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK075(bu)002:3521: skye ba'o // cig char ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:3523: steng sgo rim gyis pa gong du song nas phyi
NK075(bu)002:3524: ma 'og sgo cig char ba ni yab kyi dbang
NK075(bu)002:3525: po dang yum gyi gsang ba yul gnyis 'dzom pa
NK075(bu)002:3526: ste / de yang yab kyi rdo rje las nor
NK075(bu)002:3527: bu ste thig le las bde ba kun tu 'byung
NK075(bu)002:3528: ste / ba dang / yum gyi chu skyes te
NK075(bu)002:3529: pad+ma dang 'dra bar bde ba bskyed kyang nyon mongs
NK075(bu)002:3530: pa'i dri mas ma gos pa'i thabs nyams su blangs
NK075(bu)002:3531: pa la dbyer med du ldan par gyur dgos pas
NK075(bu)002:3532: ste / ba dang / / de yang gang zag gi dgongs pa mtho na dbye mi dgos /
NK075(bu)002:3533: dgongs pa dma' na rig ma lo bcu drug lon
NK075(bu)002:3534: pa lus ngag yid dang spyod lam gyi yon tan
NK075(bu)002:3535: bzhi rgyud gzhung nas bshad pa bzhin rdzogs pa la
NK075(bu)002:3536: / yab yum gyi mkha' gsang bsnol mar brlab cing sbyor ba'i brdas bsnol mar bskul nas /
NK075(bu)002:3541: de ltar phyag rgya bzhis rol la yab yum gyi
NK075(bu)002:3542: dbang po kha sbyor bas bde ba g.yo ba'i tshul
NK075(bu)002:3545: mas brtan gyi dga' ba bzhi bskyed pa de yang /
NK075(bu)002:3546: rten yab thabs kyi cha yin pas bde ba dang tshul mthun /
NK075(bu)002:3547: yum shes rab kyi cha yin pas stong pa dang cha mthun pa /
NK075(bu)002:3548: de bas kha sbyor ba'i bde stong dbyer med kyi
NK075(bu)002:3549: don rnal 'byor pas dngos su mthong ba yin no
NK075(bu)002:3550: // de yang dga' ba bzhi'i skye tshul rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:3551: dang po yas 'bab kyi dga' ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:3552: de yang bde ba'i byang sems kyi chu rgyun klad
NK075(bu)002:3553: pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo nas mgrin par babs
NK075(bu)002:3554: pa dga' ba / snying khar mchog dga' /
NK075(bu)002:3556: gsang ba'i rdo rje'i lam nas 'byung ba'i tshe /
NK075(bu)002:3557: dga' ba bzhi'i mthar thug lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba nyams su myong zhing /
NK075(bu)002:3558: rten byang chub kyi sems theg le yum gyi pad+mora reg pa'i gnas su 'khyil bas /
NK075(bu)002:3559: yum gyi nyi ma byang chub sems dang rtse sprad nas /
NK075(bu)002:3560: thig le phyed shor phyed ma shor te /
NK075(bu)002:3561: yab yum gnyis kyi gsang rtsar phan tshun 'dres pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3562: nyon mongs pa rang sar grol nas kun rdzob bde stong gi ye shes mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3563: de nas lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'i ye shes
NK075(bu)002:3564: kyi bdag nyid thig le nyi zla gnyis 'dres te
NK075(bu)002:3565: / 'gro 'ong byang chub kyi sems tshur log nas
NK075(bu)002:3566: gsang ba rdo rje'i bu gar bstims shing thig le
NK075(bu)002:3567: rdo rje'i lam nas yar log pa ni mas brtan
NK075(bu)002:3568: gyi dga' ba ste lte bar brtan pa dga' ba
NK075(bu)002:3571: spyi bor brtan pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:3572: de tsam na bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyis rdzogs shing /
NK075(bu)002:3573: de'i yon tan gyis thig le lus thams cad khyab
NK075(bu)002:3574: cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pa
NK075(bu)002:3575: bcu gnyis ma chags pad+ma can gyi sa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3576: rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK075(bu)002:3577: 'khor rang snang bas bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo
NK075(bu)002:3581: thabs lam 'di skabs gar bshad na mchod pa la
NK075(bu)002:3582: phyi nang gsang gsum yod pa las gsang ba'i mchod
NK075(bu)002:3583: pa'i skabs la / dkyil 'khor la bdun yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:3584: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor skabs la bshad /
NK075(bu)002:3585: chags pa can la thabs lam 'di nyid ma gtogs
NK075(bu)002:3586: pa thos bsam sgom gsum gyi shes rab gsum gyis
NK075(bu)002:3587: nyon mongs mi 'byang ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:3588: de bas chags pa can gyi gang zag des /
NK075(bu)002:3589: dang nas bde ba la sems 'dzin cing nyon mongs
NK075(bu)002:3590: pa ma spangs rang dag tu mthar bde stong gi
NK075(bu)002:3591: ye shes mngon du rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:3592: thabs lam zhes bya ba'i nges tshig gi ming thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3597: spyir lam gyi gtso bo dang cha rkyen 'di rnams la /
NK075(bu)002:3598: bi ma la mi tra'i bzhed kyis /
NK075(bu)002:3599: lam gyi gtso bo gang zag ste /
NK075(bu)002:3600: dam tshig dang spyod pa gnyis gcig tu bsdus pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:3601: rgyud kyi dngos po brgyad du dabye'o //
NK075(bu)002:3602: sgeg rdor gyis gtso bo ting nge 'dzin te /
NK075(bu)002:3603: sngags phyag rgya mchod pa gsum spyir btang ba'i yan lag bdun du dbye /
NK075(bu)002:3605: gtso bo mchog gi sems lnga la bzhed do //
NK075(bu)002:3606: ting nge 'dzin brtsi ba'i yan lag bcur bzhed /
NK075(bu)002:3607: sangs rgyas gsang ba ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:3608: sngags phyag rgya gnyis su dbye ba'i yan lag bcur dbye /
NK075(bu)002:3610: shesa rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i lam gyi
NK075(bu)002:3611: rjes su sbyor ba grol lam la'ang lam gyi gtso
NK075(bu)002:3612: bo dang / lam gyi yan lag cha rkyen du /
NK075(bu)002:3622: rgyud don rnam pa bcu po yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3631: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i grol lam gyi sgor
NK075(bu)002:3632: 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor pa kun gyis don du gnyer
NK075(bu)002:3633: bar bya ba la'ang lam gyi gtso bo'i mchog tu
NK075(bu)002:3634: ting nge 'dzin bsgom par bya ba yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3635: de la yang sngon thabs lam la rim cig char
NK075(bu)002:3636: byung ba bzhin du 'dir grol lam gyi ting nge
NK075(bu)002:3637: 'dzin la yang rim cig char gnyis su shes par
NK075(bu)002:3642: cig char ba ni blo'i mchoga ste ma h+aa rtogs
NK075(bu)002:3643: pa'i skal ba dang ldana pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK075(bu)002:3644: kyis gdod ma nas bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta
NK075(bu)002:3645: ba blo la ngesa par chud nas rtogs pas /
NK075(bu)002:3646: ting nge 'dzin yang der gnas pa la 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:3647: byang ba stong pa chub pa ste snang ba sems dbyer med mngon gyur du bsgom pa la /
NK075(bu)002:3651: sems bsgom rnam gsum dus gcig tu rdzogs shing chig char du sgom pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3652: de la cig char ba'i cig char ba rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3653: cig char ba'i rim gyis pa sgom pa la gnyug bsring dgos /
NK075(bu)002:3656: rim gyis pa ni cig char ba de las bzlog pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:3657: dpe rgyud snga ma la 'bras bu phyi ma byung ba'i rten 'brel bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:3658: bden gsum dbyer med cig char du ma rtogs nas go bas /
NK075(bu)002:3663: phyag rgya spros pa man chad lnga pa'i lam la rim pa ltar brten nas don du gnyer bas /
NK075(bu)002:3664: phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du gyur pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:3665: dbyer med spyod dang bral ba'i 'go zug ste /
NK075(bu)002:3667: zag bcas bden mthong yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3668: zag med bden mthong ni tshe rnam gnyis yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3669: bden mthong chen po sangs rgyas kyi sa na yod do //
NK075(bu)002:3683: lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su rim gyis pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom lugs rgyas par bashada pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:3688: bgrod bya lam gyi gtso bo ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK075(bu)002:3689: sngon du lam gyi yana lag la rgyud dngos bcur
NK075(bu)002:3690: dbye ba'i nang nas dang po lta ba 'gro bas
NK075(bu)002:3691: / lta ba de'i sdom tshig ni lta ba'i dgos ched /
NK075(bu)002:3692: rtogs thabs dang lta ba'i ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)002:3693: ma rtogs pa'i skyon dang rtogs pa'i yona tan dang lnga'i rima pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3694: dbang po mchoga gi mig dang 'dra bas shes rab
NK075(bu)002:3695: kyi spyan lta ba'i don ni rdzogs par bshad pa'o
NK075(bu)002:3706: sngags las gzhan pa'i theg 'og gi lta ba ngan pa'i mig de basla ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:3707: theg mchoga gi gsang sngags kyi dgongs don shes rab
NK075(bu)002:3708: kyi spyan lta ba rab mchog de mngon du bya
NK075(bu)002:3709: dgos pa'i phyir / de yang 'og ma'i lta ba
NK075(bu)002:3710: ngan pa go cha dang 'dra ba rdol zhing 'bigs
NK075(bu)002:3712: rang la bden pa dbyer med kyi lta ba the
NK075(bu)002:3713: tshom med pa'i don mdel thung rnon po 'dra ba
NK075(bu)002:3714: zhig rtogs par gces pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3720: 'og ma'i lta ba rnams phyogs 'dzin yin cing phyogs med lhun grub mi rtog pa'i dpe ni /
NK075(bu)002:3721: gling bzhi lta ba'i yul rgya chung phal pa'i ri nag po dgu 'das nas de bas rgya che /
NK075(bu)002:3722: gser gyi ri bdun rim pa bzhin lta bas mthong rgya che ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:3723: ri rab lhun po'i gnas nas lta ba'i bye brag
NK075(bu)002:3724: thams cad gsal ba'i rim pa de ltar du yod
NK075(bu)002:3731: lta bas gzhan sel la lugs dang /
NK075(bu)002:3733: ma rtogs pa phyal rgyang gnyis la /
NK075(bu)002:3734: rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs yod kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3735: rgyas 'gyur kyi rigs sad ma nus pas rigas med pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3736: rang bzhin log par rtogsa pa mu stug mu stegs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3737: phra ba chos bdag ma chod pas nang pa la ltos na phyi pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3738: rags pa gang zag gi bdag chad pas phyi pa
NK075(bu)002:3739: la ltos na nang pa'i lta ba dang cha mthun
NK075(bu)002:3741: snang ba sems yin par 'dod pa'i phyogs tsam bsgrub
NK075(bu)002:3742: pa gsang sngags dang mthun kyang sems rang rig rang
NK075(bu)002:3743: gsal du 'dod pa'i sems tsam pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3744: don dam bden pa rtogs kyang kun rdzob bden pa
NK075(bu)002:3745: spang bya mi mthun pa'i phyogs byas nas 'gegs pa
NK075(bu)002:3746: dag 'dod pa'i dbu ma pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3747: 'di rnams phyogs 'dzin gyi lta ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:3748: dpe zas la dug btab pa'i cha yod na zas
NK075(bu)002:3749: dug can de la gang gis mi rig ste mi
NK075(bu)002:3750: za ba bzhin du gsang sngags kyi lta ba rtogs
NK075(bu)002:3751: pa'i gang zag gang gis dbu ma man chad phyogs
NK075(bu)002:3752: 'dzin gyi lta ba gol bar shes nas phyogs 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:3753: gyi lta ba der ni blo mi gnas pa yin
NK075(bu)002:3756: chos nyid bsam gyis ma khyab pa gsang sngags bden
NK075(bu)002:3757: gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba ma shes na sgom
NK075(bu)002:3758: pa bsam med zhi gnas tsam la brten pa'i rnal
NK075(bu)002:3759: 'byor bla med kyi dgongs pa gnyis med kyi don
NK075(bu)002:3760: nyams su myong zhing 'bras bu thob pa ma yin
NK075(bu)002:3763: gang zag gang gis gong gi lta sgom phyogs re
NK075(bu)002:3764: ba'i skyon ni de ltar du yod pa shes nas
NK075(bu)002:3765: / lta ba dbyer med du rtogs pa'i thabs du
NK075(bu)002:3766: ma'i sgo nas 'ub chub par byas pas snang stong
NK075(bu)002:3767: dbyer med rtogsa pa'i sgom pa la yang rnal ma
NK075(bu)002:3768: don la rang rig pa'i blo 'byor zhing /
NK075(bu)002:3770: sgrib gnyis byang sangs rgyas kyi sar chub pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:3771: 'di ni sa bcad dang po'i mchan gyi dbang btsan yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3773: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lta ba mi shes nas /
NK075(bu)002:3774: sgom pa bsam med tsam la brten nas /
NK075(bu)002:3775: rnal 'byor gnyis med kyi don yin par /
NK075(bu)002:3777: de ltar bsam rtsal la blos chub par byas nas /
NK075(bu)002:3778: snang stong dbyer med mi rtogs /
NK075(bu)002:3782: sangs rgyas kyi sar mi chub po //
NK075(bu)002:3783: de bas lta ba dbyer med kyi don rtogs dgos zhes bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:3786: gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa gang gis lam gyi
NK075(bu)002:3787: thog mar lta ba 'gro bas lta ba de gtan
NK075(bu)002:3788: tshigs la brten nas rtogs pa'i thabs la ting nge
NK075(bu)002:3789: 'dzin gyi bye brag mi 'dra ba'i bskyed rim rnams
NK075(bu)002:3790: dang / thig le dang nam mkha'i ba gzho ba'i
NK075(bu)002:3791: bsam gtan la sogs pa'i sems gnas thabs du ma
NK075(bu)002:3793: gzhan yang rtogs thabs kyi yan lag mang po ste /
NK075(bu)002:3799: nya stong brgyad la sogs pa la dus mchod dang /
NK075(bu)002:3805: snying rje sems bskyed rnams dang /
NK075(bu)002:3812: dge ba'i dpung tshogs thams cad la 'bad pa de rnams kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3814: dngos su gtan la phab la lung rigs man ngag
NK075(bu)002:3815: rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas gtan tshigs thun mong
NK075(bu)002:3816: la rang spyi'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:3819: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs rnams yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3820: thun mong min pa'i tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs ni /
NK075(bu)002:3825: rang bzhin bden pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs rnams bshad rgyud rgyas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3826: rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po la sogs pa'ii gzhung
NK075(bu)002:3827: las grags pas lta ba rtogs pa'i rkyen byas te
NK075(bu)002:3828: rtogs bya lta ba ni dpe ri rgyal lhun po'i
NK075(bu)002:3829: kha nas thams cad gsal ba lta bur dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:3830: kyi ngang nas 'jig rten pa dang 'jig rten las
NK075(bu)002:3831: 'das pa'i lta ba kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK075(bu)002:3833: de mthong bar byed pa'i mtshungs rgyu ni blo'i mtshan
NK075(bu)002:3834: nyid bdun dang ldan pa des gsang sngags kyi rgyud
NK075(bu)002:3835: lung man ngag dang bcas pa'i bla ma la brten
NK075(bu)002:3836: nas lhan cig byed pa'ii rkyen byas pas /
NK075(bu)002:3837: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)002:3838: thos bsam sgom gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyis smal ba
NK075(bu)002:3839: la gtan tshigs gang yin gcig gi thogs nas bden
NK075(bu)002:3840: pa dbyer med kyi nges shes skyes pa'ang /
NK075(bu)002:3841: bden gnyis dbyer med yin min gyi the tshom za
NK075(bu)002:3842: bas yin min la rtog dpyod byas pa yis yid
NK075(bu)002:3843: gnyis su zhugs pa'i dbang gis tha dad byung bsam
NK075(bu)002:3844: gyi som nyi za ba de dag meda pa la
NK075(bu)002:3845: bden pa la dbyer med kyi lta bar brjod kyis
NK075(bu)002:3846: de yang bden pa dbyer med byung bsam gyi nges
NK075(bu)002:3847: 'jog gis blo'i rtog dpyod med pa dgos shing rtog
NK075(bu)002:3848: dpyod kyi blo de nyid kyis ngo bo la ngos
NK075(bu)002:3849: bzung med cing kun la shar bas dgag bsgrub dang
NK075(bu)002:3850: spang blang meda pa'i rgyu de las lta ba dgag
NK075(bu)002:3851: bsgrub dang bral ba 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:3852: gong gi rgyu rkyen gang gis 'di la chos rjes /
NK075(bu)002:3853: rkyen bzhi'i bzhed pa snang ste /
NK075(bu)002:3854: lam rim dang bstun na rgyu gnyis rkyen gcig kho na ltar 'thad de /
NK075(bu)002:3856: rang bzhin bdun dang ldan pa la //
NK075(bu)002:3857: gcig shos rgyu ru gsungs pa yin //
NK075(bu)002:3858: gang dag nyan bsam shes rab tshe //
NK075(bu)002:3859: bsam pa'i tshe na rtog dpyod pa //
NK075(bu)002:3860: gnyis po 'di dag shes pa'i rgyu //
NK075(bu)002:3861: mkhan po lung dang man ngag bcas //
NK075(bu)002:3862: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen du 'dod //
NK075(bu)002:3868: lta ba'i ngo bo sems nyid mig la sogs pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3869: dbang po drug gi yul du 'char nas snang ba
NK075(bu)002:3870: yin yang / tshogs drug gi snang ba la snang grags gnyis rgya che /
NK075(bu)002:3871: de la yang snang ba 'di rgya che bas /
NK075(bu)002:3872: de bas spyan la mchog tu brjod pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:3873: mig gzugs thog tu ngo sprod pa ni sgo lnga'i snang rkyang dag /
NK075(bu)002:3876: kun gzhi gnas pa rang stong du song nas tshogs
NK075(bu)002:3877: brgyad dam tshogs drug ye shes su shar ba'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:3878: / mig gis gzugs mthong ba'i dus su dmigs bya
NK075(bu)002:3879: med par rang gsal du song zhing shar ba la
NK075(bu)002:3880: shes rab skye ba med pa'i don de nyid mig
NK075(bu)002:3881: la sogs pa tshogs drug gi yul du shar ba
NK075(bu)002:3882: dang dbyer med pas rang rig pa'i mngon sum rtogsa
NK075(bu)002:3883: pa ni rjes dpag gis rtogs pa las dpags pas
NK075(bu)002:3884: / mchog yin no // 'o na mig gzugs thog tu ngo sprod kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3885: tshogs drug gzhan rnams ngo ma 'phrod par lus sam zhen mi lus te /
NK075(bu)002:3886: brjod pa tshig gi yul las 'das //
NK075(bu)002:3887: go ba blo yis dpyod pa bral //
NK075(bu)002:3888: myong ba nyams kyi 'khri ba dag nas /
NK075(bu)002:3889: rang rig pa'i ye shes ni tshogs drug kun gyi
NK075(bu)002:3890: ngo bor shar la shar dus rang rig ye shes
NK075(bu)002:3891: gcig po las ma g.yos pas shes rab skye ba
NK075(bu)002:3892: med pa de nyid mig gzugs thog tu ngo 'phrod
NK075(bu)002:3893: pa'i spyan gyi lta ba dama pa de bas logs
NK075(bu)002:3894: nas ngo sprad rgyu med do //
NK075(bu)002:3895: spyan gyi lta ba de la phyi ngan pa spang
NK075(bu)002:3896: ba dang nang bzang po bsgrub tu med par chos
NK075(bu)002:3898: shes bya gshis kyi gnas lugs chos nyid rang gi
NK075(bu)002:3899: mtshan nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs mthong ba yin no
NK075(bu)002:3902: spyir chos la tshad ma dang tshad min gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:3907: snang ba la ma nges yid dpyod dang lnga'o //
NK075(bu)002:3908: tshad ma la mngon sum dang /
NK075(bu)002:3910: rjes dpag la lung rigs gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:3912: rigs pa la tshad ma sde bdun yod kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3913: gang zag phyogs 'dzin can gyis rang gi zhe 'dod ltar du 'dod pas /
NK075(bu)002:3914: de bas mngon sum tshad ma ma rtogs bar du
NK075(bu)002:3915: rjes dpag tshad ma rdzun tshig tu 'gro ba yin
NK075(bu)002:3916: no // mngon sum la yang bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:3917: mtshan nyid pa ltar du dbang po'i mngon sum /
NK075(bu)002:3918: dbang po skyon med du mthong ba /
NK075(bu)002:3919: yid kyi mngon sum yid bcad shes /
NK075(bu)002:3920: rang rig mngon sum chos thams cad spros bral du rtogs pa /
NK075(bu)002:3921: rnal 'byor mngon sum de nyid du blo gnas pa /
NK075(bu)002:3922: de yang sa mtshams dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)002:3923: dbang po dang yid gnyis tshogs lam /
NK075(bu)002:3924: rang rig mngon sum sbyor lam /
NK075(bu)002:3925: rnal 'byor mngon sum mthong lam la yod par 'dod pas /
NK075(bu)002:3926: mngon sum bzhi rim gyis 'dod pa 'di yang /
NK075(bu)002:3927: gsang sngags kyi mngon sum bzhi la ltos na rjes dpag yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3929: dbang po'i mngon sum rig pa cer 'phrad /
NK075(bu)002:3930: yid kyi mngon sum yid 'gyu ba rang grol /
NK075(bu)002:3931: rang rig mngon sum snang stong dbyer med /
NK075(bu)002:3932: rnal 'byor mngon sum chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:3933: mngon sum bzhi cig char du rtogs pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3936: 'o na tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang khyad par mi snang zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:3937: mnyam bzhag la chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid de ltar du mthong na'ang /
NK075(bu)002:3938: rjes thob la log rtog ma zad pas /
NK075(bu)002:3939: dpe 'khor lo sgyur rgyal gyi bu chung de'i sha khrag dang rigs las 'gyur ba med kyang /
NK075(bu)002:3940: stobs ma rdzogs pas mnga' thang thams cad dbang bsgyur mi nus pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:3941: zag bcas bden mthong gi skabs yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:3942: chos nyid rang mtshan mthong yang rgyal bu stobs ma
NK075(bu)002:3943: rdzogs pa de lta bur ting nge 'dzin stobs ma
NK075(bu)002:3944: rdzogs pas mnyam rjes yod la /
NK075(bu)002:3945: zag med bden mthong tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin ni mnyam rjes med pas /
NK075(bu)002:3947: de bas zag bcas bden mthong las khyad para du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3950: gsang ba'i snying po sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i rgyud las 'di skad du gsung ste /
NK075(bu)002:3951: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo la lta bya'i yul
NK075(bu)002:3952: dang blta bar bya ba'i mkhan po gnyis med pa'i
NK075(bu)002:3953: ngang nas sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba'i ye shes /
NK075(bu)002:3954: de ma 'dres par rang gsal bas na sgron ma
NK075(bu)002:3955: de rgyud chad med pa bsgreng bar shar ba ni
NK075(bu)002:3956: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcu'i zhing
NK075(bu)002:3957: khams dag ma dag thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK075(bu)002:3958: su mthonga la / yul dang yul can gyi ngang
NK075(bu)002:3959: du gang du yang mi mthong ba ni shes rab
NK075(bu)002:3960: lta ba'i spyan gyi mchog yin no //
NK075(bu)002:3961: zhar la spyi'i mtshan nyid du 'dod pa ni nor ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:3964: spyi'i mtshan nyid du lta bas gsang sngags mi rtogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3966: rang rig mngon sum du rtogs pa lta ba'i ngo bo yin la /
NK075(bu)002:3967: de bas spyi mtshan gyi go ba tsam la /
NK075(bu)002:3968: gang zag gang zhiga zhen te mi zhen /
NK075(bu)002:3969: ci'i phyir mi zhen na gsang sngagsa kyis don yid
NK075(bu)002:3970: du byas pa la gang zag gang gis brtags dpyad
NK075(bu)002:3971: byas pas bden pa dbyer med kyi don mi rnyed
NK075(bu)002:3972: pa'i phyir / yid kyis dmigs pa gzung 'dzin can du dang /
NK075(bu)002:3974: gnyis med skye 'jig dang bral ba rdo rje'i don
NK075(bu)002:3975: de nyid yida kyis yul du byas na sgra tsam
NK075(bu)002:3976: la brten pa ni gol ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:3977: gol tshul la ni chos nyid 'dus ma byas stong
NK075(bu)002:3978: pa tsam gyi ngo bo la skye 'jig mi snang
NK075(bu)002:3979: bsams nas yul du dmigas pa dag la brten nas
NK075(bu)002:3980: / gsang sngags kyi lta ba'i ngo bo ni nges
NK075(bu)002:3981: par 'di kho na'o snyam nas lta ba de'i rjes
NK075(bu)002:3982: la rnal 'byor mi rtog pa'i don la bsgom dgos
NK075(bu)002:3983: / ces / rgyud gzhung nas bshad pa yang /
NK075(bu)002:3984: lta ba de dang phyogs nas mthun par skyes par 'dod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:3985: yid yul gyi blo yis nges par 'joga pas chos
NK075(bu)002:3986: nyid yul du rtog pa'i gzunga 'dzin can du gyur
NK075(bu)002:3988: sgra ci bzhin du rtog cing ldog pa tshol bas lta ba dam pas dbul ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:3990: de bas 'og ma'i lta ba la phyogs 'dzin dang bcas pas /
NK075(bu)002:3991: lta ba lhun grub mi rtogs nas gol ba'i rgyu rkyen gyi dpe don ni /
NK075(bu)002:3992: tshong pa yul kun tu rgyu bas thams cad shes pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:3993: byis pa gzhon nu ni gar yang mi phyin nas
NK075(bu)002:3994: thams cad mi shes pa ltar du ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:3995: la goms ma goms mchog lta ba rtogs ma rtogs
NK075(bu)002:3996: / thos pa byas ma byas rgya che chung de'i khyad par 'byung lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:3997: rigas brgyad kyi dbye ba ston pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad
NK075(bu)002:3998: cu pa'i le'u lnga pa las 'byung ba ni 'di
NK075(bu)002:3999: lta ste / chos nyid kyi rigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4000: bla na med pa'i theg pa'i rigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4001: byang chub sems pa'i theg pa'i rigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4002: rang rgyal ba'i theg pa'i rigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4003: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i rigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4005: lha dang mi'i theg pa'i rigs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4007: de rnams kyi lta ba'i khyad par gsungas pa'i nang nas sngags bla med mchog yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:4008: sngags de nyid kyi lta ba la /
NK075(bu)002:4011: gnyis med la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs rnam grangs tsam
NK075(bu)002:4012: shes pa la lta ba dam pa'i don yin par
NK075(bu)002:4014: gsang sngags kyi lta ba lhun grub la gol ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:4016: dag mnyam la sogs pa de yi sgra tsam la
NK075(bu)002:4017: brten nas brtags dpyad byas pas ci bzhin pa'i don
NK075(bu)002:4019: dag pa de dang ni ma dag pa mi mthun
NK075(bu)002:4020: pa'i ma dag pa las ldog par byed pas dag
NK075(bu)002:4021: pa zhig 'dod pa la sogs pa lta ba dag
NK075(bu)002:4023: lhun gyis grub pa'i lta ba mi rtogs pas dbul po dang 'dra bas /
NK075(bu)002:4024: 'bras bu thams cad mi grub pa'i stong pa nyid tshe ba'i lta ba de nyid kho na'o //
NK075(bu)002:4027: lta ba'i mdor bstan la lnga yod la /
NK075(bu)002:4028: gsum gong du song nas bzhi pa lta ba ma rtogs pa'i skyon ni /
NK075(bu)002:4029: 'di skad du sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i lung las 'byung ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:4030: thabs la mkhas pas lta ba'i rtsis ma zin na
NK075(bu)002:4031: dge ba bcu lam gyi stegsa bcas kyang 'bras bu
NK075(bu)002:4032: la mtho ris kyi lha dang mi ru skye la
NK075(bu)002:4033: skye 'chi med pa'i sangs rgyas kyis mi thob pa
NK075(bu)002:4034: yin no // rtogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)002:4036: lnga pa lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK075(bu)002:4039: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub bla na med pa mchog gi snying po ni lta ba yin la /
NK075(bu)002:4040: dang po lta ba'i don rtogas nas mthar 'bras bu
NK075(bu)002:4041: ma thob kyi bar du lta ba de dang mi
NK075(bu)002:4042: 'bral nas ngan song du mi gtong ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:4043: dpe chu srin gre bar phyag rgya ste rin po
NK075(bu)002:4044: che chud na phyir mi gtong ba ci bzhin du'o
NK075(bu)002:4045: // gzhan yang dge ba'i spyod yul gang byas kun tu yon tan la tshad dpag tu med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4050: lta ba rtogs pa de'i rjes su lam gyi gtso
NK075(bu)002:4051: bo ting nge 'dzin des mchoga lta ba'i don de
NK075(bu)002:4052: rim 'jug tu goms par byed pa yi thabs ni
NK075(bu)002:4056: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)002:4058: 'byung ba gsum rlung sems 'dus pa'i rten 'brel las
NK075(bu)002:4059: grub pa'i lus 'di nyid lus sems bral nas 'chi
NK075(bu)002:4060: ba'i tshe / dang po chos nyid bar do la
NK075(bu)002:4061: rig pa 'gags nas 'gyel ba'i tshul ni de bzhin
NK075(bu)002:4063: lhun grub 'od gsal gyi bar do la sgra 'od thams cad shar bas /
NK075(bu)002:4065: mngal nas bu chung skyes ma thag gi bar /
NK075(bu)002:4066: phyag rgya gcig pa'i dpe bzhin du yin pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4067: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni
NK075(bu)002:4068: rang sgom thabs gang gi yan lag lam rim nas
NK075(bu)002:4069: bshad pa ltar don bco lnga ste /
NK075(bu)002:4070: sgom gyi sngon du bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4074: mi mthun pa'i skyon bcos thabs /
NK075(bu)002:4084: de rnams rdzogs pa yi sgo nas nyams su len pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4085: khyad par du ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK075(bu)002:4086: yul yul can gang du'ang 'dus shes med par rang gsal ba la ma yengs par bsgom dgos so //
NK075(bu)002:4087: de ltar sgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang yin pa
NK075(bu)002:4088: de dag gi nyams lnga rtags lnga ste bcu mthar
NK075(bu)002:4089: phyin pa dang ldan pa yi mthus snga ma de
NK075(bu)002:4090: bzhin nyid bsgoms pa las kyang /
NK075(bu)002:4091: phyi ma kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin la gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:4092: gal te lam snga ma la brtan pa ma thob na phyi ma mi skye ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4094: g.yo ba'i nyams ni ri gzar gyi 'bab chu lta bu /
NK075(bu)002:4095: thob pa'i nyams ni phu gsum gyi chu bran lta bu /
NK075(bu)002:4096: goms pa'i nyams ni dal 'bab kyi chu bo lta bu /
NK075(bu)002:4097: brtan pa'i nyams ni mtsho chung rlung gis mi skyod pa lta bu /
NK075(bu)002:4098: mthar phyin pa'i nyams ni rgya mtsho gting rlung gis mi spyod pa lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:4104: rdzu 'phrul rnams kyang cha re 'ong tshul lam rim du gsal lo //
NK075(bu)002:4107: dpe nyi ma 'phosa pa med par 'od du snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4108: sa bon 'pho ba med par myu gu 'byung /
NK075(bu)002:4109: skyur 'phos pa med par 'gram par chu ldang /
NK075(bu)002:4110: sgra 'pho ba med par brag cha las grag pa dang bzhira snang ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4111: de nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la 'phos pa med
NK075(bu)002:4112: par gdangs 'gag med du kun snang shar ba de
NK075(bu)002:4113: yi yan lag la don bco lnga bstan pa yang
NK075(bu)002:4114: de bzhin nyid ltar du yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:4115: khyad par du ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK075(bu)002:4116: rgyu de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni dbyings las brtan pa thob par byas nas ni /
NK075(bu)002:4117: de nyid rtsal rang la gnas pa'i ye shes ma
NK075(bu)002:4118: 'gags par snang ba kun tu khyab pa sgom pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4119: thabs ni snying rje chen po yin /
NK075(bu)002:4120: snying rje skye ba'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:4121: phyi'i snying rje snang stong dbyer med dam /
NK075(bu)002:4122: yang na phyi la skyed pa'i yul dang /
NK075(bu)002:4123: nang la skye byed kyi mkhan po med par rang
NK075(bu)002:4124: snang du ma yengs par goms bcug la kun snang
NK075(bu)002:4125: gi nyams rtags lam rim nas bshad pa bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:4126: / mthu rnams rdzogs par bya ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4129: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa de
NK075(bu)002:4130: yi stobs las phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:4131: skye ba ni / rim cig char gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:4132: dpe rten 'brel bcu gnyis yod pa la bzhi pa'i so nas /
NK075(bu)002:4133: ming gzugs rnams rim gyis lus 'byung ba'am /
NK075(bu)002:4134: cig shos te lus cig char du bardzusa te skye ba ci bzhin du yin pa la'ang /
NK075(bu)002:4135: de yang rgyud las zhi ba phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4136: khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa gnyis gsungs pa las sam /
NK075(bu)002:4137: yang na rgyud gzhan gyi sgo nas /
NK075(bu)002:4138: zhi khro gnyis su dbye ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:4139: gdul bya rang gang mos kyis zhi khro gcig nyams su len pa la'ang /
NK075(bu)002:4140: blo che chung gi dbang gis /
NK075(bu)002:4141: dang po phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa /
NK075(bu)002:4142: de nas rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'i rim pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4143: dang nas rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'i cig
NK075(bu)002:4144: char ba gnyis kyi tshul gyis phyag rgya gcig pa
NK075(bu)002:4145: yab rkyang pa bsgom pa sku phyag rgya chen po
NK075(bu)002:4146: // de'i thugs kar rigs rang rang gi sa bon gang yin bsgom pa gsung chos rgya /
NK075(bu)002:4147: thugs kar thugs phyag mtshan bsgom pa thugs dam tshig gi /
NK075(bu)002:4148: 'od zer spro bsdus byas pa la sogs rnams 'phro
NK075(bu)002:4149: 'du phrin las kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4150: sku la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga /
NK075(bu)002:4151: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum /
NK075(bu)002:4152: thugs ye shes sems dpa' ste lha dgu dang ldan par bsgom pa de la yang /
NK075(bu)002:4153: phyag rgya gcig pa rang gi cha rkyen lam rim
NK075(bu)002:4154: nas bshad pa bzhin don bco lnga tshanga ba yi
NK075(bu)002:4155: sgo nas nyams su blang ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK075(bu)002:4156: de bzhin nyid la stong zhen yod la /
NK075(bu)002:4157: kun snang de la snang zhen yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:4158: de gnyis las grol bar 'gyur ba'i thabs la dbyer
NK075(bu)002:4159: med phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha bsgom zhing nyams su
NK075(bu)002:4160: len pa la / phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa lha'i sku bsgom pa las /
NK075(bu)002:4161: nyams g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa lnga dang
NK075(bu)002:4162: ldan par byas nas phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge
NK075(bu)002:4166: byis pa chung ngu gang yin pa de lo nyi shu lon pa dang lus smin stobs rdzogs pas /
NK075(bu)002:4167: rigs mthun pa'i khyim thabs shig len pas rgyud mang
NK075(bu)002:4168: du 'phel ba bzhin du phyag rgya gcig pa de
NK075(bu)002:4169: yi sgo nas zhi khro gang bsgom la gzhi blang
NK075(bu)002:4170: ba las tshangs pa ste zhi ba ya ma ste
NK075(bu)002:4171: khro bo'i lha rnams kyi gzugs can du bzhi bcu
NK075(bu)002:4172: rtsa gnyis dang / lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa phyag rgya spros pa sgom pa de yang /
NK075(bu)002:4173: med pa las yod par sgom pa ma yin //
NK075(bu)002:4174: ye gdod nas rtog tshogs rang la gnas pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:4175: de nyid 'gag med du lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor shar ba de la /
NK075(bu)002:4176: cig char du rgya mtsho nang du nyi zla gza'
NK075(bu)002:4177: dang skar ma shar ba bzhin du lam bskyed byed
NK075(bu)002:4178: pa'am / de tsam mi gsal na rten 'brel bzhin du rim gyis gsung yig 'bru /
NK075(bu)002:4180: sku yongs rdzogs su rdo rje'i cha ga gsum gyis bskyed pas sam /
NK075(bu)002:4182: phyag rgya spros pa'i bslab par bya ba gang yin rang gi cha rkyen du /
NK075(bu)002:4183: don bco lnga lam rim nas bshad pa bzhin tshang
NK075(bu)002:4184: ba'i sgo nas nyams su len pa la mthar phyin
NK075(bu)002:4185: nas / zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam /
NK075(bu)002:4186: 'bar ba lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa gang
NK075(bu)002:4187: bsgom gyis lha rnams la lung gi lhag pa'i lha
NK075(bu)002:4189: sku gsung thugs lha gsum dang /
NK075(bu)002:4190: thugs ye shes sems dpa' dang dgu /
NK075(bu)002:4191: kho rang de nyid dang bcu dang ldan pa gsal nas /
NK075(bu)002:4192: de la yang spro ste zhi ba ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:4193: gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rtog pa'i gnas su /
NK075(bu)002:4194: yab la yab bcu bdun dang thub drug /
NK075(bu)002:4195: yum la yum bcu bdun te bzhi bcu bkod la /
NK075(bu)002:4196: de rnams la sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum ste brgya nyi shu /
NK075(bu)002:4197: ye shes sems dpa' re re ste bzhi bcu dang /
NK075(bu)002:4199: gzhi ma thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu ste gnyis bargya'o //
NK075(bu)002:4200: de yang thugs ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu la dbu rgyan med /
NK075(bu)002:4201: brgya drug cu la dbu rgyan lnga lnga bsgoms pas lha stong gsal bas mthong lam rdzogs la /
NK075(bu)002:4202: de bzhin tu kun bzang yab yum rigs bzhi yab yum dang lnga la stong tsho lnga /
NK075(bu)002:4203: sems dpa' yab yum brgyad sgo ba yab yum bzhi
NK075(bu)002:4204: dang bcu gnyis la stong tshe bcu gnyis thub drug
NK075(bu)002:4206: de ltar nyi khri bzhi stong gsal bar sgom lam rdzogs la /
NK075(bu)002:4207: nam mkha' khyab pa sogs su gsal bas mthar lam rdzogs pas /
NK075(bu)002:4208: phyag rgya spros pa'i sgo nas lam bgrod pa'am yang
NK075(bu)002:4209: na phyag rgya spros pa'i lha rnams la lha dgu
NK075(bu)002:4210: nyid bcu dang ldan par byas nas /
NK075(bu)002:4211: de la longs spyod lnga la sogs pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:4212: yang na thod rgal ba 'ga' zhig gis /
NK075(bu)002:4215: phyag rgya gcig phra rags gnyis dang bzhi gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)002:4216: lnga pa'i phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor sgom pa
NK075(bu)002:4217: 'ba' zhig gis lhag bcas dang lhag med gnyis su
NK075(bu)002:4218: mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul du tshe rnam gnyis
NK075(bu)002:4219: kyi 'bras bu thob par 'gyur ba'ang gi sgras yod
NK075(bu)002:4220: pa tsam bar chad med pa'i tshogs bsgrub pa dang
NK075(bu)002:4222: thod rgal ba ltar phyag rgya spros pa de nyid kyi sgo nas mthong lam thob pa /
NK075(bu)002:4223: mthar chags pa'i blo dang mi 'tsham pa longs spyod
NK075(bu)002:4224: lnga lnga spyod pa'i thabs tshom bu tshogs bsgrub rang
NK075(bu)002:4225: gi sgo nas mthong lam la sbyor bar byed pa
NK075(bu)002:4226: la bsgrub gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga'am bzhi yis
NK075(bu)002:4227: gzhi bzung ste / bzhi gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:4228: sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4232: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa lngar bshad pa yang snang /
NK075(bu)002:4233: de la sgrub pa po ni /
NK075(bu)002:4234: ston pa rdo rje rgyal po /
NK075(bu)002:4240: rdul phyags kyi skyes bu la sogs rnal 'byor pho mo rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:4243: mi dang mi ma yin gyi gnod pa med pa'i sar sa chog tshar nas /
NK075(bu)002:4244: gnas skor khang sum rim du rtsig cing byug bsrung bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4245: dus ni brgyad dang rgyal 'dzom pa la sogs dus
NK075(bu)002:4246: tshod gza' skar bkra shis pa la zhugs nas zla
NK075(bu)002:4247: ba drug gam / lo gcig gam /
NK075(bu)002:4248: zla ba bcu drug rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:4254: sgrub pa'i yo byad rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:4255: lam rim dang sgrub thabs rnams nas ji ltar bshad pa bzhin tshogs par byas la sgrub thabs /
NK075(bu)002:4256: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi yis gzhung bsrangs te /
NK075(bu)002:4257: de la bsnyen sgrub bzhi la 'dod lugs mang yang /
NK075(bu)002:4259: dang po lam dus kyi bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:4262: phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis nye bsnyen /
NK075(bu)002:4263: longs spyod lnga'i tshogs bsgrub pa ni sgrub pa /
NK075(bu)002:4264: de'i dus su +aa li k+aa nyams su len pa ni sgrub pa chen po /
NK075(bu)002:4265: sgrub pa dus kyi bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:4266: dkyil 'khor bris shing rdzas bkod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4267: phyi mchod bya zhing mtshams gcod pa rnams ni sngon du 'gro ba bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4268: sngon 'gro nas bzung ste rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyi mi grangs lha grangs sprad pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:4269: yang rnal 'byor pa gcig gis lha kun bsgoms nas
NK075(bu)002:4270: sgrub pa ci tsam byed pa'i zhag grangs phyed yan
NK075(bu)002:4271: chad la / 'od zer dkar po phyir spros pa
NK075(bu)002:4272: ting nge 'dzin gyi snod dag par byed pa ni
NK075(bu)002:4273: chad la / nye ba bsnyen / nub tha ma
NK075(bu)002:4274: ma gtogs pa'i phyed man chod la 'od zer dmar
NK075(bu)002:4275: po'i 'phro 'du'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bcud dag nas
NK075(bu)002:4276: dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byed pa ni
NK075(bu)002:4277: chad la / nye ba bsnyen / sgrub pa /
NK075(bu)002:4278: nub tha ma la 'od zer mthing ga tshur bsdu
NK075(bu)002:4279: chad la / nye ba bsnyen / sgrub pa /
NK075(bu)002:4280: bas / ting nge 'dzin snod bcud gnyis ka'i rgyud
NK075(bu)002:4281: dag par byed pa ni sgrub pa chen po ste
NK075(bu)002:4282: chad la / nye ba bsnyen / sgrub pa /
NK075(bu)002:4283: bas / / de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang ldan
NK075(bu)002:4284: pa'i sgo nas lam tshogs bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs kyi
NK075(bu)002:4285: tshad rgyud nas bshad pa ltar tshang nas /
NK075(bu)002:4286: dngos grub kyi rtags byung na dngos grub blang ba'i rtags sgrub chen rgyas bshad las /
NK075(bu)002:4288: dang po lha'i sgo nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:4289: lha ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK075(bu)002:4290: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' dngos grub kyi snying po bzlas shing blangs pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4291: de yang sku gsung thugs sogs dkyil 'khor rang dang mthun par sbyar te /
NK075(bu)002:4292: sku'i dkyil 'khor yin na spyi bo nas bstim pa
NK075(bu)002:4293: la sogs pa rang rang gi gnas su bstim zhing
NK075(bu)002:4295: yang na thugs sgyu dra ba dbang btsan du /
NK075(bu)002:4296: tshom bu lnga pa la gnas lngar bstim /
NK075(bu)002:4297: tshom bu gsum pa la gnas gsum /
NK075(bu)002:4298: tshom bu gcig pa la thugs kar bstims par yang bzhed do //
NK075(bu)002:4299: lam rim dang rgyas pa gnyis las /
NK075(bu)002:4300: dkyil 'khor mthun pa nyid du sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:4301: gnas su bstim zhing brtan par bya //
NK075(bu)002:4303: rdzas kyi sgo nas dngos grub blang ba'i thabs la 'dod yon lnga la longs spyod kyang /
NK075(bu)002:4304: khyad par du sbyor sgrol gnyis po blang dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:4305: de la sbyor ba dus kyi bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:4306: yum mtshan nyid dang ldan pa khrus dang chos bshad nas sta gon la gnas pa bsnyen pa /
NK075(bu)002:4307: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs sbyor ba'i brdas bskul /
NK075(bu)002:4308: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byas
NK075(bu)002:4309: pa nye bsnyen phyag rgya bzhis rol pa ni sgrub
NK075(bu)002:4310: pa / nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blang ba ni bsgrub pa chen po ste /
NK075(bu)002:4311: nub tha ma la mthong lam gyi ye shes chen
NK075(bu)002:4312: po rgyud la skye bar byed pa dngos grub chen
NK075(bu)002:4313: po yum gyi mkha' nas blang ba'i thabs /
NK075(bu)002:4315: dngos su mchod pa rnam gnyis su //
NK075(bu)002:4316: gtso ru dgos pa gang yin la //
NK075(bu)002:4318: de yang sgrub pa'i yan lag ni /
NK075(bu)002:4320: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK075(bu)002:4321: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK075(bu)002:4322: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pa //
NK075(bu)002:4325: lta sgom gding du gyur cing /
NK075(bu)002:4326: shes rab dang brtson 'grus de rnams tshangas na lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa med pa /
NK075(bu)002:4328: de 'og rnam smin rig 'dzin tshe 'dir thob la /
NK075(bu)002:4329: gang gi sgrub pa'i yan lag lnga gsum bco lnga la sogs /
NK075(bu)002:4330: de tsam cung min te ma tshang na /
NK075(bu)002:4331: skye ba phyi ma'am lan grangas bdun tshun chad tshe dbang thob la /
NK075(bu)002:4332: der ma thob na skye ba lan grangs gzhan nyid du rnam smin thob pa la mi 'da' ba'am /
NK075(bu)002:4333: de yang mtshan nyid ltar bskal pa grangs med ni thogs pa ma yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4334: 'o na tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi skabs der thod rgal 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:4335: rtsa rgyud kyi nang du tshom bu gcig pa'i skabs su /
NK075(bu)002:4336: gnyis med gyur na phyag rgya che //
NK075(bu)002:4338: 'bras bu phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang gsum pa'i skabs na /
NK075(bu)002:4342: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK075(bu)002:4344: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob par bshad //
NK075(bu)002:4345: ce na tshogs sgrub nas thod rgal 'byung ba'i lugs ni ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4346: tshe dbang nas thod rgal 'byung ba'i lung yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4347: tshom bu gcig pa bsgrubs nas tshe dbang bsgrub pa des /
NK075(bu)002:4348: lo stong drug brgya red nas /
NK075(bu)002:4349: phyag rgya chen po thob la /
NK075(bu)002:4350: tshom bu gsum pa bsgrubs nas tshe dbang thob pa des /
NK075(bu)002:4351: lo stong drug brgya red nas lhun grub thob pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:4353: brgya phrag cha rdzogs dus bar du //
NK075(bu)002:4354: goms byas gnyis thob mtha' skad cig /
NK075(bu)002:4356: tshom bu lnga pa bsgrubs nas tshe dbang thob pa des /
NK075(bu)002:4357: lo stong drug brgya red nas sangs rgyas thob pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4359: de tshe bcu drug tshun chod kyis //
NK075(bu)002:4360: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)002:4363: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4364: brgya phrag dag tu bsgyur zhing gnas //
NK075(bu)002:4365: lus mi bor bar sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4367: 'o na tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha la bzang ngan yod par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:4369: lha la bzang ngan yod pa ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4370: lam pa'i blo la che chung yod pas rgyu tshogs
NK075(bu)002:4371: bsgrub pa'i dus su lha yang mang nyung gi khyad
NK075(bu)002:4372: par gyis / 'bras bu lam gong mar sbyor ba'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:4374: 'o na tshom bu gcig gsum lnga bsgrub pa'i rnam smin rig 'dzin la yang /
NK075(bu)002:4375: blo rab 'bring tha ma gsum yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:4378: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi dngos 'bras phyag rgya chen
NK075(bu)002:4379: po yi rig 'dzin kho na las mi thob pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4380: phyir / brgyud 'bras lam gong ma lhun grub la sbyor ba'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:4381: myur bul yod pas khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK075(bu)002:4386: dang po thod rgal 'byung ba'i sa ni /
NK075(bu)002:4387: zag bcas lam gyi skabs su phyag rgya gcig spros na 'byung srid la /
NK075(bu)002:4389: zag med kyi lam gyi skabs su tshe dbang dang
NK075(bu)002:4390: phyag rgya chen po gnyis kyi nang nas 'byung srid
NK075(bu)002:4391: kyi khyab pa ni med do //
NK075(bu)002:4392: gnyis pa thod rgal gyi go ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:4393: lam bar nas bor nas grangs kyi 'og ma dor cing gong ma la sbyar ba zhig yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4394: gsum pa thod rgal 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)002:4395: lam rim gyis sa gang zhig gis /
NK075(bu)002:4396: lam bar nas bor du yod pa dang gcig /
NK075(bu)002:4397: ngang gi blo che ba dang gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:4398: snang stong dbyer med bsgom nus pa dang gsum po gzhi gcig la tshogs nas 'byung gis /
NK075(bu)002:4399: de las gzhan du ni mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4402: snang stong dbyer med bsgom mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:4404: tshom bu sgrub pa dang mthar lam lhun grub rig
NK075(bu)002:4405: 'dzin gnyis ni lam bar nas bor du med pas
NK075(bu)002:4407: 'o na tshogs sgrub lam bor du yod ce na ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4408: tshogs sgrub pa'i steng nas lus ma bor 'bras bu
NK075(bu)002:4409: thob na tshe dbang lus bor nas thob na rnam
NK075(bu)002:4412: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4414: rnam smin rig 'dzin ni snang stong dbyer med bsgom nus /
NK075(bu)002:4416: ngang gis blo chung bas snang ba las shugs bkag /
NK075(bu)002:4417: zhad tsam red pas lus por dgos pas thod rgal mi 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:4419: stobs chung rkyen smon zhan pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:4421: mthar lam gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK075(bu)002:4423: des rgya mtsho'i nang du nyi 'od rin po che dang /
NK075(bu)002:4425: rlan med pa'i rin po che dang /
NK075(bu)002:4426: mthar thug pa'i nor bu rin po che dang bzhi
NK075(bu)002:4427: yod pa yi stobs kyis rgya mtsho la 'phel 'grib
NK075(bu)002:4428: mi 'byung / 'byung ba 'jig chags 'byung ba'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:4429: nyi 'od kyi 'od phog pas rgya mtsho'i chu spangs pa med par zho ru 'gyur /
NK075(bu)002:4431: rlan med pa'i 'od phog pas me ru 'gro /
NK075(bu)002:4432: mthar thug pa'i nor bu'i 'od phog pas thams cad
NK075(bu)002:4433: stong zhing mi snang bar 'gyur ba ci bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:4434: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa dang
NK075(bu)002:4435: / mthar sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba la'ang /
NK075(bu)002:4436: dpe 'di ltar gyi don ni mthong lam sgom lam mthar lam gyi bar du rim par sbyar nas /
NK075(bu)002:4437: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa thob pa la gdon mi za yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4438: tshogs sgrub 'di nyid kyi steng nas /
NK075(bu)002:4439: mthar lam tshe rnam gnyis thob pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:4440: nyi 'od kyis chu zhor 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4441: zag bcas kyi nyon mongs de nyid /
NK075(bu)002:4442: zag med kyi ye shes su 'gyur la /
NK075(bu)002:4443: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob pa de'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:4444: de bas kyang stobs zhugs te /
NK075(bu)002:4445: me 'od phog pas mar du 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4446: mthong lam du da rung kun 'gro'i sgrib pa yod pa de /
NK075(bu)002:4447: 'dir ye shes su shar nas rang lus rgyal ba'i skur gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4448: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi skabs su de bas stobs su gyur te /
NK075(bu)002:4449: rlan med pa'i 'od phog pas me ru 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4450: sgom lam la lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma yod de /
NK075(bu)002:4451: 'dir ye shes su shar nas sku lnga lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin du gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4452: sangs rgyas pa'i dus su de bas stobs su gyur te /
NK075(bu)002:4453: mthar thug pa'i nor bu'i 'od phog pas thams cad
NK075(bu)002:4454: stong pa bzhin du mthar lam la da rung kun
NK075(bu)002:4455: gzhi bag la nyal gyi dri ma yod pa de
NK075(bu)002:4456: / ye shes su shar bas gzung 'dzin sa bon dang bcas pa btsal bas mi rnyed nas /
NK075(bu)002:4457: thams cad ye shes kyi 'khor yug shar ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:4460: kye rgyal ba'i sras po dag /
NK075(bu)002:4461: rgya mtsho chen po 'dus pa'i chu'i phung po de
NK075(bu)002:4462: dag kyang nor bu nyi ma'i snying po'i 'od phog
NK075(bu)002:4463: nas chu'i rang bzhin spangs te /
NK075(bu)002:4464: 'o ma dang zho ru 'gyur te 'dug go //
NK075(bu)002:4465: nor bu rin po che'i rlan med pa'i 'od phog na /
NK075(bu)002:4466: 'o ma dang zho'i rang bzhin spangs nas mar gyi nying khu ltar 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:4467: me'i 'od kyi nor bu rin po che'i 'od phog na /
NK075(bu)002:4468: mar gyi nying khu'i rang bzhin spangs te /
NK075(bu)002:4470: nor bu rin po che ma lus pa mthar thug pa'i 'od phog na /
NK075(bu)002:4471: thams cad lhag ma med cing ma lus pa'i snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:4477: lam gyi yan lag la rgyud don bcu yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:4478: lta ba gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)002:4480: lta ba de nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par
NK075(bu)002:4481: byed pa'i skabs 'dir spyod pa'i don rnams shes nas
NK075(bu)002:4482: nyams su blang dgos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4483: thabs lam grol lam lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin de dag las su rung bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:4486: spyod pa byed pa'i dus dang ni /
NK075(bu)002:4487: spyod pa ma byas pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:4489: lnga po de nyid kyis nang du yo byad don rgyas bshad de rdzogs pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4495: bdag dang gzhan gyi dona du spyod pa byas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4496: stobs kyis bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis lhun gyis grub
NK075(bu)002:4497: pa'i phyir dang / gzhan yang sgrib pa dbri ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4499: khyad par du thabs lam gyi spyod pa bag chags kyis mi dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4500: grol lam gyi spyod pa ting nge 'dzin gamas par
NK075(bu)002:4501: byed cing stobs su gyur pa'i phyir spyod pa la
NK075(bu)002:4507: de la spyod pa'i rnam grangs ni gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)002:4508: po sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i rgyud de nyid la gsungs
NK075(bu)002:4509: pa yi don ni so so skye bo barlanga po
NK075(bu)002:4510: rang kha ma'i spyod pa dang tshul mthun par /
NK075(bu)002:4515: sha chen te dam rdzas lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:4525: ngag barlanga po ste spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK075(bu)002:4530: reg bya ste 'dod yon lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:4531: 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs pa lnga ste /
NK075(bu)002:4532: de ltar nyi shu rtsa lnga ni 'khor ba nag po'i spyod pa dang tshul mthun yang /
NK075(bu)002:4533: gsang sngags kyi lta bas zin na nyon mongs pa
NK075(bu)002:4534: ma spangs longs spyod kyang nyon mongs pa de nyid
NK075(bu)002:4535: kyis mi gos na nag pos 'dul ba'i thabs ji
NK075(bu)002:4536: snyed pa zhig gsungs pa ni sngags phyi pa man
NK075(bu)002:4537: chad dang thun mong min pa ste thabs lam gyi
NK075(bu)002:4538: spyod pa dang / de las bzlog pa dkar po'i
NK075(bu)002:4539: spyod pa'i khyad par grol lam gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:4540: gyi skabs kyi spyod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:4541: grol lam gyi spyod pa de dang theg pa 'og
NK075(bu)002:4542: ma'i lam gyi skabs so sor spyod lugs su mthun
NK075(bu)002:4546: thun mongs ma yin pa'i thabs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4548: 'dod chags la zhen pa'i gang zag gi lam bgrod
NK075(bu)002:4549: pa la chags rtog de nyid ma spangs pas lam
NK075(bu)002:4550: du khyer ba mthar chags su rtogs pa de nyid
NK075(bu)002:4551: ye shes su shar nas grol ba na /
NK075(bu)002:4552: de ltar du dug nad can la sman du dug
NK075(bu)002:4553: kho rang bcud len du btang bas dug nad la
NK075(bu)002:4554: phan pa bzhin du zhen chags can gyi rnal 'byor
NK075(bu)002:4555: pa bdag grol ba dang rang rgyud grol ba'i stobs
NK075(bu)002:4556: kyis / chags zhen gyis gang zag gzhan rnams kyi rgyud grol bar nus pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:4557: des na bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don rnams nyams su
NK075(bu)002:4558: blang ba la chags rtog de nyid spang mi dgos
NK075(bu)002:4559: pas na thabas che ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4560: de nyid kyi dri mas mi gos shing nyon mongs
NK075(bu)002:4561: ye shes su shar bas na thabs mkhas pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:4562: na / thabs kyi spyod pa zhes bya ba'i sgo nas 'jog pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4563: grol lam gyi khyad par lam dang sar mthun pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4566: dpe'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4568: cig shos te kha cig grol lam pa'i spyod pa
NK075(bu)002:4569: de ni lta ba gtan la pheb pa'i dus su
NK075(bu)002:4570: damngas te bran lta bu'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4573: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su rje ste blon po lta bu'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4574: phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs su bram ze lta bu'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4575: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa'i skabs su rgyal phran lta bu'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4576: zag med rig 'dzin bzhi'i skabs su stong 'khor lo
NK075(bu)002:4577: bsgyur ba'i rgyal po lta bu'i spyod pa dang lnga
NK075(bu)002:4578: mi 'dra ba'i rim pa yod pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4579: dpe don rgyas par bshad pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:4580: don gyi sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK075(bu)002:4582: rgyu shes pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4584: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba gtan la phab pa'i skabs kyi spyod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:4585: dpe dmangs te bran gyis las bzang ngan sna tshogs byed dgos pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4586: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba
NK075(bu)002:4587: shesa par bya ba'i bslab bya mang po kun la
NK075(bu)002:4588: brtson para byed cing spang blang gi dmigs shes par
NK075(bu)002:4589: bya ba'i phyir phyi rol pa'i grub mtha' dang /
NK075(bu)002:4590: nang pa'i grub mtha' gang la yang dor bar bya
NK075(bu)002:4591: ba yoda pa ma yina de kun la bslab par
NK075(bu)002:4592: bya'o // ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4594: de ltar gtan la phab pa lta ba'i rjes su /
NK075(bu)002:4595: ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par byed pa la yang /
NK075(bu)002:4596: dpe don mtshon par byed pa gnyis pa rje ste
NK075(bu)002:4597: blun po'i spyod pa ltar du nyams su blangs dgos
NK075(bu)002:4598: te / de yang rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK075(bu)002:4602: phyag rgya gcig pa dang gsum la blon po yig
NK075(bu)002:4603: tshang ste shes rig 'byed cha dang ldan pa des
NK075(bu)002:4605: rgyal po'i mthun phyogs bsgrub mi mthun phyogs bsal pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4606: thabas la brtson pa bzhin du de ting bying ba
NK075(bu)002:4607: dang cha mthun pas de sel ba'i thabs kyis gadmas
NK075(bu)002:4608: ngag gi sgo nas bying ba de bsal nas /
NK075(bu)002:4609: spyod lam rnam bzhir rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting
NK075(bu)002:4610: nge 'dzin dang mi 'bral bar bya ba ni stong
NK075(bu)002:4611: thog tu sbyang ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4612: kun ting rgod pa dang cha mthun pas de bsal
NK075(bu)002:4613: nas spyod lam rnam bzhir stong pa de nyid kyi
NK075(bu)002:4614: rtsal snying rje 'gag med du shar ba dang ma
NK075(bu)002:4615: bral bar bya ba ni 'gyu thog nas sbyang ba'o
NK075(bu)002:4616: // phyag rgya gcig pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:4617: rim gyis pas dang po yig 'bru de nas sogas
NK075(bu)002:4618: sgras thugs phyag mtshan sku yongs rdzogs kyi grangs rim
NK075(bu)002:4621: rim gyis pa las bzlog la dang nas lha sku
NK075(bu)002:4622: cig char du bskyed pa'i thabs dang gnyis la brten
NK075(bu)002:4623: nas gnas 'gyu dbyer med la sbyang ba'i spyod pa
NK075(bu)002:4624: bya'o // spros pa'i spyod pa dang /
