NK075(bu)002:4626: phyag rgya spros pa'i dus su dpe bram ze gtsang
NK075(bu)002:4627: ma'i rigas kyis rdzas gang la longs spyod pa'i dus
NK075(bu)002:4628: su sngags kyi nus mthus sbyangs nas longs spyod du
NK075(bu)002:4629: rung ba bzhina du rim gyis pa'i dbang du zag
NK075(bu)002:4630: bcas kyi bden pa mthong nas gomas par byed pa
NK075(bu)002:4631: ni tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi la phyag rgya spros
NK075(bu)002:4632: pa 'di nyid kyi skabs yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:4634: spros bcas kyi ting 'dzin gyis mthu snang thog tu
NK075(bu)002:4635: zhen pa'i spyod yul sna tshogs su shar ba la
NK075(bu)002:4636: sbyang bar bya'o // bar chad med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4638: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi gong du song nas lnga
NK075(bu)002:4639: pa bar chad med pa'i tshogs bsgrub pa'i skabs su
NK075(bu)002:4640: dpe skye 'gro thams cad kyis sri zhu gus pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4641: gnas ni rgyal po yin la /
NK075(bu)002:4642: rgyal po de'i chos lugs ni 'dod yon lnga la
NK075(bu)002:4643: dad cing longs spyod pa bzhin du 'dir yang longas
NK075(bu)002:4644: spyod dang yo byad lnga spyod cing shin tu phyag
NK075(bu)002:4645: rgya spros bcas kyi spyod pa nyams su blangs bar
NK075(bu)002:4646: bya yang lnga pa bsgrub par bya ba'i skabs la
NK075(bu)002:4647: / snang ba so ma'i zhen pa la sbyangs dgos
NK075(bu)002:4648: pas 'dod yon lnga po spyod pa'i gtso bo la
NK075(bu)002:4649: nyams su blangsa pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4652: de nas tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi yi sgo nas
NK075(bu)002:4653: zag bcas kyi spyod pa mthar phyin byas nas spros
NK075(bu)002:4654: pa'i tshogs bsgrub pa'i sgo nas lus khams skye gnas
NK075(bu)002:4655: kyi zag pa dang brala nas rig 'dzin thob pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4656: dus spyod pa lhun gyis grub kyang rgya che chung
NK075(bu)002:4657: yod de / de bas 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal
NK075(bu)002:4658: po la bsod nams lhun gyis grub kyang lcagsa 'khor
NK075(bu)002:4659: can gling gcig dang zangs 'khor can shar lho'i gling
NK075(bu)002:4660: gnyis dang gser 'khor can gling bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:4661: dngul 'khor can gling gsum la dbang byed pa'i gdul
NK075(bu)002:4662: bya rgya che chung gi go rim yod pa bzhin
NK075(bu)002:4663: du / rig 'dzin bzhi la yang bdag don ting
NK075(bu)002:4664: nge 'dzin stobs che chung dang gzhan don byed pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4665: yul gdul bya la rgya che chung gyi khyad par
NK075(bu)002:4668: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi bdag don gyi spyod pa
NK075(bu)002:4669: ni spyod yul lha dang lha mor rol pa'i tshul
NK075(bu)002:4670: du spyod la / gzhan don du 'phrin las rnam
NK075(bu)002:4671: bzhi'i sgo nas gling bzhi tshun chad gdul bya yang
NK075(bu)002:4672: dag pa'i don la dgos ched do //
NK075(bu)002:4673: zangs 'khor can gyis de bas stobs che ba bzhin
NK075(bu)002:4674: du tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyis bdag don du lo
NK075(bu)002:4676: kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag par byed cing /
NK075(bu)002:4677: lam gong ma rnams khob 'og tu tshud par byed do //
NK075(bu)002:4678: gzhan don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya tshun chad kyi gdul bya rnams la /
NK075(bu)002:4679: bskal pa grangs med gnas nas 'pho lugs kyi tshul
NK075(bu)002:4680: bstan nas cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo nas sems can gyi
NK075(bu)002:4681: don byed do // dngul 'khor can de bas kyang stobs che ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4683: bdag don du nyi khri gcig stong grangs can gyi
NK075(bu)002:4684: 'khor lo mngon du snang zhing lhan cig gnas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4685: dri ma dag par byed cing /
NK075(bu)002:4686: gzhan don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya
NK075(bu)002:4687: phrag stong de 'dra ba bcu'i rdul snyed dang mnyam
NK075(bu)002:4688: pa'i 'jig rten brgya phrag stong de 'dra ba bcu'i
NK075(bu)002:4689: rdul snyed kyii zhing khams su rngon dang smad 'tshong
NK075(bu)002:4690: ma la sogs pa sprul pa'i lus kyi sgo nas
NK075(bu)002:4692: gser 'khor can de bas kyang stobs che ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:4693: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis rang don du bag la nyal phra ba sbyangs shing /
NK075(bu)002:4694: gzhan don du zhing khams mtha' yas par gdul bya
NK075(bu)002:4695: sna tshogs la sprul sku'i mdzad pa sna tshogs ston
NK075(bu)002:4696: pa'o // lam rang rang spyod pa khyad par gyi spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4698: 'o na lam gong ma'i skabs su /
NK075(bu)002:4700: rang rang gi spyod pa dang gnyis ka la spyod dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:4701: spyod pa la khyad med do //
NK075(bu)002:4704: lam snga ma'i dus kyi spyod pa de /
NK075(bu)002:4705: lam phyi ma la 'jug pa'i gang zag gi rgyud la rang shugs kyis ldan nas yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:4706: lam 'og ma'i spyod pa gong ma'i skabs su dngos
NK075(bu)002:4707: su spyod pa'i rtsol ba med cing de bas na
NK075(bu)002:4708: lam rang rang gi spyod pa'i bslab pa gang yin
NK075(bu)002:4709: pa de / lam rang rang gi skabs su spyod pa gces pa nas /
NK075(bu)002:4710: lam gyi sa tshod mtho dman gyis phye bas na spyod pa la khyad par yod pa yina no //
NK075(bu)002:4713: de yang spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:4714: lam dang sa yi rim pa mtho dman gyi skabs
NK075(bu)002:4715: dang sbyar nas spyod pa rgyud gzhung nas gragsa pa
NK075(bu)002:4717: de lam mtho dman gyi don go ba tsam gyis
NK075(bu)002:4718: mi chog ting nge 'dzin gyi ro rang rang gis
NK075(bu)002:4719: nyams su myong ba'i tshod rang rang gis bzung nas
NK075(bu)002:4720: / ting nge 'dzin de dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:4721: de bas na lam snga ma'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK075(bu)002:4722: goms pa mthar ma phyin gyi bar du snga ma'i
NK075(bu)002:4724: lam phyi ma la 'jug pa'i tshe de nas lam
NK075(bu)002:4725: phyi ma rang gi spyod yul rgyud gzhung nas ci
NK075(bu)002:4726: ltar bshad pa bzhin du nyams su blang bar bya'o
NK075(bu)002:4729: khyad par grol lam gyi skabs su lam rang rang
NK075(bu)002:4730: gi skabs su bshad pa'i spyod pa ma byas dor
NK075(bu)002:4731: ba na lam mthar phyin nas 'bras bu thob tu
NK075(bu)002:4732: med do // thabs lam gyi spyod pa'i 'dod yon
NK075(bu)002:4733: lnga la sogs nyi shu rtsa lnga po rnams barlanga
NK075(bu)002:4734: po rang khar spyod pa ni bdag don du mi
NK075(bu)002:4735: med do // 'gyur / bdag ngan song du 'gro /
NK075(bu)002:4737: gzhan gyis theg chen du mi mos mi dad nas skur pa btab pas ngan song du 'gro ba'am /
NK075(bu)002:4738: rjes su 'jug nas ngan song du 'gro /
NK075(bu)002:4742: chos de bshad pa bzhin nyams len byas nas ngan
NK075(bu)002:4743: song du 'gro zhes kun gyis smad pa dang bzhi
NK075(bu)002:4746: 'dod yon dang nyon mongs pa rang khar spyod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4747: dbang du song basa nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs
NK075(bu)002:4748: pa'i sgo nas so so'i rnam smin tshad las 'das
NK075(bu)002:4749: pa zhig bsags nas 'bras bu ngan song gis sdug
NK075(bu)002:4750: bsngal tshad las 'das pa cig myong bar byed do
NK075(bu)002:4751: // gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' lta ba la phyogs gcig ltos kyang /
NK075(bu)002:4752: spyod pas rtsal sprug ma nus pas bskal pa grangs
NK075(bu)002:4753: med gsum thogs mu stegs pas lta ba ma rtogs
NK075(bu)002:4754: pas spyod pa byas pas ngan song du 'gro /
NK075(bu)002:4755: zhes sgyu 'phrul rgyas par gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:4758: gong gis de rnams rang rang gi skabs la bshad pa'i spyod pa de yi /
NK075(bu)002:4759: lam rang rang gi don mthar phyin nus pa'i yon tan de yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK075(bu)002:4760: lam gyi yon tan de yod pa'i don gyis spyod
NK075(bu)002:4761: pa des bdag gzhan gnyis po 'khor bar mi ltung
NK075(bu)002:4762: nas 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i yon tan yod
NK075(bu)002:4763: do // thabs lam gyis spyod pa 'dod yon lnga
NK075(bu)002:4764: la sogs pa so so rang rang khar spyod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:4765: dbang gis ngan song du ltung la /
NK075(bu)002:4766: thabs mkhas pa'i lta bas zin nas tshul bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:4767: spyod na 'bras bu sangs rgyas 'thob par byed ces
NK075(bu)002:4768: rgyud gzhung las gragas pa bzhina yin la /
NK075(bu)002:4769: gzhan yang basga bya tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)002:4770: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa lam du khyer bas /
NK075(bu)002:4772: de'i dus su chos nyid rang las ma g.yos pas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4773: nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs nyi shu rtsa lnga po spyod pa'i dri mas mi gos la /
NK075(bu)002:4774: sgrib pa dbri ba ste dag par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:4779: lam gyi cha rkyen la gsum pa 'phrin las bya ba'i sdom tshig ni /
NK075(bu)002:4781: 'phrin las bya ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)002:4782: 'phrin las kyi ngo bo ngos bzung dang /
NK075(bu)002:4783: 'phrin las kyi nges tshig gam sgra don bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4784: 'phrin las la rnam grangs du yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4785: 'phrin las bya ba'i thabas dngos dang skabsa gar mkho ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4786: 'phrin las khyad par yod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:4788: byas pa'i yon tan dang dgu yis ni phrin las rgyas bshad de rdzogas pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4794: badga don bsgrub pa dang gzhan don bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4795: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don lhun grub bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4796: dam pa'i chos don du 'gyur bas byed pa'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)002:4801: lhun gyi grub pa'i 'phrin las rnam pa lnga po
NK075(bu)002:4802: de dpe zhing la sa bon btab pa dang rkyen
NK075(bu)002:4803: chu lud bkye nas 'bras bu smin te chud mi
NK075(bu)002:4805: bdag gzhan gyi don bsgrubs nas 'bras bu chud mi za bar 'byung bar byed pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4806: 'phrin las rnam pa lnga dang dang du blang dgos pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4807: de'ang dbang po rab kyis ting nge 'dzin kho nas
NK075(bu)002:4808: 'bring gis ting nge 'dzin dang sngags gnyis tha ma
NK075(bu)002:4812: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi sgo nas nus tshad dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:4815: de yang phrin las rnam bzhi'i gdul bya la phyi
NK075(bu)002:4816: nang gnyis gnyis te zung du brtsis pas bzhi po
NK075(bu)002:4821: nang du nyon mongs pa rnam rtog ma zhi ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:4822: rgyas pa la phyi la gso 'phel gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:4825: lo thog sri'u la sogs gso dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4826: tshe dang rigs rgyud longs spyod bsod nams ma 'phel ba dag dang /
NK075(bu)002:4827: nang du sku dang ye shes ma rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4829: phyi la gzungs ma 'gugs pa la sogs dang /
NK075(bu)002:4830: dagra bgegs rnam gnyis dbang po bsgyur ma nus pa /
NK075(bu)002:4831: nang du sku lnga la sogs 'bras bu'i chos dbang du bsdu ma nus pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4833: phyi la dgra bgegs bskrad mnan /
NK075(bu)002:4834: smyo 'bogs byed dang skam pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4836: gtan spangs rgyud gzhung du 'pho ba rnams ma nus pa /
NK075(bu)002:4837: nang la nyon mongs pa'i dgra bgegs ma 'joms pa
NK075(bu)002:4838: yod pas de rnams 'dul bar nus pa'i mthu chena
NK075(bu)002:4839: po zhi rgyas dbang drag gi 'phrin las rnam pa
NK075(bu)002:4841: phrin las gcig gis gdul bya phyi nang zung bzhi po kun 'dul nus pa'i mthu can ni /
NK075(bu)002:4842: lhun grub phrin las te sogs kyi sgras /
NK075(bu)002:4843: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bya byed kyi las kun kyang 'phrin las kyi nang du bsdus pas /
NK075(bu)002:4844: de ltar lnga po gdul bya gdul byed gang yin /
NK075(bu)002:4845: 'joms pa de phrin las kyi ngo bo yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4848: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu ste /
NK075(bu)002:4849: phyi la nad bgegs dgra dang /
NK075(bu)002:4850: nang du nyon mongs pa rnam rtog zhi ba'i phyir na zhi ba'i sgrar 'jug pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4851: 'phel bar bya ba phyi la na shi la sogs gso ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4852: tshe ring rgyud la sogs 'phel ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4853: nang du sku dang ye shes te /
NK075(bu)002:4854: de ltar gnyis po 'phel ba'i phyir na rgyas pa'i sgrar 'jug pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4855: gzungs ma la sogs dgug pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4856: dgra bgegs gnyis dbang po bsgyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:4857: 'bras bu sku lnga la sogs bzhi po dbang du
NK075(bu)002:4858: bsdus pa'i phyir na dbang gi sgrar 'jug pa dang
NK075(bu)002:4859: / phyi la dgra bgegs dang nang du nyon mongs
NK075(bu)002:4860: pa'i gdug rnam pa gnyis 'joms pa'i phyir na drag
NK075(bu)002:4862: lnga pa lhun grub ni sngon du ngo bo'i dus
NK075(bu)002:4863: su bashada pa bzhin du 'phrin las gcig gis kun
NK075(bu)002:4864: 'dul ba'i phyir na lhun grub kyi sgrar 'jug pa
NK075(bu)002:4865: dang / de nas 'phrin las rnam pa lnga'i nges
NK075(bu)002:4866: tshig gi sgra don te nges par grub pa yin
NK075(bu)002:4867: dang / no // bye brag tu sbyin sreg gi 'phrin las kyi rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:4871: 'phrin las kyi don gyi dmigas su ngos bzung ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:4872: rnam grangs rnam par dbye nas /
NK075(bu)002:4873: gzhi sems can gyi dus su 'phrin las rnam bzhi
NK075(bu)002:4874: lhun grub tu rang bzhin gyis gnas lam nyams su
NK075(bu)002:4875: blang ba'i dus su phrin las rnam bzhi las ma
NK075(bu)002:4876: g.yos pa dang / mthar thug sangs rgyas thugs rjes sems can gyi don byed pa yang /
NK075(bu)002:4877: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi 'phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas byed dgos pa yin /
NK075(bu)002:4878: yang gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyis phye bas gsum ste /
NK075(bu)002:4879: dang po gzhi'i dus su 'phrin las gnas tshul /
NK075(bu)002:4880: don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:4881: don dam ltar sems dang so so'i gnas lugs la /
NK075(bu)002:4882: gzhi sems nyid kyi ngo bo la ngos bzung med pa na /
NK075(bu)002:4883: nyon mangas rnam rtog ma zhi rang zhi /
NK075(bu)002:4884: ngos bzung med bzhin du thams cad la gsal bas na /
NK075(bu)002:4885: sku dang ye shes ma rgyas rang rgyas /
NK075(bu)002:4886: gsal stong dbyer med gcig pas na /
NK075(bu)002:4887: mtha' gnyis dbang du ma bsdus rang bsdus sems nyid
NK075(bu)002:4888: kyi rtsal rang thams cad la shar bas na gzung
NK075(bu)002:4889: 'dzin mtshan ma ma bcom rang bcom yin no //
NK075(bu)002:4890: kun rdzob ltar lus dngos po'i gnas lugs la /
NK075(bu)002:4891: snying kha'i rtsa 'khor lo bzhi'i dbyibs la zlum po /
NK075(bu)002:4895: 'od la dkar ser dmar nag bzhi yod pa 'phrin las rnam bzhi yin /
NK075(bu)002:4897: gnas bzhi'i 'byung ba'ang las bzhi ste //
NK075(bu)002:4899: steng sgo'i rtsa 'khor lo bzhi las bzhi'i dbyibs su yod par bshad de /
NK075(bu)002:4901: spyi bor sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi rgyas pa /
NK075(bu)002:4902: mgrin par rlung gi dal zla gam dbang /
NK075(bu)002:4903: snying gar me'i dal gru gsum drag po /
NK075(bu)002:4904: lte bar chu'i dal zlum po zhi ba yin gsungs /
NK075(bu)002:4908: sgrom mdo bzhi la zhi rgyas dbang drag gi gzugs su dod nas yod /
NK075(bu)002:4910: 'og sgo yum gyi mkha' la yang las bzhi'i las bzhi'i dbyibs su dod nas yod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4911: bye brag tu lam gyi rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)002:4914: las bzhi ngo bo'i rnams grangs so //
NK075(bu)002:4919: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi 'phrin las yod pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4920: 'dir bar ma lam gyi 'phrin las ngos bzung ba la /
NK075(bu)002:4921: thabs lam dang shes rab grol lam gnyis yin la /
NK075(bu)002:4922: thabs shes rab kyis rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4924: mdor bstan gyi snga ma thabs lam la steng 'og
NK075(bu)002:4925: gnyis kyi sgo nas lam nyams su len pa yang
NK075(bu)002:4926: las bzhi'am sbyin sreg yin pa dang phyi ma la
NK075(bu)002:4927: yang shes rab grol lam gyis lta ba rtogs pa
NK075(bu)002:4928: dang / ting nge 'dzin sgom pa rnam pa gnyis po yang las bzhi'i sbyin sreg yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4929: za tshogs gtor lung ltar du zas la longsa spyod pa yang las bzhi'i sbyin sreg yin la /
NK075(bu)002:4930: las bzhi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi sgo nas dngos su byed pa la /
NK075(bu)002:4931: mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bzhi byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:4932: me'i sgo nas las bzhi'i sbyin sreg byed thabs gnyisa so //
NK075(bu)002:4933: de rnams sbyin sreg yin tshul gyi go don bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:4934: thabs lam ni 'chad par 'gyur ba'i bya thabs kyi skabs su bshad la /
NK075(bu)002:4936: dang po lta ba la las bzhi'i spyin sreg tshang lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:4937: gzhi chos nyid kyi ngo bo la don las bzhi tshang ba ni hom khung /
NK075(bu)002:4938: snang srid kyi chos ni bsreg rdzas /
NK075(bu)002:4939: de rnams gang la yang zhen pa med par sbyin pas /
NK075(bu)002:4940: yid 'gyu ba rang sar grol nas /
NK075(bu)002:4941: ye shes su shar ba'i me des nyon mongs dang dngos po thams cad bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4942: ting nge 'dzin la las bzhi'i sbyin sreg tshang lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:4943: rtogs pa chos nyid kyi ngo bo la /
NK075(bu)002:4944: don las bzhi tshang ba ni hom khung /
NK075(bu)002:4945: rnam rtog phra rags ni bsreg rdzas /
NK075(bu)002:4946: gang shar chos nyid kyi ngo bo khyer nas sbyin pa /
NK075(bu)002:4947: mnyam gzhag ye shes chen po'i me des /
NK075(bu)002:4948: rjes shes kyi mtshan ma bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4949: 'dod yon tshogs su rol pa la las bzhi'i sbyin sreg tshang lugs ni /
NK075(bu)002:4953: 'dod yon zhen med lam du khyer nas sbyin pa zhen chags ye shes su shar ba'i mi des /
NK075(bu)002:4954: 'dod yon rang rgyud du zhen cing chags pa de bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:4955: lhag pa gzugs brnyan 'og bya thabs kyi skabs su shes so //
NK075(bu)002:4956: gzhan yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi bya thabs kyi rnam grangs la /
NK075(bu)002:4957: me'i sgo nas bya thabs le'u dgu pa nas gsungs pa 'dir bshad la /
NK075(bu)002:4958: rdzas kyi sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:4960: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga las //
NK075(bu)002:4961: mtshan ma ming dang bcas par bya //
NK075(bu)002:4963: lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:4964: lu gu rgyud du sgrel bsdams te /
NK075(bu)002:4966: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba ma gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:4967: phyag rgya bca' ba'i sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:4969: lus ngag snying po gcig tu bsdoms //
NK075(bu)002:4970: rtse lnga rtse bcu rtse dgu dang //
NK075(bu)002:4971: las rnams so sor rab tu bsgom //
NK075(bu)002:4973: rdo rje'i dril bu'i sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:4974: rdo rje lan gsum gsor ba yi //
NK075(bu)002:4975: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK075(bu)002:4980: gong gi rnam grangs de dag tshur la bsdu na /
NK075(bu)002:4981: lhag pa gzugs brnyan phyi yin la /
NK075(bu)002:4984: ting nge 'dzin longs spyod bzhi nang yin /
NK075(bu)002:4985: thabs lam 'og sgo ni gsang bar bshad pa dang gsum du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:4986: yang na phyi nang gsang gsum de kho na nyid dang bzhi las /
NK075(bu)002:4987: phyi ni 'og lhag pa gzugs brnyan dang mthun la /
NK075(bu)002:4988: nang gi rkang pa zla gam dbang gi thab khung /
NK075(bu)002:4990: gsus pa zlum po zhi ba /
NK075(bu)002:4991: brang gru bzhi rgyas pa'i thab khung ngo //
NK075(bu)002:4992: yid kyi rnam par shes pa me lhar shes nas /
NK075(bu)002:4995: kha zas za ba thams cad bsreg rdzas /
NK075(bu)002:4996: phung po khams dang skye mched thams cad lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du shes nas /
NK075(bu)002:4997: de nyid gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK075(bu)002:4998: rang bzhin gyi mchod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5000: gsang ba ni mkha' hom khung sna rtse me lha /
NK075(bu)002:5005: sems nyid rtog pa dang bral ba ni thab khung /
NK075(bu)002:5006: rnam par shes pa me lha /
NK075(bu)002:5009: sems dang sems las byung ba'i 'du byed lnga bcu rtsa gcig yam shing /
NK075(bu)002:5010: 'dod yon yul dang bcas pa mchod rdzas /
NK075(bu)002:5011: nyon mongs pa lnga bsreg rdzas su shes nas /
NK075(bu)002:5012: sems kyi ting nge 'dzin dag dgang blug gzar du shes pa de kun rdzob /
NK075(bu)002:5013: sems spros pa thams cad dang bral ba de don dam /
NK075(bu)002:5014: de gnyis su med pa de ye shes kyi mer shes par byas nas bsregs pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:5016: las bzhi ngo bo'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)002:5018: las bzhi'i ngo bo ngos bzung gi skabs dang rjes
NK075(bu)002:5019: su mthun par zhi ba'i rnam grangs la phyi nang
NK075(bu)002:5020: gnyis te / phyi la nad dang /
NK075(bu)002:5021: bgegsa dang dgra zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5022: nang la nyon mongs rnam rtog zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5023: rgyas pa la phyi nang gnyis po ngos bzung na /
NK075(bu)002:5024: phyi la gso ba dang 'phel ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:5025: gso ba la yang na ba gso ba shi ba
NK075(bu)002:5026: gso ba lo thog gso ba sri'u gso ba sogs
NK075(bu)002:5027: khong du rta mchog la sogs rgyas par gso ba
NK075(bu)002:5028: rnams so // 'phel ba la tshe 'phel ba ste ring ba'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:5029: rigas rgyud 'phel te mang ba'i dang /
NK075(bu)002:5030: longsa spyod 'phel te che ba'i dang /
NK075(bu)002:5031: bsod namsa 'phel te skye thabs dang bzhi po phyi yin la nang la 'bras bu sku dang /
NK075(bu)002:5033: dbang ni dgug pa dang bsdu ba gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:5034: phyi rol la d+ha ri ste gzungs ma'i rigs sogs
NK075(bu)002:5035: rnam par dgug par byed pa'i thabs dang mi mthun
NK075(bu)002:5036: pa'i dgra bgegs rnam pa gnyis po dbang po bsgyur
NK075(bu)002:5037: te ma dad pa dad par byed nas dbang du
NK075(bu)002:5038: bya ba dang / nang la rang gi sems nyid
NK075(bu)002:5039: kyi ngo bo la 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon
NK075(bu)002:5040: tan phrin las lnga bsdu bar bya ba'i thabs so
NK075(bu)002:5041: bya ba dang / // mangna spyod drag po la dgra bgegs yul gzhan du bskrad pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:5042: gtan nas mi ldang bar bya ba'i phyir mnan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5043: dran pa nyams nas smyo ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5044: kha nas ca co smra ba 'bogas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5045: lus 'gul mi shes nas byad du bcug pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5046: lus dang yan lag gi sha med nas bskomsa pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5047: dran pa mi dran nas rmongs pa dang gtan nas
NK075(bu)002:5048: gling gzhan du 'phangs nas spo ba dang lus sems
NK075(bu)002:5049: phral nas rgyud gzhan gyi sems can la gzhug pa'o
NK075(bu)002:5050: // de rnams kyi sgo nas rnal 'byor pa rang
NK075(bu)002:5051: gi phyi'i dgra bgegs 'joms par byed la nang du
NK075(bu)002:5052: nyon mongs pa'i dgra bgegsa 'jomsa par byed pa'i thabs
NK075(bu)002:5053: // rnams so // bya thabs la gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:5055: thabs lam gyi bya thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:5057: 'phrin las dngos su bya thabs rgyas par bshad pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:5058: de la thabs lam gyi bya thabs la yang gsang ba dang nang gnyis so //
NK075(bu)002:5059: nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo'i rtsa khamas kyi 'khor lo bzhi dang sbyar nas bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:5060: rtsa 'khor gyi gnas su las bzhi'i gzugs su dod nas yod pa hom khung /
NK075(bu)002:5062: sgrom mdo'i yam las rlung byung /
NK075(bu)002:5063: sum mdo'i ram la phog me sbar ba'i drod kyis /
NK075(bu)002:5064: bsreg rdzas rtsa gnas kyi thig le bzhus nas /
NK075(bu)002:5065: rtsa khams rnams su sbyin pas /
NK075(bu)002:5066: rtog med kyi ye shes skyes pas /
NK075(bu)002:5067: nyon mongs rnam rtog rnams bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5068: gsang ba ltar 'og sgo'i dbang yul yum /
NK075(bu)002:5070: dbang shes kyi khamas gsum la sbyar bar bya nas bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:5071: yum gyi mkha' las bzhi'i gzugs su yod pa hom khung /
NK075(bu)002:5072: yab kyi rdo rje hom gzar /
NK075(bu)002:5073: yab kyi thig le bsreg rdzas de sbyin pas /
NK075(bu)002:5074: bde stong gi ye shes skyes pas /
NK075(bu)002:5075: nyon mongs chags rtog rang kha ma de bsregs nas so //
NK075(bu)002:5076: shes rab grol lam gyi bya thabs so //
NK075(bu)002:5078: lta ba'i don nyams su len thabs kyi las dang /
NK075(bu)002:5080: dang po la phyi nang gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:5083: nang gi las thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5085: shes rab lam gyi sgo nas bya thabs la lta
NK075(bu)002:5086: ba'i rjes su nyams su len thabs la phyi nang
NK075(bu)002:5087: gnyis kyi sgo nas len dgos te nang ltar ting
NK075(bu)002:5088: nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas nyams su blangs lugs gong
NK075(bu)002:5089: du gsal // phyi rol la tshad med pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5091: phyi rol rjes su tshad med nyid bsgom pa la yang las bzhi tshang ste /
NK075(bu)002:5093: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings su 'gugs pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:5094: 'gugs byed chen po badz+ra am gu sha /
NK075(bu)002:5095: rgyas pas byams pas ye shes 'phel ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:5096: 'phel byed chen po badz+ra p+aa sha h+r+aih dga' ba chen po mtha' gnyis dbang du bsdu ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:5097: sdom byed chen po badz+ra s+pho ta bam /
NK075(bu)002:5098: btang snyoms dril bus rdul du brlag pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:5099: rlag byed chen po badz+ra g+han+de ho //
NK075(bu)002:5105: btang snyoms dbang yin par gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5106: mnyam gzhag ngo bo la tshang tshul yin la /
NK075(bu)002:5107: 'di phyi rol tshad med pa rnyed pa las bzhi cha gsungs pas /
NK075(bu)002:5108: rjes shes tshad med bzhi la las bzhi tshang lugs yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:5110: lhag pa gzugs brnyan la gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:5112: spyi dang drang lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:5113: mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:5114: sbyin sreg gi sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs dag ste /
NK075(bu)002:5115: de la mchod rten gyi sgo nas bya thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:5117: las bzhi tsha tsha btab thabs dang //
NK075(bu)002:5118: rgyas pa'i le'u nyi shu pa las kyang /
NK075(bu)002:5120: bgegs kyi ling+ga mnan par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5122: bye brag tu sbyin sreg gi bya ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:5127: mchod rten gong du song nas phyi ma sbyin sreg
NK075(bu)002:5128: gi sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs la don bco
NK075(bu)002:5130: dang po gnas ni zhi rgyas gnyis kyi bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK075(bu)002:5131: dbang drag gnyis gnyen po'i gnas su bya ba'am /
NK075(bu)002:5134: rgyas pa la nags tshal sman ljongs kyi tshal /
NK075(bu)002:5135: dbang chu bo 'dus pa'i sum mdo /
NK075(bu)002:5136: drag po dur khrod chen pa'i gnas su'o //
NK075(bu)002:5137: de nas sgrub pa po'i lta sgom spyod gsum gyi
NK075(bu)002:5138: gdeng dang ldan pa 'phrin las kyi las 'grig la
NK075(bu)002:5139: mkhas pa des / thab brtseg pa la zhi ba la zlum po'am 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK075(bu)002:5140: rgyas pa la gru bzhi'am rin chen zur brgyad /
NK075(bu)002:5141: dbang la zla gam mam pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK075(bu)002:5142: drag po la gru gsum mam brtsigs pa'i khro zhal te thabs brgyad byed pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:5143: yang na zhi ba la dbyibs zlum po /
NK075(bu)002:5144: rgyas pa rgyas pa la gru bzhi /
NK075(bu)002:5147: thams cad kyang khru gang ba /
NK075(bu)002:5148: bang rim gsum gsum yod pa la go rim bzhin /
NK075(bu)002:5149: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dkar po dang /
NK075(bu)002:5150: rin chen zur brgyad ser po dang /
NK075(bu)002:5152: khro zhal rdo rje rgya gram nag po'i lte ba la gnas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5156: dbang pad+ma h+r+aih drag po la rdo rje'i kha t+w+aam la h'u gis mtshan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5157: thabs khung de'i lho nub mtshams su ling+ga'i snod las bzhi rang rang gi dbyibs can gyi brub khung /
NK075(bu)002:5158: tshad mtho gang ba re re bcas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5159: kha lta ba'i phyogs gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:5160: dang po gdul bya dang bstun na /
NK075(bu)002:5161: zhi ba la nub gsum po la des 'gres /
NK075(bu)002:5162: 'dul byed dam ye shes dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)002:5165: sgrub pa po'i chas gos dang /
NK075(bu)002:5166: thab khung gi kha dog ni /
NK075(bu)002:5181: nam gung drag po'i sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5182: phur pa ni zhi ba la ni dngul lam shing dkar po'i phur pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5183: dbal la zlum por byas pa drug /
NK075(bu)002:5184: rgyas pa la gser ram shing ser po'i phur pa /
NK075(bu)002:5185: dbal gru bzhir gnas pa bzhi /
NK075(bu)002:5186: dbang la zangs sam shing dmar po'i phur pa zla gam du byas pa lnga /
NK075(bu)002:5187: drag po la lcags sam shing nag po'i phur pa gru gsum byas pa gsum /
NK075(bu)002:5189: las byed phur pa nyi shu rtsa gcig re dang bcas pa bshom mo //
NK075(bu)002:5191: las sbyor gyi lha ni zhi khro'i gzhung bzhin no //
NK075(bu)002:5193: sbyin lha dang bsreg lha ste /
NK075(bu)002:5194: dang po las bzhi dang gang yin gyi sku mdog phyag mtshan can gyi me lha ste /
NK075(bu)002:5195: zhi ba la me lha dkar po /
NK075(bu)002:5196: phyag g.yas na gun+d+he bsnams pa /
NK075(bu)002:5197: rgyas pa la ser po rin po che sgrom bu /
NK075(bu)002:5198: dbang la dmar po zhags pa /
NK075(bu)002:5199: drag po la mthing nag tri shu la /
NK075(bu)002:5200: kun kyang phyag g.yon pas bgrang 'phreng 'dzin pa /
NK075(bu)002:5201: drang srong gi cha byad can /
NK075(bu)002:5203: bsreg lha ni zhi ba la rnam snang dang /
NK075(bu)002:5204: b+hud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i zhi khro'i lha tshogs kun sku mdog dkar po /
NK075(bu)002:5205: rgyas pa la rin 'byung dang rat+na he ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha kun ser po /
NK075(bu)002:5207: pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha kun dmar po /
NK075(bu)002:5208: drag po la rdo rje sems dpa' dang badz+ra he ru kas /
NK075(bu)002:5209: gtso byas pa'i lha kun mthing gar bskyed do //
NK075(bu)002:5210: semsa la don sems dang stong sems te don gyi
NK075(bu)002:5211: sems bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar
NK075(bu)002:5212: rtogs shing stongs sems la ni zhi ba la zhi
NK075(bu)002:5213: zhing dwangs pa / rgyas pa la spro zhing dga' ba /
NK075(bu)002:5214: dbang la chags shing zhen pa /
NK075(bu)002:5215: drag po la zhe sdang khro bo'i sems kyis bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5216: las bzhi'i yum ni zhi ba la bong chung bzhin lus mdzes /
NK075(bu)002:5217: rgyas pa la bzhin gru bzhi sha rgyas mdog ser /
NK075(bu)002:5219: dbang la bzhin zla gam sha dmar lus mdzes spun zla med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5220: drag po'i bzhin gru gsum sha rtsa nag la rtsub pa ngag gtum pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5222: zhi ba la gtum zhing rngam pa /
NK075(bu)002:5223: rgyas pa la tshe dang bsod nams rgyas su mi ster ba /
NK075(bu)002:5224: dbang la gang dbang du bya bar 'dod pa /
NK075(bu)002:5225: drag po la bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'o //
NK075(bu)002:5226: de dag gang yin gyi dri ma drug gam rkang
NK075(bu)002:5227: rjes kyi sa las byas pa'i ling+ga dpral bar rus
NK075(bu)002:5231: 'doms su las bzhi gang byed kyi sngags spu gri
NK075(bu)002:5232: dang bcas pa bris la las bzhi gang byed kyi
NK075(bu)002:5235: las gang byed kyi bsreg shing /
NK075(bu)002:5239: gzhan yang rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la mchod pa la
NK075(bu)002:5240: sogs pa'i yo byad gang mkho ba rnams tshang bar
NK075(bu)002:5241: sbyar bar bya'o // las kyi rim pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5243: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg lag len du bya thabs la /
NK075(bu)002:5244: las bzhi gang byed kyi lhas gtso bo byas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:5245: zhi khro'i lha tshogs la sbyin sreg gi rim pa
NK075(bu)002:5246: mchod pa dang / bar skabs su las bzhi rang rang gi bsgrub bya de bkug cing bsgral /
NK075(bu)002:5247: dgos pa'i phur pa ling+gar gadba pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5248: 'phrin las kyi mtha' rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir bro
NK075(bu)002:5249: bstabsa dang bcas pa'i cha rkyen rnams dang bcas pa
NK075(bu)002:5250: tshang bar bya ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:5252: zhes tshig gsum pa 'di la sa bcad nor ba 'dra /
NK075(bu)002:5253: gong du bshad pa'i gnas nas bzung ste /
NK075(bu)002:5254: dkyil 'khor yo byad tshang bar bsags pa yan chad 'di /
NK075(bu)002:5255: skabs gar mkho na las bzhi'i bya thabs gtso bo
NK075(bu)002:5256: sbyin sreg skabs su dgos pa'i ling+ga la phur pa
NK075(bu)002:5258: tha ma bro stabs yan chad kyi bar du mkho ba'i cha rkyen yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:5260: las kyi rim pa dngos ni sbyin sreg bya thabs
NK075(bu)002:5261: de dag gi rnam grangs ngos bzung zhing bshad na
NK075(bu)002:5262: dang po zhi khro gang yin gyi rtsa ba'i dkyil
NK075(bu)002:5263: 'khor sngon 'gro yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste
NK075(bu)002:5264: / mchod 'bul bstod pa bsnyen pa yan chad tshang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5265: de nas ta na sgrol ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:5268: tha ma bstab pa la ling+ga la 'gugs gzhug la sogs bsgral las bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5269: de nas ga na sbyor ba ste rnam shes spar chog bya /
NK075(bu)002:5270: de nas me mchod sbyin sreg gi rima pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5273: dang po me bgegs bskrad pa la sogs byas la
NK075(bu)002:5274: me lha ni las bzhi gang byed kyi me lha
NK075(bu)002:5275: dam tshig pa bskyed la dbang bskur /
NK075(bu)002:5277: ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab /
NK075(bu)002:5281: las bzhi gang byed kyi smon lam gdab bo //
NK075(bu)002:5282: bsreg lha ni las bzhi gang byed kyi dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK075(bu)002:5285: ye shes kyi bsreg lha dbab /
NK075(bu)002:5288: dang po mchod rdzas rnams 'bul de nas las bzhi gang byed kyi bsreg rdzas sngags kyis 'bul /
NK075(bu)002:5289: bden pa dang smon lam brjod nas bstod bro bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5290: de nas lhag ma'i las dag bya /
NK075(bu)002:5292: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha bskangs /
NK075(bu)002:5293: bsreg lha dang me lha'i ye shes pa gshegs /
NK075(bu)002:5294: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu /
NK075(bu)002:5297: las kyi rjes mi mngon par byas la /
NK075(bu)002:5298: bkra shis brjod pa yan chad kyis sbyin sreg gi las rdzogs par 'dug go //
NK075(bu)002:5301: sbyin sreg bya ba'i skabs ni dbang bskur ba'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:5302: sa chog la zhi ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5304: rab gnas dus su rgyas pa dbang ngo bo'i dus su dbang ngo //
NK075(bu)002:5305: bsgrub pa'i dus su las sbyor la las bzhi bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5306: mchod pa byed pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:5307: dam tshig nyams chag bshags pa'i tshe la dgos pa
NK075(bu)002:5308: dang las bzhi rang rang gi gdul bya 'dul ba'i
NK075(bu)002:5309: dus la bab pa'i tshe na dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5312: 'phrin las kyi rim pa mtho dman gyi khyad para
NK075(bu)002:5313: ni zag bcas tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'i dus su
NK075(bu)002:5314: dngos su lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan la brten pas rgya
NK075(bu)002:5315: chung / bar chad med pa tshogs bsgrub pa'i dus su ting nge 'dzin la brten pas 'bring la /
NK075(bu)002:5316: mthong lam rig 'dzin thob nas mthar phyin gyi bar
NK075(bu)002:5317: du 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun grub tu rang snang
NK075(bu)002:5318: bas lam gyi sa tshod mtho dman gyis phye ba'am
NK075(bu)002:5319: / blo'i shes rab dbang po rab 'bring tha ma rnam pa gsum gyis phye bas /
NK075(bu)002:5320: las bzhi la nus mthu che chung dang /
NK075(bu)002:5321: byin rlabs kyis yul gdul bya la don 'gyur che
NK075(bu)002:5322: chung dang ngo bo la mos pa dang nus pa'i
NK075(bu)002:5323: khyad par dang / las bzhi bya thabs la rdzas
NK075(bu)002:5324: sngags ting nge 'dzin dgongs mi dgongs dang zhi la
NK075(bu)002:5326: dpe skas ka'i gdang bu ste /
NK075(bu)002:5327: skas kyi them pa ltar mtho dman gyi rim pa ji lta ba lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:5330: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg ma byas na /
NK075(bu)002:5331: dam tshig chag nyams mi bskang sgrib pa mi 'byong tshogs mi rdzogsa pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5332: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis mi 'grub pa rnams 'phrin las ma byas pa de yi skyon yin no //
NK075(bu)002:5335: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg de byas na /
NK075(bu)002:5336: skyon de la zlog pa'i tshula dang ldan pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:5340: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis 'grub pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:5341: yon tan nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5342: rgyas par lung dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:5344: gnas rdzas thab kyi rim pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:5345: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK075(bu)002:5346: phur pa lha dus lam rim dang //
NK075(bu)002:5347: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5349: sbyin sreg bya ba'i gnas bstan par bya /
NK075(bu)002:5351: thabs kyi rnam pa bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5353: gtso bo'i sems bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5358: las kyi rim pa bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5359: lhag ma'i rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5360: dang po gnas bstan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5362: ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse dag dang //
NK075(bu)002:5363: chu klung 'jam pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK075(bu)002:5364: dwang bar byed pa'i las rnams brtsoms //
NK075(bu)002:5366: nags tshal sman ljongs me tog tshal //
NK075(bu)002:5367: lhun sdug ri bo rgyas par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5369: sum mdo chu bo 'dus pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:5370: bzhi mdo khang stong sdud can bya //
NK075(bu)002:5372: dur khrod ngan pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK075(bu)002:5373: lhag par brtsom ste nges par 'grub //
NK075(bu)002:5375: las bzhi'i gnas de dag shin tu gal che bar bstan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5376: rang bzhin nus mthu ldan pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5377: shin tu dgos par bstan pa yin //
NK075(bu)002:5380: gnyis pa rnam pa lngar bshad de //
NK075(bu)002:5381: zhes pas rdzas la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)002:5382: las bzhi gang byed kyi bsreg shing /
NK075(bu)002:5388: me yi rdzas gnyis bsreg shing ni //
NK075(bu)002:5391: shing gcig pa la byed na /
NK075(bu)002:5396: shing tha dad la byed na /
NK075(bu)002:5397: shing dkar ser 'jam po la zhi rgyas gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:5398: dmar nag gi tsher ma can dbang drag gnyis kyi bsreg shing bya ste /
NK075(bu)002:5399: kha dog las kyis sbyar bar bya //
NK075(bu)002:5402: shug pa tsan+dana dkar po dang //
NK075(bu)002:5403: u du m+w+aa ra 'o ma'i shing //
NK075(bu)002:5404: zhi rgyas yam shing shes par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5405: dmar la dri zhim shing rnams dang //
NK075(bu)002:5406: dug shing tsher ma can dag la //
NK075(bu)002:5407: tshil byug dbang drag me sbar ro //
NK075(bu)002:5409: bsgrub bya'i dam rdzas gos sogs dang //
NK075(bu)002:5410: longs spyod de bzhin shes par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5411: dug dang tsha ba sa gsum dang //
NK075(bu)002:5412: sha chen ra dang ban glang sha /
NK075(bu)002:5413: mchog tu gsod bar byed pa yin //
NK075(bu)002:5414: skyur ba dbang ste ling+ga'i rdzas //
NK075(bu)002:5419: me tog dkar po'i gtor ma zhi //
NK075(bu)002:5421: ldong ros gro chan zho rgun phrum //
NK075(bu)002:5422: me tog gser phye rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5424: zangs phye nas ram 'bras chan dmar //
NK075(bu)002:5426: thams cad sdud pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK075(bu)002:5428: dug rnams lcags phye rdo phye dang //
NK075(bu)002:5429: ra khyi'i sha dang sha chen dang //
NK075(bu)002:5430: dur sol dur ka'i chan rnams ni //
NK075(bu)002:5431: gsod par byed pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK075(bu)002:5433: lnga pa bsreg rdzas la yang /
NK075(bu)002:5435: mar dkar til dkar nas dkar chan //
NK075(bu)002:5436: mngar gsum tsan+dana dkar po'i shing //
NK075(bu)002:5437: thams cad ye shes bdud rtsi ste /
NK075(bu)002:5438: tha mas ye shes mi bskyed do //
NK075(bu)002:5440: zho dang mar rnying bu ram sbrang //
NK075(bu)002:5441: rgun 'brum star rga sha chen dang //
NK075(bu)002:5442: dri zhim gser phye rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5444: tan+ti mi dang shang tshe dang //
NK075(bu)002:5445: ske tshe tsha ba'i mar dag dang //
NK075(bu)002:5446: dmar po'i shing dang 'bras dag gis //
NK075(bu)002:5447: thams cad 'gugs pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK075(bu)002:5449: dug dang tshil chen ske tshe'i mar //
NK075(bu)002:5450: sran chen khrag sna tshogs tshad dang //
NK075(bu)002:5451: tsher ma ban glang sha yis gsod //
NK075(bu)002:5452: 'bras bu gdon phyir tshogs par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5454: gsum pa thab kyi rnam pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5455: sa gzhi legs par sbyangs byas nas //
NK075(bu)002:5457: sa gzhi legs par sbyangs par byas nas las bzhi'i thab bya ba la /
NK075(bu)002:5458: dkyil 'khor zlum po rim pa gsum //
NK075(bu)002:5459: khru gang dpangs dang zheng du yin //
NK075(bu)002:5460: zabs dang gyen ni phyed du bshad //
NK075(bu)002:5463: mda' bzhi zhags pa dkar pos dkris //
NK075(bu)002:5464: gzhan yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang //
NK075(bu)002:5465: rig bzhi'i phyag rgya rab shes na //
NK075(bu)002:5466: dang seng mgo spel ma bri //
NK075(bu)002:5467: mu khyud bskor ba'i phyi ru bshad //
NK075(bu)002:5468: thams cad zhi byed dkyil 'khor yin //
NK075(bu)002:5469: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:5471: gru chad la sogs rim rjes mthun //
NK075(bu)002:5472: rdo rje rin chen zhags pas bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5473: dbus su rin chen t+r+aa snying ldan //
NK075(bu)002:5474: gzhan yang rin chen dbyibs gnyis su //
NK075(bu)002:5475: rim pa la sogs rjes su mthun //
NK075(bu)002:5476: zhags pa ser po'am 'dab bzhis bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5478: gsum pa dbang gi thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:5479: hom khung zla gam gdengs pa la //
NK075(bu)002:5481: lcags sgrog gtams pas bsdoms par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5483: gzhan yang 'dab brgyad de bzhin te //
NK075(bu)002:5484: tha ma ljon shing mdzes pas bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5485: 'dab bzhi zhags sdud dbang gi yin //
NK075(bu)002:5486: bzhi pa drag po'i thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:5487: dkyil 'khor gru gsum gdengs pa la //
NK075(bu)002:5488: dur khrod sol bas khyad par sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:5489: rdo rje rtse gsum gdegs pa la //
NK075(bu)002:5490: thod pa lcags kyu gtams pas bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5491: h'u bcas rdo rje snying po ldan //
NK075(bu)002:5492: mda' bzhi zhags pa nag pos bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5493: gzhan yang zhal gdangs spyan bgrad pa'i //
NK075(bu)002:5494: khro zhal shin tu 'jigs pa yis //
NK075(bu)002:5495: me dpung 'bar bas rab mdzes pa //
NK075(bu)002:5496: 'di ni gsod pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK075(bu)002:5500: bong chung lus mdzes zla ba'i mdog /
NK075(bu)002:5501: g.yas 'khyil lus kyang de bzhin shes //
NK075(bu)002:5502: skad gsal sngags bzla yid mi skyo //
NK075(bu)002:5503: khro spangs de bzhin zhi la sbyor //
NK075(bu)002:5505: ban glang ser mo gru bzhi las //
NK075(bu)002:5506: rna ba 'gram slar ring sha rgyas //
NK075(bu)002:5507: yan lag sla mang las la mkhas //
NK075(bu)002:5508: dal zhing blo gros ldan pa ni //
NK075(bu)002:5509: 'phel ba'i dus su shes par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5511: dmar mo zla gam mdzes pa'i zhal //
NK075(bu)002:5512: yal ga rgyud nas rnam spangs pas //
NK075(bu)002:5513: thabs mkhas brtson 'grus ldan pas ni //
NK075(bu)002:5514: thams cad sdud par byed pa'i mchog /
NK075(bu)002:5516: nag mo gru gsum rtsid mgo ma //
NK075(bu)002:5517: khro gnyer can la gel bag chags //
NK075(bu)002:5518: gtum zhing barlanga tshig 'dzem bag med //
NK075(bu)002:5519: sngags zlos brtul zhugs ldan pas ni //
NK075(bu)002:5520: tha ma'i dus su 'di shes bya //
NK075(bu)002:5522: lnga pa gtso bo'i sems ni /
NK075(bu)002:5523: rang rig sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK075(bu)002:5524: thams cad rang dbang bdag bsgyur phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5525: bsgrub pa'i gtso bo 'di gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:5527: don gyi sems chos nyid bden pa dbyer med kyi don khong du chud cing /
NK075(bu)002:5528: byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:5531: ma lus sems ni mtha' bral phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5532: rang bzhin rnam dag mngon du bya //
NK075(bu)002:5534: sems gter rtog tshogs dkyil 'khor phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5535: byin bsdus 'phel ba mngon du bsgom //
NK075(bu)002:5536: dbang la thams cad bdag phyir tha mi dad //
NK075(bu)002:5537: shin tu zhen pa nyid kyis bsgrub //
NK075(bu)002:5538: chags pa chen po nyid du bshad //
NK075(bu)002:5540: rang bzhin gcig phyir dngos med 'jigs //
NK075(bu)002:5541: log rtog khros pa'i sems kyis bskul //
NK075(bu)002:5542: yang dag zhe sdang chen por gsungs //
NK075(bu)002:5546: bdag gzhan gnod pa'i sems dang ni //
NK075(bu)002:5547: sbyor ba ngan pa'i rigs sngags las //
NK075(bu)002:5548: khams rkyen las gyur gnod mang ba //
NK075(bu)002:5549: nyon mongs bag chags sdug bsngal rnams //
NK075(bu)002:5550: thabs phyir gcig kyang dor mi bya //
NK075(bu)002:5552: yon tan 'phel ba mang nyung phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5553: tshe dang longs spyod sgo gsum gyi //
NK075(bu)002:5554: yon tan mngon par mi ldan pa'i //
NK075(bu)002:5556: yon tan bsdus te bstim pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:5557: sems ni rin chen gter gyi phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5560: mos 'dud med pa'i las rkyen can //
NK075(bu)002:5561: las gsum bdag gzhan don gyi phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5562: gsum pa'i las la sbyar bya zhing //
NK075(bu)002:5563: lha yang de bzhin shes par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5565: zhing bcur gyur pa'i sems can dang //
NK075(bu)002:5566: dam pa'i chos 'jig ma rungs byed //
NK075(bu)002:5567: dpa' bos dgos pa yod pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5568: kun la phan phyir de bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5570: bdun pa phur pa la yang /
NK075(bu)002:5572: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)002:5573: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur zlum //
NK075(bu)002:5574: steng 'og logs la khro bcu bsgom //
NK075(bu)002:5576: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs las //
NK075(bu)002:5577: mtha' skor yan lag snying la sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:5579: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)002:5580: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK075(bu)002:5581: lha rnams de bzhin rin chen 'phro //
NK075(bu)002:5582: zur bzhir gnas pa lus gnas bzhir //
NK075(bu)002:5583: gdab pas yon tan 'du bar bshad //
NK075(bu)002:5585: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)002:5586: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK075(bu)002:5587: de bzhin chags pa'i phur bur shes //
NK075(bu)002:5588: zla gam mtha' skor dbang la sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:5589: de dag bsgyur te 'dus par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5591: lcags sam drag po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)002:5592: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK075(bu)002:5593: de bzhin rdo rje phur brlabs pas //
NK075(bu)002:5594: zur gsum lus ngag sems la sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:5596: las byed nyi shu rtsa gcig tu'ang gsungs //
NK075(bu)002:5599: las sbyor gyi lha ni zhi khro'i gzhung gi lha bzhin no //
NK075(bu)002:5601: sbyin dang bsreg pa'i lha gnyis te //
NK075(bu)002:5603: me lha dang bsreg lha gnyis las dang po me lha ni /
NK075(bu)002:5604: las gang yin gyi sku mdog phyag mtshan can yin te /
NK075(bu)002:5605: sangs rgyas rigs kyi sprul pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)002:5606: las thams cad la thogs med 'jug /
NK075(bu)002:5607: sku mdog cha lugs las bzhi bzhin //
NK075(bu)002:5609: rigs kyi phyag rgyas gdab par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5611: ag+ne d+he wa las bzhi'i sngags //
NK075(bu)002:5613: zhal phyir sbyin pa'i lhar bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:5616: gzugs brnyan lha bu'i gzhal yas nas //
NK075(bu)002:5619: rgyan rnams zhi la dkar ba dang //
NK075(bu)002:5621: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK075(bu)002:5622: kun kyang gti mug rdo rje'i tshul //
NK075(bu)002:5624: khams gsum thams cad khyab par sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:5625: sa bon dang rang sngags ldan //
NK075(bu)002:5626: gzhan yang de bzhin shes par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5627: rin chen dga' 'phro ser skya ni //
NK075(bu)002:5629: sngags sogs gzhan ni snga ma'i tshul //
NK075(bu)002:5630: sprul pa'ang rjes su mthun pa ste //
NK075(bu)002:5631: dzahmh'u bam ho ldan par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5632: 'dod chags rdo rje lcags sgrog dang //
NK075(bu)002:5633: mdog ni dmar smug 'od po che //
NK075(bu)002:5634: sngags ni yi ge ra dang h+r+aih phyogs bcur khyab cing h+r+ai la bsdu //
NK075(bu)002:5635: zhe sdang rdo rje gtum chen 'bar //
NK075(bu)002:5636: dud kha nag po'i mdog 'dra ba //
NK075(bu)002:5638: nyi ma thod sbrul gdug pas brgyan //
NK075(bu)002:5639: seng ge glang chen stag rngam dang //
NK075(bu)002:5640: rbod gtong rngam pa'i phyag rgya ldan //
NK075(bu)002:5641: sgra skad drag pos khams gsum dkrug /
NK075(bu)002:5642: bsgrub bya phyag rgya goms pa yis //
NK075(bu)002:5647: dbyar dgun ston dpyid las rim dang //
NK075(bu)002:5650: snga dro gung dgong nam phyed dus //
NK075(bu)002:5651: las rim brtsam par shes par bshad //
NK075(bu)002:5653: bcu pa sbyin sreg gi las rim la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:5656: dang po sngon du bya ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:5660: rdzas dang yo byad ldan byas la //
NK075(bu)002:5661: sa gzhi sbyangs te gzugs brnyan sbyar //
NK075(bu)002:5662: stongs 'gyur mgon la las bcol zhing //
NK075(bu)002:5663: kun kyang tshim byas bsgom par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5664: shing gnyis mchod rdzas legs bkod de //
NK075(bu)002:5665: kha dog me dar legs par bkab //
NK075(bu)002:5666: ling+ga'i gnas ni gzugs brnyan tshul //
NK075(bu)002:5667: ming rus ldan pa phur pas bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5668: gnyis pa sngon 'gro'i cho ga dngos ni /
NK075(bu)002:5669: rdo rje gur gyis phyogs bcing zhing //
NK075(bu)002:5670: nyi ma zla ba las gnyis kyis //
NK075(bu)002:5671: gzhong pa snod kyi rdzas rnams la //
NK075(bu)002:5672: las kyi h'u la 'bru lnga bkod //
NK075(bu)002:5674: mang zhing sna tshogs ror ldan bya //
NK075(bu)002:5676: gnyis pa las rim dngos la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)002:5677: las sbyor gyi phrin las zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5679: sbyin sreg las rim dngos bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5680: dang po las sbyor gyi 'phrin las zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:5681: dkyil 'khor las kyi gzhung bsrang la //
NK075(bu)002:5682: sna tshogs mchod yon rgyas par 'bul //
NK075(bu)002:5683: tshogs kyi 'khor lo legs par brtag /
NK075(bu)002:5684: mchod pa chen po'ang 'bul bar bya //
NK075(bu)002:5686: ye shes dkyil 'khor bskul bar bya //
NK075(bu)002:5687: khams gsum byin rlabs dag bsdus te //
NK075(bu)002:5688: bsgrub bya nye bar sbyar ba dang //
NK075(bu)002:5689: srog dang ldan pa'i bzlas pa ni //
NK075(bu)002:5691: rnam pa gsum gyis bya ba dag /
NK075(bu)002:5692: shin tu stongs 'gyur rgyas par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5694: gnyis pa ling+ga 'gugs gzhug bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:5695: khams gsum gang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK075(bu)002:5697: bdag nyid 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya ste //
NK075(bu)002:5698: mtshan ma bzung nas rang sngags 'don //
NK075(bu)002:5699: rol pa'i pho nya bka' nyan tshogs //
NK075(bu)002:5700: phyag rgya bzhi ldan sgra skad grags //
NK075(bu)002:5701: khams gsum dkrugs te phral byas nas //
NK075(bu)002:5702: bsgrub bya mngon du sbyar bar bya /
NK075(bu)002:5703: tshogs tha ma la ling+ga byas la /
NK075(bu)002:5708: phur bskul byas la phur pas gdab //
NK075(bu)002:5709: mtshon cha'i char dbab gris gtubs la //
NK075(bu)002:5710: bsreg rdzas dang bsres la bzhag go //
NK075(bu)002:5711: gsum pa sbyin sreg las rim la gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:5713: rjes su mthun pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK075(bu)002:5714: sbyin lha so so'i gdan ltar bsgom //
NK075(bu)002:5715: me dpung 'bar ba'i tshogs can du //
NK075(bu)002:5716: me lha ag+ne dzahs bkug la //
NK075(bu)002:5717: phyag rgya bzhi yis nges bkug la //
NK075(bu)002:5718: ram zhes bya bas me sbar nas //
NK075(bu)002:5719: gzar bu rigs kyis mtshan bcas la //
NK075(bu)002:5720: mchod pa bdud rtsi rgyas par 'bul //
NK075(bu)002:5721: gnyis pa bsreg lha'i las kyi rim pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:5722: de dbus 'khor lo gsal brtag ste //
NK075(bu)002:5723: gnyis pa lha rnams spyan drang bstim //
NK075(bu)002:5724: mar dang shing bu chan la sogs //
NK075(bu)002:5726: cig min thams cad bdud rtsi ste //
NK075(bu)002:5727: yang na lan gsum brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK075(bu)002:5729: dug gsum mchod pa de bzhin bya //
NK075(bu)002:5730: dbang med zhal du thim par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)002:5731: ming dang las bzhi'i sngags kyis 'bul //
NK075(bu)002:5734: gzugs brnyan lu gu rgyud bskor la //
NK075(bu)002:5735: e la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK075(bu)002:5736: rjes su mthun pa'i lha bsgoms la //
NK075(bu)002:5737: slas dang byi mo'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK075(bu)002:5738: khams gsum gang bar sbyar bar bya //
NK075(bu)002:5739: srog dang ldan pa'i bro stabs gar //
NK075(bu)002:5740: phyogs bcu ma lus bkug nas ni //
NK075(bu)002:5741: bsgrub bya dbus su log brtag ste //
NK075(bu)002:5742: sa bon 'od zer las gzhan du //
NK075(bu)002:5743: bstims nas bsam pa 'grub par bya //
NK075(bu)002:5744: rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam btab //
NK075(bu)002:5745: ces pas skabs 'dir las bzhi'i bro bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5746: bcu gcig pa lhag ma'i las ni /
NK075(bu)002:5747: bdag nyid 'dul ba'i dbang phyug tu //
NK075(bu)002:5748: las bzhin mnyam gzhag khro bo yin //
NK075(bu)002:5749: 'khor gyi phra men de bzhin shes //
NK075(bu)002:5750: phra men tshogs rnams bskul btul te //
NK075(bu)002:5751: las bzhi'i dkyil 'khor de dag tu //
NK075(bu)002:5752: lhag ma kha chus bkod pa sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:5756: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad bskang //
NK075(bu)002:5758: me lha'i ye shes pa gshegs /
NK075(bu)002:5759: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu /
NK075(bu)002:5760: tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor bsdu la /
NK075(bu)002:5761: las rjes mi mngon par bya zhing /
NK075(bu)002:5762: bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa brjod par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5767: lam gyi yan lag gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ba la /
NK075(bu)002:5768: sa gzhi gshin mo dang 'dra ba de'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:5769: dam tshig bsrung ba rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)002:5770: dam tshig rnam grangs rgyas bsdus kyi bye brag dang /
NK075(bu)002:5771: dam tshig bsrung ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)002:5772: dam tshig bsrung ba'i dus la rim pa yod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:5773: bla med kyi dam tshig la gnas na 'og ma'i
NK075(bu)002:5774: bsrung bya rnams ngo bo nyid kyis rdzogs pas che
NK075(bu)002:5775: ba dang / dam tshig bsrungs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)002:5776: nyams na bskang ba'i thabas dang /
NK075(bu)002:5777: ma bsrungs pa'i skyon dang brgyad dag gis nang du
NK075(bu)002:5778: ngesa par ma nor bar 'og rgyas bshad kyis dmigsa
NK075(bu)002:5779: kyi rnam dbye yongs su shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5785: gsang sngags bla med 'di nyid kyi sgor zhugs pa'i
NK075(bu)002:5786: gang zag thams cad kyi lus ngag yid dang sgo
NK075(bu)002:5787: gsum gyi bla med rang gzhung gi rtsa ba dang
NK075(bu)002:5788: yan lag gi dam tshig bsrung bya'i kun las /
NK075(bu)002:5789: dpe rgyal po'i bka' 'og gi mi rnams kyis rgyal
NK075(bu)002:5790: po'i bka' shog gi rtagsa snang na 'da' mi phod
NK075(bu)002:5791: pa ci lta bar bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:5792: nyams par mi byed cing mi 'bral ba nas bsrung
NK075(bu)002:5793: bya'i tshul la sdom pa de dam tshig gi ngo
NK075(bu)002:5794: bo yin no // rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)002:5796: de la thun mong dang khyad par las /
NK075(bu)002:5797: dang po thun mong spyi'i dam tshig gi rnam grangs ni /
NK075(bu)002:5800: byang sems kyi bslab pa don 'gyur snang na mu stegs dang /
NK075(bu)002:5801: 'gro drug gi spyod pa rnams kyang nyams su blang
NK075(bu)002:5802: tshul gzhung gzhan nas bshad pa'i bsrung bya rnams kyang
NK075(bu)002:5803: 'gro ba sems can 'dren pa'i don du bsrung dgos
NK075(bu)002:5804: pa dang / khyad par gsang sngags rang gzhung gi dam tshig rtsa ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5805: yan lag gi dam tshig de rnams kyi srung thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:5806: blo rab la mdo don bsdus nas bden gsum dbyer med mnyam pa'i ngang du bsrung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:5808: mnyam la mnyam par sbyar ba yi //
NK075(bu)002:5809: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK075(bu)002:5810: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)002:5816: thugs kyi dam tshig rtsa ba la lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:5817: dri chen la sogs pa'i dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:5818: 'dod chags la sogs mi spang ba lnga ste yan lag gi dam tshi ga bcu /
NK075(bu)002:5819: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang bco lngar 'dus par gsungs te /
NK075(bu)002:5821: mi spang mi 'dor lnga nyid la //
NK075(bu)002:5823: 'o na yan lag gi dam tshig la nyi shu rtsa lnga gsungs pa la /
NK075(bu)002:5825: shes par bya ba lnga ni /
NK075(bu)002:5826: lta ba dug lnga ye shes sogs shes thabs yin la /
NK075(bu)002:5827: bsgrub par bya ba lnga ni /
NK075(bu)002:5829: spyad par bya ba lnga ni /
NK075(bu)002:5830: de bsgrub pa'i dus kyi spyod pa yin gsungs /
NK075(bu)002:5831: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga yang /
NK075(bu)002:5832: bla med mi spang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:5833: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)002:5834: bsgrub pa'i dam tshig yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5837: gsang ba gzhan la mi spel ba dang gsum ni /
NK075(bu)002:5838: bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin te /
NK075(bu)002:5840: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK075(bu)002:5842: blo tha ma'i don rgyas pa sum brgya drug cu'i rnam grangs rnams ni /
NK075(bu)002:5843: tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang snying gi rtsa bshad kyi nang
NK075(bu)002:5844: du gsung ba der bsnyad de shes par bya ba
NK075(bu)002:5845: ni / rtsa ba lnga po'i gcig la yang /
NK075(bu)002:5846: shes rab lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:5847: thabs ma 'gags pa spyod pa gnyis su phye ba bcu dang /
NK075(bu)002:5848: de dag spyi ru bzhag nas /
NK075(bu)002:5849: bye brag rtsa ba re re la sum cu ste /
NK075(bu)002:5851: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu la re re la nyi shur dbye bas gnyis brgya ste /
NK075(bu)002:5852: bsdoms pas sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK075(bu)002:5853: 'di dag rnam grangs ngos bzung la /
NK075(bu)002:5858: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra rnams kyi bzhed gzhung mi 'dra ba lnga yod zer ro //
NK075(bu)002:5859: gzhan yang theg chen ma h+aa rang gzhung gi sa
NK075(bu)002:5860: lam gong 'og la bsrung bya'i khyad par yod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:5862: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa la sogs pa
NK075(bu)002:5863: lam rang rang gi skabsa kyi lam gyi ngo bo'i
NK075(bu)002:5864: chos nyid de dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnams bsrung
NK075(bu)002:5865: thabs rnams so // dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)002:5867: dam tshig 'di nyid bsrungs pa de yi dgos ched ni /
NK075(bu)002:5868: khyad par gsang sngags rang gi dam tshig dang /
NK075(bu)002:5869: thun mong spyi'i dam tshig rnams ma bsrungs pa'i skyon
NK075(bu)002:5870: gyi cha yis 'khor ba dang ngan song du 'gro
NK075(bu)002:5872: bsrungs pa'i yon tan gyi cha yis mtho ris byang chub thob pa'i dgos cheda che bas /
NK075(bu)002:5873: de bas na ma bsrungs na nyes che bas de dang /
NK075(bu)002:5874: bsrungs na yon tan che ba de yi dgos ched kyi nges tshig de 'grub pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:5875: gzhan yang khyad par gsang sngags rang gi dam tshig dang /
NK075(bu)002:5876: thun mong spyi'i dam tshig rnams srung ba'i gdul bya
NK075(bu)002:5877: rten gyi gang zag gang yin pa de'i sgrib pa
NK075(bu)002:5881: thun mong dang khyad par gyi dam tshig gi bsrung bya rnams la zag bcas dang /
NK075(bu)002:5882: zag med lam gyis phye ba'i /
NK075(bu)002:5883: nyams su blang ba'i dus la babs ma babs kyi
NK075(bu)002:5884: rima pa yada pa'i phyir de la yang las dang
NK075(bu)002:5885: po'i dus su thun mong gi dam tshig rang don
NK075(bu)002:5886: du bsrungs la / khyad par gyi dam tshig phal cher mos srung byed /
NK075(bu)002:5887: cung zad ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob nas /
NK075(bu)002:5888: thun mong gi dam tshig gzhan don du bsrungs la /
NK075(bu)002:5889: khyad par gyi dam tshig nus srung byed pa yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:5890: de bas na zag bcas zag med kyi sa lam gyi rim pa gang thob pa de yi tshe /
NK075(bu)002:5891: de'i dus kyi mnyam gzhag de la mi 'da' ba'i thabs la dam tshig de dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:5892: de bas sa lam rang rang gi ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:5893: dang mthun pa'i dam tshig bsrung bar byed pa'i thabs
NK075(bu)002:5894: rnams nyams su blang ba'i dus la babas pa yin
NK075(bu)002:5895: no // de ltar sa lam gang thob kyi thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin de dang /
NK075(bu)002:5896: rang gis bsrung bya'i dam tshig mgo 'byor na phan yon la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:5897: sgrib pa byang tshogs rdzogs nas lam nar son pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5904: 'dir bsrung bya mchog ni ma h+aa yo ga'i dam tshig yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:5905: de la bskul nas nyams su len zhing mngon du gyur nas /
NK075(bu)002:5906: 'og ma'i 'dul sdom dam tshig rnams ngo bo nyid kyis rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:5908: rgyud gsang snying la sogs pa'i nang nas smos pa'i
NK075(bu)002:5909: gsang sngags bla med kyi dam tshig rnams bsrung thub
NK075(bu)002:5910: na / nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK075(bu)002:5911: byang sems kyi sdom pa thams cad ngo bo nyid kyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5912: 'o na 'og ma 'dul sdom rnams 'dir dngos su bsrung ngo zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:5917: phyi rgyud kyis bsgyur nas dag par byed la /
NK075(bu)002:5918: 'dir bla med kyis rang bzhin shes nas nyon mongs ma spangs kyang /
NK075(bu)002:5919: nyon mongs de nyid ngo bo dang mi ldan par rang dag pas /
NK075(bu)002:5920: de bas 'og ma'i bsrung bya rnams /
NK075(bu)002:5921: 'di nyid kyi skabs su dngos su bsrung bya /
NK075(bu)002:5922: srung byed med par nyams pa'ang med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5925: ma h+aa 'di nyid kyis lta sgom ma nor ba'i
NK075(bu)002:5926: don la mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig la gnas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:5927: phan yon ni / rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK075(bu)002:5928: dam tshig rnam grangs rnams kyis rjes su zhugs la
NK075(bu)002:5929: spyi rgyud gsang snying 'di nyid la gragas pa ni
NK075(bu)002:5930: phan yon ni / / gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun bzang gi //
NK075(bu)002:5931: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yis //
NK075(bu)002:5932: bsgrub med dam pa ma lus 'grub //
NK075(bu)002:5933: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK075(bu)002:5934: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa de //
NK075(bu)002:5936: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK075(bu)002:5937: sras dang spun dgongs byin brlabs so //
NK075(bu)002:5938: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK075(bu)002:5939: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK075(bu)002:5940: ci bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK075(bu)002:5941: ji snyed sdom pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK075(bu)002:5942: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK075(bu)002:5943: nyams na bskangs pas rdzogs pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:5944: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK075(bu)002:5946: gzhan yang dam tshig bsrungs na ngan song 'khor bar mi ltung ba'i gzung dang /
NK075(bu)002:5947: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i dbye ba'ang bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5948: yon tan yod pa de bas bdag don dang gzhan don gang la yang dam tshig bsrung dgos pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:5949: de bas dam tshig rnam grangs ma lus pa rdzogs
NK075(bu)002:5950: par bya ba'i lug rdzi'i tshul du bsrung bar bya'o
NK075(bu)002:5953: rtsa ba'i dam tshig de dang /
NK075(bu)002:5954: yan lag gi dam tshig de las rtsa ba nas nyams pa zhig pa'am /
NK075(bu)002:5955: sna re nyams nas ral ba byung ba'i tshe /
NK075(bu)002:5956: gang nyams kyi dmigs de shes par byas la /
NK075(bu)002:5957: gso ba'i thabs la rtsa ba lnga ni /
NK075(bu)002:5959: las dang rdzas dang 'dun pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:5960: ting nge 'dzin dang de nyid do //
NK075(bu)002:5962: las kyis bskang ba'i sbyin sreg ste /
NK075(bu)002:5963: rtsa ba nyams na khri tsho lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:5965: yan lag la stong tsho lnga dang brgya tsho gsum blug /
NK075(bu)002:5966: zla nyams la brgya tsho lnga dang bcu tsho gsum blug /
NK075(bu)002:5967: zhar nyams la lnga bcu rtsa gsum blug /
NK075(bu)002:5969: rigs gang nyams dang mthun pa'i nor 'bul ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:5970: de pa'i rigs la rgyal srid 'bul /
NK075(bu)002:5971: rdo rje'i rigs la rang gi lus /
NK075(bu)002:5972: rin chen rigs la rin po che /
NK075(bu)002:5973: pad+ma'i rigs la bu dang chung ma /
NK075(bu)002:5974: las kyi rigs la khal rta dang 'khor g.yog gam
NK075(bu)002:5975: rang la rab tu gces pa de 'bul bar gsung
NK075(bu)002:5978: ting 'dzin gyis bskang ba ra ya kha /
NK075(bu)002:5979: de kho na nyid kyis bskang ba lta ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:5980: yang na slob dpon sgeg rdor ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:5981: 'das pa'i dam tshig lnga las bsdus na /
NK075(bu)002:5985: byang sems la bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis bskangs /
NK075(bu)002:5986: sku la nor dang sbyin sreg /
NK075(bu)002:5987: gsung la sgrub pa chen po gsum /
NK075(bu)002:5989: yan lag gang nyams pa sor bcug la tshogs kyi mchod pas bskangs bar 'dod de /
NK075(bu)002:5990: de ltar gso ba'i thabs gang la yang le lo
NK075(bu)002:5991: med pas brtson 'grus kyi sgo nas mos 'dun dang
NK075(bu)002:5992: bcas pas lcog tshad sbyar bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:5993: desa na nyams chag bskangs ba'i yon tan gyis lam
NK075(bu)002:5994: chud mi za bar nges par tshogs rdzogsa ngan song
NK075(bu)002:5995: 'khor ba la mi ltung nas gzung /
NK075(bu)002:5996: mchog thun mong gi 'bras bu rnams thob pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:5997: nyams pa'i rgyu nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:5999: bsrung ba'i dmigs mi shes pas phyal ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6000: dmigs shes kyang brtson 'grus ma byas na le lo byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6001: sngar dam tshig ma nos kyang mi bsrung nas sdig
NK075(bu)002:6002: pa byas pa'i log pa dang grogs ngan gyi zlas
NK075(bu)002:6003: nyams pa dang / nyams pa can gyi grib 'gos pas zhar la nyams shor ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6004: nyon mongs pa che bas de'i dbang du song nas nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6005: dngos su bdud kyis bslus te de'i dbang du song nas nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6006: rang bzhin gyi gshis ngan pas slob dpon dang mched la nyams chag khur ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6007: brgyad po des dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu byas nas
NK075(bu)002:6008: dka' thub sdom pa'i dam tshig de nyams nas ral
NK075(bu)002:6009: ba dag gis gso ba la mi brtson na dus
NK075(bu)002:6010: 'di nyid la nyams pa che chung gis phyi mar
NK075(bu)002:6011: rnam smin myong ba la yang /
NK075(bu)002:6012: tshe 'dir nyams pa che na phyi mar sdug bsngal
NK075(bu)002:6013: drag la 'dir nyams pa chung na phyi mar sdug
NK075(bu)002:6014: bsngal zhan pa'i stobs kyis thun mong spyi'i dam tshig
NK075(bu)002:6015: nyams pa dang / sgos su rang gis dam tshig
NK075(bu)002:6016: nyams pa'i skyon gyi bdag gzhan gnyis la gnoda de
NK075(bu)002:6017: ngan song du 'gro zhing mchog thun mong gi dngos
NK075(bu)002:6019: 'o na dam tshig dang spyod pa la khyad ci yod ce na /
NK075(bu)002:6020: dam tshig ni da nas bzung sangs rgyas kyi bar du bsrung bya'i dmigs kun tshang dgos /
NK075(bu)002:6021: spyod pa ni lam rang rang gi skabs kyi bsrung bya rnams ma gtogs pa /
NK075(bu)002:6022: gong 'og gang du bsrung mi dgos /
NK075(bu)002:6027: yan lag lnga pa gtso bo 'khor du bkod pa'i
NK075(bu)002:6028: thabs dkyil 'khor la rgyud rgyan pa'i le'u dgu pa
NK075(bu)002:6029: las nang tshan bdun du gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6031: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK075(bu)002:6033: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan /
NK075(bu)002:6034: ces pas de rnams kun gyis sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:6037: dkyil 'khor gyi rnam grangs dang skabs gar dgosa pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6038: dkyil 'khor gyi bya thabs dang dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:6039: dkyil 'khor gyi nges tshig gam sgra don dang /
NK075(bu)002:6040: dkyil 'khor ched du gnyer ba'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)002:6041: mi gnyer ba'i skyon dang dgu yis 'og dkyil 'khor gyis rgyas bshad 'byung ba'i gzhi ru bzhag pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6047: dkyil 'khor rang rang gi gnas skabs bdun du snying po len pa ste dkyil 'khor yin la /
NK075(bu)002:6048: 'khor du bkod pa gang rdzogs pa de dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo yin no //
NK075(bu)002:6049: de la dkyil 'khor bdun gyi ngo bo dmigs ngos bzung na /
NK075(bu)002:6050: dang po rang bzhin dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:6052: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6054: rgyas pa'i don bzhi pa las /
NK075(bu)002:6055: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK075(bu)002:6056: chos dbyings b+ha ga dbyer med pas //
NK075(bu)002:6057: mnyam par sbyor zhing dag pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6059: rang bzhin kun rdzob kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)002:6062: phyi nang snod bcud bdag rnams la //
NK075(bu)002:6063: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ye nas nas //
NK075(bu)002:6065: de'i dkyil 'khor ni rang gi ye shes 'khor ni ye shes bzhir shar ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6066: gnyis pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)002:6070: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK075(bu)002:6072: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK075(bu)002:6073: yon tan 'phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK075(bu)002:6075: de'i dkyil ni mya ngan las 'das pa yin la /
NK075(bu)002:6076: 'khor ni 'jig rten pa'i tshul du snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6077: gnyis pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)002:6078: la las don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'byung ba la bzhed /
NK075(bu)002:6079: la las rtog pa phra rags kyi lha yab yum mtshon pa la bzhed do //
NK075(bu)002:6080: gnyis ka mthun pa'i lung ni /
NK075(bu)002:6082: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK075(bu)002:6083: chen po rags pa thabs su rtogs //
NK075(bu)002:6084: so so'i mtshan nyid shes rab rtogs //
NK075(bu)002:6085: gnyis med 'brel ba thabs chen yin //
NK075(bu)002:6087: de'i dkyil ni rang rig ye shes la /
NK075(bu)002:6089: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)002:6090: las dang bya bas lhag pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6092: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshang thig dang //
NK075(bu)002:6093: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6094: rab gnas 'jug pa'i sbyin sreg dang //
NK075(bu)002:6095: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas shes bya //
NK075(bu)002:6097: de yang dgos ched kyi dbang gis skabs lngar dbye ste /
NK075(bu)002:6098: zhi khro'i lha tshogs mchod cing bsgrub pa mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:6099: dbang bskur ba dbang gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:6100: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:6101: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi 'phrin las bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:6102: sku gsung thugs rab gnas ni /
NK075(bu)002:6103: bsod nams rten gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK075(bu)002:6104: de'i dkyil ni rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs rigs gtso gong phud /
NK075(bu)002:6106: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)002:6108: rgyas pa'i nyi shu pa las /
NK075(bu)002:6110: thams cad dbyings su bsdus nas ni //
NK075(bu)002:6111: nyid kyi thugs la thim byas te //
NK075(bu)002:6112: thams cad chos sku'i phyag rgya che //
NK075(bu)002:6114: dkyil ni rang rig ye shes te //
NK075(bu)002:6115: 'khor ma 'gags pa ye shes bzhir shar ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6116: lnga pa lhag pa ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)002:6117: bsgom pa'i bya bas lhag pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6118: tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi rim gyis bsgom pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6119: de'i dkyil ni rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs /
NK075(bu)002:6120: 'khor rigs bzhi lha dang lha mor bcas pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6121: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la yang /
NK075(bu)002:6122: phyi byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor rtsa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6123: nang byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor thig le /
NK075(bu)002:6124: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor bde ba'i ye shes so //
NK075(bu)002:6125: bdun pa tshom bu tshogs bsgrub kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)002:6127: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor ni rdo
NK075(bu)002:6128: rje sems dpa' la sogs 'khor ni rigs bzhi lha
NK075(bu)002:6129: dang lha mo'o // khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)002:6131: dkyil 'khor bdun gyi dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la yang /
NK075(bu)002:6132: rang bzhin gzhi'i dkyil 'khor de nyid dang /
NK075(bu)002:6133: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:6134: de la gdul bya lugs 'byung dang lugs bzlog gi
NK075(bu)002:6135: snang basa phye ba'i khyad par gyis zhi ba dang
NK075(bu)002:6137: de gnyis la gdul bya rang rang gi mos pas phyes te /
NK075(bu)002:6142: la la 'phrin las la mos pa'i stobs kyis 'khor
NK075(bu)002:6143: la khyad med kyang rigs lnga la gtso bo gang
NK075(bu)002:6144: byed des phye bas zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis po
NK075(bu)002:6145: la yang sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyi
NK075(bu)002:6149: de yang rtsa ba rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de
NK075(bu)002:6150: la yang byed las gnas skabsa kyi sgo nas rnam
NK075(bu)002:6156: rang bzhin gzhi'i dkyil 'khor dang sbyar nas rnam grangs dbye ba'am /
NK075(bu)002:6157: yang na sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyis
NK075(bu)002:6158: gtso bos phye ba'i rnam grangas dang rjes mthun pa
NK075(bu)002:6160: mchod pa la sogs pa'i bzhi po sku gsung thugs
NK075(bu)002:6161: yon tan 'phrin las lnga kun gyi rjes la 'jug
NK075(bu)002:6165: bsgrub pa la lnga ste nyi shu'o //
NK075(bu)002:6166: de zhi khro gnyis kyi dbye ba'i rnam grangs bcu /
NK075(bu)002:6167: bcu po bzhi ste bzhi bcu dang /
NK075(bu)002:6168: yang na rang bzhiin gzhi'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK075(bu)002:6169: rang bzhin gzhi la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lhun grub tu gnas pa'i lnga /
NK075(bu)002:6170: de nyid 'bras bu mthar phyin zhi khro gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:6171: de re re la lnga lnga ste bco lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:6172: de bzhin du mchod pa la lnga /
NK075(bu)002:6175: sgrub pa lnga ste bsdoms na sum cu rtsa lngar gyur pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:6176: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi rnam grangs de'i rjes
NK075(bu)002:6177: su dkyil 'khor drug po'i rnam grangs kyang de ltar
NK075(bu)002:6178: du sbyar nas shes par bya ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6180: 'di la dkyil 'khor bdun ka la sku gsung thugs
NK075(bu)002:6181: yon tan phrin las lnga lnga brtsis pa'i sum cu
NK075(bu)002:6183: dkyil 'khor bdun ka zhi khro gnyis su phye bas bcu bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:6184: de'i steng du mchod pa la lnga /
NK075(bu)002:6187: sgrub pa lnga ste nyi shu /
NK075(bu)002:6188: go nga gi bcu bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:6190: dkyil 'khor dbyer med pa'i ngo bo spyi gzhi dang so lnga /
NK075(bu)002:6193: gong ma ltar mthun par gsung ste /
NK075(bu)002:6194: de yi rjes su drug sbyar ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6197: dus thun mongs du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6202: sgrub pa dang bzhi po'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:6203: dkyil 'khor bsgoms pas bdag gzhan gyis don bsgrubs pa la /
NK075(bu)002:6204: ma bsgoms na mi 'grub pa'i phyir de bas na ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6205: rten dang 'brel ba'i dbang bskur ram rab tu gnas pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:6206: mtshan bcas dang mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa la dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6207: bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)002:6208: 'phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas bdag gzhan gyi
NK075(bu)002:6209: don rdzogsa par byed pa'i dus su dkyil 'khor dgos
NK075(bu)002:6210: pa dang / mchod pa 'bul nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs
NK075(bu)002:6211: te mchog thun mong gi 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i thabs
NK075(bu)002:6214: gang gis dkyil 'khor bdun po'i don rnams blos shin
NK075(bu)002:6215: tu nan tan gyi sgo nas nyams su blang bar
NK075(bu)002:6218: 'dir lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi bya thabs la sa
NK075(bu)002:6219: yi cho ga bya ba'i rim pa nas bzung ste
NK075(bu)002:6223: sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma dgod pa /
NK075(bu)002:6227: 'jug pa'i yon tan dang bcu'i sgo nas nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6228: lhag pa gzugs brnyan de yi cho ga'i byed thabas
NK075(bu)002:6229: ji bzhin pa dag ni rang bzhin gyi dkyiil 'khor
NK075(bu)002:6230: la sogas bdun po lhag ma dag la yang lhag
NK075(bu)002:6231: pa gzugs brnyan gang la bya thabs bcu po yada
NK075(bu)002:6232: pa de dkyil 'khor lhag ma kun la yang bya
NK075(bu)002:6233: thabs bcu po don gyi yod de /
NK075(bu)002:6234: tshul ji ltar du dbye na thabs ma 'gags pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6235: shes rab ma dmigs pa'i byed las kyi cha nas
NK075(bu)002:6236: phye bas des na dkyil 'khor lhag ma rnams kyi
NK075(bu)002:6237: bya thabs de mngon du 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)002:6239: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6240: chos nyid mnyam par rtogs shing de'i ngang la 'jog pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6242: rig pas ci tsam dpogs pa'i tshad tsam du bsgom par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6244: rang rig pa nyid dkyil 'khor du gsal ba las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6246: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mtshon pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6248: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid la sku dang ye shes
NK075(bu)002:6249: kyi dkyil 'khor mnyam pa nyid ma 'dres la yongs
NK075(bu)002:6251: drug pa rnam par dgod pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6252: snang ba sku'i dkyil 'khor grags pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK075(bu)002:6253: dran rtog thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du ma 'gags par dgod pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6255: rgyun bshags ltar bskyed dbab bstims /
NK075(bu)002:6256: mchod pa rim pa rnams bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6258: bde ba chen po'i don rgyud la sbyin zhing rnam rtog rang rgyud pa bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6259: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6260: rgyun bshags kyis gsal btab nas rgyun chad med pa nyams su len pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6261: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK075(bu)002:6262: sngon 'og min du mthar lam pa zhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:6263: de yang rang bzhin gzhi'i dus su gong gi bcu po gnas la /
NK075(bu)002:6264: de nyid 'bras bu mthar phyin dus su mngon du gyur la /
NK075(bu)002:6265: ting nge 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor de nyid cig char bsgom la /
NK075(bu)002:6266: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rim gyis sgom la /
NK075(bu)002:6267: gzugs brnyan gyis rtog tshogs ye shes su gnas pa'i ngos nas tshang la /
NK075(bu)002:6268: tshom bu tshogs kyi sa ni de'i don bsgrub pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6269: byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor la bcu ste /
NK075(bu)002:6270: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6271: rig ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6273: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK075(bu)002:6276: yum gyi mkha' sor bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:6277: de nyid las sor bzhi'i tshad du rang bzhin gnas /
NK075(bu)002:6280: bde ba'i ye shes mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:6282: bde ba'i ye shes thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK075(bu)002:6285: yum gyi pad+mo kha dog dmar po /
NK075(bu)002:6287: e wam ma ya bzhi'i tshul du gnas pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6289: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6292: rdo rje dang sna rtse la sku gsung thugs kyi gzugs dgod pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6294: rdo rje mdzub mo rtse dag tu //
NK075(bu)002:6295: til 'bru nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK075(bu)002:6296: ri rab tsam gyi phyag rgya dgod //
NK075(bu)002:6299: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byed pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6301: thabs kyi cho ga rab gnas dang //
NK075(bu)002:6310: gsang ba'i sbyin sreg lugs su 'bul //
NK075(bu)002:6313: 'jug pa pos kyang gsol bas gdab //
NK075(bu)002:6315: yon tan ni gong dang mthun no //
NK075(bu)002:6318: dkyil 'khor bdun gyi skabs su gtso bo snying po gang dang gang ldan pa la /
NK075(bu)002:6319: dkyil 'khor de yi 'khor gang yin dang ldana na /
NK075(bu)002:6320: dkyil 'khor ces bya ba'i nges pa'i tshig gam sgra don yin te /
NK075(bu)002:6321: rgyas pa'i le'u gsum pa'i rgyud las gragsa pas the tshom med pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:6322: de yang rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:6324: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)002:6325: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa dkyil //
NK075(bu)002:6328: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)002:6329: 'dus pa rtag tu dkyil yin te //
NK075(bu)002:6332: lhag pa gzugs brnyan lhag pa ting 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)002:6333: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)002:6334: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil yin te //
NK075(bu)002:6335: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK075(bu)002:6337: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gsum gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)002:6338: snying po thams cad dus su dkyil //
NK075(bu)002:6339: gang yang yan lag 'khor du gsungs //
NK075(bu)002:6340: bco brgyad khams su snying po nyid //
NK075(bu)002:6341: de dag 'khor de bde ba'i khams //
NK075(bu)002:6342: byang sems bde ba'i ye shes te //
NK075(bu)002:6343: rten can ci bzhin rten ci bzhin //
NK075(bu)002:6345: de ltar gtso 'khor du tha dad pa'i dus na /
NK075(bu)002:6346: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos pa du ma'i mtha' dang bral /
NK075(bu)002:6347: ma g.yos bzhin du gtso 'khor gyi tshul du gsal bas gciga gi mtha' dang bral basa /
NK075(bu)002:6348: phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa'i bcing ba dang bral ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6351: dkyil 'khor gyi don nyams su blangs pas /
NK075(bu)002:6354: gnas skabs dang mthar thug la phan pa'i yon tan gyi 'bras bu thams cad thob /
NK075(bu)002:6355: las gang bsam pa 'grub pa'i yon tan dang bzhi
NK075(bu)002:6356: po de bye brag tu dkyil 'khor bdun po so
NK075(bu)002:6357: so'i rnam grangsa bzhin du yon tan bzhi po gang
NK075(bu)002:6361: dkyil 'khor nyams su ma blangs na //
NK075(bu)002:6362: gong gi yon tan bzhi po de las bzlog pa'i
NK075(bu)002:6363: skyon gyi cha ni yon tan gyi rnam grangs kyi
NK075(bu)002:6367: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu mi thob /
NK075(bu)002:6373: yan lag drug pa mnyes par byed pa mchod pa'i sdom tshig ni /
NK075(bu)002:6376: mchod pa'i ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6377: mchod pa la rnam grangs du yod bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6378: skabsa gar mkho ba'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:6380: 'bul ba'i yon tan la sogs pas /
NK075(bu)002:6381: spyi don drug pa'i nang du /
NK075(bu)002:6383: ci lta ba bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6390: bdag gzhan gnyis kyi sgrib pa dag /
NK075(bu)002:6393: dam tshig nyams pa bskang ba'i yon tan tshe 'di la thun mong dang /
NK075(bu)002:6394: phyi mar mchog gi dngos grub thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6395: gzhan yang mchod pa 'bul ba'i yon tan ni sangs
NK075(bu)002:6396: rgyas kyi bka' mdo rgyud rnams nas gsungsa pa dang
NK075(bu)002:6397: / gzhan yang nyams pa mi bskang na yang dam
NK075(bu)002:6398: tshig nyams pa'i chad pa'i skyon mi 'byung ba bya
NK075(bu)002:6399: / ba'i phyir / dang la mchod pa brtson dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6402: mchod pa 'bul bya'i yul de la /
NK075(bu)002:6403: 'bul byed kyi mkhan po des 'bul bar bya ba'i
NK075(bu)002:6404: rgyu de phul bar byed pa dang gsum du 'dus
NK075(bu)002:6405: pa'i dus na / mchod bya'i zhing de la dga'
NK075(bu)002:6406: nas dgyes te yid tshimsa par 'gyur ba ni mchod
NK075(bu)002:6407: pa'i dngos po'i ngo bo nyid ngos bzung ba de
NK075(bu)002:6408: pa'i dus na / yin no // rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6410: dpe 'jig rten 'di na rgyal po la 'bangs kyis gus pa'i sgo nas /
NK075(bu)002:6411: zhabs thog gis mnyes par bya ba'i spyod pa de dang cha mthun par /
NK075(bu)002:6412: sangs rgyas la mnyes bya mnyes byed med kyang /
NK075(bu)002:6413: gdul bya lam la mos pa'i gang zag de drang
NK075(bu)002:6414: bar bya ba'i phyir zhi khro'i lha tshogs gang yin
NK075(bu)002:6415: la / gus pas phyag gi mchod pa dang /
