NK075(bu)002:6416: phyag rgya gar gyi glu ye shes /
NK075(bu)002:6419: tshig su ra to bcu drug ste lha mo bcu drug gi mchod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6424: lha mo bzhi bsnol la sogs 'dod yon rnams dang /
NK075(bu)002:6425: nang mchod sman rag gtor gsum dang /
NK075(bu)002:6428: zhe sdang sgrol ba'i mchod pa /
NK075(bu)002:6431: yang na mchod pa thams cad phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod par 'dus te /
NK075(bu)002:6432: phyi 'dod yon rdzas kyi mchod pa ni dngos su bshams pa /
NK075(bu)002:6433: nang dgongas pa ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa /
NK075(bu)002:6434: gsang ba dam rdzas rang gnas kyi mchod pa de rnams 'bul ba'i tshe /
NK075(bu)002:6435: srog ting nge 'dzin dang ldan dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:6436: de la mchod pa'i dngos po ci ltar snang yang /
NK075(bu)002:6437: ngo bo sems kyi chos nyid spros bral las ma g.yos pa /
NK075(bu)002:6438: ma g.yos bzhin du mchod pa'i dngos po rnams ma 'dres par shar /
NK075(bu)002:6439: shar ba'i dus su chu dang chu'i rlabs bzhin du dbyer med pas /
NK075(bu)002:6440: bden pa gsum dbyer med kyi tshul du bsgom mo //
NK075(bu)002:6441: ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsis ma zin na 'jig rten rang kha ma'i mchod pa dang khyad med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6442: skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6444: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa la gsum lasa spros
NK075(bu)002:6445: pa'i mchod pa rnam grangs gong du bshad pa de
NK075(bu)002:6446: dag / rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la sogs dkyil
NK075(bu)002:6447: 'khor bdun gyi gnas dag la 'bul dgos pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)002:6448: dag / dang / gzhan yang dgos ched kyi rjes
NK075(bu)002:6449: su zhugs pas sgrib pa dag par byed pa'i dus
NK075(bu)002:6450: dag / dang / dang / tshogs rdzogs par lha
NK075(bu)002:6451: mnyes par nyams chag skong bar byed pa'i dus rnams
NK075(bu)002:6453: khyad par du phrin las rnam bzhi la spyod pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:6454: bsgrub pa byed pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:6456: mchod pa rang 'bul ba'i tshe na dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6460: skabs gang la mkho ba'i dus kyi rjes su zhugs pa'i yon tan dag yin te /
NK075(bu)002:6461: de la spyi dang khyad par gyi dus kyi sgo nas dmigs ngos su bzung na /
NK075(bu)002:6462: spyi ni dgos ched bshad pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:6463: mchod pa 'bul bas sgrib pa dag /
NK075(bu)002:6467: khyad par du mchod pa 'bul bas las bzhi gang brtsams 'grub /
NK075(bu)002:6468: thun mong dang mchog gi sgrub pa 'grub /
NK075(bu)002:6469: dbang bskur ba la slob bu smin /
NK075(bu)002:6471: lha mnyes pa la chud mi za bas tshe 'di thun mong thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6472: phyi mar mchog gi 'bras bu ni /
NK075(bu)002:6473: gong gi spyi dang khyad par gang yin gyi rang rang gi mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK075(bu)002:6480: mthar thug sangs rgyas thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6481: khyad par du 'phrin las kyis mthar thug gi 'bras bu gzung 'dzin zhi /
NK075(bu)002:6485: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu la gnas skabs thun mong mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas /
NK075(bu)002:6486: dbang gi 'bras bu mthar thug gi 'bras bu la /
NK075(bu)002:6487: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur /
NK075(bu)002:6488: mchod pa'i mnyes pas don gyi 'bras bu la reg pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6491: gzhan don gyi yon tan dang gnyis su 'gyur ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6495: yon tan de las bzlog tu 'gro ste /
NK075(bu)002:6496: dam tshig chag nyams mi skong /
NK075(bu)002:6497: ye shes kyi lha dang dam can srung ma rnams g.yel dam tshig nyams pa'i chad pa 'byung /
NK075(bu)002:6498: khyad par du 'phrin las dang sgrub pa dang dbang gi dus su mchod pa ma phul na /
NK075(bu)002:6499: 'phrin las la sogs pa'i gang byed la mthu byin rlabs dang bral bar 'gyur te med pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6504: bdun pa sngar ma thob pa thob par bya ba'i thabs dbang gi sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:6505: dbang bskur ba'i dgosa ched dang /
NK075(bu)002:6507: dbang rang gi ngo bo ngos bzung ba /
NK075(bu)002:6508: dbang gi rnam grangs du yod /
NK075(bu)002:6512: dbang bskur ba'i snod kyi rim pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6513: dbang thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)002:6514: ma thob pa'i skyon dang bcu'i nang du /
NK075(bu)002:6515: dbang gi las rim de nyid dkyila 'khora las rim
NK075(bu)002:6516: dang sbyar nas rgyas par bshad pa de rdzogs pa
NK075(bu)002:6522: bdag don gzhan don gnyis don chos don du 'gyur
NK075(bu)002:6523: ba dang bzhi lasa khyad par du bdag don du
NK075(bu)002:6524: yang lam du 'jug pa'i sngon du dbang thob dgos
NK075(bu)002:6525: pas gzhan don du slob bu lam du 'jug nus
NK075(bu)002:6526: par byed pa la dbang bskur dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6527: dbang thob pas tshogs sgrub la sogs 'grub pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6528: kyang gi sgras dbang thob nas phrin las gang byed 'grub pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6529: gzhan yang dbang thob pas sgrib pa byang ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6530: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyis dngos su chub par byed
NK075(bu)002:6531: dgos pa la tshe gcig gi nang du myur bar
NK075(bu)002:6532: 'grub thub pas / de bas na dbang de la
NK075(bu)002:6533: yon tan de yod pa'i phyir dbang de nyid nod
NK075(bu)002:6534: par bya ste bskur bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6537: lung rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu pa dang bshad rgyud bla ma la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6538: man ngag las rim pa sogs pa rnams kyi nang
NK075(bu)002:6539: nas byung ba'i rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi'i sgo nas phyi
NK075(bu)002:6542: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum gyis yan lag rgyas par bsnyad de bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:6543: dang po phan dbang gi rgyu gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)002:6547: rnam shes tshogs lnga ye shes lnga ni dbu rgyan
NK075(bu)002:6548: gyi dbang gi mtshungs rgyu ro rkyang cod pan gyi
NK075(bu)002:6549: mtshungs rgyu / dbu mar thig le sum cu so gnyis phreng ba /
NK075(bu)002:6550: lus la rtsa'i dra bas khyab pa go cha'o //
NK075(bu)002:6551: pho mo'i dbang po rgyal mtshan gyi /
NK075(bu)002:6552: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag rgya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6553: klad pa bde chen 'khor lo gdugs kyi rtsa gnas
NK075(bu)002:6554: thig les gang ba bum pa'i rtse la drod 'bab
NK075(bu)002:6556: khams lnga'i dam rdzas lnga ni snying po lnga'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu yin no //
NK075(bu)002:6557: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)002:6558: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:6559: de yang dbu rgyan la rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rab gnas bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6561: cod pan la rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK075(bu)002:6565: phyag rgya lha rang rang gi /
NK075(bu)002:6569: snying po lnga rang rang gi rigs kyis rab tu gnas pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:6570: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi las /
NK075(bu)002:6571: phan dbang bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6572: bskur nus pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6573: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6574: dbang snga mas phyi ma go phye ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK075(bu)002:6575: nus pa'i dbang lnga'i mtshungs rgyu ni slob bu'i rna
NK075(bu)002:6576: ba gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa na sgra nyan pa'i rig
NK075(bu)002:6577: shes kyi thig le gnas pa nyan dbang gi mtshungs
NK075(bu)002:6578: rgyu / de bzhin du snying gi rig shes kyi thig le sgom dbang gi mtshungs rgyu /
NK075(bu)002:6579: lag pa'i 'dom rtsa na skyod byed thig le phrin las kyi /
NK075(bu)002:6580: lce'i smra byed kyi thig le 'chad dbang gi /
NK075(bu)002:6581: yan lag lnga'i thig le lnga ni rdo rje rgyal
NK075(bu)002:6582: po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi
NK075(bu)002:6583: rgyu'o // lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6584: ka pa li glegs bam can rin 'byung gi rab gnas nyan dbang /
NK075(bu)002:6585: phreng ba yi dam gyi lha gang yin gyi rab gnas sgom dbang /
NK075(bu)002:6586: rgya gram don yod grub kyis rab gnas can 'phrin las /
NK075(bu)002:6587: dung dang phyag shing 'khor lo gsum snang mtha'i rab gnas can 'chad pa'i /
NK075(bu)002:6588: rdo rje dril bu kun bzang yab yum kyi rab
NK075(bu)002:6589: gnas can ni rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams
NK075(bu)002:6590: kyi dbang gi lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)002:6592: nus dbang bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6593: gsum po gong phan dbang dang gcig /
NK075(bu)002:6594: zab mo'i dbang gsum gyi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)002:6595: don dam dkor bdun rang chas su yod pa gsang dbang /
NK075(bu)002:6596: kun rdzob tu sku dang ye shes rang chas su yod pa shes rab ye shes /
NK075(bu)002:6597: bden gnyis dbyer med rang chas su yod pa bde ba chen po'i mtshungs rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)002:6599: phyag rgya mtshan ldan lo nyi shu ma gsang dbang /
NK075(bu)002:6601: bcu gnyis ma dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang gi lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu yin no //
NK075(bu)002:6603: zab dbang gsum bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6604: dbang bskur nus pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6605: phyag rgya mtshan dang ldan pa dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)002:6606: dbang snga mas go phye nas phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK075(bu)002:6609: rgyu rkyen drug gi sgo nas rang la gnas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:6610: dbang don dngos su thob par bya ba la grangs
NK075(bu)002:6612: dbang gi ngo bo nyid de yin ces lung las rnam par bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:6615: zhi ba'i dbang gi rnam grangs la /
NK075(bu)002:6618: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum dang rtsa ba rnam pa lnga la yan lag bco brgyad de /
NK075(bu)002:6619: phan dbang bcu nus dbang lnga dang bco lnga /
NK075(bu)002:6620: zab mo'i dbang gsum dang bco brgyad /
NK075(bu)002:6621: bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gi dbang la /
NK075(bu)002:6627: rtsa ba lnga las gyes pa'i yan lag sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK075(bu)002:6629: phyi dbang zhes par grags pa ni //
NK075(bu)002:6630: phan pa'i dbang bcu nus dbang lnga //
NK075(bu)002:6631: rgyan cha rol po'i dbang brgyad dang //
NK075(bu)002:6632: sgrub pa brgyad dang dam rdzas lnga //
NK075(bu)002:6633: ming gi dbang dang sum cu bdun //
NK075(bu)002:6634: rim pa bzhin du bskur bar bya //
NK075(bu)002:6636: ming dbang kun gyi mgo ru phyung //
NK075(bu)002:6637: zhes pa'i ming dbang mi brtsi na sum cu rtsa drug tu dabye'o //
NK075(bu)002:6643: gsang dbang la dbye ba med /
NK075(bu)002:6644: shes rab ye shes dang bde ba chen po gnyis dang sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK075(bu)002:6645: rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo'i le'u bcu bdun pa nas gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6646: rnam grangs go rim mtshan nyid ni //
NK075(bu)002:6647: dang po phyi yi dbang bcu bskur //
NK075(bu)002:6648: de nas nang dbang bcu gcig dang //
NK075(bu)002:6649: de nas sgrub pa'i bcu dang gsum //
NK075(bu)002:6650: tha mar gsang ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK075(bu)002:6651: bcu phrag gsum dang drug dag gis //
NK075(bu)002:6652: dbang mchog dam pa bskur ba yin //
NK075(bu)002:6653: dang po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6654: gnyis pa rtags kyi mtshan ma'i dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6655: gsum pa shes rab gzugs kyi dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6656: bzhi pa bkra shis bum pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6657: lnga pa bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6658: drug pa rin chen sna bdun dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6659: bdun pa gdan mchog dam pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6660: brgyad pa mdzes pa rgyan gyi dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6661: dgu pa gsang ba ming gi dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6662: bcu pa rgyal rtags 'khor lo ste //
NK075(bu)002:6663: phyi dbang bcu po rdzogs pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6664: rdo rje nang du gzhug bya ba //
NK075(bu)002:6665: dang po gsang ba nyan cing slob pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6666: gnyis pa glegs bam zab mo gtad par bya //
NK075(bu)002:6667: gsum pa rnam bzhi las kyi rdzas kyang sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6668: bzhi pa rgyal tshab dam pa'i mdzod gsum sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6669: lnga pa slob dpon theg chen dgu yi rtags //
NK075(bu)002:6670: drug pa pad+ma nyi zla sems can sems can gdan //
NK075(bu)002:6671: bdun pa rgyal po gsang ba rin chen bdun //
NK075(bu)002:6672: brgyad pa gzugs brnyan spyi bor bzhag /
NK075(bu)002:6673: dgu pa sku gzugs ye shes sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6674: bcu pa bkra shis dam rdzas dbang //
NK075(bu)002:6675: de gsal lag tu rdo rje sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6676: bcu dang bcu gcig nang sbyin nas //
NK075(bu)002:6677: bsgrub pa'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6678: dang po sems kyi gtan tshigs sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6679: gnyis pa snying rje'i dbang bskur sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6680: gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6681: bzhi pa thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6682: b+han+d+ha gang ba sbyin dang lnga //
NK075(bu)002:6683: drug pa mtshon cha sna tshogs te //
NK075(bu)002:6684: bdun pa skyon med pad+ma sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6685: brgyad pa sti ra dbyug pa sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6686: dgu pa sbrul nag chun po sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6687: bcu pa dri med lha mo sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6688: gcig pa 'dod pa'i longs spyod sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6689: gnyis pa bsgrub rdzas thams cad sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6690: gsum pa rdo rje gsang ming sbyin //
NK075(bu)002:6691: bcu dang gsum dang rdzogs pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6692: gsang ba dam pa sbyin pa yang //
NK075(bu)002:6693: dkar dmar 'dres pa'i byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)002:6694: bu mchog de yi lce la bzhag /
NK075(bu)002:6695: snying po don dam byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)002:6696: de yi blo la bzhag par bya //
NK075(bu)002:6698: 'di ni lung ltar phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo /
NK075(bu)002:6700: bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo /
NK075(bu)002:6701: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo ste /
NK075(bu)002:6703: dbang gi chu bo bzhis gtan la phab pa ltar yin la /
NK075(bu)002:6705: khrag 'thung rtsa rgyud ltar yin par gsungs /
NK075(bu)002:6708: de yang dang po dkyil 'khor rdo rje las kyi rim pa'i rjes su zhugs pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6709: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK075(bu)002:6710: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6711: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6712: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas zhes bya //
NK075(bu)002:6713: zhes pas gzhung bzhin du nyams su blangs la /
NK075(bu)002:6714: de nas dad brtson brtul zhugs kyi snod dang /
NK075(bu)002:6715: phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang rim pa ltar sbyar nas bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK075(bu)002:6716: dbang rdo rje las rim gyi gzhung ltar rgyu rkyen 'bras bu ngo bo dang //
NK075(bu)002:6719: zhes pa ltar du dbang rdzogs par bskur bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6721: dpe lcags rkang bzang po la gri la sogs rnon
NK075(bu)002:6722: po gang byas la til mar bskus nas ngar blud
NK075(bu)002:6723: na / de ltar du rno ba rim bzhin shes
NK075(bu)002:6724: bya'i nus mthu gazhana la de ltar du mi smin
NK075(bu)002:6725: na / la / dbang ni snod bcud rgyu rkyen gnyis 'dzom na /
NK075(bu)002:6726: bskur ma thag tu nges par nus mthu dang ldan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6730: gsang sngags kyi lam gyi rgyud du 'jug pa la sngon du dbang thob dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:6731: de yang shes rab grol lam la rgyud ma smin pa smin par byed dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:6732: sngon du dbang 'gro ba yin la /
NK075(bu)002:6733: thabs lam la dbang thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6734: zab mo'i dbang gsum de nyid kyi don la rim par bslab dgos la /
NK075(bu)002:6736: grol lam gnyis ka la lam dang sa yi rim pa mtho dman gyis phye bas /
NK075(bu)002:6743: slob ma la las dang po pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6745: phyir mi ldog pa'i gang zag gsum gyis /
NK075(bu)002:6746: rig ma las kyi phyag rgya mo dang /
NK075(bu)002:6747: rig pa'i phyag rgya mo dang /
NK075(bu)002:6748: ye shes kyi phyag rgya mo dang gsum la rim par rol pa dbang gsum thob dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:6749: de yang rgyu dus kyi dbang ni /
NK075(bu)002:6750: slob dpon drod thob pa des /
NK075(bu)002:6751: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas /
NK075(bu)002:6752: slob ma las dang po pa de la /
NK075(bu)002:6753: rig ma las kyi phyag rgya mtshan nyid dang ldan pa de la sbyor nas /
NK075(bu)002:6754: bde stong gi nges shes skye bas /
NK075(bu)002:6755: gsang sngags bla med la 'jug nus pa'i tshig gis dbang thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6756: lam dus kyi dbang ni slob dpon sgom lam dang mthar lam pas /
NK075(bu)002:6757: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas /
NK075(bu)002:6758: slob ma sbyor lam drod rnyed pa'i gang zag de la rig ma rig pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6759: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya mo la rol cing sbyor bas /
NK075(bu)002:6760: rjes shes dngos 'dzin gyi dri ma dag nas /
NK075(bu)002:6761: zag med mthong lam che rnams gnyis kyi dgongs pa la mngon du gyur pas don dbang thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6763: slob dpon phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK075(bu)002:6764: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas su /
NK075(bu)002:6765: slob ma phyir mi ldog pa'i mthar lam pa de la /
NK075(bu)002:6766: rig ma ye shes kyi phyag rgya mo la rol cing sbyor bas /
NK075(bu)002:6767: shes bya bag la nyal gyi dri ma dag nas
NK075(bu)002:6768: dbyings ye shes kyi mtha' gru ma lus pa rgyas
NK075(bu)002:6769: pas / sangs rgyas pa de ni dbang gi ngo bo thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:6772: de yang rgyud gsang snying nyid las /
NK075(bu)002:6773: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab brtan nas /
NK075(bu)002:6778: gnyis don nus pa gsum dang /
NK075(bu)002:6782: mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs nus pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6783: gsum po de rnams gdul bya gang la yod pa de /
NK075(bu)002:6784: phyi nang gsang ba de yi snod du gyur pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:6785: de la dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu bskur la /
NK075(bu)002:6786: brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga ste /
NK075(bu)002:6788: bdag don du brtson 'grus nus na /
NK075(bu)002:6791: gzhan don du brtson 'grus nus na 'chad dbang dang 'phrin las dbang gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:6792: gnyis ka'i don du brtson 'grus nus na /
NK075(bu)002:6793: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6794: brtul zhugs can la gsang ba zab dbang ste /
NK075(bu)002:6796: bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa yab yum gyi byang sems la spyod nus na //
NK075(bu)002:6799: yum la sbyor ba'i dus su bde stong de nyid rig pas nyams su myong nus na /
NK075(bu)002:6801: de la shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur /
NK075(bu)002:6802: bde stong gi ye shes kyi ngos nas thams cad mnyam par rtogs nus na /
NK075(bu)002:6804: de la bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:6807: dbang bskur thob pa la tshe 'di dang phyi ma
NK075(bu)002:6808: phan yon gyi rnam grangs ni rgyud gsang snying nas
NK075(bu)002:6809: gsungs pa ji bzhin yin te /
NK075(bu)002:6810: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK075(bu)002:6811: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6812: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK075(bu)002:6813: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK075(bu)002:6815: dbang thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad //
NK075(bu)002:6816: rgyal ba'i gdung 'di 'dzin pa'i sras yin pas //
NK075(bu)002:6817: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal kun med pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6818: skye ba 'dir yang tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6819: skye ba phyi mar yang phan dbang gi 'bras bu mtho ris kyi nang nas kyang /
NK075(bu)002:6821: nus dbang gi 'bras bu thar pa'i lam ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK075(bu)002:6822: zab dbang gi 'bras bu rigs thams cad kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)002:6825: dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK075(bu)002:6826: yon tan de las bzlog pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:6827: dbang ma thob par rang byan gyis brtag dpyad byas kyang chos nyid mi rtogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6828: yang na nyan dbang ma thob par /
NK075(bu)002:6829: nyan pa la sogs byas kyang /
NK075(bu)002:6830: gsang sngags mnyan pa'i dbang gis rang bzhin gyis ltung zhing 'jigs pas /
NK075(bu)002:6831: gzhan yang phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang ma thob par /
NK075(bu)002:6836: thig dbang la sogs pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi byed las la 'bras bu med cing /
NK075(bu)002:6837: gsang ba'i snying po gzhung nas bshad pa'i dam tshig de dag nyams pas ngan song du ltung zhing /
NK075(bu)002:6838: sdug bsngal gyis 'jigsa pa chen po 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)002:6839: dpe rdza so ma btang ba'i rdzas kyi nang du
NK075(bu)002:6840: chu blugs nas spyod tsam na zhig pa ltar du
NK075(bu)002:6841: 'gyur ba ni gsang ba'i snying po rtsa rgyud bshad
NK075(bu)002:6842: rgyud kun la ltos dang der gsal lo //
NK075(bu)002:6847: yan lag brgyad pa rnal 'byor pas lam don du
NK075(bu)002:6848: gnyer ba des 'bras bu thob par bya ba yi
NK075(bu)002:6850: de yang thun mong dang mchog gi phye bas bsgrub
NK075(bu)002:6851: pa la gnyis sogsa kyi sgras thun mong mchog gnyis
NK075(bu)002:6852: la yang bsgrub thabs mi 'dra ba'i yan lag mang
NK075(bu)002:6853: du yod kyang / de rnams kyi don mdor bsdus nas sdoms pa'i tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:6855: sgrub pa rang gi ngo bo dngos po //
NK075(bu)002:6860: bsgrubs pa'i yon tan dang rnam grangsa bdun gyi sgo nas 'og rgyas bshad de shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6866: thun mong gi sgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6867: mchog gi dngos grub kyi sgrub pa'i thabs mi 'dra
NK075(bu)002:6868: ba'i bye brag rnams bdag don dang gzhan don du
NK075(bu)002:6869: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob pa'i thabs la
NK075(bu)002:6871: don gnyis lhun gyis grub nas thob pa'i thabs la bsgrub dgos la /
NK075(bu)002:6872: chos don du 'gyur ba'i thabs la bsgrub pa mi dgos pas /
NK075(bu)002:6873: de bas na don 'gyur bzhi yod pa'i phyir na sgrub pa la brtson 'grus bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:6876: rnal 'byor pa gang gis mchog thun mong gi 'bras
NK075(bu)002:6877: bu gang thob par 'dod pa'i don de bsgrub pa'i
NK075(bu)002:6879: lam gyi yan lag cha rkyen bcu dang ldan pa de /
NK075(bu)002:6880: don du gnyer bdo ba ni sgrub pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK075(bu)002:6883: rnam grangs la thun mong dang /
NK075(bu)002:6885: thun mong gi rnam grangs ni /
NK075(bu)002:6889: rgyas pa'i le'u re lnga pa nas /
NK075(bu)002:6890: byis pa gtsang ma la pra phab thabs la sogs pa /
NK075(bu)002:6891: thun mong gi mngon shes lnga la sogs sgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6893: rgyas pa'i re bzhi pa nas bshad pa la sogs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6895: rgyas pa'i so bdun pa las a la shes pa gtad nas /
NK075(bu)002:6896: lus mi snang bar bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6897: kun bzang yab yum gyi gsang bar bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis nas dkyil 'khor re re bsgoms la /
NK075(bu)002:6898: sbyor ba byas nas 'od du zhu nas /
NK075(bu)002:6899: thams cad kun bzang yab yum la bstims pa la
NK075(bu)002:6900: sogs pa'i sgo nas te mi gnas nam mkha'i mtha'
NK075(bu)002:6901: klas par / goms par 'dod pa thob pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6902: chu la sa bzhin 'gro ba dang //
NK075(bu)002:6903: tsha ba rlung gis bteg pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:6904: phyogs bcu kun tu phyin pa 'gyur //
NK075(bu)002:6905: zhes rdzu 'phrul thob pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6906: gzhan yang rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus kyi rgyud na yang /
NK075(bu)002:6912: sol ba la ljon shing bsgrub pa la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6914: chang 'phel la sogs rgyud gzhan du'ang mang du gsungs so //
NK075(bu)002:6915: gzhan yang rgyas pa'i bdun cu pa nas /
NK075(bu)002:6916: ro lang bsgrub pa'i sgo nas /
NK075(bu)002:6918: ma h+aa de wa la sogs dbang du 'du /
NK075(bu)002:6919: ro gser du 'gyur nas longs spyod kyi rkyen du 'gyur /
NK075(bu)002:6920: ro'i lce bcad pas gar bsam phyin /
NK075(bu)002:6926: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa bzhi'i sgo nas /
NK075(bu)002:6928: ro langs pa'i lce bcad pa'i mtshon dang /
NK075(bu)002:6930: gser dang rkang mgyogs la sogs kyi rdzu 'phrul sgrub thabs rnams dang /
NK075(bu)002:6931: pags pa la lham byas nas chus mi bying ba la sogs rdzu 'phrul thob thabs rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:6933: rgyas pa'i le'u lnga pa nas drug cu rtsa gcig gi bar du /
NK075(bu)002:6934: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub lnga /
NK075(bu)002:6935: me'i sgo nas las bzhi sgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6937: mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bzhi sgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6939: zhi ba la mi mthun kun sel dang /
NK075(bu)002:6940: rgyas pa la 'dod pa kun grub /
NK075(bu)002:6941: dbang la gsang ba gnad kyi lcags kyu /
NK075(bu)002:6942: drag po la dgra bgegs bdud 'joms /
NK075(bu)002:6943: gzhan yang rgyas pa'i nang tshan las /
NK075(bu)002:6945: lo thog gso thabs rgyud gzhan du gsal /
NK075(bu)002:6946: klu'i gags sel dgos pas le'u zhe drug pas ston /
NK075(bu)002:6947: gzhan yang dbang gi nang tshan la /
NK075(bu)002:6948: rgyas pa'i le'u zhe gnyis dang zhe gsum pa'i nang nas /
NK075(bu)002:6949: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gzungs ma rigs lnga'i yum 'gugs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6951: 'jig rten pa'i gzungs ma 'gugs pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:6952: rgyal pa sa 'dzin gyi chung ma dang /
NK075(bu)002:6953: blon po sa 'dzin gyi chung ma dang /
NK075(bu)002:6954: lha chen gzhan gyi chung ma bkug lugs le'u zhe lnga pas ston la /
NK075(bu)002:6959: mi'i bu mo yang 'gugs par yang ston no //
NK075(bu)002:6960: yul khams dbang du bya ba'i thabs /
NK075(bu)002:6961: le'u so brgyad pa nas ston la /
NK075(bu)002:6962: gzhan yang ma h+aa de wa dbang du byas nas bsgrubs pas /
NK075(bu)002:6963: las gang bsam bsgrub bcol ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:6964: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi bsgrubs nas dbang du byas pas /
NK075(bu)002:6965: las gang bsam bsgrub bcol ba'i thabs /
NK075(bu)002:6966: le'u re gsum pa nas ston la /
NK075(bu)002:6967: drag po la nang tshan du /
NK075(bu)002:6968: dgra bgegs gling gzhan la 'pho ba'i thabs /
NK075(bu)002:6969: le'u so brgyad pa nas ston la /
NK075(bu)002:6973: dgra bgegs dang nyi zla gsad pa la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6974: gzhan gyi yul khams 'pham par byed pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:6975: sku de bzhin rigs kyis rgyal po'i lus la 'jug nas /
NK075(bu)002:6976: rang rgyal po red thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6977: gsung pad+ma'i rigs kyis zhang blon dbang chen gyi lus la 'jug nas dbang du bya thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6978: thugs rdo rje rigs kyis lcags spyang gi lus la 'jug nas /
NK075(bu)002:6980: yon tan rin chen rigs kyis blon po nor mang gi lus la 'jug nas /
NK075(bu)002:6981: rang blon po nor mang red thabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:6982: 'phrin las kyis lha min gyi lus la 'jug nas /
NK075(bu)002:6983: dmag mang sgrub thabs rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:6984: yang na sku rdzu 'phrul gyis sgrub pa /
NK075(bu)002:6989: de ltar sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi
NK075(bu)002:6990: sgo nas thun mong dag gi sgrub thabas mi mthun
NK075(bu)002:6991: par gragsa pa de rnams ni thun mong gi sgrub
NK075(bu)002:6992: pa'i rnam grangs yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:6993: zag med kyi 'bras bu thob thabs mchog gi sgrub pa la /
NK075(bu)002:6998: 'phrin las don grub dang lnga po'i bsgrub thabs /
NK075(bu)002:7003: 'phrin las phur pa la sogs pa'i sgrub thabs rnams ni /
NK075(bu)002:7004: rgyud gzhung spyi'i chings yin la /
NK075(bu)002:7005: khyad par sgyu 'phrul rang gzhung la zhi khro gnyis kyi sgo nas tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa /
NK075(bu)002:7006: dkyil 'khor rgyas bsdus 'bring gsum gyi thog nas sgrub thabs rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:7009: gong gi rnam grangs kyi skabs su bshad pa'i thun
NK075(bu)002:7010: mong dang mchog gi sgrub pa'i thabas su grags pa
NK075(bu)002:7011: kun / tshul ci ltar du bsgrub na /
NK075(bu)002:7015: yo byad de phun sum tshogs pa bzhir ldan nasa /
NK075(bu)002:7018: sa brtagsa shing byin gyis brlabs pa yan chad kyis cho ga rgyas par bya la gnas der /
NK075(bu)002:7019: sgrub khang brtsig la byug bsrung bya /
NK075(bu)002:7020: de nas sgrub pa'i sngon 'gro la s+aats+tsha chu gtor
NK075(bu)002:7021: la sogs tshogas kyi dpung bskyed la sgrib pa sbyangs
NK075(bu)002:7022: byas la / de nas bsnyen pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7025: sgrub pa chen po bzhi'i gzhung bsrangs la /
NK075(bu)002:7026: sngags gra ngas dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa so sor
NK075(bu)002:7027: phye bas rgyud rgyas pa nas gsung pa bzhin ma
NK075(bu)002:7028: rdzogs par du bsgrub dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:7030: rgyud rang rang gi nang du bshad pa'i sngags grangs them pa ste /
NK075(bu)002:7031: phal cher dbang gi skabs yin la /
NK075(bu)002:7033: zla ba drug gam bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug go //
NK075(bu)002:7034: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa rtags ma byung bar du'o //
NK075(bu)002:7037: rnal 'byor pa gang gis lta ba bden pa dbyer
NK075(bu)002:7038: med mngon du rtogsa shing ting nge 'dzin gyis gomas
NK075(bu)002:7039: par byed pa gnyis mgo 'byor ba'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)002:7042: thugs ye shes sems dpa' dang bzhi dbu rgyan gyi
NK075(bu)002:7043: lha lnga gcig tu brtsis pa'i lha lnga rdzogs dang
NK075(bu)002:7044: / phyag rgya bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam /
NK075(bu)002:7045: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa la brtana pa thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7046: phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs kyi spyod pa la sogs
NK075(bu)002:7047: pa rnams la mi lcog pa med pa gang yod
NK075(bu)002:7048: pa dang / gzhan yang sgrub pa'i cha rkyen tshang
NK075(bu)002:7049: bar byas la tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin
NK075(bu)002:7050: mthong lam ma thob pa'i sngon sbyor lam du bsgrub
NK075(bu)002:7051: pa dang / par bya'o // 'o na thun mong gi sgrub pa 'dir mi smos sam /
NK075(bu)002:7053: thun mong gi sgrub pa'i dus kyang /
NK075(bu)002:7054: phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:7056: gso dang gsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK075(bu)002:7061: ma bsgrubs na lha yal bas sgrub pa mi 'phyang /
NK075(bu)002:7062: 'bras bu mi thob de yang thun mong dang mchog
NK075(bu)002:7063: gi sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga lngas
NK075(bu)002:7064: phye ba'i 'bras bu bcu po mi thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7065: ma bsgrubs na skyon yod pas de bas na /
NK075(bu)002:7066: mchog thun mong gi sgrub thabs kyi skyon yon bye
NK075(bu)002:7067: brag mi 'dra ba de rnams kyi don rgyas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7068: dmigs khong du chud par byas la sgrub pa la
NK075(bu)002:7069: brtson par bya'o // yon tan no //
NK075(bu)002:7071: sgrub pa ma byas na skyon de las bzlog pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7072: tshe 'di dang phyi mar thun mong gi 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga dang /
NK075(bu)002:7073: mchog gi 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin
NK075(bu)002:7074: las lnga thob pas bdag gzhan gyi don gnyisa rdzogsa
NK075(bu)002:7075: pa yin no // sngags dang phyag rgya la gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:7079: yan lag dgu pa sngagas dang bcu pa phyaga rgya'i sdom tshigsa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:7080: sngags dang phyag rgya'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)002:7081: sngags dang phyag rgya'i ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7082: sngags dang phyag rgya'i rnam grangsa du yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7083: sngags gsum bzla phyag rgya bzhi sgom thabsa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7084: sngags phyag rgya'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)002:7085: skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7086: sngags bzlas phyag rgya bsgoms pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)002:7087: sngags ma bzlas phyag rgya ma bsgoms pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)002:7088: rnal 'byor pa gang gi spyod yul yin pa bzhin
NK075(bu)002:7089: dgu'i sngags dang phyag rgya'i don 'og rgyas bashada de
NK075(bu)002:7095: gnas skabs kyi sgrib pa sbyang zhing ye shes kyi lha nye bar bsnyen pa sngags dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7096: mthar thug thob par bya ba'i 'bras bu rigs lnga'am
NK075(bu)002:7097: sku lnga po rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir phyag rgya
NK075(bu)002:7098: dgos pas / de bas na bdag don dngos yin la /
NK075(bu)002:7100: bdag gazhanaganyisa ka'i don 'grub pas ched du sngags phyag
NK075(bu)002:7101: rgya gnyis po shin tu gces pas nyams su blang
NK075(bu)002:7104: lus kyi yi ge k+aa li dang /
NK075(bu)002:7105: yan lag gi yi ge +aa li bu drug gnyis lhan du 'dus pa las ming red /
NK075(bu)002:7106: ming de la grub pa bzhisa brgyan pas /
NK075(bu)002:7107: nus mthu chen po can du red pa'i ming tshig
NK075(bu)002:7108: gang yin pa de ni sngags kyi ngo bo yin
NK075(bu)002:7109: te / de yang grub pa bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)002:7110: chos rje rin chen ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:7111: rang bzhin chos nyid kyis grub pa don las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7112: chos can rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa ni
NK075(bu)002:7113: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub thams cad snang
NK075(bu)002:7114: ba dang / byin rlabs lha'i grub pa sngags kyi nus pa mthu can red pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7115: mthus grub pa sngags kyi nus pa mthu can du
NK075(bu)002:7116: lta ba'i thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub thams
NK075(bu)002:7117: cad snang ba'o // zhes bzhed kyang /
NK075(bu)002:7118: dgongs 'dus kyi gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo bkod pa'i le'u so bzhi pa'i skabs dang /
NK075(bu)002:7119: gsang snying gi le'u bzhi pa'i skabs la brtags na /
NK075(bu)002:7120: spyir shes bya 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK075(bu)002:7122: de la tshig tu byung bas des mtshon nas byed
NK075(bu)002:7123: las mi 'dra ba dngos su grub pa bzhi ste
NK075(bu)002:7124: / chos nyid ces sogs kyis tshig gis chos nyid kho na las mi mtshon la /
NK075(bu)002:7125: ka ba zhes sogs kyis chos can kho na las mi mtshon /
NK075(bu)002:7126: lha zhes sogs kyis lha kho na las mi mtshon /
NK075(bu)002:7127: 'di sbyin 'di sod lta bus phan gnod kho na nus mthu la mi 'byung bas /
NK075(bu)002:7128: grub pa bzhi phyogs re ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:7129: sngags ni tshig shad gcig la yang /
NK075(bu)002:7130: grub pa bzhis brgyan pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7131: de yang zhi ba'i snying po /
NK075(bu)002:7132: h'u badz+ra d+h+ri ka rkyang pa la yang /
NK075(bu)002:7134: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste snang stong dbyer skye 'jig dang bral ba /
NK075(bu)002:7136: don las mi 'da' ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)002:7137: rang bzhin chos nyid kyi grub pas brgyan la /
NK075(bu)002:7138: badz+ra d+h+rika rdo rje 'dzin pa mtshon pas /
NK075(bu)002:7139: chos can gyi mtshan ma grub pas brgyan la /
NK075(bu)002:7140: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika brjod pa'i byin rlabs des lha rdo
NK075(bu)002:7141: rje sems dpa'i sku wal gyis gsal bas byin rlabs
NK075(bu)002:7143: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika de bzlas pas /
NK075(bu)002:7144: bdag gzhan thams cad la gnas skabs kyi thun mong la bar chad zhi la /
NK075(bu)002:7145: mthar thug sangs rgyas thob pas /
NK075(bu)002:7146: mchog gi dngos grub thob pa'i nus mthu yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:7147: mthu'i grub pas brgyan ces bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:7150: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK075(bu)002:7151: 'phrin las 'phro 'du'i phyag rgya dang bzhi rdzogsa pa
NK075(bu)002:7152: de nyid la mi 'da' ba'i don de gang la
NK075(bu)002:7153: snang ba de ni phyag rgya'i ngo bo yin no
NK075(bu)002:7159: rigsa spyir 'di la sa mtha' med pas mi 'thad sngags ni /
NK075(bu)002:7160: rig pa yab kyis 'dzin pas yab sngags yin la /
NK075(bu)002:7161: gsang sngags ni theg 'og la gsang ba'i bde stong yum gyis 'dzin pas yum sngags yin la /
NK075(bu)002:7163: yab yum gnyis la 'brel ba'i sngags yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7164: de yang rgyal po dzah'i dgongs 'dus 'grel par gsang sngags zhes pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7165: lha mo rnams shes rab kyi rang bzhin te /
NK075(bu)002:7166: dgongs pa zab pas rtogs par daka'o //
NK075(bu)002:7167: rigs sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7168: rig pa'i rgyal po lha pho'i rang bzhin thabs des rig pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:7169: gzungs sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7170: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i kha sbyor gyis gzung ba'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:7171: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun la /
NK075(bu)002:7172: yang gsang ba grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)002:7173: sngags rnams kun gyi dbye ba ni //
NK075(bu)002:7174: rig sngags thabs kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK075(bu)002:7175: gzungs sngags shes rab ngo bo ste //
NK075(bu)002:7176: gsang sngags gnyis med ye shes yin //
NK075(bu)002:7178: dbang yon tan rim pa las /
NK075(bu)002:7179: stong pa dang ni snying rje nyid //
NK075(bu)002:7180: gnyis su med dang gnyis tshul gyis //
NK075(bu)002:7181: gsang sngags zhes ni de la bshad //
NK075(bu)002:7184: yum gyis bde ba gzungs pas gzungs sngags /
NK075(bu)002:7185: yab yum gnyis kyi dgongs pa zab pas gsang sngags zhes bshad do //
NK075(bu)002:7186: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags /
NK075(bu)002:7189: de la zhi ba ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:7191: badz+ra d+h+rika rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed pa'i rkyen sngags /
NK075(bu)002:7192: rtsa sngags dang bskyed sngags dril ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7193: bzlas pa las kyi sngags su shes so //
NK075(bu)002:7196: badz+ra m+aa h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka bskyed sngags /
NK075(bu)002:7197: ma h+aa tsan+da badz+ra sarba dush+tana ta ka da ha
NK075(bu)002:7198: pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata phata ni bzlas pa
NK075(bu)002:7201: gzhal yas khang bskyed sngags kyang bskyed pa rkyen sngags yin no //
NK075(bu)002:7203: ru lu ru lu 'bru brgyad lta bu yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:7204: de la che yon gyi sgo nas bstod pa /
NK075(bu)002:7206: thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba'i sngags dang gsum yod do //
NK075(bu)002:7210: ye shes kyi snyan gsan dbab pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7215: rig pa'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7216: dngos grub bskul ba'i sngags rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:7225: dbang bskur ba'i sngags las thams cad pa'i sngags /
NK075(bu)002:7230: 'gro lding la sogs rnams ni sngags kyi rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)002:7238: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK075(bu)002:7239: 'phro 'du phrin las kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:7243: phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)002:7245: sku phyag rgya chen po la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)002:7246: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK075(bu)002:7247: phung khams skye med rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7248: rgyas pa'i le'u don drug pa las /
NK075(bu)002:7249: rang bzhin phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK075(bu)002:7250: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kun //
NK075(bu)002:7251: thabs dang shes rab ngang du gnas //
NK075(bu)002:7252: rigs lnga bde gshegs yab yum dang //
NK075(bu)002:7253: ma bcos ye nas de ltar gnas //
NK075(bu)002:7255: 'di ni gzhi'i gnas lugs la dgongs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7257: rang bzhin gzugs kyi sku ni /
NK075(bu)002:7258: 'og min na bzhugs pa nyid dang /
NK075(bu)002:7260: yon tan rdzogs pa'i gzhir gyur pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7261: zhes mthar phyin 'bras bu la dgongs pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7262: ting nga 'dzina gyi phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK075(bu)002:7263: rang gnas de nyid lta bas rtogs nas /
NK075(bu)002:7264: ting nge 'dzin gyis sku phyag rgya chen po nas /
NK075(bu)002:7265: dbu'i gtsug tor nas 'og gdan khri'i bar gsal bar bsgom pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7267: lhag pa'i phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK075(bu)002:7268: nang gi rtags ni phyi ru ste //
NK075(bu)002:7269: mdor bsdus phyag rgya drug pa dang //
NK075(bu)002:7270: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK075(bu)002:7272: lha bsgom pa de nyid dngos su gzugs brnyan gyis mtshon pa ni mtshon pa'i phyag rgya chen po /
NK075(bu)002:7273: ras dang shog gu sa thang gyang la bris pa /
NK075(bu)002:7275: shing dang rdo la 'bur du btod pa /
NK075(bu)002:7276: gser dngul zangs la sogs la lugs su blugs pa /
NK075(bu)002:7277: 'jims pa la 'dir so byas pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:7278: ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par rtogs pa la mtshan ma'i phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK075(bu)002:7279: sku gdung dang ring bsrel la sogs pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)002:7280: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7282: bde ba 'dzin pa la mi 'da' bas yum dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7283: dgongs pa chos nyid la mi 'da' ba'i rtags su rigs rang rang gi phyag mtshan 'dzin pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7284: 'dzin pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7285: gung mo la sogs pa'i rtse mo la rdo rje
NK075(bu)002:7286: la sogs pa'i rang rang gi phyag mtshan gsal ba
NK075(bu)002:7287: ni bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7288: 'bru bzhi sbas nas gung mo la sogs lnga rim
NK075(bu)002:7289: pa ltar gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs
NK075(bu)002:7291: bca' ba'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:7294: yum la 'khyud par bsam pa ni bsam pa 'phro 'du las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7295: yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos
NK075(bu)002:7296: kyi rigs la brten pa'i phyag rgya dngos su bca'
NK075(bu)002:7297: ba ni bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7298: 'o na de nyid las kyi phyag rgya ci ltar yin ce na /
NK075(bu)002:7300: des thabs dang shes rab 'khril bar sbyor bar bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:7303: phyed byung tshul gyis gar bskyod pa //
NK075(bu)002:7304: ltung ba med phyir brten par bshad //
NK075(bu)002:7306: yab yum 'khril ba'i las byas pas //
NK075(bu)002:7307: byang sems kyi 'phro 'du 'byung bar byed pas bde stong bskyed de /
NK075(bu)002:7308: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i ngo bo la gnas pas 'phrin las thams cad rdzogs par byed pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7309: rang bzhin las kyi phyag rgya yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7310: de yang rgyas pa'i le'u so drug pa las /
NK075(bu)002:7311: bya ba med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK075(bu)002:7312: las rnams ma lus rdzogs par byed //
NK075(bu)002:7321: zhes grol lam dang 'bras bu mthar phyin la dgongs so //
NK075(bu)002:7323: rang bzhin gzhi la dgos so //
NK075(bu)002:7324: mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas sems can gyi don byed pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7325: ting nge 'dzin 'phro 'du las kyi phyag rgya yin pa dang bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:7326: chos kyi phyag rgya'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)002:7328: bde stong gi ye shes myong ba ni bde ba chos kyi phyag dang /
NK075(bu)002:7329: dbyer med ma bcos pa'i don nyams su myong ba ni rang bzhin chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7330: sngags brjod pa ni bzlas pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)002:7332: thugs kar yig 'bru bsgom pa ni bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:7333: phyag rgya bzhi po de dag re re la yang don bzhi bzhir 'byung ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7335: grol lam la bskyed rdzogs rnams kyis phye bas grangs mang po 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7336: de yang sku phyag rgya chen po la /
NK075(bu)002:7342: bsam bca' gnyis ni thabs lam gtso che la /
NK075(bu)002:7343: rang bzhin grol lam rdzogs rim /
NK075(bu)002:7347: rang bzhin ni grol lam rdzogs rim mo //
NK075(bu)002:7348: bzlas bsam gnyis ni bskyed rim mo //
NK075(bu)002:7352: mthar lam gyis phye bas grangs mang po byung /
NK075(bu)002:7353: gsungs pa ni dpyad par bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:7356: sngags bzla ba la skyon bcu po de le lo mi byed nas dor bar bya dgos /
NK075(bu)002:7367: g.yeng ba dang lnga ste bcu'o //
NK075(bu)002:7368: de la sgra che na 'byung pos lad mo byed
NK075(bu)002:7369: nas bzlas pas nus pa nyams par 'byung ba dang
NK075(bu)002:7370: / snod med kyis thos mi nyan pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)002:7371: tshig zur mi phyin na bar chad pas mthu med la /
NK075(bu)002:7372: myur drag na lce dub pas log chad pas sngags bzla mi nus la /
NK075(bu)002:7374: dus 'das na ma bzlas na bar chad 'byung /
NK075(bu)002:7376: sbrid pa de lu ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7377: mi dang gtam byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7379: sems g.yeng na srog med pas bar chad na /
NK075(bu)002:7380: yid btags dang bdud la sogs pas bar chad byed do //
NK075(bu)002:7383: snod med thos par gyur bar 'byung //
NK075(bu)002:7384: sgra med bar chad mthu med 'gyur //
NK075(bu)002:7385: skyon gyi lus kyi 'phrod pa nyams //
NK075(bu)002:7386: de las sngags kyi nus pa med //
NK075(bu)002:7387: bul nas bzlas pa'i grangs med pas //
NK075(bu)002:7389: glo dang sbrid dang gtam dang ni //
NK075(bu)002:7390: gnyid la sogs pas bar chad na //
NK075(bu)002:7391: des ni yid btags bdud la sogs //
NK075(bu)002:7392: spro na bar chod sbyor bar byed //
NK075(bu)002:7393: sems yengs nus mthu mi 'byung ngo //
NK075(bu)002:7395: phyag rgya sgom pa la skyon brgyad spang ba'i sgo
NK075(bu)002:7396: nas lha bsgoms pa brtson pas nan tan sbyar dgos
NK075(bu)002:7397: te / de la skyon brgyad ni /
NK075(bu)002:7405: dang po kha dog gsal la de nas rim par nus nas mi gsal ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7408: thun mong dang mchog la sogs pa gang bsgrub la bzlas pa byas pas /
NK075(bu)002:7409: mthu dang byin rlabs dang ldan zhing yid skyob pa'i phyir sngags zhes zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:7411: brda sprod pas kyang phyag rgya /
NK075(bu)002:7412: don la mi 'da' bas phyag rgya ste /
NK075(bu)002:7413: de phyir sngags phyag rgya zhes ming gi sgra don ni nges tshig 'jug go //
NK075(bu)002:7414: skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7416: dkyil 'khor dgos pa'i dus lnga'i skabs la sngags phyag rgya dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:7418: zhi khro'i lha tshogs bsgrub cing mchod pa la dkyil 'khor dgos pa mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:7419: dbang bskur dgos pas dbang gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)002:7420: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob pa'i thabs la
NK075(bu)002:7421: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang zhi rgyas dbang
NK075(bu)002:7422: drag gang byed kyis phrin las dkyil 'khor dgos pa
NK075(bu)002:7423: dang / sku gsung thugs kyi rten rab gnas la
NK075(bu)002:7424: dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang bsod nams rten gyi dkyil
NK075(bu)002:7425: dang / 'khor dang lnga'o // gzhan yang bsnyen sgrub
NK075(bu)002:7426: rnam bzhi'i sgo nas don nyams su len pa'i tshe
NK075(bu)002:7427: na sngags dang phyag rgya dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7431: phyag rgya bzhi bsgom pa la rab tu brtan pa thob na /
NK075(bu)002:7432: mchog thun mong gi dangsa grub ya mtshan chen por snang ba de dngos su grub par 'gyur la /
NK075(bu)002:7433: yid la gang bsam pa'i 'bras bu thams cad 'grub pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:7436: dpe ral gri'i yu ba nas bzung na phar la
NK075(bu)002:7437: thams cad gcod la so la bzung na tshul la
NK075(bu)002:7439: sngags dang phyag rgya la brtson 'grus kyis nan tan
NK075(bu)002:7440: med pa'i gzhung gzhan du ma spyad pa'i gsang sngags
NK075(bu)002:7441: pa 'ga' zhig gis ni dam tshig nyams pas tshe
NK075(bu)002:7442: 'dir phung zhing phyi mar mtho ris dang thar pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7444: gang gi spyod yul yin pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7446: gsang ba sngags kyi nang tshan la /
NK075(bu)002:7449: gzungs sngags gsum gang la mos pa'i rim pa rnams nyams len gang byed /
NK075(bu)002:7450: de'i spyod yul yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7451: phyag rgya bzhi gang la spyod pa'i gang zag de yi spyod yul lo //
NK075(bu)002:7452: sngags dang phyag rgya khyad par 'phags //
NK075(bu)002:7454: sngags dang phyag rgya rnams kyi don nyams su mi
NK075(bu)002:7455: len pa rnams kyi spyod yul ni ma yin no
NK075(bu)002:7456: // tha ma drod tshad ldan pas 'bras bu mthong lam la sbyor ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7458: dang po shes par bya ba'i yul lnga /
NK075(bu)002:7459: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam gnyis gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)002:7460: tha ma rtogs pa'i rig pa la dbyer med kyi drod thob pa'i tshad dang ldan pa des /
NK075(bu)002:7461: mthong lam la nye bar sbyor ba'i zag med kyis
NK075(bu)002:7462: non thab de ni 'di lta ste rnal 'byor pa
NK075(bu)002:7463: rang gi nyams su gang len gyi lha de bsgrub
NK075(bu)002:7464: pa dang / de yang sngon du tshogs lam gyi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7465: dam tshig dang sdom pa la sel med na zag
NK075(bu)002:7466: bcas de nyid zag med kyi lam la sbyor nus
NK075(bu)002:7467: pa yin te / de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)002:7468: zag bcas zag med la sbyor ba'i thabs la bsgrubs pa la'ang tshogsa bsgrub dgos te /
NK075(bu)002:7469: de'ang zhi khro gnyis nyams len gang byed kyi tshogs
NK075(bu)002:7470: sgrub thabs kyi rnam grangs rang gi gzhung nas bshad
NK075(bu)002:7471: pa bzhin du bsgrub dgos la /
NK075(bu)002:7472: de'ang dang po tshogs sgrub kyi dus su thabs lam
NK075(bu)002:7473: dang shes rab grol lam gang 'jug gi ting nge
NK075(bu)002:7475: thabs lam steng sgo la rtsa rlung thig le la sbyang thabs rnams dang /
NK075(bu)002:7476: 'og sgo la thig le dbab bzlog /
NK075(bu)002:7482: phyag rgya spros pa rnams la sbyang thabs /
NK075(bu)002:7483: rgyal ba'i lung tshad ma bla ma'i man ngag tshad
NK075(bu)002:7484: ma gnyis las gragas pa'i don de dag la legsa
NK075(bu)002:7485: par sbyangs nas thabs grol gyi ting nge 'dzin la
NK075(bu)002:7486: brtan pa thob nas sgrub pa byas pas zag bcas
NK075(bu)002:7487: de nyid zag pa med pa'i sa la sbyar ba
NK075(bu)002:7488: yin no // thabs grol gyi ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob na /
NK075(bu)002:7489: sgrub pa byas kyang sbyor mi nus so //
NK075(bu)002:7490: tha ma 'bras bu lam gyis 'thob par byed pas lam shes par rgyu 'bru re nas bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7492: thugs kyi thigas pa la rab la mtshan bstan /
NK075(bu)002:7493: 'bring la rnam dbye gnyis gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)002:7494: blo tha ma la 'bru re nas gnyer cing bshad pas /
NK075(bu)002:7495: lam gyi snga ma lta ba rtogs pa'i rgyu byas nas /
NK075(bu)002:7496: lam mthar phyin nas 'bras bu thob par byed pa de'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:7497: 'bru gnyer la brten nas lta ba rtogs /
NK075(bu)002:7498: de nyid nyams su blangs pa la lam lnga rim pa ltar bgrod nas mthar phyina pa la /
NK075(bu)002:7499: 'bras bu bde bar gshegas rgyal ba de nyid dngos su thob pa yin no //
NK075(bu)002:7500: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i yon tan de yod pa'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)002:7501: blo tha ma'i gang zag la gzhung don gtan la phab pa la /
NK075(bu)002:7502: bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu yi sgo nas 'bru re dang sbyar dgos de /
NK075(bu)002:7503: khyad par du rus sbal nur shugs kyi sgo nas 'bru gnyer nyams su blang bar bya ste /
NK075(bu)002:7504: tshig 'bru re nas gnyer ba de bsam byung gis gzhal ba'i yul du byas nas gzhal bas /
NK075(bu)002:7505: don mngon sum du rnyed cing rtogs so //
NK075(bu)002:7506: rtogs nas don dbyer med gcig pu nyams su len
NK075(bu)002:7507: cing bsgrub pa la gong gi tshig tha snyad kyi
NK075(bu)002:7508: don ma lus pa rnams der 'dus pas tshig re
NK075(bu)002:7509: res don re mtshon pa rnams so sor nyams len
NK075(bu)002:7513: thugs kyi thigas pa las 'bru mthun /
NK075(bu)002:7514: thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam /
NK075(bu)002:7515: skye ru rung ba zhig la gdul bya dag pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7516: blo dang 'tsham par gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa
NK075(bu)002:7517: snang ba'i / don gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas le'u ste /
NK075(bu)002:7518: yas bgrang gsum pa'i don du gda' 'o //
NK075(bu)002:7519: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la gsum /
NK075(bu)002:7523: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i yan lag la snang ba bzhi yod pa las /
NK075(bu)002:7526: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba dang gsum gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)002:7527: bzhi pa 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)002:7528: yang na mtshan nyid gsum ltar na /
NK075(bu)002:7529: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK075(bu)002:7530: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid gnyis gong du song nas
NK075(bu)002:7531: tha ma 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ma
NK075(bu)002:7532: nor par gsal bar lung bstan pa la gnas skabs
NK075(bu)002:7533: kyi 'bras bu rig pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7534: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas thob tshul gnyis so //
NK075(bu)002:7543: snga ma gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa'i tshul la yang /
NK075(bu)002:7545: rig 'dzin gyi rnam grangs dang rig 'dzin zhes bya ba'i nges tshiga dang /
NK075(bu)002:7546: gnas su bzhugs tshul dang bzhi'i sgo nas rig 'dzin gyi don rgyas bshad de rnam para bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7552: sems bud nas 'gro la lus mal du lhag nas
NK075(bu)002:7553: lus pas lhag ma'i lus ma dor nas yod pa
NK075(bu)002:7554: dang / dor nas med pa'i myang 'das thob tshul
NK075(bu)002:7555: gnyis kyi dbye ba nyan thos la yod pa bzhin
NK075(bu)002:7556: dang / du / lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum dang /
NK075(bu)002:7558: gzhan gyis mi basngagasa pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7559: 'khor ba la ltung dogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7560: 'khor ba la lan mi thebs dogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7561: 'chi dogs pa'i 'jigs pa lnga dang bral nas /
NK075(bu)002:7562: zag med mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin thob pa la yang /
NK075(bu)002:7563: lhag bcas tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi lus dor ma
NK075(bu)002:7564: dgos par tshe 'di nyid la phyag rgya chen po
NK075(bu)002:7566: lhag med rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi lus dor nas
NK075(bu)002:7567: bar ma dor phyag chen la rnam par sbyar ba'o
NK075(bu)002:7570: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dpe bya khyung gi
NK075(bu)002:7571: phru gu sgo nga de bcag tshar ba dang ma
NK075(bu)002:7573: gcan gzan seng phrug gi mngal rgya la ma'i mchu
NK075(bu)002:7574: zur gyis dbral ma thag tu ma dang rtsal mnyam
NK075(bu)002:7575: pa'i tshul du / rnal 'byor pa lus rgya dang
NK075(bu)002:7576: bral ma thag tu phyag chen gyi skur 'gyur ro
NK075(bu)002:7577: pa'i tshul du / // tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i
NK075(bu)002:7578: rig 'dzin ni phung po la 'jig pa med par
NK075(bu)002:7579: pa'i tshul du / // mthar khyer ba'o // phyag rgya chen por gyur pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7580: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi lus de nyid lha gang bsgom rigs gcig gi skur snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7582: sku lnga sogs sku rigs rgyan 'khor nyi shu rtsa lngar lhan grub tu rig pa rang snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7583: 'o na sangs rgyas dang khyad med dam zhe na /
NK075(bu)002:7584: mnyam gzhag la khyad med kyang lhun grub rig 'dzin pa de la /
NK075(bu)002:7585: rjes shes bag la nyal de yi dri ma /
NK075(bu)002:7586: yun se gol gtogs pa tsam gcig la yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:7587: da rung mnyam rjes kyi rtsol ba can yin no //
NK075(bu)002:7588: de ltar mthong lam la tshe rnam gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:7589: sgom lam la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin /
NK075(bu)002:7590: mthar lam la lhun grub rig 'dzin dang bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)002:7591: 'o na mtshan nyid kyi mthong sgom mthar phyin pa'i lam gsum dang /
NK075(bu)002:7592: rig 'dzin bzhi khyad med dam zhe na mthong lam tshe rnam gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)002:7593: rgyu'i theg pa'i mthong lam gnyis /
NK075(bu)002:7594: mthong lam tsam du skal pa mnyam yang dgongs pa rgyu'i sa brgyad pa dang mnyam la /
NK075(bu)002:7595: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)002:7596: rgyu'i sa brgyad pa gnyis sgom lam tsam du skal
NK075(bu)002:7597: ba mnyam yang dgongs pa rgyu'i mthar lam pa dang
NK075(bu)002:7598: mnyam mo // mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)002:7599: rgyu'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' gnyis mthar lam
NK075(bu)002:7600: tsam du skal ba mnyam yang dgongs pa kun tu
NK075(bu)002:7603: de yang dang po'i dang po dang //
NK075(bu)002:7604: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rig mchog ste //
NK075(bu)002:7605: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK075(bu)002:7606: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mo //
NK075(bu)002:7607: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho khyad par 'phags //
NK075(bu)002:7611: me la gnas pa'i sems can gyi rigs la /
NK075(bu)002:7613: ri dwags me byi dkar po gnyis kyi gnas kyang me /
NK075(bu)002:7614: zas gos la sogs pa rnams kyang me la longs spyod la /
NK075(bu)002:7617: chu la gnas pa'i sems can rnams kyi gnas kyang chu la /
NK075(bu)002:7618: zas gos la sogs pa yang chu la longs spyod byed /
NK075(bu)002:7619: chu dang bral na 'chi ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7621: rlung la gnas pa'i sems can gyi rigsa la /
NK075(bu)002:7622: bya mkha' lding nam mkha' la tshang 'jug bya ba des /
NK075(bu)002:7624: zas gos longs spyod rlung la byed /
NK075(bu)002:7626: rlung las mi 'da' ba bzhin du'am /
NK075(bu)002:7627: yang na me'i rigs kyi mtshan nyid tsha ba la gnas /
NK075(bu)002:7628: chu rigs kyi mtshan nyid gsher ba gnas /
NK075(bu)002:7629: rlung rigs kyi mtshan nyid yang zhing g.yo ba la gnas pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7630: sems can gang yang sangs rgyas kyi rigsa kyis zin nas mi gtong ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7631: sangs rgyas kyi rigs yin kyang /
NK075(bu)002:7632: mngon du ma gyur pas 'dzin mi nus pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7634: dang po sangs rgyas yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7635: lta ba rtogs pa las byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7636: bar du lta sgom gyis nyams su blangs pas 'bras
NK075(bu)002:7637: bu 'thob pas byed pa'i bya ba byed pa dang
NK075(bu)002:7638: / tha ma zag med kyi mthong lam yan chad
NK075(bu)002:7639: nas sangs rgyas kyi rgyud 'dzin pa dang gsum gyis
NK075(bu)002:7640: rig 'dzin zhes bya ba'i nges tshig de 'grub pa
NK075(bu)002:7641: / yin no // sangs rgyas nas rig 'dzin mi 'dzin gyi tha snyad dang bral ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7644: rig 'dzin de yi bzhugs gnas la nges pa med de /
NK075(bu)002:7645: sems sam rig pa de nyid lha'i skur shar bas /
NK075(bu)002:7646: snang ba 'di nyid gnas su dag nas /
NK075(bu)002:7647: sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas su snang bas de bas na gnas gang yang rung ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:7652: lam lnga'i bya ba ma lus pa kun byas pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7653: 'bras bu sangs rgyas grub pa dag gi rnam grangs
NK075(bu)002:7654: ni / 'bras bu thob tshul dang 'bras bu'i ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)002:7656: gdul bya'i spyod yul la gzigs tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7657: thugs rje'i sprul pa 'char tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7658: gzhan don mdzad pa'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7659: dgongs pa ye shes la bzhugs tshul dang bdun gyi
NK075(bu)002:7660: sdom tshig gis 'og rgyas bshad de shes par bya'o
NK075(bu)002:7666: bdag don du rang snang thob tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7668: bdag don gi dbang du 'bras bu thob tshul ni /
NK075(bu)002:7669: rgyas pa las 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK075(bu)002:7670: dpe dpag bsam gyi shing nor bu rin po che
NK075(bu)002:7671: de dag la rta dang glang po la sogs dgos
NK075(bu)002:7672: 'dod kyi rdzas rnams rang rgyud du yod pa ma
NK075(bu)002:7673: yin te / gdul bya so so'i rang sems kyi
NK075(bu)002:7674: bsod namsa dpag tu med pa'i mthu brtan pa'i stobs
NK075(bu)002:7675: las dgos 'dod gang bsam 'grub pa yin pa bzhin
NK075(bu)002:7676: yin te / du / gzhi sems nyid ngos bzung dang bral ba mngon du gyur pa de la /
NK075(bu)002:7677: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan ci yang snang ba nas /
NK075(bu)002:7678: ngo mtshar zhing sems kyi cho 'phrul la yon tan
NK075(bu)002:7679: rmad byung kyi 'bras bu'i chos kyi rnams grangs nyer
NK075(bu)002:7680: lnga po la sogs thob pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7681: gzhan nas bkug pa'i yod pa cig /
NK075(bu)002:7682: 'dir 'bras bu thob dus la gsar du 'ong nas thob pa ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7683: de'i sgras tshul ci ltar du byung na /
NK075(bu)002:7684: thabas snying rje'i chags rtog 'di nyid lam du khyer
NK075(bu)002:7685: ba la brten pa'i shes rab stong pa de nyid
NK075(bu)002:7686: mthar phyin nas / sku dang ye shes /
NK075(bu)002:7687: dbyings dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas /
NK075(bu)002:7688: gong gi dpe de lta bu yi bdag don rnam
NK075(bu)002:7689: kun mchog ldan gyi chos sku mngon du gyur pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7690: ngang du sangs rgyas kyi che yon thams cad 'bad
NK075(bu)002:7691: med lhun grub tu rang byung ba yin no //
NK075(bu)002:7692: thabs 'gag med la ma brten pa'i stong nyid phyogs
NK075(bu)002:7693: gcig mngon du gyur pa'i ngang du sangs rgyas kyi
NK075(bu)002:7694: che yon thams cad 'bad med lhun grub tu rang
NK075(bu)002:7696: gzhan don mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs nas sangs rgyas thob tshul lo //
NK075(bu)002:7698: gzhan gyi don du gzugs sku'i sangs rgyas thob tshul
NK075(bu)002:7699: ni rgyas pa'i lung las 'di skad du gsungs te
NK075(bu)002:7700: / lam lnga'i bya ba ma lus pa kun byas
NK075(bu)002:7701: nas mthar 'bras bu ni skye 'jig med pa rdo
NK075(bu)002:7702: rje'i sku thob nas sprul pa sna tshogs kyis 'gro
NK075(bu)002:7703: ba'i don byed ces rgyud las gsungs pa'i don no
NK075(bu)002:7704: / // srid pa tha ma sa lhun grub rig 'dzin pa de la /
NK075(bu)002:7705: sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal ba kun bzang des dbang bskur ba la /
NK075(bu)002:7706: lhun grub rig 'dzin pa des dbang thob pa dang
NK075(bu)002:7707: ston pa rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sku dang dbyer med
NK075(bu)002:7708: du sangs rgyas / sangs rgyas ma thag tu /
NK075(bu)002:7709: gsang sngags rtogs nus kyi snang ngo la longs sku dang /
NK075(bu)002:7710: rtogs mi nus pa rnams kyi snang ngo la sku rdo rje /
NK075(bu)002:7712: thugs rdo rje gsum dbyer med las sprul pa thub
NK075(bu)002:7713: pa drug gi dabnga po ste gtso bo snang nas
NK075(bu)002:7714: gang la gang 'dul yis don byed de /
NK075(bu)002:7715: khyad par mi'i thub pas mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogas
NK075(bu)002:7716: nas sangs rgyas pa'i tshul du sems can gyi don
NK075(bu)002:7717: la / chos kyi sgo mo brgyad bzhi stong gsungs nas don mdzad de /
NK075(bu)002:7718: de yang rgyas bshad ni gsang ba'i snying po'i le'u
NK075(bu)002:7719: gsum pa'i stod chos thams cad gtan la phab pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7723: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa de nyid sems
NK075(bu)002:7724: su mngon du rtogs shing mtha' gru ma lus par
NK075(bu)002:7725: rgyas par byas na bden gnyis dbyer med cing skye
NK075(bu)002:7726: 'jig dang bral ba rdo rje'i sku thob ste /
NK075(bu)002:7727: de yang dpe chu yi nang gi zla ba yi gzugs brnyan du snang dus /
NK075(bu)002:7728: chu las ma g.yos nas dbyer med du snang ba
NK075(bu)002:7729: lta bu yi don yin pa la shes bya ma
NK075(bu)002:7730: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs shing thams cad du rig
NK075(bu)002:7731: par rang snang zhing gzhan gyi lhad med pas na
NK075(bu)002:7732: rang bzhina 'khor 'das kun dang tha mi dad par
NK075(bu)002:7733: dbyer med pa'o // rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)002:7740: de ltar nyer lnga ma 'gags pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7741: chos sku'i rgyan gyi mchog yin cing /
NK075(bu)002:7742: rgyun chad med pas 'khor lo ste /
NK075(bu)002:7743: de ltar nyer lnga po de /
NK075(bu)002:7744: bdag don chos sku mngon du gyur pa'i dus su
NK075(bu)002:7745: logs na glo bur du 'ong pa ma yin pas
NK075(bu)002:7746: na rang bzhin gansa zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:7748: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun snang la rang bzhin med par shar ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7749: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa ste chos sku /
NK075(bu)002:7750: thams cad rig rang snang ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7751: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK075(bu)002:7752: snang stong dbyer med cing 'khor 'das dbyer med pas na longs sku /
NK075(bu)002:7753: rig rtsal 'gag med du shar ba'i ngo bo la thams cad lhun gyis grub pas /
NK075(bu)002:7754: dgongs pa la 'gro 'ong med kyang sprul pa sna
NK075(bu)002:7755: tshogs kyis 'gro ba'i don byed pa ni sprul sku
NK075(bu)002:7756: dgongs pa skye 'jig dang bral ba rdo rje'i sku'o
NK075(bu)002:7758: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung ni /
NK075(bu)002:7759: chos nyid rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral ba lam pas brda mjal nas grol ba la bya'o //
NK075(bu)002:7760: mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ni /
NK075(bu)002:7761: ye shes lnga rang la gnas pa dang rtogs byed
NK075(bu)002:7762: kyi blo'i shes rab gnyis 'brel ba'i byin rlabs dpe
NK075(bu)002:7763: nyi ma shar ba dang thams cad gsal ba bzhin
NK075(bu)002:7764: du / 'khor 'das thams cad du rig pa rang shar ba /
NK075(bu)002:7766: longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsungs ni /
NK075(bu)002:7767: dpe me long la bltas na byad la dri ma gang yod sel ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7768: longs sku la bltas pas shes pas shes bya'i dri
NK075(bu)002:7769: ma rig cing snang stong dbyer med lam pas brda
NK075(bu)002:7770: mjal ba'o // sprul sku tshig gi gsung ni /
NK075(bu)002:7771: tshangs pa'i gsung gcig gis rigs drug so so'i skad du go ba ltar /
NK075(bu)002:7773: yan lag drug cu dang ldan zhing /
NK075(bu)002:7774: so sor rang rang dang mthun par go ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7775: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung grags stong dbyer med ni /
NK075(bu)002:7779: stong pa nyid ni chos dbyings ye shes te /
NK075(bu)002:7784: gsal stong dbyer med ni mnyam pa nyid ye shes te /
NK075(bu)002:7786: rig pa rang snang don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7789: shes bya so sor ma 'dres par gsal ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7793: spyir gzung yul gnas su dag cing rig pa rang
NK075(bu)002:7794: snang ba sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams su shar ba
NK075(bu)002:7795: ni / zhing khams yon tan can dang /
NK075(bu)002:7796: snang ba gnas su dag nas 'bras bu'i chos nyid
NK075(bu)002:7797: lhun grub tu rdzogs par rig pa rang snang ba
NK075(bu)002:7798: ni / gzhal yas khang yon tan can dang /
NK075(bu)002:7799: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa ma spangs par longs spyod cing /
NK075(bu)002:7800: rang rig pa'i ye shes su lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:7801: dbu rgyan sogs du mas brgyan pa ni /
NK075(bu)002:7802: rgyan cha yon tan can dang /
NK075(bu)002:7803: snying rje mthar phyin nas chos nyid ma bsgribs par ye shes su rang gsal ba'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)002:7804: 'od zer kha dog sna tshogs 'phro ba ni /
NK075(bu)002:7806: gdan khri yon tan can ni /
NK075(bu)002:7807: thun mong rtags kyi gleng gzhi dang mthun no //
NK075(bu)002:7809: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub dang lnga ni /
NK075(bu)002:7810: 'phrin las kyi skabs dang mthun no //
NK075(bu)002:7811: gdul bya la gzigs tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7813: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yul
NK075(bu)002:7814: gdul bya sems can thams cad la gzigs tshul ni
NK075(bu)002:7815: / gsang snying las 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK075(bu)002:7816: gnyis med kyi ye shes rang ngo ma shes pa'i lhan skyes ma rig pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7817: der ma zad log par rtog par rtog pa gzung
NK075(bu)002:7818: 'dzin kun brtagsa kyi ma rig pa glo bur gyi
NK075(bu)002:7819: dri ma gnyis / ye nas rnam par dag cing
NK075(bu)002:7820: ye shes dang dbyings gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo
NK075(bu)002:7821: dri ma gnyis / las / gdul bya sems can rnams kyang mi gazhana pa'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)002:7822: yul yul can gnyis su med pa'i thugsa rje chen po sangs rgyas kyi ye shes dang /
NK075(bu)002:7825: ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel pas na 'gro ba rigs drug gi dus snga phyi dang /
NK075(bu)002:7826: gnas mtho dman la sogs shes bya ji snyed ma lus pa kun snang bas mkhyen pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7827: ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'i dus de nyid na yang /
NK075(bu)002:7828: rgyas pa nas 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK075(bu)002:7829: yul yul can gyi rnam par rtog pa mi mang'a ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:7830: ji lta ba mkhyen pa las ma g.yos /
NK075(bu)002:7831: ma g.yos bzhin sangs rgyas de yisa mi mkhyen pa
NK075(bu)002:7832: dang mi gzigs pa gang yang med mi gzigs pa'i
NK075(bu)002:7834: yang kun byed las 'di skad gsungs te /
NK075(bu)002:7835: dpe me long la gzugs brnyan 'char dus me long las ma g.yos bzhin lta bu'i tshul bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7836: ji lta ba mkhyen pa la ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7837: shes bya sna tshogsa so so'i kha dog mi 'dra ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7838: dbyibs mi 'dra ba du mar ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su shar nas snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)002:7839: thugs rje'i sprul pa snang tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7841: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK075(bu)002:7842: cad kyi dgongs pa'i rang bzhin de 'khor ba dang
NK075(bu)002:7843: dngos 'dzin 'di ltar gyi chos thams cad dang dbyer
NK075(bu)002:7844: med rang snang ba'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)002:7845: sprul pa sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)002:7846: dpe sur+ya ste nyi ma tsan+d+ra zla ba'i gzugs brnyan nam mkha' la shar ba dang /
NK075(bu)002:7847: chu lding tha dag la thogs chags med par gzugs brnyan shar ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7848: dgongs pa chos sku nyag gcig las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7849: gzugs sku sna tshogs su snang nas 'gro ba'i don
NK075(bu)002:7850: byed cing de yang don byed bya byed kyi rtsol
NK075(bu)002:7851: rtog gi 'gro 'ong ga la yod de med /
NK075(bu)002:7852: gal te rtsol rtog 'gro 'ong de yod na ni gzung 'dzin can du 'gyur bas /
NK075(bu)002:7853: sems can dang khyad med do //
NK075(bu)002:7854: mdzad pa bya byed kyi rtsol ba med par don mdzad tshul dang /
NK075(bu)002:7856: dpe sgyu ma mkhan gyi sprul pa'i rta glang po snang yang bden dngos kyis stong pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)002:7857: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor gzugs sku gnyis su
NK075(bu)002:7858: snang nas 'gro ba rnams sangs rgyas kyi sar sgrol
NK075(bu)002:7859: bar byed / de yis dus su don bya ba'i yul /
NK075(bu)002:7861: don byas pa'i dngos po gsum du 'dzin pa med pa rang rig pa'i dkyil 'khor du spyod do //
NK075(bu)002:7862: dgongs pa rgyud kyi gnas tshul gcig dang du ma
NK075(bu)002:7863: las grol ba smra bsam las 'das pa ni sangs
NK075(bu)002:7864: rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas su bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7866: 'das ma 'ongs da lta dus gsum du rim pa
NK075(bu)002:7867: ltar sangas rgyas pa'i dus su gzung 'dzin log rtog
NK075(bu)002:7868: gi 'khrul snang tha dad brtags pa'i phra rags ma
NK075(bu)002:7869: rig bag la nyal gyi dri ma dang bcas pa
NK075(bu)002:7870: dag nas rig pa rang snang gi tha gru rgyas
NK075(bu)002:7871: pa yin yang / yang gi sgras /
NK075(bu)002:7873: dgongs pa'i ngo bo gcig kyang sbyangs pa'i ye shes mi 'dra ba ste /
NK075(bu)002:7874: shing gi me dpung ltar du 'dod la /
NK075(bu)002:7876: dbyings kyi ngo bo la dbye ba med pa'i cha la btags pas /
NK075(bu)002:7877: chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin du gcig par 'dod kyang /
NK075(bu)002:7878: drang don kyi sangs rgyas tsam ma gtogs pa /
NK075(bu)002:7879: nges don gyis sangs rgyas ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7880: sangs rgyas ni ye gdod ma nas gnas pa'i don mngon du gyur te /
NK075(bu)002:7881: dbyings ye shes phyogs rer bzung ba'i mtha' las grol ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)002:7882: dbyings kyi cha nas sangs rgyas thams cad gcig pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7883: ye shes kyi cha nas mi gcig ces ngag tu
NK075(bu)002:7884: brjod pa dang yid kyis bsam pa las 'das shing
NK075(bu)002:7885: / chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa
NK075(bu)002:7886: gzung 'dzin thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes ni
NK075(bu)002:7887: / / 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi de bzhin gshegsa pa sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs gnas yin ces /
NK075(bu)002:7888: rgyud rgyas pa las gsungs pas lung de nyid 'dir drang zhing bgrod pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7890: de ltar sangs rgyas pa'i tshe na /
NK075(bu)002:7891: dpe rgya mtsho'i chu dang rlabs dbye ba med pa
NK075(bu)002:7892: bzhin du sku gzugs sna tshogs su shar nas 'gro
NK075(bu)002:7893: ba'i don byed dus chos sku nyag gcig rang las
NK075(bu)002:7894: ma g.yos par don gnyis lhun gyi grub pas sangs
NK075(bu)002:7897: thugs kyi thigsa pa las 'bru mthun /
NK075(bu)002:7898: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu med pas bde ba nar son pas na gshegs /
NK075(bu)002:7899: rtogs pa'i rig pa la sku dang ye shes su
NK075(bu)002:7900: rang snang ba ste gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pa na
NK075(bu)002:7901: le'u ste yas bgrang bzhi pa'i don du gda' 'o
NK075(bu)002:7904: dpe nam mkha' la 'aja'a tshon shar ba bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:7905: rgyud thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i don rnams ma 'dres
NK075(bu)002:7906: pa bkra zhing gsal bar byed pa'i man ngag thugs
NK075(bu)002:7908: rgyud kyi don bshad pa la gzhung 'di bzhin du
NK075(bu)002:7909: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid mi shes par
NK075(bu)002:7910: mkhas par rngams pa'i nga rgyal nyams shing /
NK075(bu)002:7911: khams gsum nyon mongs kyi dgra kun las rgyal ba'i
NK075(bu)002:7912: dpa' bo'i ru mtshon gnam lcags shak+ti ral gri dang
NK075(bu)002:7913: 'dra ba'o // de ltar brtsams pa rang bzo ma yin te /
NK075(bu)002:7914: thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud kyi don bcud snang ba bzhi po /
NK075(bu)002:7915: gcig thog nas gcig 'ong bas na 'khora lo dang 'dra ba 'di /
NK075(bu)002:7916: dpe bya ngang pa'i machu la skyur rtsi yod pas /
NK075(bu)002:7917: rgya mtsho la 'o ma thigs pa gcig yod na
NK075(bu)002:7918: sdud pa ltar thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud ste
NK075(bu)002:7919: rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba'i nang nas slob dpon sangs
NK075(bu)002:7920: rgyas gsang ba'i nyer len gyi shes rab skyur rtsi
NK075(bu)002:7922: 'o ma dang 'dra ba snang ba bzhi'i bstan bcos man ngag 'di blangs pas /
NK075(bu)002:7923: dge ba des rgyud kyi gsang don mi shes shing
NK075(bu)002:7924: nyon mongs pa'i dra bar chud pa'i skye 'gro phal
NK075(bu)002:7925: pa rnams kyis gsang ba'i snying po 'di'i don rtogs
NK075(bu)002:7926: par shog / ces pa'i smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK075(bu)002:7927: thugs kyi thigs pa'i sgyu 'phrul zhes pa 'bru mthun la spyi gcod ni khog dbub ste /
NK075(bu)002:7928: rdzogsa so ni tshig don ma lus pa'i tha tshig gam /
NK075(bu)002:7929: gnas skabs re zhig rdzogs nas bshad du ma mchis pa'i don du gada'o //
NK075(bu)002:7931: // 'on kyang 'grel bshad 'di ni rang bzo min //
NK075(bu)002:7932: mkhas grub du ma'i gzhung lugs la dpyad cing //
NK075(bu)002:7933: bla ma dam pa'i gsung tshig la brten nas //
NK075(bu)002:7934: bdag blo sbyong phyir 'grel bshad 'di byas la //
NK075(bu)002:7935: 'khrul na bzod gsol ma 'khrul dge ba des //
NK075(bu)002:7936: 'gro rnams kun mkhyen sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK075(bu)002:7937: 'di ni chos rje'i 'grel pa las gzhi blangs zhing /
NK075(bu)002:7938: de ltar kha 'phangs pa dang ma 'grel ba rnams ni /
NK075(bu)002:7939: rgyal ba g.yung ston pa'i gsang snying gi khog dbub 'grel pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7943: sgrol ma ba'i 'grel pa la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7945: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa la sogs pa'i rgyud rnams la brtag dpyad byas pa dang /
NK075(bu)002:7946: rje bla ma rin po che dz+ny+aa na ke tu'i
NK075(bu)002:7947: gsung gi bdud rtsi dri ma med pa la brten
NK075(bu)002:7948: nas / las dang po pa'i don du tika bklag chog gyu ru lugs su bris pa 'di ni /
NK075(bu)002:7949: bdag blo sbyang phyir sh+aakya'i dge slong nam mkha' rgyal mtshan gyis /
NK075(bu)002:7950: chu mo phag gi lo sgra brgya pa'i zla ba'i
NK075(bu)002:7951: dkar phyogs kyi nya la kah thog ri khrod du
NK075(bu)002:7952: sbyar ba 'dis 'gro ba dpag tu med pa rdo
NK075(bu)002:7953: rje 'dzin pa'i sa la 'khod par gyur cig //
